            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>I.<br>\nA SCANDAL IN BOHEMIA</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h3>I.</h3></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">T</span>o Sherlock Holmes she is always <i>the</i> woman. I have seldom heard him mention her under any other name. In his eyes she eclipses and predominates the whole of her sex. It was not that he felt any emotion akin to love for Irene Adler. All emotions, and that one particularly, were abhorrent to his cold, precise but admirably balanced mind. He was, I take it, the most perfect reasoning and observing machine that the world has seen, but as a lover he would have placed himself in a false position. He never spoke of the softer passions, save with a gibe and a sneer. They were admirable things for the observer—excellent for drawing the veil from men’s motives and actions. But for the trained reasoner to admit such intrusions into his own delicate and finely adjusted temperament was to introduce a distracting factor which might throw a doubt upon all his mental results. Grit in a sensitive instrument, or a crack in one of his own high-power lenses, would not be more disturbing than a strong emotion in a nature such as his. And yet there was but one woman to him, and that woman was the late Irene Adler, of dubious and questionable memory.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had seen little of Holmes lately. My marriage had drifted us away from each other. My own complete happiness, and the home-centred interests which rise up around the man who first finds himself master of his own establishment, were sufficient to absorb all my attention, while Holmes, who loathed every form of society with his whole Bohemian soul, remained in our lodgings in Baker Street, buried among his old books, and alternating from week to week between cocaine and ambition, the drowsiness of the drug, and the fierce energy of his own keen nature. He was still, as ever, deeply attracted by the study of crime, and occupied his immense faculties and extraordinary powers of observation in following out those clues, and clearing up those mysteries which had been abandoned as hopeless by the official police. From time to time I heard some vague account of his doings: of his summons to Odessa in the case of the Trepoff murder, of his clearing up of the singular tragedy of the Atkinson brothers at Trincomalee, and finally of the mission which he had accomplished so delicately and successfully for the reigning family of Holland. Beyond these signs of his activity, however, which I merely shared with all the readers of the daily press, I knew little of my former friend and companion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>One night—it was on the twentieth of March, 1888—I was returning from a journey to a patient (for I had now returned to civil practice), when my way led me through Baker Street. As I passed the well-remembered door, which must always be associated in my mind with my wooing, and with the dark incidents of the Study in Scarlet, I was seized with a keen desire to see Holmes again, and to know how he was employing his extraordinary powers. His rooms were brilliantly lit, and, even as I looked up, I saw his tall, spare figure pass twice in a dark silhouette against the blind. He was pacing the room swiftly, eagerly, with his head sunk upon his chest and his hands clasped behind him. To me, who knew his every mood and habit, his attitude and manner told their own story. He was at work again. He had risen out of his drug-created dreams and was hot upon the scent of some new problem. I rang the bell and was shown up to the chamber which had formerly been in part my own.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>His manner was not effusive. It seldom was; but he was glad, I think, to see me. With hardly a word spoken, but with a kindly eye, he waved me to an armchair, threw across his case of cigars, and indicated a spirit case and a gasogene in the corner. Then he stood before the fire and looked me over in his singular introspective fashion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Wedlock suits you,” he remarked. “I think, Watson, that you have put on seven and a half pounds since I saw you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Seven!” I answered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed, I should have thought a little more. Just a trifle more, I fancy, Watson. And in practice again, I observe. You did not tell me that you intended to go into harness.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, how do you know?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see it, I deduce it. How do I know that you have been getting yourself very wet lately, and that you have a most clumsy and careless servant girl?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Holmes,” said I, “this is too much. You would certainly have been burned, had you lived a few centuries ago. It is true that I had a country walk on Thursday and came home in a dreadful mess, but as I have changed my clothes I can’t imagine how you deduce it. As to Mary Jane, she is incorrigible, and my wife has given her notice, but there, again, I fail to see how you work it out.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He chuckled to himself and rubbed his long, nervous hands together.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is simplicity itself,” said he; “my eyes tell me that on the inside of your left shoe, just where the firelight strikes it, the leather is scored by six almost parallel cuts. Obviously they have been caused by someone who has very carelessly scraped round the edges of the sole in order to remove crusted mud from it. Hence, you see, my double deduction that you had been out in vile weather, and that you had a particularly malignant boot-slitting specimen of the London slavey. As to your practice, if a gentleman walks into my rooms smelling of iodoform, with a black mark of nitrate of silver upon his right forefinger, and a bulge on the right side of his top-hat to show where he has secreted his stethoscope, I must be dull, indeed, if I do not pronounce him to be an active member of the medical profession.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I could not help laughing at the ease with which he explained his process of deduction. “When I hear you give your reasons,” I remarked, “the thing always appears to me to be so ridiculously simple that I could easily do it myself, though at each successive instance of your reasoning I am baffled until you explain your process. And yet I believe that my eyes are as good as yours.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so,” he answered, lighting a cigarette, and throwing himself down into an armchair. “You see, but you do not observe. The distinction is clear. For example, you have frequently seen the steps which lead up from the hall to this room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Frequently.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How often?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, some hundreds of times.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then how many are there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How many? I don’t know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so! You have not observed. And yet you have seen. That is just my point. Now, I know that there are seventeen steps, because I have both seen and observed. By the way, since you are interested in these little problems, and since you are good enough to chronicle one or two of my trifling experiences, you may be interested in this.” He threw over a sheet of thick, pink-tinted notepaper which had been lying open upon the table. “It came by the last post,” said he. “Read it aloud.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The note was undated, and without either signature or address.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There will call upon you to-night, at a quarter to eight o’clock,” it said, “a gentleman who desires to consult you upon a matter of the very deepest moment. Your recent services to one of the royal houses of Europe have shown that you are one who may safely be trusted with matters which are of an importance which can hardly be exaggerated. This account of you we have from all quarters received. Be in your chamber then at that hour, and do not take it amiss if your visitor wear a mask.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is indeed a mystery,” I remarked. “What do you imagine that it means?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have no data yet. It is a capital mistake to theorise before one has data. Insensibly one begins to twist facts to suit theories, instead of theories to suit facts. But the note itself. What do you deduce from it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I carefully examined the writing, and the paper upon which it was written.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The man who wrote it was presumably well to do,” I remarked, endeavouring to imitate my companion’s processes. “Such paper could not be bought under half a crown a packet. It is peculiarly strong and stiff.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Peculiar—that is the very word,” said Holmes. “It is not an English paper at all. Hold it up to the light.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did so, and saw a large “E” with a small “g,” a “P,” and a large “G” with a small “t” woven into the texture of the paper.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you make of that?” asked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The name of the maker, no doubt; or his monogram, rather.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. The ‘G’ with the small ‘t’ stands for ‘Gesellschaft,’ which is the German for ‘Company.’ It is a customary contraction like our ‘Co.’ ‘P,’ of course, stands for ‘Papier.’ Now for the ‘Eg.’ Let us glance at our Continental Gazetteer.” He took down a heavy brown volume from his shelves. “Eglow, Eglonitz—here we are, Egria. It is in a German-speaking country—in Bohemia, not far from Carlsbad. ‘Remarkable as being the scene of the death of Wallenstein, and for its numerous glass-factories and paper-mills.’ Ha, ha, my boy, what do you make of that?” His eyes sparkled, and he sent up a great blue triumphant cloud from his cigarette.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The paper was made in Bohemia,” I said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely. And the man who wrote the note is a German. Do you note the peculiar construction of the sentence—‘This account of you we have from all quarters received.’ A Frenchman or Russian could not have written that. It is the German who is so uncourteous to his verbs. It only remains, therefore, to discover what is wanted by this German who writes upon Bohemian paper and prefers wearing a mask to showing his face. And here he comes, if I am not mistaken, to resolve all our doubts.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As he spoke there was the sharp sound of horses’ hoofs and grating wheels against the curb, followed by a sharp pull at the bell. Holmes whistled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A pair, by the sound,” said he. “Yes,” he continued, glancing out of the window. “A nice little brougham and a pair of beauties. A hundred and fifty guineas apiece. There’s money in this case, Watson, if there is nothing else.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that I had better go, Holmes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not a bit, Doctor. Stay where you are. I am lost without my Boswell. And this promises to be interesting. It would be a pity to miss it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But your client—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never mind him. I may want your help, and so may he. Here he comes. Sit down in that armchair, Doctor, and give us your best attention.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A slow and heavy step, which had been heard upon the stairs and in the passage, paused immediately outside the door. Then there was a loud and authoritative tap.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come in!” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A man entered who could hardly have been less than six feet six inches in height, with the chest and limbs of a Hercules. His dress was rich with a richness which would, in England, be looked upon as akin to bad taste. Heavy bands of astrakhan were slashed across the sleeves and fronts of his double-breasted coat, while the deep blue cloak which was thrown over his shoulders was lined with flame-coloured silk and secured at the neck with a brooch which consisted of a single flaming beryl. Boots which extended halfway up his calves, and which were trimmed at the tops with rich brown fur, completed the impression of barbaric opulence which was suggested by his whole appearance. He carried a broad-brimmed hat in his hand, while he wore across the upper part of his face, extending down past the cheekbones, a black vizard mask, which he had apparently adjusted that very moment, for his hand was still raised to it as he entered. From the lower part of the face he appeared to be a man of strong character, with a thick, hanging lip, and a long, straight chin suggestive of resolution pushed to the length of obstinacy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You had my note?” he asked with a deep harsh voice and a strongly marked German accent. “I told you that I would call.” He looked from one to the other of us, as if uncertain which to address.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray take a seat,” said Holmes. “This is my friend and colleague, Dr. Watson, who is occasionally good enough to help me in my cases. Whom have I the honour to address?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You may address me as the Count Von Kramm, a Bohemian nobleman. I understand that this gentleman, your friend, is a man of honour and discretion, whom I may trust with a matter of the most extreme importance. If not, I should much prefer to communicate with you alone.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I rose to go, but Holmes caught me by the wrist and pushed me back into my chair. “It is both, or none,” said he. “You may say before this gentleman anything which you may say to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Count shrugged his broad shoulders. “Then I must begin,” said he, “by binding you both to absolute secrecy for two years; at the end of that time the matter will be of no importance. At present it is not too much to say that it is of such weight it may have an influence upon European history.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I promise,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will excuse this mask,” continued our strange visitor. “The august person who employs me wishes his agent to be unknown to you, and I may confess at once that the title by which I have just called myself is not exactly my own.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was aware of it,” said Holmes dryly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The circumstances are of great delicacy, and every precaution has to be taken to quench what might grow to be an immense scandal and seriously compromise one of the reigning families of Europe. To speak plainly, the matter implicates the great House of Ormstein, hereditary kings of Bohemia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was also aware of that,” murmured Holmes, settling himself down in his armchair and closing his eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our visitor glanced with some apparent surprise at the languid, lounging figure of the man who had been no doubt depicted to him as the most incisive reasoner and most energetic agent in Europe. Holmes slowly reopened his eyes and looked impatiently at his gigantic client.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If your Majesty would condescend to state your case,” he remarked, “I should be better able to advise you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man sprang from his chair and paced up and down the room in uncontrollable agitation. Then, with a gesture of desperation, he tore the mask from his face and hurled it upon the ground. “You are right,” he cried; “I am the King. Why should I attempt to conceal it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, indeed?” murmured Holmes. “Your Majesty had not spoken before I was aware that I was addressing Wilhelm Gottsreich Sigismond von Ormstein, Grand Duke of Cassel-Felstein, and hereditary King of Bohemia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you can understand,” said our strange visitor, sitting down once more and passing his hand over his high white forehead, “you can understand that I am not accustomed to doing such business in my own person. Yet the matter was so delicate that I could not confide it to an agent without putting myself in his power. I have come <i>incognito</i> from Prague for the purpose of consulting you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, pray consult,” said Holmes, shutting his eyes once more.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The facts are briefly these: Some five years ago, during a lengthy visit to Warsaw, I made the acquaintance of the well-known adventuress, Irene Adler. The name is no doubt familiar to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Kindly look her up in my index, Doctor,” murmured Holmes without opening his eyes. For many years he had adopted a system of docketing all paragraphs concerning men and things, so that it was difficult to name a subject or a person on which he could not at once furnish information. In this case I found her biography sandwiched in between that of a Hebrew rabbi and that of a staff-commander who had written a monograph upon the deep-sea fishes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let me see!” said Holmes. “Hum! Born in New Jersey in the year 1858. Contralto—hum! La Scala, hum! Prima donna Imperial Opera of Warsaw—yes! Retired from operatic stage—ha! Living in London—quite so! Your Majesty, as I understand, became entangled with this young person, wrote her some compromising letters, and is now desirous of getting those letters back.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely so. But how—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was there a secret marriage?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No legal papers or certificates?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I fail to follow your Majesty. If this young person should produce her letters for blackmailing or other purposes, how is she to prove their authenticity?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is the writing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pooh, pooh! Forgery.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My private note-paper.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Stolen.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My own seal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Imitated.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My photograph.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Bought.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We were both in the photograph.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, dear! That is very bad! Your Majesty has indeed committed an indiscretion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was mad—insane.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have compromised yourself seriously.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was only Crown Prince then. I was young. I am but thirty now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It must be recovered.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have tried and failed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your Majesty must pay. It must be bought.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She will not sell.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Stolen, then.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Five attempts have been made. Twice burglars in my pay ransacked her house. Once we diverted her luggage when she travelled. Twice she has been waylaid. There has been no result.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No sign of it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Absolutely none.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes laughed. “It is quite a pretty little problem,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But a very serious one to me,” returned the King reproachfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very, indeed. And what does she propose to do with the photograph?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To ruin me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But how?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am about to be married.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So I have heard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To Clotilde Lothman von Saxe-Meningen, second daughter of the King of Scandinavia. You may know the strict principles of her family. She is herself the very soul of delicacy. A shadow of a doubt as to my conduct would bring the matter to an end.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And Irene Adler?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Threatens to send them the photograph. And she will do it. I know that she will do it. You do not know her, but she has a soul of steel. She has the face of the most beautiful of women, and the mind of the most resolute of men. Rather than I should marry another woman, there are no lengths to which she would not go—none.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are sure that she has not sent it yet?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am sure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because she has said that she would send it on the day when the betrothal was publicly proclaimed. That will be next Monday.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, then we have three days yet,” said Holmes with a yawn. “That is very fortunate, as I have one or two matters of importance to look into just at present. Your Majesty will, of course, stay in London for the present?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly. You will find me at the Langham under the name of the Count Von Kramm.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I shall drop you a line to let you know how we progress.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray do so. I shall be all anxiety.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, as to money?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have <i>carte blanche</i>.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Absolutely?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I tell you that I would give one of the provinces of my kingdom to have that photograph.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And for present expenses?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The King took a heavy chamois leather bag from under his cloak and laid it on the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There are three hundred pounds in gold and seven hundred in notes,” he said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes scribbled a receipt upon a sheet of his note-book and handed it to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And Mademoiselle’s address?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is Briony Lodge, Serpentine Avenue, St. John’s Wood.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes took a note of it. “One other question,” said he. “Was the photograph a cabinet?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, good-night, your Majesty, and I trust that we shall soon have some good news for you. And good-night, Watson,” he added, as the wheels of the royal brougham rolled down the street. “If you will be good enough to call to-morrow afternoon at three o’clock I should like to chat this little matter over with you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h3>II.</h3></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At three o’clock precisely I was at Baker Street, but Holmes had not yet returned. The landlady informed me that he had left the house shortly after eight o’clock in the morning. I sat down beside the fire, however, with the intention of awaiting him, however long he might be. I was already deeply interested in his inquiry, for, though it was surrounded by none of the grim and strange features which were associated with the two crimes which I have already recorded, still, the nature of the case and the exalted station of his client gave it a character of its own. Indeed, apart from the nature of the investigation which my friend had on hand, there was something in his masterly grasp of a situation, and his keen, incisive reasoning, which made it a pleasure to me to study his system of work, and to follow the quick, subtle methods by which he disentangled the most inextricable mysteries. So accustomed was I to his invariable success that the very possibility of his failing had ceased to enter into my head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was close upon four before the door opened, and a drunken-looking groom, ill-kempt and side-whiskered, with an inflamed face and disreputable clothes, walked into the room. Accustomed as I was to my friend’s amazing powers in the use of disguises, I had to look three times before I was certain that it was indeed he. With a nod he vanished into the bedroom, whence he emerged in five minutes tweed-suited and respectable, as of old. Putting his hands into his pockets, he stretched out his legs in front of the fire and laughed heartily for some minutes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, really!” he cried, and then he choked and laughed again until he was obliged to lie back, limp and helpless, in the chair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s quite too funny. I am sure you could never guess how I employed my morning, or what I ended by doing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I can’t imagine. I suppose that you have been watching the habits, and perhaps the house, of Miss Irene Adler.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so; but the sequel was rather unusual. I will tell you, however. I left the house a little after eight o’clock this morning in the character of a groom out of work. There is a wonderful sympathy and freemasonry among horsey men. Be one of them, and you will know all that there is to know. I soon found Briony Lodge. It is a <i>bijou</i> villa, with a garden at the back, but built out in front right up to the road, two stories. Chubb lock to the door. Large sitting-room on the right side, well furnished, with long windows almost to the floor, and those preposterous English window fasteners which a child could open. Behind there was nothing remarkable, save that the passage window could be reached from the top of the coach-house. I walked round it and examined it closely from every point of view, but without noting anything else of interest.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I then lounged down the street and found, as I expected, that there was a mews in a lane which runs down by one wall of the garden. I lent the ostlers a hand in rubbing down their horses, and received in exchange twopence, a glass of half-and-half, two fills of shag tobacco, and as much information as I could desire about Miss Adler, to say nothing of half a dozen other people in the neighbourhood in whom I was not in the least interested, but whose biographies I was compelled to listen to.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what of Irene Adler?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, she has turned all the men’s heads down in that part. She is the daintiest thing under a bonnet on this planet. So say the Serpentine-mews, to a man. She lives quietly, sings at concerts, drives out at five every day, and returns at seven sharp for dinner. Seldom goes out at other times, except when she sings. Has only one male visitor, but a good deal of him. He is dark, handsome, and dashing, never calls less than once a day, and often twice. He is a Mr. Godfrey Norton, of the Inner Temple. See the advantages of a cabman as a confidant. They had driven him home a dozen times from Serpentine-mews, and knew all about him. When I had listened to all they had to tell, I began to walk up and down near Briony Lodge once more, and to think over my plan of campaign.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This Godfrey Norton was evidently an important factor in the matter. He was a lawyer. That sounded ominous. What was the relation between them, and what the object of his repeated visits? Was she his client, his friend, or his mistress? If the former, she had probably transferred the photograph to his keeping. If the latter, it was less likely. On the issue of this question depended whether I should continue my work at Briony Lodge, or turn my attention to the gentleman’s chambers in the Temple. It was a delicate point, and it widened the field of my inquiry. I fear that I bore you with these details, but I have to let you see my little difficulties, if you are to understand the situation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am following you closely,” I answered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was still balancing the matter in my mind when a hansom cab drove up to Briony Lodge, and a gentleman sprang out. He was a remarkably handsome man, dark, aquiline, and moustached—evidently the man of whom I had heard. He appeared to be in a great hurry, shouted to the cabman to wait, and brushed past the maid who opened the door with the air of a man who was thoroughly at home.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He was in the house about half an hour, and I could catch glimpses of him in the windows of the sitting-room, pacing up and down, talking excitedly, and waving his arms. Of her I could see nothing. Presently he emerged, looking even more flurried than before. As he stepped up to the cab, he pulled a gold watch from his pocket and looked at it earnestly, ‘Drive like the devil,’ he shouted, ‘first to Gross &amp; Hankey’s in Regent Street, and then to the Church of St. Monica in the Edgeware Road. Half a guinea if you do it in twenty minutes!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Away they went, and I was just wondering whether I should not do well to follow them when up the lane came a neat little landau, the coachman with his coat only half-buttoned, and his tie under his ear, while all the tags of his harness were sticking out of the buckles. It hadn’t pulled up before she shot out of the hall door and into it. I only caught a glimpse of her at the moment, but she was a lovely woman, with a face that a man might die for.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The Church of St. Monica, John,’ she cried, ‘and half a sovereign if you reach it in twenty minutes.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This was quite too good to lose, Watson. I was just balancing whether I should run for it, or whether I should perch behind her landau when a cab came through the street. The driver looked twice at such a shabby fare, but I jumped in before he could object. ‘The Church of St. Monica,’ said I, ‘and half a sovereign if you reach it in twenty minutes.’ It was twenty-five minutes to twelve, and of course it was clear enough what was in the wind.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My cabby drove fast. I don’t think I ever drove faster, but the others were there before us. The cab and the landau with their steaming horses were in front of the door when I arrived. I paid the man and hurried into the church. There was not a soul there save the two whom I had followed and a surpliced clergyman, who seemed to be expostulating with them. They were all three standing in a knot in front of the altar. I lounged up the side aisle like any other idler who has dropped into a church. Suddenly, to my surprise, the three at the altar faced round to me, and Godfrey Norton came running as hard as he could towards me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Thank God,’ he cried. ‘You’ll do. Come! Come!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What then?’ I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Come, man, come, only three minutes, or it won’t be legal.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was half-dragged up to the altar, and before I knew where I was I found myself mumbling responses which were whispered in my ear, and vouching for things of which I knew nothing, and generally assisting in the secure tying up of Irene Adler, spinster, to Godfrey Norton, bachelor. It was all done in an instant, and there was the gentleman thanking me on the one side and the lady on the other, while the clergyman beamed on me in front. It was the most preposterous position in which I ever found myself in my life, and it was the thought of it that started me laughing just now. It seems that there had been some informality about their license, that the clergyman absolutely refused to marry them without a witness of some sort, and that my lucky appearance saved the bridegroom from having to sally out into the streets in search of a best man. The bride gave me a sovereign, and I mean to wear it on my watch chain in memory of the occasion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is a very unexpected turn of affairs,” said I; “and what then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I found my plans very seriously menaced. It looked as if the pair might take an immediate departure, and so necessitate very prompt and energetic measures on my part. At the church door, however, they separated, he driving back to the Temple, and she to her own house. ‘I shall drive out in the park at five as usual,’ she said as she left him. I heard no more. They drove away in different directions, and I went off to make my own arrangements.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which are?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Some cold beef and a glass of beer,” he answered, ringing the bell. “I have been too busy to think of food, and I am likely to be busier still this evening. By the way, Doctor, I shall want your co-operation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall be delighted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You don’t mind breaking the law?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not in the least.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nor running a chance of arrest?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not in a good cause.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, the cause is excellent!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I am your man.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was sure that I might rely on you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what is it you wish?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When Mrs. Turner has brought in the tray I will make it clear to you. Now,” he said as he turned hungrily on the simple fare that our landlady had provided, “I must discuss it while I eat, for I have not much time. It is nearly five now. In two hours we must be on the scene of action. Miss Irene, or Madame, rather, returns from her drive at seven. We must be at Briony Lodge to meet her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You must leave that to me. I have already arranged what is to occur. There is only one point on which I must insist. You must not interfere, come what may. You understand?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am to be neutral?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To do nothing whatever. There will probably be some small unpleasantness. Do not join in it. It will end in my being conveyed into the house. Four or five minutes afterwards the sitting-room window will open. You are to station yourself close to that open window.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are to watch me, for I will be visible to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And when I raise my hand—so—you will throw into the room what I give you to throw, and will, at the same time, raise the cry of fire. You quite follow me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Entirely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is nothing very formidable,” he said, taking a long cigar-shaped roll from his pocket. “It is an ordinary plumber’s smoke-rocket, fitted with a cap at either end to make it self-lighting. Your task is confined to that. When you raise your cry of fire, it will be taken up by quite a number of people. You may then walk to the end of the street, and I will rejoin you in ten minutes. I hope that I have made myself clear?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am to remain neutral, to get near the window, to watch you, and at the signal to throw in this object, then to raise the cry of fire, and to wait you at the corner of the street.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you may entirely rely on me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is excellent. I think, perhaps, it is almost time that I prepare for the new role I have to play.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He disappeared into his bedroom and returned in a few minutes in the character of an amiable and simple-minded Nonconformist clergyman. His broad black hat, his baggy trousers, his white tie, his sympathetic smile, and general look of peering and benevolent curiosity were such as Mr. John Hare alone could have equalled. It was not merely that Holmes changed his costume. His expression, his manner, his very soul seemed to vary with every fresh part that he assumed. The stage lost a fine actor, even as science lost an acute reasoner, when he became a specialist in crime.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a quarter past six when we left Baker Street, and it still wanted ten minutes to the hour when we found ourselves in Serpentine Avenue. It was already dusk, and the lamps were just being lighted as we paced up and down in front of Briony Lodge, waiting for the coming of its occupant. The house was just such as I had pictured it from Sherlock Holmes’ succinct description, but the locality appeared to be less private than I expected. On the contrary, for a small street in a quiet neighbourhood, it was remarkably animated. There was a group of shabbily dressed men smoking and laughing in a corner, a scissors-grinder with his wheel, two guardsmen who were flirting with a nurse-girl, and several well-dressed young men who were lounging up and down with cigars in their mouths.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You see,” remarked Holmes, as we paced to and fro in front of the house, “this marriage rather simplifies matters. The photograph becomes a double-edged weapon now. The chances are that she would be as averse to its being seen by Mr. Godfrey Norton, as our client is to its coming to the eyes of his princess. Now the question is, Where are we to find the photograph?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where, indeed?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is most unlikely that she carries it about with her. It is cabinet size. Too large for easy concealment about a woman’s dress. She knows that the King is capable of having her waylaid and searched. Two attempts of the sort have already been made. We may take it, then, that she does not carry it about with her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Her banker or her lawyer. There is that double possibility. But I am inclined to think neither. Women are naturally secretive, and they like to do their own secreting. Why should she hand it over to anyone else? She could trust her own guardianship, but she could not tell what indirect or political influence might be brought to bear upon a business man. Besides, remember that she had resolved to use it within a few days. It must be where she can lay her hands upon it. It must be in her own house.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it has twice been burgled.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pshaw! They did not know how to look.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But how will you look?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will not look.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will get her to show me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But she will refuse.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She will not be able to. But I hear the rumble of wheels. It is her carriage. Now carry out my orders to the letter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As he spoke the gleam of the sidelights of a carriage came round the curve of the avenue. It was a smart little landau which rattled up to the door of Briony Lodge. As it pulled up, one of the loafing men at the corner dashed forward to open the door in the hope of earning a copper, but was elbowed away by another loafer, who had rushed up with the same intention. A fierce quarrel broke out, which was increased by the two guardsmen, who took sides with one of the loungers, and by the scissors-grinder, who was equally hot upon the other side. A blow was struck, and in an instant the lady, who had stepped from her carriage, was the centre of a little knot of flushed and struggling men, who struck savagely at each other with their fists and sticks. Holmes dashed into the crowd to protect the lady; but, just as he reached her, he gave a cry and dropped to the ground, with the blood running freely down his face. At his fall the guardsmen took to their heels in one direction and the loungers in the other, while a number of better dressed people, who had watched the scuffle without taking part in it, crowded in to help the lady and to attend to the injured man. Irene Adler, as I will still call her, had hurried up the steps; but she stood at the top with her superb figure outlined against the lights of the hall, looking back into the street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is the poor gentleman much hurt?” she asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is dead,” cried several voices.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, there’s life in him!” shouted another. “But he’ll be gone before you can get him to hospital.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s a brave fellow,” said a woman. “They would have had the lady’s purse and watch if it hadn’t been for him. They were a gang, and a rough one, too. Ah, he’s breathing now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He can’t lie in the street. May we bring him in, marm?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Surely. Bring him into the sitting-room. There is a comfortable sofa. This way, please!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Slowly and solemnly he was borne into Briony Lodge and laid out in the principal room, while I still observed the proceedings from my post by the window. The lamps had been lit, but the blinds had not been drawn, so that I could see Holmes as he lay upon the couch. I do not know whether he was seized with compunction at that moment for the part he was playing, but I know that I never felt more heartily ashamed of myself in my life than when I saw the beautiful creature against whom I was conspiring, or the grace and kindliness with which she waited upon the injured man. And yet it would be the blackest treachery to Holmes to draw back now from the part which he had intrusted to me. I hardened my heart, and took the smoke-rocket from under my ulster. After all, I thought, we are not injuring her. We are but preventing her from injuring another.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes had sat up upon the couch, and I saw him motion like a man who is in need of air. A maid rushed across and threw open the window. At the same instant I saw him raise his hand and at the signal I tossed my rocket into the room with a cry of “Fire!” The word was no sooner out of my mouth than the whole crowd of spectators, well dressed and ill—gentlemen, ostlers, and servant maids—joined in a general shriek of “Fire!” Thick clouds of smoke curled through the room and out at the open window. I caught a glimpse of rushing figures, and a moment later the voice of Holmes from within assuring them that it was a false alarm. Slipping through the shouting crowd I made my way to the corner of the street, and in ten minutes was rejoiced to find my friend’s arm in mine, and to get away from the scene of uproar. He walked swiftly and in silence for some few minutes until we had turned down one of the quiet streets which lead towards the Edgeware Road.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You did it very nicely, Doctor,” he remarked. “Nothing could have been better. It is all right.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have the photograph?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I know where it is.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how did you find out?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She showed me, as I told you she would.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am still in the dark.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not wish to make a mystery,” said he, laughing. “The matter was perfectly simple. You, of course, saw that everyone in the street was an accomplice. They were all engaged for the evening.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I guessed as much.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, when the row broke out, I had a little moist red paint in the palm of my hand. I rushed forward, fell down, clapped my hand to my face, and became a piteous spectacle. It is an old trick.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That also I could fathom.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then they carried me in. She was bound to have me in. What else could she do? And into her sitting-room, which was the very room which I suspected. It lay between that and her bedroom, and I was determined to see which. They laid me on a couch, I motioned for air, they were compelled to open the window, and you had your chance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did that help you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was all-important. When a woman thinks that her house is on fire, her instinct is at once to rush to the thing which she values most. It is a perfectly overpowering impulse, and I have more than once taken advantage of it. In the case of the Darlington Substitution Scandal it was of use to me, and also in the Arnsworth Castle business. A married woman grabs at her baby; an unmarried one reaches for her jewel-box. Now it was clear to me that our lady of to-day had nothing in the house more precious to her than what we are in quest of. She would rush to secure it. The alarm of fire was admirably done. The smoke and shouting were enough to shake nerves of steel. She responded beautifully. The photograph is in a recess behind a sliding panel just above the right bell-pull. She was there in an instant, and I caught a glimpse of it as she half drew it out. When I cried out that it was a false alarm, she replaced it, glanced at the rocket, rushed from the room, and I have not seen her since. I rose, and, making my excuses, escaped from the house. I hesitated whether to attempt to secure the photograph at once; but the coachman had come in, and as he was watching me narrowly, it seemed safer to wait. A little over-precipitance may ruin all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And now?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Our quest is practically finished. I shall call with the King to-morrow, and with you, if you care to come with us. We will be shown into the sitting-room to wait for the lady, but it is probable that when she comes she may find neither us nor the photograph. It might be a satisfaction to his Majesty to regain it with his own hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And when will you call?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At eight in the morning. She will not be up, so that we shall have a clear field. Besides, we must be prompt, for this marriage may mean a complete change in her life and habits. I must wire to the King without delay.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had reached Baker Street and had stopped at the door. He was searching his pockets for the key when someone passing said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good-night, Mister Sherlock Holmes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There were several people on the pavement at the time, but the greeting appeared to come from a slim youth in an ulster who had hurried by.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ve heard that voice before,” said Holmes, staring down the dimly lit street. “Now, I wonder who the deuce that could have been.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h3>III.</h3></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I slept at Baker Street that night, and we were engaged upon our toast and coffee in the morning when the King of Bohemia rushed into the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have really got it!” he cried, grasping Sherlock Holmes by either shoulder and looking eagerly into his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not yet.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you have hopes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have hopes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, come. I am all impatience to be gone.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We must have a cab.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, my brougham is waiting.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then that will simplify matters.” We descended and started off once more for Briony Lodge.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Irene Adler is married,” remarked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Married! When?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yesterday.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But to whom?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To an English lawyer named Norton.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But she could not love him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am in hopes that she does.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And why in hopes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because it would spare your Majesty all fear of future annoyance. If the lady loves her husband, she does not love your Majesty. If she does not love your Majesty, there is no reason why she should interfere with your Majesty’s plan.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is true. And yet—! Well! I wish she had been of my own station! What a queen she would have made!” He relapsed into a moody silence, which was not broken until we drew up in Serpentine Avenue.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The door of Briony Lodge was open, and an elderly woman stood upon the steps. She watched us with a sardonic eye as we stepped from the brougham.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Sherlock Holmes, I believe?” said she.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am Mr. Holmes,” answered my companion, looking at her with a questioning and rather startled gaze.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed! My mistress told me that you were likely to call. She left this morning with her husband by the 5:15 train from Charing Cross for the Continent.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What!” Sherlock Holmes staggered back, white with chagrin and surprise. “Do you mean that she has left England?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never to return.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the papers?” asked the King hoarsely. “All is lost.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We shall see.” He pushed past the servant and rushed into the drawing-room, followed by the King and myself. The furniture was scattered about in every direction, with dismantled shelves and open drawers, as if the lady had hurriedly ransacked them before her flight. Holmes rushed at the bell-pull, tore back a small sliding shutter, and, plunging in his hand, pulled out a photograph and a letter. The photograph was of Irene Adler herself in evening dress, the letter was superscribed to “Sherlock Holmes, Esq. To be left till called for.” My friend tore it open, and we all three read it together. It was dated at midnight of the preceding night and ran in this way:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“MY DEAR MR. SHERLOCK HOLMES,—You really did it very well. You took me in completely. Until after the alarm of fire, I had not a suspicion. But then, when I found how I had betrayed myself, I began to think. I had been warned against you months ago. I had been told that, if the King employed an agent, it would certainly be you. And your address had been given me. Yet, with all this, you made me reveal what you wanted to know. Even after I became suspicious, I found it hard to think evil of such a dear, kind old clergyman. But, you know, I have been trained as an actress myself. Male costume is nothing new to me. I often take advantage of the freedom which it gives. I sent John, the coachman, to watch you, ran upstairs, got into my walking clothes, as I call them, and came down just as you departed.<br>\n    “Well, I followed you to your door, and so made sure that I was really an object of interest to the celebrated Mr. Sherlock Holmes. Then I, rather imprudently, wished you good-night, and started for the Temple to see my husband.<br>\n    “We both thought the best resource was flight, when pursued by so formidable an antagonist; so you will find the nest empty when you call to-morrow. As to the photograph, your client may rest in peace. I love and am loved by a better man than he. The King may do what he will without hindrance from one whom he has cruelly wronged. I keep it only to safeguard myself, and to preserve a weapon which will always secure me from any steps which he might take in the future. I leave a photograph which he might care to possess; and I remain, dear Mr. Sherlock Holmes,</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"right\">“Very truly yours,<br>\n“IRENE NORTON, <i>née</i> ADLER.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“What a woman—oh, what a woman!” cried the King of Bohemia, when we had all three read this epistle. “Did I not tell you how quick and resolute she was? Would she not have made an admirable queen? Is it not a pity that she was not on my level?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“From what I have seen of the lady, she seems, indeed, to be on a very different level to your Majesty,” said Holmes coldly. “I am sorry that I have not been able to bring your Majesty’s business to a more successful conclusion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary, my dear sir,” cried the King; “nothing could be more successful. I know that her word is inviolate. The photograph is now as safe as if it were in the fire.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am glad to hear your Majesty say so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am immensely indebted to you. Pray tell me in what way I can reward you. This ring—” He slipped an emerald snake ring from his finger and held it out upon the palm of his hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your Majesty has something which I should value even more highly,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have but to name it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This photograph!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The King stared at him in amazement.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Irene’s photograph!” he cried. “Certainly, if you wish it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I thank your Majesty. Then there is no more to be done in the matter. I have the honour to wish you a very good morning.” He bowed, and, turning away without observing the hand which the King had stretched out to him, he set off in my company for his chambers.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">And that was how a great scandal threatened to affect the kingdom of Bohemia, and how the best plans of Mr. Sherlock Holmes were beaten by a woman’s wit. He used to make merry over the cleverness of women, but I have not heard him do it of late. And when he speaks of Irene Adler, or when he refers to her photograph, it is always under the honourable title of <i>the</i> woman.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>II.<br>\nTHE RED-HEADED LEAGUE</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">I</span> had called upon my friend, Mr. Sherlock Holmes, one day in the autumn of last year and found him in deep conversation with a very stout, florid-faced, elderly gentleman with fiery red hair. With an apology for my intrusion, I was about to withdraw when Holmes pulled me abruptly into the room and closed the door behind me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You could not possibly have come at a better time, my dear Watson,” he said cordially.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was afraid that you were engaged.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So I am. Very much so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I can wait in the next room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. This gentleman, Mr. Wilson, has been my partner and helper in many of my most successful cases, and I have no doubt that he will be of the utmost use to me in yours also.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The stout gentleman half rose from his chair and gave a bob of greeting, with a quick little questioning glance from his small fat-encircled eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Try the settee,” said Holmes, relapsing into his armchair and putting his fingertips together, as was his custom when in judicial moods. “I know, my dear Watson, that you share my love of all that is bizarre and outside the conventions and humdrum routine of everyday life. You have shown your relish for it by the enthusiasm which has prompted you to chronicle, and, if you will excuse my saying so, somewhat to embellish so many of my own little adventures.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your cases have indeed been of the greatest interest to me,” I observed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will remember that I remarked the other day, just before we went into the very simple problem presented by Miss Mary Sutherland, that for strange effects and extraordinary combinations we must go to life itself, which is always far more daring than any effort of the imagination.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A proposition which I took the liberty of doubting.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You did, Doctor, but none the less you must come round to my view, for otherwise I shall keep on piling fact upon fact on you until your reason breaks down under them and acknowledges me to be right. Now, Mr. Jabez Wilson here has been good enough to call upon me this morning, and to begin a narrative which promises to be one of the most singular which I have listened to for some time. You have heard me remark that the strangest and most unique things are very often connected not with the larger but with the smaller crimes, and occasionally, indeed, where there is room for doubt whether any positive crime has been committed. As far as I have heard, it is impossible for me to say whether the present case is an instance of crime or not, but the course of events is certainly among the most singular that I have ever listened to. Perhaps, Mr. Wilson, you would have the great kindness to recommence your narrative. I ask you not merely because my friend Dr. Watson has not heard the opening part but also because the peculiar nature of the story makes me anxious to have every possible detail from your lips. As a rule, when I have heard some slight indication of the course of events, I am able to guide myself by the thousands of other similar cases which occur to my memory. In the present instance I am forced to admit that the facts are, to the best of my belief, unique.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The portly client puffed out his chest with an appearance of some little pride and pulled a dirty and wrinkled newspaper from the inside pocket of his greatcoat. As he glanced down the advertisement column, with his head thrust forward and the paper flattened out upon his knee, I took a good look at the man and endeavoured, after the fashion of my companion, to read the indications which might be presented by his dress or appearance.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did not gain very much, however, by my inspection. Our visitor bore every mark of being an average commonplace British tradesman, obese, pompous, and slow. He wore rather baggy grey shepherd’s check trousers, a not over-clean black frock-coat, unbuttoned in the front, and a drab waistcoat with a heavy brassy Albert chain, and a square pierced bit of metal dangling down as an ornament. A frayed top-hat and a faded brown overcoat with a wrinkled velvet collar lay upon a chair beside him. Altogether, look as I would, there was nothing remarkable about the man save his blazing red head, and the expression of extreme chagrin and discontent upon his features.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes’ quick eye took in my occupation, and he shook his head with a smile as he noticed my questioning glances. “Beyond the obvious facts that he has at some time done manual labour, that he takes snuff, that he is a Freemason, that he has been in China, and that he has done a considerable amount of writing lately, I can deduce nothing else.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Jabez Wilson started up in his chair, with his forefinger upon the paper, but his eyes upon my companion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How, in the name of good-fortune, did you know all that, Mr. Holmes?” he asked. “How did you know, for example, that I did manual labour. It’s as true as gospel, for I began as a ship’s carpenter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your hands, my dear sir. Your right hand is quite a size larger than your left. You have worked with it, and the muscles are more developed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, the snuff, then, and the Freemasonry?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I won’t insult your intelligence by telling you how I read that, especially as, rather against the strict rules of your order, you use an arc-and-compass breastpin.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, of course, I forgot that. But the writing?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What else can be indicated by that right cuff so very shiny for five inches, and the left one with the smooth patch near the elbow where you rest it upon the desk?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, but China?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The fish that you have tattooed immediately above your right wrist could only have been done in China. I have made a small study of tattoo marks and have even contributed to the literature of the subject. That trick of staining the fishes’ scales of a delicate pink is quite peculiar to China. When, in addition, I see a Chinese coin hanging from your watch-chain, the matter becomes even more simple.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Jabez Wilson laughed heavily. “Well, I never!” said he. “I thought at first that you had done something clever, but I see that there was nothing in it after all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I begin to think, Watson,” said Holmes, “that I make a mistake in explaining. ‘<i>Omne ignotum pro magnifico</i>,’ you know, and my poor little reputation, such as it is, will suffer shipwreck if I am so candid. Can you not find the advertisement, Mr. Wilson?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I have got it now,” he answered with his thick red finger planted halfway down the column. “Here it is. This is what began it all. You just read it for yourself, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I took the paper from him and read as follows:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“TO THE RED-HEADED LEAGUE: On account of the bequest of the late Ezekiah Hopkins, of Lebanon, Pennsylvania, U.S.A., there is now another vacancy open which entitles a member of the League to a salary of £ 4 a week for purely nominal services. All red-headed men who are sound in body and mind and above the age of twenty-one years, are eligible. Apply in person on Monday, at eleven o’clock, to Duncan Ross, at the offices of the League, 7 Pope’s Court, Fleet Street.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What on earth does this mean?” I ejaculated after I had twice read over the extraordinary announcement.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes chuckled and wriggled in his chair, as was his habit when in high spirits. “It is a little off the beaten track, isn’t it?” said he. “And now, Mr. Wilson, off you go at scratch and tell us all about yourself, your household, and the effect which this advertisement had upon your fortunes. You will first make a note, Doctor, of the paper and the date.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is <i>The Morning Chronicle</i> of April 27, 1890. Just two months ago.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very good. Now, Mr. Wilson?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it is just as I have been telling you, Mr. Sherlock Holmes,” said Jabez Wilson, mopping his forehead; “I have a small pawnbroker’s business at Coburg Square, near the City. It’s not a very large affair, and of late years it has not done more than just give me a living. I used to be able to keep two assistants, but now I only keep one; and I would have a job to pay him but that he is willing to come for half wages so as to learn the business.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is the name of this obliging youth?” asked Sherlock Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“His name is Vincent Spaulding, and he’s not such a youth, either. It’s hard to say his age. I should not wish a smarter assistant, Mr. Holmes; and I know very well that he could better himself and earn twice what I am able to give him. But, after all, if he is satisfied, why should I put ideas in his head?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, indeed? You seem most fortunate in having an <i>employé</i> who comes under the full market price. It is not a common experience among employers in this age. I don’t know that your assistant is not as remarkable as your advertisement.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, he has his faults, too,” said Mr. Wilson. “Never was such a fellow for photography. Snapping away with a camera when he ought to be improving his mind, and then diving down into the cellar like a rabbit into its hole to develop his pictures. That is his main fault, but on the whole he’s a good worker. There’s no vice in him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is still with you, I presume?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. He and a girl of fourteen, who does a bit of simple cooking and keeps the place clean—that’s all I have in the house, for I am a widower and never had any family. We live very quietly, sir, the three of us; and we keep a roof over our heads and pay our debts, if we do nothing more.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The first thing that put us out was that advertisement. Spaulding, he came down into the office just this day eight weeks, with this very paper in his hand, and he says:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I wish to the Lord, Mr. Wilson, that I was a red-headed man.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Why that?’ I asks.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Why,’ says he, ‘here’s another vacancy on the League of the Red-headed Men. It’s worth quite a little fortune to any man who gets it, and I understand that there are more vacancies than there are men, so that the trustees are at their wits’ end what to do with the money. If my hair would only change colour, here’s a nice little crib all ready for me to step into.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Why, what is it, then?’ I asked. You see, Mr. Holmes, I am a very stay-at-home man, and as my business came to me instead of my having to go to it, I was often weeks on end without putting my foot over the door-mat. In that way I didn’t know much of what was going on outside, and I was always glad of a bit of news.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Have you never heard of the League of the Red-headed Men?’ he asked with his eyes open.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Never.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Why, I wonder at that, for you are eligible yourself for one of the vacancies.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And what are they worth?’ I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, merely a couple of hundred a year, but the work is slight, and it need not interfere very much with one’s other occupations.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, you can easily think that that made me prick up my ears, for the business has not been over good for some years, and an extra couple of hundred would have been very handy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Tell me all about it,’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well,’ said he, showing me the advertisement, ‘you can see for yourself that the League has a vacancy, and there is the address where you should apply for particulars. As far as I can make out, the League was founded by an American millionaire, Ezekiah Hopkins, who was very peculiar in his ways. He was himself red-headed, and he had a great sympathy for all red-headed men; so, when he died, it was found that he had left his enormous fortune in the hands of trustees, with instructions to apply the interest to the providing of easy berths to men whose hair is of that colour. From all I hear it is splendid pay and very little to do.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘But,’ said I, ‘there would be millions of red-headed men who would apply.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Not so many as you might think,’ he answered. ‘You see it is really confined to Londoners, and to grown men. This American had started from London when he was young, and he wanted to do the old town a good turn. Then, again, I have heard it is no use your applying if your hair is light red, or dark red, or anything but real bright, blazing, fiery red. Now, if you cared to apply, Mr. Wilson, you would just walk in; but perhaps it would hardly be worth your while to put yourself out of the way for the sake of a few hundred pounds.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, it is a fact, gentlemen, as you may see for yourselves, that my hair is of a very full and rich tint, so that it seemed to me that if there was to be any competition in the matter I stood as good a chance as any man that I had ever met. Vincent Spaulding seemed to know so much about it that I thought he might prove useful, so I just ordered him to put up the shutters for the day and to come right away with me. He was very willing to have a holiday, so we shut the business up and started off for the address that was given us in the advertisement.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I never hope to see such a sight as that again, Mr. Holmes. From north, south, east, and west every man who had a shade of red in his hair had tramped into the city to answer the advertisement. Fleet Street was choked with red-headed folk, and Pope’s Court looked like a coster’s orange barrow. I should not have thought there were so many in the whole country as were brought together by that single advertisement. Every shade of colour they were—straw, lemon, orange, brick, Irish-setter, liver, clay; but, as Spaulding said, there were not many who had the real vivid flame-coloured tint. When I saw how many were waiting, I would have given it up in despair; but Spaulding would not hear of it. How he did it I could not imagine, but he pushed and pulled and butted until he got me through the crowd, and right up to the steps which led to the office. There was a double stream upon the stair, some going up in hope, and some coming back dejected; but we wedged in as well as we could and soon found ourselves in the office.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your experience has been a most entertaining one,” remarked Holmes as his client paused and refreshed his memory with a huge pinch of snuff. “Pray continue your very interesting statement.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There was nothing in the office but a couple of wooden chairs and a deal table, behind which sat a small man with a head that was even redder than mine. He said a few words to each candidate as he came up, and then he always managed to find some fault in them which would disqualify them. Getting a vacancy did not seem to be such a very easy matter, after all. However, when our turn came the little man was much more favourable to me than to any of the others, and he closed the door as we entered, so that he might have a private word with us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘This is Mr. Jabez Wilson,’ said my assistant, ‘and he is willing to fill a vacancy in the League.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And he is admirably suited for it,’ the other answered. ‘He has every requirement. I cannot recall when I have seen anything so fine.’ He took a step backward, cocked his head on one side, and gazed at my hair until I felt quite bashful. Then suddenly he plunged forward, wrung my hand, and congratulated me warmly on my success.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It would be injustice to hesitate,’ said he. ‘You will, however, I am sure, excuse me for taking an obvious precaution.’ With that he seized my hair in both his hands, and tugged until I yelled with the pain. ‘There is water in your eyes,’ said he as he released me. ‘I perceive that all is as it should be. But we have to be careful, for we have twice been deceived by wigs and once by paint. I could tell you tales of cobbler’s wax which would disgust you with human nature.’ He stepped over to the window and shouted through it at the top of his voice that the vacancy was filled. A groan of disappointment came up from below, and the folk all trooped away in different directions until there was not a red-head to be seen except my own and that of the manager.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘My name,’ said he, ‘is Mr. Duncan Ross, and I am myself one of the pensioners upon the fund left by our noble benefactor. Are you a married man, Mr. Wilson? Have you a family?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I answered that I had not.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“His face fell immediately.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Dear me!’ he said gravely, ‘that is very serious indeed! I am sorry to hear you say that. The fund was, of course, for the propagation and spread of the red-heads as well as for their maintenance. It is exceedingly unfortunate that you should be a bachelor.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My face lengthened at this, Mr. Holmes, for I thought that I was not to have the vacancy after all; but after thinking it over for a few minutes he said that it would be all right.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘In the case of another,’ said he, ‘the objection might be fatal, but we must stretch a point in favour of a man with such a head of hair as yours. When shall you be able to enter upon your new duties?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well, it is a little awkward, for I have a business already,’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, never mind about that, Mr. Wilson!’ said Vincent Spaulding. ‘I should be able to look after that for you.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What would be the hours?’ I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Ten to two.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now a pawnbroker’s business is mostly done of an evening, Mr. Holmes, especially Thursday and Friday evening, which is just before pay-day; so it would suit me very well to earn a little in the mornings. Besides, I knew that my assistant was a good man, and that he would see to anything that turned up.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘That would suit me very well,’ said I. ‘And the pay?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Is £ 4 a week.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And the work?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Is purely nominal.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What do you call purely nominal?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well, you have to be in the office, or at least in the building, the whole time. If you leave, you forfeit your whole position forever. The will is very clear upon that point. You don’t comply with the conditions if you budge from the office during that time.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It’s only four hours a day, and I should not think of leaving,’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No excuse will avail,’ said Mr. Duncan Ross; ‘neither sickness nor business nor anything else. There you must stay, or you lose your billet.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And the work?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Is to copy out the <i>Encyclopædia Britannica</i>. There is the first volume of it in that press. You must find your own ink, pens, and blotting-paper, but we provide this table and chair. Will you be ready to-morrow?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Certainly,’ I answered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Then, good-bye, Mr. Jabez Wilson, and let me congratulate you once more on the important position which you have been fortunate enough to gain.’ He bowed me out of the room and I went home with my assistant, hardly knowing what to say or do, I was so pleased at my own good fortune.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I thought over the matter all day, and by evening I was in low spirits again; for I had quite persuaded myself that the whole affair must be some great hoax or fraud, though what its object might be I could not imagine. It seemed altogether past belief that anyone could make such a will, or that they would pay such a sum for doing anything so simple as copying out the <i>Encyclopædia Britannica</i>. Vincent Spaulding did what he could to cheer me up, but by bedtime I had reasoned myself out of the whole thing. However, in the morning I determined to have a look at it anyhow, so I bought a penny bottle of ink, and with a quill-pen, and seven sheets of foolscap paper, I started off for Pope’s Court.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, to my surprise and delight, everything was as right as possible. The table was set out ready for me, and Mr. Duncan Ross was there to see that I got fairly to work. He started me off upon the letter A, and then he left me; but he would drop in from time to time to see that all was right with me. At two o’clock he bade me good-day, complimented me upon the amount that I had written, and locked the door of the office after me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This went on day after day, Mr. Holmes, and on Saturday the manager came in and planked down four golden sovereigns for my week’s work. It was the same next week, and the same the week after. Every morning I was there at ten, and every afternoon I left at two. By degrees Mr. Duncan Ross took to coming in only once of a morning, and then, after a time, he did not come in at all. Still, of course, I never dared to leave the room for an instant, for I was not sure when he might come, and the billet was such a good one, and suited me so well, that I would not risk the loss of it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Eight weeks passed away like this, and I had written about Abbots and Archery and Armour and Architecture and Attica, and hoped with diligence that I might get on to the B’s before very long. It cost me something in foolscap, and I had pretty nearly filled a shelf with my writings. And then suddenly the whole business came to an end.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To an end?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. And no later than this morning. I went to my work as usual at ten o’clock, but the door was shut and locked, with a little square of cardboard hammered on to the middle of the panel with a tack. Here it is, and you can read for yourself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He held up a piece of white cardboard about the size of a sheet of note-paper. It read in this fashion:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“THE RED-HEADED LEAGUE IS DISSOLVED. October 9, 1890.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes and I surveyed this curt announcement and the rueful face behind it, until the comical side of the affair so completely overtopped every other consideration that we both burst out into a roar of laughter.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot see that there is anything very funny,” cried our client, flushing up to the roots of his flaming head. “If you can do nothing better than laugh at me, I can go elsewhere.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no,” cried Holmes, shoving him back into the chair from which he had half risen. “I really wouldn’t miss your case for the world. It is most refreshingly unusual. But there is, if you will excuse my saying so, something just a little funny about it. Pray what steps did you take when you found the card upon the door?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was staggered, sir. I did not know what to do. Then I called at the offices round, but none of them seemed to know anything about it. Finally, I went to the landlord, who is an accountant living on the ground floor, and I asked him if he could tell me what had become of the Red-headed League. He said that he had never heard of any such body. Then I asked him who Mr. Duncan Ross was. He answered that the name was new to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well,’ said I, ‘the gentleman at No. 4.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What, the red-headed man?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh,’ said he, ‘his name was William Morris. He was a solicitor and was using my room as a temporary convenience until his new premises were ready. He moved out yesterday.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Where could I find him?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, at his new offices. He did tell me the address. Yes, 17 King Edward Street, near St. Paul’s.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I started off, Mr. Holmes, but when I got to that address it was a manufactory of artificial knee-caps, and no one in it had ever heard of either Mr. William Morris or Mr. Duncan Ross.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what did you do then?” asked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I went home to Saxe-Coburg Square, and I took the advice of my assistant. But he could not help me in any way. He could only say that if I waited I should hear by post. But that was not quite good enough, Mr. Holmes. I did not wish to lose such a place without a struggle, so, as I had heard that you were good enough to give advice to poor folk who were in need of it, I came right away to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you did very wisely,” said Holmes. “Your case is an exceedingly remarkable one, and I shall be happy to look into it. From what you have told me I think that it is possible that graver issues hang from it than might at first sight appear.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Grave enough!” said Mr. Jabez Wilson. “Why, I have lost four pound a week.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As far as you are personally concerned,” remarked Holmes, “I do not see that you have any grievance against this extraordinary league. On the contrary, you are, as I understand, richer by some £ 30, to say nothing of the minute knowledge which you have gained on every subject which comes under the letter A. You have lost nothing by them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir. But I want to find out about them, and who they are, and what their object was in playing this prank—if it was a prank—upon me. It was a pretty expensive joke for them, for it cost them two and thirty pounds.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We shall endeavour to clear up these points for you. And, first, one or two questions, Mr. Wilson. This assistant of yours who first called your attention to the advertisement—how long had he been with you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“About a month then.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did he come?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In answer to an advertisement.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was he the only applicant?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I had a dozen.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why did you pick him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because he was handy and would come cheap.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At half wages, in fact.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is he like, this Vincent Spaulding?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Small, stout-built, very quick in his ways, no hair on his face, though he’s not short of thirty. Has a white splash of acid upon his forehead.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes sat up in his chair in considerable excitement. “I thought as much,” said he. “Have you ever observed that his ears are pierced for earrings?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. He told me that a gipsy had done it for him when he was a lad.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hum!” said Holmes, sinking back in deep thought. “He is still with you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, sir; I have only just left him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And has your business been attended to in your absence?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing to complain of, sir. There’s never very much to do of a morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That will do, Mr. Wilson. I shall be happy to give you an opinion upon the subject in the course of a day or two. To-day is Saturday, and I hope that by Monday we may come to a conclusion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, Watson,” said Holmes when our visitor had left us, “what do you make of it all?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I make nothing of it,” I answered frankly. “It is a most mysterious business.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As a rule,” said Holmes, “the more bizarre a thing is the less mysterious it proves to be. It is your commonplace, featureless crimes which are really puzzling, just as a commonplace face is the most difficult to identify. But I must be prompt over this matter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What are you going to do, then?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To smoke,” he answered. “It is quite a three pipe problem, and I beg that you won’t speak to me for fifty minutes.” He curled himself up in his chair, with his thin knees drawn up to his hawk-like nose, and there he sat with his eyes closed and his black clay pipe thrusting out like the bill of some strange bird. I had come to the conclusion that he had dropped asleep, and indeed was nodding myself, when he suddenly sprang out of his chair with the gesture of a man who has made up his mind and put his pipe down upon the mantelpiece.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Sarasate plays at the St. James’s Hall this afternoon,” he remarked. “What do you think, Watson? Could your patients spare you for a few hours?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have nothing to do to-day. My practice is never very absorbing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then put on your hat and come. I am going through the City first, and we can have some lunch on the way. I observe that there is a good deal of German music on the programme, which is rather more to my taste than Italian or French. It is introspective, and I want to introspect. Come along!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We travelled by the Underground as far as Aldersgate; and a short walk took us to Saxe-Coburg Square, the scene of the singular story which we had listened to in the morning. It was a poky, little, shabby-genteel place, where four lines of dingy two-storied brick houses looked out into a small railed-in enclosure, where a lawn of weedy grass and a few clumps of faded laurel bushes made a hard fight against a smoke-laden and uncongenial atmosphere. Three gilt balls and a brown board with “JABEZ WILSON” in white letters, upon a corner house, announced the place where our red-headed client carried on his business. Sherlock Holmes stopped in front of it with his head on one side and looked it all over, with his eyes shining brightly between puckered lids. Then he walked slowly up the street, and then down again to the corner, still looking keenly at the houses. Finally he returned to the pawnbroker’s, and, having thumped vigorously upon the pavement with his stick two or three times, he went up to the door and knocked. It was instantly opened by a bright-looking, clean-shaven young fellow, who asked him to step in.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you,” said Holmes, “I only wished to ask you how you would go from here to the Strand.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Third right, fourth left,” answered the assistant promptly, closing the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Smart fellow, that,” observed Holmes as we walked away. “He is, in my judgment, the fourth smartest man in London, and for daring I am not sure that he has not a claim to be third. I have known something of him before.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Evidently,” said I, “Mr. Wilson’s assistant counts for a good deal in this mystery of the Red-headed League. I am sure that you inquired your way merely in order that you might see him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The knees of his trousers.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what did you see?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What I expected to see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why did you beat the pavement?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear doctor, this is a time for observation, not for talk. We are spies in an enemy’s country. We know something of Saxe-Coburg Square. Let us now explore the parts which lie behind it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The road in which we found ourselves as we turned round the corner from the retired Saxe-Coburg Square presented as great a contrast to it as the front of a picture does to the back. It was one of the main arteries which conveyed the traffic of the City to the north and west. The roadway was blocked with the immense stream of commerce flowing in a double tide inward and outward, while the footpaths were black with the hurrying swarm of pedestrians. It was difficult to realise as we looked at the line of fine shops and stately business premises that they really abutted on the other side upon the faded and stagnant square which we had just quitted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let me see,” said Holmes, standing at the corner and glancing along the line, “I should like just to remember the order of the houses here. It is a hobby of mine to have an exact knowledge of London. There is Mortimer’s, the tobacconist, the little newspaper shop, the Coburg branch of the City and Suburban Bank, the Vegetarian Restaurant, and McFarlane’s carriage-building depot. That carries us right on to the other block. And now, Doctor, we’ve done our work, so it’s time we had some play. A sandwich and a cup of coffee, and then off to violin-land, where all is sweetness and delicacy and harmony, and there are no red-headed clients to vex us with their conundrums.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My friend was an enthusiastic musician, being himself not only a very capable performer but a composer of no ordinary merit. All the afternoon he sat in the stalls wrapped in the most perfect happiness, gently waving his long, thin fingers in time to the music, while his gently smiling face and his languid, dreamy eyes were as unlike those of Holmes the sleuth-hound, Holmes the relentless, keen-witted, ready-handed criminal agent, as it was possible to conceive. In his singular character the dual nature alternately asserted itself, and his extreme exactness and astuteness represented, as I have often thought, the reaction against the poetic and contemplative mood which occasionally predominated in him. The swing of his nature took him from extreme languor to devouring energy; and, as I knew well, he was never so truly formidable as when, for days on end, he had been lounging in his armchair amid his improvisations and his black-letter editions. Then it was that the lust of the chase would suddenly come upon him, and that his brilliant reasoning power would rise to the level of intuition, until those who were unacquainted with his methods would look askance at him as on a man whose knowledge was not that of other mortals. When I saw him that afternoon so enwrapped in the music at St. James’s Hall I felt that an evil time might be coming upon those whom he had set himself to hunt down.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You want to go home, no doubt, Doctor,” he remarked as we emerged.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it would be as well.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I have some business to do which will take some hours. This business at Coburg Square is serious.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why serious?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A considerable crime is in contemplation. I have every reason to believe that we shall be in time to stop it. But to-day being Saturday rather complicates matters. I shall want your help to-night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At what time?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ten will be early enough.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall be at Baker Street at ten.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well. And, I say, Doctor, there may be some little danger, so kindly put your army revolver in your pocket.” He waved his hand, turned on his heel, and disappeared in an instant among the crowd.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I trust that I am not more dense than my neighbours, but I was always oppressed with a sense of my own stupidity in my dealings with Sherlock Holmes. Here I had heard what he had heard, I had seen what he had seen, and yet from his words it was evident that he saw clearly not only what had happened but what was about to happen, while to me the whole business was still confused and grotesque. As I drove home to my house in Kensington I thought over it all, from the extraordinary story of the red-headed copier of the <i>Encyclopædia</i> down to the visit to Saxe-Coburg Square, and the ominous words with which he had parted from me. What was this nocturnal expedition, and why should I go armed? Where were we going, and what were we to do? I had the hint from Holmes that this smooth-faced pawnbroker’s assistant was a formidable man—a man who might play a deep game. I tried to puzzle it out, but gave it up in despair and set the matter aside until night should bring an explanation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a quarter-past nine when I started from home and made my way across the Park, and so through Oxford Street to Baker Street. Two hansoms were standing at the door, and as I entered the passage I heard the sound of voices from above. On entering his room, I found Holmes in animated conversation with two men, one of whom I recognised as Peter Jones, the official police agent, while the other was a long, thin, sad-faced man, with a very shiny hat and oppressively respectable frock-coat.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha! Our party is complete,” said Holmes, buttoning up his pea-jacket and taking his heavy hunting crop from the rack. “Watson, I think you know Mr. Jones, of Scotland Yard? Let me introduce you to Mr. Merryweather, who is to be our companion in to-night’s adventure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We’re hunting in couples again, Doctor, you see,” said Jones in his consequential way. “Our friend here is a wonderful man for starting a chase. All he wants is an old dog to help him to do the running down.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I hope a wild goose may not prove to be the end of our chase,” observed Mr. Merryweather gloomily.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You may place considerable confidence in Mr. Holmes, sir,” said the police agent loftily. “He has his own little methods, which are, if he won’t mind my saying so, just a little too theoretical and fantastic, but he has the makings of a detective in him. It is not too much to say that once or twice, as in that business of the Sholto murder and the Agra treasure, he has been more nearly correct than the official force.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, if you say so, Mr. Jones, it is all right,” said the stranger with deference. “Still, I confess that I miss my rubber. It is the first Saturday night for seven-and-twenty years that I have not had my rubber.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think you will find,” said Sherlock Holmes, “that you will play for a higher stake to-night than you have ever done yet, and that the play will be more exciting. For you, Mr. Merryweather, the stake will be some £ 30,000; and for you, Jones, it will be the man upon whom you wish to lay your hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“John Clay, the murderer, thief, smasher, and forger. He’s a young man, Mr. Merryweather, but he is at the head of his profession, and I would rather have my bracelets on him than on any criminal in London. He’s a remarkable man, is young John Clay. His grandfather was a royal duke, and he himself has been to Eton and Oxford. His brain is as cunning as his fingers, and though we meet signs of him at every turn, we never know where to find the man himself. He’ll crack a crib in Scotland one week, and be raising money to build an orphanage in Cornwall the next. I’ve been on his track for years and have never set eyes on him yet.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I hope that I may have the pleasure of introducing you to-night. I’ve had one or two little turns also with Mr. John Clay, and I agree with you that he is at the head of his profession. It is past ten, however, and quite time that we started. If you two will take the first hansom, Watson and I will follow in the second.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes was not very communicative during the long drive and lay back in the cab humming the tunes which he had heard in the afternoon. We rattled through an endless labyrinth of gas-lit streets until we emerged into Farrington Street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We are close there now,” my friend remarked. “This fellow Merryweather is a bank director, and personally interested in the matter. I thought it as well to have Jones with us also. He is not a bad fellow, though an absolute imbecile in his profession. He has one positive virtue. He is as brave as a bulldog and as tenacious as a lobster if he gets his claws upon anyone. Here we are, and they are waiting for us.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had reached the same crowded thoroughfare in which we had found ourselves in the morning. Our cabs were dismissed, and, following the guidance of Mr. Merryweather, we passed down a narrow passage and through a side door, which he opened for us. Within there was a small corridor, which ended in a very massive iron gate. This also was opened, and led down a flight of winding stone steps, which terminated at another formidable gate. Mr. Merryweather stopped to light a lantern, and then conducted us down a dark, earth-smelling passage, and so, after opening a third door, into a huge vault or cellar, which was piled all round with crates and massive boxes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are not very vulnerable from above,” Holmes remarked as he held up the lantern and gazed about him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nor from below,” said Mr. Merryweather, striking his stick upon the flags which lined the floor. “Why, dear me, it sounds quite hollow!” he remarked, looking up in surprise.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I must really ask you to be a little more quiet!” said Holmes severely. “You have already imperilled the whole success of our expedition. Might I beg that you would have the goodness to sit down upon one of those boxes, and not to interfere?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The solemn Mr. Merryweather perched himself upon a crate, with a very injured expression upon his face, while Holmes fell upon his knees upon the floor and, with the lantern and a magnifying lens, began to examine minutely the cracks between the stones. A few seconds sufficed to satisfy him, for he sprang to his feet again and put his glass in his pocket.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have at least an hour before us,” he remarked, “for they can hardly take any steps until the good pawnbroker is safely in bed. Then they will not lose a minute, for the sooner they do their work the longer time they will have for their escape. We are at present, Doctor—as no doubt you have divined—in the cellar of the City branch of one of the principal London banks. Mr. Merryweather is the chairman of directors, and he will explain to you that there are reasons why the more daring criminals of London should take a considerable interest in this cellar at present.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is our French gold,” whispered the director. “We have had several warnings that an attempt might be made upon it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your French gold?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. We had occasion some months ago to strengthen our resources and borrowed for that purpose 30,000 napoleons from the Bank of France. It has become known that we have never had occasion to unpack the money, and that it is still lying in our cellar. The crate upon which I sit contains 2,000 napoleons packed between layers of lead foil. Our reserve of bullion is much larger at present than is usually kept in a single branch office, and the directors have had misgivings upon the subject.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which were very well justified,” observed Holmes. “And now it is time that we arranged our little plans. I expect that within an hour matters will come to a head. In the meantime Mr. Merryweather, we must put the screen over that dark lantern.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And sit in the dark?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am afraid so. I had brought a pack of cards in my pocket, and I thought that, as we were a <i>partie carrée</i>, you might have your rubber after all. But I see that the enemy’s preparations have gone so far that we cannot risk the presence of a light. And, first of all, we must choose our positions. These are daring men, and though we shall take them at a disadvantage, they may do us some harm unless we are careful. I shall stand behind this crate, and do you conceal yourselves behind those. Then, when I flash a light upon them, close in swiftly. If they fire, Watson, have no compunction about shooting them down.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I placed my revolver, cocked, upon the top of the wooden case behind which I crouched. Holmes shot the slide across the front of his lantern and left us in pitch darkness—such an absolute darkness as I have never before experienced. The smell of hot metal remained to assure us that the light was still there, ready to flash out at a moment’s notice. To me, with my nerves worked up to a pitch of expectancy, there was something depressing and subduing in the sudden gloom, and in the cold dank air of the vault.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They have but one retreat,” whispered Holmes. “That is back through the house into Saxe-Coburg Square. I hope that you have done what I asked you, Jones?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have an inspector and two officers waiting at the front door.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then we have stopped all the holes. And now we must be silent and wait.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>What a time it seemed! From comparing notes afterwards it was but an hour and a quarter, yet it appeared to me that the night must have almost gone, and the dawn be breaking above us. My limbs were weary and stiff, for I feared to change my position; yet my nerves were worked up to the highest pitch of tension, and my hearing was so acute that I could not only hear the gentle breathing of my companions, but I could distinguish the deeper, heavier in-breath of the bulky Jones from the thin, sighing note of the bank director. From my position I could look over the case in the direction of the floor. Suddenly my eyes caught the glint of a light.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At first it was but a lurid spark upon the stone pavement. Then it lengthened out until it became a yellow line, and then, without any warning or sound, a gash seemed to open and a hand appeared, a white, almost womanly hand, which felt about in the centre of the little area of light. For a minute or more the hand, with its writhing fingers, protruded out of the floor. Then it was withdrawn as suddenly as it appeared, and all was dark again save the single lurid spark which marked a chink between the stones.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Its disappearance, however, was but momentary. With a rending, tearing sound, one of the broad, white stones turned over upon its side and left a square, gaping hole, through which streamed the light of a lantern. Over the edge there peeped a clean-cut, boyish face, which looked keenly about it, and then, with a hand on either side of the aperture, drew itself shoulder-high and waist-high, until one knee rested upon the edge. In another instant he stood at the side of the hole and was hauling after him a companion, lithe and small like himself, with a pale face and a shock of very red hair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s all clear,” he whispered. “Have you the chisel and the bags? Great Scott! Jump, Archie, jump, and I’ll swing for it!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes had sprung out and seized the intruder by the collar. The other dived down the hole, and I heard the sound of rending cloth as Jones clutched at his skirts. The light flashed upon the barrel of a revolver, but Holmes’ hunting crop came down on the man’s wrist, and the pistol clinked upon the stone floor.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s no use, John Clay,” said Holmes blandly. “You have no chance at all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So I see,” the other answered with the utmost coolness. “I fancy that my pal is all right, though I see you have got his coat-tails.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There are three men waiting for him at the door,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, indeed! You seem to have done the thing very completely. I must compliment you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I you,” Holmes answered. “Your red-headed idea was very new and effective.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’ll see your pal again presently,” said Jones. “He’s quicker at climbing down holes than I am. Just hold out while I fix the derbies.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I beg that you will not touch me with your filthy hands,” remarked our prisoner as the handcuffs clattered upon his wrists. “You may not be aware that I have royal blood in my veins. Have the goodness, also, when you address me always to say ‘sir’ and ‘please.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“All right,” said Jones with a stare and a snigger. “Well, would you please, sir, march upstairs, where we can get a cab to carry your Highness to the police-station?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is better,” said John Clay serenely. He made a sweeping bow to the three of us and walked quietly off in the custody of the detective.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really, Mr. Holmes,” said Mr. Merryweather as we followed them from the cellar, “I do not know how the bank can thank you or repay you. There is no doubt that you have detected and defeated in the most complete manner one of the most determined attempts at bank robbery that have ever come within my experience.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have had one or two little scores of my own to settle with Mr. John Clay,” said Holmes. “I have been at some small expense over this matter, which I shall expect the bank to refund, but beyond that I am amply repaid by having had an experience which is in many ways unique, and by hearing the very remarkable narrative of the Red-headed League.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“You see, Watson,” he explained in the early hours of the morning as we sat over a glass of whisky and soda in Baker Street, “it was perfectly obvious from the first that the only possible object of this rather fantastic business of the advertisement of the League, and the copying of the <i>Encyclopædia</i>, must be to get this not over-bright pawnbroker out of the way for a number of hours every day. It was a curious way of managing it, but, really, it would be difficult to suggest a better. The method was no doubt suggested to Clay’s ingenious mind by the colour of his accomplice’s hair. The £ 4 a week was a lure which must draw him, and what was it to them, who were playing for thousands? They put in the advertisement, one rogue has the temporary office, the other rogue incites the man to apply for it, and together they manage to secure his absence every morning in the week. From the time that I heard of the assistant having come for half wages, it was obvious to me that he had some strong motive for securing the situation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But how could you guess what the motive was?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Had there been women in the house, I should have suspected a mere vulgar intrigue. That, however, was out of the question. The man’s business was a small one, and there was nothing in his house which could account for such elaborate preparations, and such an expenditure as they were at. It must, then, be something out of the house. What could it be? I thought of the assistant’s fondness for photography, and his trick of vanishing into the cellar. The cellar! There was the end of this tangled clue. Then I made inquiries as to this mysterious assistant and found that I had to deal with one of the coolest and most daring criminals in London. He was doing something in the cellar—something which took many hours a day for months on end. What could it be, once more? I could think of nothing save that he was running a tunnel to some other building.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So far I had got when we went to visit the scene of action. I surprised you by beating upon the pavement with my stick. I was ascertaining whether the cellar stretched out in front or behind. It was not in front. Then I rang the bell, and, as I hoped, the assistant answered it. We have had some skirmishes, but we had never set eyes upon each other before. I hardly looked at his face. His knees were what I wished to see. You must yourself have remarked how worn, wrinkled, and stained they were. They spoke of those hours of burrowing. The only remaining point was what they were burrowing for. I walked round the corner, saw the City and Suburban Bank abutted on our friend’s premises, and felt that I had solved my problem. When you drove home after the concert I called upon Scotland Yard and upon the chairman of the bank directors, with the result that you have seen.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how could you tell that they would make their attempt to-night?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, when they closed their League offices that was a sign that they cared no longer about Mr. Jabez Wilson’s presence—in other words, that they had completed their tunnel. But it was essential that they should use it soon, as it might be discovered, or the bullion might be removed. Saturday would suit them better than any other day, as it would give them two days for their escape. For all these reasons I expected them to come to-night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You reasoned it out beautifully,” I exclaimed in unfeigned admiration. “It is so long a chain, and yet every link rings true.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It saved me from ennui,” he answered, yawning. “Alas! I already feel it closing in upon me. My life is spent in one long effort to escape from the commonplaces of existence. These little problems help me to do so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you are a benefactor of the race,” said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He shrugged his shoulders. “Well, perhaps, after all, it is of some little use,” he remarked. “‘<i>L’homme c’est rien—l’œuvre c’est tout</i>,’ as Gustave Flaubert wrote to George Sand.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>III.<br>\nA CASE OF IDENTITY</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">“M</span>y dear fellow,” said Sherlock Holmes as we sat on either side of the fire in his lodgings at Baker Street, “life is infinitely stranger than anything which the mind of man could invent. We would not dare to conceive the things which are really mere commonplaces of existence. If we could fly out of that window hand in hand, hover over this great city, gently remove the roofs, and peep in at the queer things which are going on, the strange coincidences, the plannings, the cross-purposes, the wonderful chains of events, working through generations, and leading to the most <i>outré</i> results, it would make all fiction with its conventionalities and foreseen conclusions most stale and unprofitable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And yet I am not convinced of it,” I answered. “The cases which come to light in the papers are, as a rule, bald enough, and vulgar enough. We have in our police reports realism pushed to its extreme limits, and yet the result is, it must be confessed, neither fascinating nor artistic.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A certain selection and discretion must be used in producing a realistic effect,” remarked Holmes. “This is wanting in the police report, where more stress is laid, perhaps, upon the platitudes of the magistrate than upon the details, which to an observer contain the vital essence of the whole matter. Depend upon it, there is nothing so unnatural as the commonplace.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I smiled and shook my head. “I can quite understand your thinking so,” I said. “Of course, in your position of unofficial adviser and helper to everybody who is absolutely puzzled, throughout three continents, you are brought in contact with all that is strange and bizarre. But here”—I picked up the morning paper from the ground—“let us put it to a practical test. Here is the first heading upon which I come. ‘A husband’s cruelty to his wife.’ There is half a column of print, but I know without reading it that it is all perfectly familiar to me. There is, of course, the other woman, the drink, the push, the blow, the bruise, the sympathetic sister or landlady. The crudest of writers could invent nothing more crude.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed, your example is an unfortunate one for your argument,” said Holmes, taking the paper and glancing his eye down it. “This is the Dundas separation case, and, as it happens, I was engaged in clearing up some small points in connection with it. The husband was a teetotaler, there was no other woman, and the conduct complained of was that he had drifted into the habit of winding up every meal by taking out his false teeth and hurling them at his wife, which, you will allow, is not an action likely to occur to the imagination of the average story-teller. Take a pinch of snuff, Doctor, and acknowledge that I have scored over you in your example.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He held out his snuffbox of old gold, with a great amethyst in the centre of the lid. Its splendour was in such contrast to his homely ways and simple life that I could not help commenting upon it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah,” said he, “I forgot that I had not seen you for some weeks. It is a little souvenir from the King of Bohemia in return for my assistance in the case of the Irene Adler papers.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the ring?” I asked, glancing at a remarkable brilliant which sparkled upon his finger.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was from the reigning family of Holland, though the matter in which I served them was of such delicacy that I cannot confide it even to you, who have been good enough to chronicle one or two of my little problems.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And have you any on hand just now?” I asked with interest.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Some ten or twelve, but none which present any feature of interest. They are important, you understand, without being interesting. Indeed, I have found that it is usually in unimportant matters that there is a field for the observation, and for the quick analysis of cause and effect which gives the charm to an investigation. The larger crimes are apt to be the simpler, for the bigger the crime the more obvious, as a rule, is the motive. In these cases, save for one rather intricate matter which has been referred to me from Marseilles, there is nothing which presents any features of interest. It is possible, however, that I may have something better before very many minutes are over, for this is one of my clients, or I am much mistaken.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He had risen from his chair and was standing between the parted blinds gazing down into the dull neutral-tinted London street. Looking over his shoulder, I saw that on the pavement opposite there stood a large woman with a heavy fur boa round her neck, and a large curling red feather in a broad-brimmed hat which was tilted in a coquettish Duchess of Devonshire fashion over her ear. From under this great panoply she peeped up in a nervous, hesitating fashion at our windows, while her body oscillated backward and forward, and her fingers fidgeted with her glove buttons. Suddenly, with a plunge, as of the swimmer who leaves the bank, she hurried across the road, and we heard the sharp clang of the bell.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have seen those symptoms before,” said Holmes, throwing his cigarette into the fire. “Oscillation upon the pavement always means an <i>affaire de cœur</i>. She would like advice, but is not sure that the matter is not too delicate for communication. And yet even here we may discriminate. When a woman has been seriously wronged by a man she no longer oscillates, and the usual symptom is a broken bell wire. Here we may take it that there is a love matter, but that the maiden is not so much angry as perplexed, or grieved. But here she comes in person to resolve our doubts.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As he spoke there was a tap at the door, and the boy in buttons entered to announce Miss Mary Sutherland, while the lady herself loomed behind his small black figure like a full-sailed merchant-man behind a tiny pilot boat. Sherlock Holmes welcomed her with the easy courtesy for which he was remarkable, and, having closed the door and bowed her into an armchair, he looked her over in the minute and yet abstracted fashion which was peculiar to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you not find,” he said, “that with your short sight it is a little trying to do so much typewriting?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did at first,” she answered, “but now I know where the letters are without looking.” Then, suddenly realising the full purport of his words, she gave a violent start and looked up, with fear and astonishment upon her broad, good-humoured face. “You’ve heard about me, Mr. Holmes,” she cried, “else how could you know all that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never mind,” said Holmes, laughing; “it is my business to know things. Perhaps I have trained myself to see what others overlook. If not, why should you come to consult me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I came to you, sir, because I heard of you from Mrs. Etherege, whose husband you found so easy when the police and everyone had given him up for dead. Oh, Mr. Holmes, I wish you would do as much for me. I’m not rich, but still I have a hundred a year in my own right, besides the little that I make by the machine, and I would give it all to know what has become of Mr. Hosmer Angel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why did you come away to consult me in such a hurry?” asked Sherlock Holmes, with his finger-tips together and his eyes to the ceiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Again a startled look came over the somewhat vacuous face of Miss Mary Sutherland. “Yes, I did bang out of the house,” she said, “for it made me angry to see the easy way in which Mr. Windibank—that is, my father—took it all. He would not go to the police, and he would not go to you, and so at last, as he would do nothing and kept on saying that there was no harm done, it made me mad, and I just on with my things and came right away to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your father,” said Holmes, “your stepfather, surely, since the name is different.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, my stepfather. I call him father, though it sounds funny, too, for he is only five years and two months older than myself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And your mother is alive?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, mother is alive and well. I wasn’t best pleased, Mr. Holmes, when she married again so soon after father’s death, and a man who was nearly fifteen years younger than herself. Father was a plumber in the Tottenham Court Road, and he left a tidy business behind him, which mother carried on with Mr. Hardy, the foreman; but when Mr. Windibank came he made her sell the business, for he was very superior, being a traveller in wines. They got £ 4700 for the goodwill and interest, which wasn’t near as much as father could have got if he had been alive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had expected to see Sherlock Holmes impatient under this rambling and inconsequential narrative, but, on the contrary, he had listened with the greatest concentration of attention.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your own little income,” he asked, “does it come out of the business?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, no, sir. It is quite separate and was left me by my uncle Ned in Auckland. It is in New Zealand stock, paying 4½ per cent. Two thousand five hundred pounds was the amount, but I can only touch the interest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You interest me extremely,” said Holmes. “And since you draw so large a sum as a hundred a year, with what you earn into the bargain, you no doubt travel a little and indulge yourself in every way. I believe that a single lady can get on very nicely upon an income of about £ 60.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I could do with much less than that, Mr. Holmes, but you understand that as long as I live at home I don’t wish to be a burden to them, and so they have the use of the money just while I am staying with them. Of course, that is only just for the time. Mr. Windibank draws my interest every quarter and pays it over to mother, and I find that I can do pretty well with what I earn at typewriting. It brings me twopence a sheet, and I can often do from fifteen to twenty sheets in a day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have made your position very clear to me,” said Holmes. “This is my friend, Dr. Watson, before whom you can speak as freely as before myself. Kindly tell us now all about your connection with Mr. Hosmer Angel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A flush stole over Miss Sutherland’s face, and she picked nervously at the fringe of her jacket. “I met him first at the gasfitters’ ball,” she said. “They used to send father tickets when he was alive, and then afterwards they remembered us, and sent them to mother. Mr. Windibank did not wish us to go. He never did wish us to go anywhere. He would get quite mad if I wanted so much as to join a Sunday-school treat. But this time I was set on going, and I would go; for what right had he to prevent? He said the folk were not fit for us to know, when all father’s friends were to be there. And he said that I had nothing fit to wear, when I had my purple plush that I had never so much as taken out of the drawer. At last, when nothing else would do, he went off to France upon the business of the firm, but we went, mother and I, with Mr. Hardy, who used to be our foreman, and it was there I met Mr. Hosmer Angel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I suppose,” said Holmes, “that when Mr. Windibank came back from France he was very annoyed at your having gone to the ball.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, well, he was very good about it. He laughed, I remember, and shrugged his shoulders, and said there was no use denying anything to a woman, for she would have her way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see. Then at the gasfitters’ ball you met, as I understand, a gentleman called Mr. Hosmer Angel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. I met him that night, and he called next day to ask if we had got home all safe, and after that we met him—that is to say, Mr. Holmes, I met him twice for walks, but after that father came back again, and Mr. Hosmer Angel could not come to the house any more.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, you know father didn’t like anything of the sort. He wouldn’t have any visitors if he could help it, and he used to say that a woman should be happy in her own family circle. But then, as I used to say to mother, a woman wants her own circle to begin with, and I had not got mine yet.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But how about Mr. Hosmer Angel? Did he make no attempt to see you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, father was going off to France again in a week, and Hosmer wrote and said that it would be safer and better not to see each other until he had gone. We could write in the meantime, and he used to write every day. I took the letters in in the morning, so there was no need for father to know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Were you engaged to the gentleman at this time?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, Mr. Holmes. We were engaged after the first walk that we took. Hosmer—Mr. Angel—was a cashier in an office in Leadenhall Street—and—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What office?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s the worst of it, Mr. Holmes, I don’t know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where did he live, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He slept on the premises.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you don’t know his address?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No—except that it was Leadenhall Street.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where did you address your letters, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To the Leadenhall Street Post Office, to be left till called for. He said that if they were sent to the office he would be chaffed by all the other clerks about having letters from a lady, so I offered to typewrite them, like he did his, but he wouldn’t have that, for he said that when I wrote them they seemed to come from me, but when they were typewritten he always felt that the machine had come between us. That will just show you how fond he was of me, Mr. Holmes, and the little things that he would think of.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was most suggestive,” said Holmes. “It has long been an axiom of mine that the little things are infinitely the most important. Can you remember any other little things about Mr. Hosmer Angel?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He was a very shy man, Mr. Holmes. He would rather walk with me in the evening than in the daylight, for he said that he hated to be conspicuous. Very retiring and gentlemanly he was. Even his voice was gentle. He’d had the quinsy and swollen glands when he was young, he told me, and it had left him with a weak throat, and a hesitating, whispering fashion of speech. He was always well dressed, very neat and plain, but his eyes were weak, just as mine are, and he wore tinted glasses against the glare.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, and what happened when Mr. Windibank, your stepfather, returned to France?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Hosmer Angel came to the house again and proposed that we should marry before father came back. He was in dreadful earnest and made me swear, with my hands on the Testament, that whatever happened I would always be true to him. Mother said he was quite right to make me swear, and that it was a sign of his passion. Mother was all in his favour from the first and was even fonder of him than I was. Then, when they talked of marrying within the week, I began to ask about father; but they both said never to mind about father, but just to tell him afterwards, and mother said she would make it all right with him. I didn’t quite like that, Mr. Holmes. It seemed funny that I should ask his leave, as he was only a few years older than me; but I didn’t want to do anything on the sly, so I wrote to father at Bordeaux, where the company has its French offices, but the letter came back to me on the very morning of the wedding.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It missed him, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir; for he had started to England just before it arrived.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha! that was unfortunate. Your wedding was arranged, then, for the Friday. Was it to be in church?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, but very quietly. It was to be at St. Saviour’s, near King’s Cross, and we were to have breakfast afterwards at the St. Pancras Hotel. Hosmer came for us in a hansom, but as there were two of us he put us both into it and stepped himself into a four-wheeler, which happened to be the only other cab in the street. We got to the church first, and when the four-wheeler drove up we waited for him to step out, but he never did, and when the cabman got down from the box and looked there was no one there! The cabman said that he could not imagine what had become of him, for he had seen him get in with his own eyes. That was last Friday, Mr. Holmes, and I have never seen or heard anything since then to throw any light upon what became of him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It seems to me that you have been very shamefully treated,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, no, sir! He was too good and kind to leave me so. Why, all the morning he was saying to me that, whatever happened, I was to be true; and that even if something quite unforeseen occurred to separate us, I was always to remember that I was pledged to him, and that he would claim his pledge sooner or later. It seemed strange talk for a wedding-morning, but what has happened since gives a meaning to it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Most certainly it does. Your own opinion is, then, that some unforeseen catastrophe has occurred to him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. I believe that he foresaw some danger, or else he would not have talked so. And then I think that what he foresaw happened.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you have no notion as to what it could have been?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One more question. How did your mother take the matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She was angry, and said that I was never to speak of the matter again.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And your father? Did you tell him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; and he seemed to think, with me, that something had happened, and that I should hear of Hosmer again. As he said, what interest could anyone have in bringing me to the doors of the church, and then leaving me? Now, if he had borrowed my money, or if he had married me and got my money settled on him, there might be some reason, but Hosmer was very independent about money and never would look at a shilling of mine. And yet, what could have happened? And why could he not write? Oh, it drives me half-mad to think of it, and I can’t sleep a wink at night.” She pulled a little handkerchief out of her muff and began to sob heavily into it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall glance into the case for you,” said Holmes, rising, “and I have no doubt that we shall reach some definite result. Let the weight of the matter rest upon me now, and do not let your mind dwell upon it further. Above all, try to let Mr. Hosmer Angel vanish from your memory, as he has done from your life.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you don’t think I’ll see him again?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I fear not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then what has happened to him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will leave that question in my hands. I should like an accurate description of him and any letters of his which you can spare.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I advertised for him in last Saturday’s <i>Chronicle</i>,” said she. “Here is the slip and here are four letters from him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. And your address?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. 31 Lyon Place, Camberwell.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Angel’s address you never had, I understand. Where is your father’s place of business?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He travels for Westhouse &amp; Marbank, the great claret importers of Fenchurch Street.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. You have made your statement very clearly. You will leave the papers here, and remember the advice which I have given you. Let the whole incident be a sealed book, and do not allow it to affect your life.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are very kind, Mr. Holmes, but I cannot do that. I shall be true to Hosmer. He shall find me ready when he comes back.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For all the preposterous hat and the vacuous face, there was something noble in the simple faith of our visitor which compelled our respect. She laid her little bundle of papers upon the table and went her way, with a promise to come again whenever she might be summoned.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes sat silent for a few minutes with his fingertips still pressed together, his legs stretched out in front of him, and his gaze directed upward to the ceiling. Then he took down from the rack the old and oily clay pipe, which was to him as a counsellor, and, having lit it, he leaned back in his chair, with the thick blue cloud-wreaths spinning up from him, and a look of infinite languor in his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite an interesting study, that maiden,” he observed. “I found her more interesting than her little problem, which, by the way, is rather a trite one. You will find parallel cases, if you consult my index, in Andover in ’77, and there was something of the sort at The Hague last year. Old as is the idea, however, there were one or two details which were new to me. But the maiden herself was most instructive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You appeared to read a good deal upon her which was quite invisible to me,” I remarked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not invisible but unnoticed, Watson. You did not know where to look, and so you missed all that was important. I can never bring you to realise the importance of sleeves, the suggestiveness of thumb-nails, or the great issues that may hang from a boot-lace. Now, what did you gather from that woman’s appearance? Describe it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, she had a slate-coloured, broad-brimmed straw hat, with a feather of a brickish red. Her jacket was black, with black beads sewn upon it, and a fringe of little black jet ornaments. Her dress was brown, rather darker than coffee colour, with a little purple plush at the neck and sleeves. Her gloves were greyish and were worn through at the right forefinger. Her boots I didn’t observe. She had small round, hanging gold earrings, and a general air of being fairly well-to-do in a vulgar, comfortable, easy-going way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes clapped his hands softly together and chuckled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“’Pon my word, Watson, you are coming along wonderfully. You have really done very well indeed. It is true that you have missed everything of importance, but you have hit upon the method, and you have a quick eye for colour. Never trust to general impressions, my boy, but concentrate yourself upon details. My first glance is always at a woman’s sleeve. In a man it is perhaps better first to take the knee of the trouser. As you observe, this woman had plush upon her sleeves, which is a most useful material for showing traces. The double line a little above the wrist, where the typewritist presses against the table, was beautifully defined. The sewing-machine, of the hand type, leaves a similar mark, but only on the left arm, and on the side of it farthest from the thumb, instead of being right across the broadest part, as this was. I then glanced at her face, and, observing the dint of a pince-nez at either side of her nose, I ventured a remark upon short sight and typewriting, which seemed to surprise her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It surprised me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But, surely, it was obvious. I was then much surprised and interested on glancing down to observe that, though the boots which she was wearing were not unlike each other, they were really odd ones; the one having a slightly decorated toe-cap, and the other a plain one. One was buttoned only in the two lower buttons out of five, and the other at the first, third, and fifth. Now, when you see that a young lady, otherwise neatly dressed, has come away from home with odd boots, half-buttoned, it is no great deduction to say that she came away in a hurry.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what else?” I asked, keenly interested, as I always was, by my friend’s incisive reasoning.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I noted, in passing, that she had written a note before leaving home but after being fully dressed. You observed that her right glove was torn at the forefinger, but you did not apparently see that both glove and finger were stained with violet ink. She had written in a hurry and dipped her pen too deep. It must have been this morning, or the mark would not remain clear upon the finger. All this is amusing, though rather elementary, but I must go back to business, Watson. Would you mind reading me the advertised description of Mr. Hosmer Angel?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I held the little printed slip to the light. “Missing,” it said, “on the morning of the fourteenth, a gentleman named Hosmer Angel. About five ft. seven in. in height; strongly built, sallow complexion, black hair, a little bald in the centre, bushy, black side-whiskers and moustache; tinted glasses, slight infirmity of speech. Was dressed, when last seen, in black frock-coat faced with silk, black waistcoat, gold Albert chain, and grey Harris tweed trousers, with brown gaiters over elastic-sided boots. Known to have been employed in an office in Leadenhall Street. Anybody bringing,” &amp;c, &amp;c.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That will do,” said Holmes. “As to the letters,” he continued, glancing over them, “they are very commonplace. Absolutely no clue in them to Mr. Angel, save that he quotes Balzac once. There is one remarkable point, however, which will no doubt strike you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They are typewritten,” I remarked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not only that, but the signature is typewritten. Look at the neat little ‘Hosmer Angel’ at the bottom. There is a date, you see, but no superscription except Leadenhall Street, which is rather vague. The point about the signature is very suggestive—in fact, we may call it conclusive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of what?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear fellow, is it possible you do not see how strongly it bears upon the case?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot say that I do unless it were that he wished to be able to deny his signature if an action for breach of promise were instituted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, that was not the point. However, I shall write two letters, which should settle the matter. One is to a firm in the City, the other is to the young lady’s stepfather, Mr. Windibank, asking him whether he could meet us here at six o’clock to-morrow evening. It is just as well that we should do business with the male relatives. And now, Doctor, we can do nothing until the answers to those letters come, so we may put our little problem upon the shelf for the interim.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had had so many reasons to believe in my friend’s subtle powers of reasoning and extraordinary energy in action that I felt that he must have some solid grounds for the assured and easy demeanour with which he treated the singular mystery which he had been called upon to fathom. Once only had I known him to fail, in the case of the King of Bohemia and of the Irene Adler photograph; but when I looked back to the weird business of the Sign of Four, and the extraordinary circumstances connected with the Study in Scarlet, I felt that it would be a strange tangle indeed which he could not unravel.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I left him then, still puffing at his black clay pipe, with the conviction that when I came again on the next evening I would find that he held in his hands all the clues which would lead up to the identity of the disappearing bridegroom of Miss Mary Sutherland.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A professional case of great gravity was engaging my own attention at the time, and the whole of next day I was busy at the bedside of the sufferer. It was not until close upon six o’clock that I found myself free and was able to spring into a hansom and drive to Baker Street, half afraid that I might be too late to assist at the <i>dénouement</i> of the little mystery. I found Sherlock Holmes alone, however, half asleep, with his long, thin form curled up in the recesses of his armchair. A formidable array of bottles and test-tubes, with the pungent cleanly smell of hydrochloric acid, told me that he had spent his day in the chemical work which was so dear to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, have you solved it?” I asked as I entered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. It was the bisulphate of baryta.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, the mystery!” I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, that! I thought of the salt that I have been working upon. There was never any mystery in the matter, though, as I said yesterday, some of the details are of interest. The only drawback is that there is no law, I fear, that can touch the scoundrel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who was he, then, and what was his object in deserting Miss Sutherland?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The question was hardly out of my mouth, and Holmes had not yet opened his lips to reply, when we heard a heavy footfall in the passage and a tap at the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is the girl’s stepfather, Mr. James Windibank,” said Holmes. “He has written to me to say that he would be here at six. Come in!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man who entered was a sturdy, middle-sized fellow, some thirty years of age, clean-shaven, and sallow-skinned, with a bland, insinuating manner, and a pair of wonderfully sharp and penetrating grey eyes. He shot a questioning glance at each of us, placed his shiny top-hat upon the sideboard, and with a slight bow sidled down into the nearest chair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good-evening, Mr. James Windibank,” said Holmes. “I think that this typewritten letter is from you, in which you made an appointment with me for six o’clock?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. I am afraid that I am a little late, but I am not quite my own master, you know. I am sorry that Miss Sutherland has troubled you about this little matter, for I think it is far better not to wash linen of the sort in public. It was quite against my wishes that she came, but she is a very excitable, impulsive girl, as you may have noticed, and she is not easily controlled when she has made up her mind on a point. Of course, I did not mind you so much, as you are not connected with the official police, but it is not pleasant to have a family misfortune like this noised abroad. Besides, it is a useless expense, for how could you possibly find this Hosmer Angel?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary,” said Holmes quietly; “I have every reason to believe that I will succeed in discovering Mr. Hosmer Angel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Windibank gave a violent start and dropped his gloves. “I am delighted to hear it,” he said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is a curious thing,” remarked Holmes, “that a typewriter has really quite as much individuality as a man’s handwriting. Unless they are quite new, no two of them write exactly alike. Some letters get more worn than others, and some wear only on one side. Now, you remark in this note of yours, Mr. Windibank, that in every case there is some little slurring over of the ‘e,’ and a slight defect in the tail of the ‘r.’ There are fourteen other characteristics, but those are the more obvious.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We do all our correspondence with this machine at the office, and no doubt it is a little worn,” our visitor answered, glancing keenly at Holmes with his bright little eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And now I will show you what is really a very interesting study, Mr. Windibank,” Holmes continued. “I think of writing another little monograph some of these days on the typewriter and its relation to crime. It is a subject to which I have devoted some little attention. I have here four letters which purport to come from the missing man. They are all typewritten. In each case, not only are the ‘e’s’ slurred and the ‘r’s’ tailless, but you will observe, if you care to use my magnifying lens, that the fourteen other characteristics to which I have alluded are there as well.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Windibank sprang out of his chair and picked up his hat. “I cannot waste time over this sort of fantastic talk, Mr. Holmes,” he said. “If you can catch the man, catch him, and let me know when you have done it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly,” said Holmes, stepping over and turning the key in the door. “I let you know, then, that I have caught him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What! where?” shouted Mr. Windibank, turning white to his lips and glancing about him like a rat in a trap.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, it won’t do—really it won’t,” said Holmes suavely. “There is no possible getting out of it, Mr. Windibank. It is quite too transparent, and it was a very bad compliment when you said that it was impossible for me to solve so simple a question. That’s right! Sit down and let us talk it over.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our visitor collapsed into a chair, with a ghastly face and a glitter of moisture on his brow. “It—it’s not actionable,” he stammered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am very much afraid that it is not. But between ourselves, Windibank, it was as cruel and selfish and heartless a trick in a petty way as ever came before me. Now, let me just run over the course of events, and you will contradict me if I go wrong.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man sat huddled up in his chair, with his head sunk upon his breast, like one who is utterly crushed. Holmes stuck his feet up on the corner of the mantelpiece and, leaning back with his hands in his pockets, began talking, rather to himself, as it seemed, than to us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The man married a woman very much older than himself for her money,” said he, “and he enjoyed the use of the money of the daughter as long as she lived with them. It was a considerable sum, for people in their position, and the loss of it would have made a serious difference. It was worth an effort to preserve it. The daughter was of a good, amiable disposition, but affectionate and warm-hearted in her ways, so that it was evident that with her fair personal advantages, and her little income, she would not be allowed to remain single long. Now her marriage would mean, of course, the loss of a hundred a year, so what does her stepfather do to prevent it? He takes the obvious course of keeping her at home and forbidding her to seek the company of people of her own age. But soon he found that that would not answer forever. She became restive, insisted upon her rights, and finally announced her positive intention of going to a certain ball. What does her clever stepfather do then? He conceives an idea more creditable to his head than to his heart. With the connivance and assistance of his wife he disguised himself, covered those keen eyes with tinted glasses, masked the face with a moustache and a pair of bushy whiskers, sunk that clear voice into an insinuating whisper, and doubly secure on account of the girl’s short sight, he appears as Mr. Hosmer Angel, and keeps off other lovers by making love himself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was only a joke at first,” groaned our visitor. “We never thought that she would have been so carried away.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very likely not. However that may be, the young lady was very decidedly carried away, and, having quite made up her mind that her stepfather was in France, the suspicion of treachery never for an instant entered her mind. She was flattered by the gentleman’s attentions, and the effect was increased by the loudly expressed admiration of her mother. Then Mr. Angel began to call, for it was obvious that the matter should be pushed as far as it would go if a real effect were to be produced. There were meetings, and an engagement, which would finally secure the girl’s affections from turning towards anyone else. But the deception could not be kept up forever. These pretended journeys to France were rather cumbrous. The thing to do was clearly to bring the business to an end in such a dramatic manner that it would leave a permanent impression upon the young lady’s mind and prevent her from looking upon any other suitor for some time to come. Hence those vows of fidelity exacted upon a Testament, and hence also the allusions to a possibility of something happening on the very morning of the wedding. James Windibank wished Miss Sutherland to be so bound to Hosmer Angel, and so uncertain as to his fate, that for ten years to come, at any rate, she would not listen to another man. As far as the church door he brought her, and then, as he could go no farther, he conveniently vanished away by the old trick of stepping in at one door of a four-wheeler and out at the other. I think that was the chain of events, Mr. Windibank!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our visitor had recovered something of his assurance while Holmes had been talking, and he rose from his chair now with a cold sneer upon his pale face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It may be so, or it may not, Mr. Holmes,” said he, “but if you are so very sharp you ought to be sharp enough to know that it is you who are breaking the law now, and not me. I have done nothing actionable from the first, but as long as you keep that door locked you lay yourself open to an action for assault and illegal constraint.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The law cannot, as you say, touch you,” said Holmes, unlocking and throwing open the door, “yet there never was a man who deserved punishment more. If the young lady has a brother or a friend, he ought to lay a whip across your shoulders. By Jove!” he continued, flushing up at the sight of the bitter sneer upon the man’s face, “it is not part of my duties to my client, but here’s a hunting crop handy, and I think I shall just treat myself to—” He took two swift steps to the whip, but before he could grasp it there was a wild clatter of steps upon the stairs, the heavy hall door banged, and from the window we could see Mr. James Windibank running at the top of his speed down the road.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There’s a cold-blooded scoundrel!” said Holmes, laughing, as he threw himself down into his chair once more. “That fellow will rise from crime to crime until he does something very bad, and ends on a gallows. The case has, in some respects, been not entirely devoid of interest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot now entirely see all the steps of your reasoning,” I remarked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, of course it was obvious from the first that this Mr. Hosmer Angel must have some strong object for his curious conduct, and it was equally clear that the only man who really profited by the incident, as far as we could see, was the stepfather. Then the fact that the two men were never together, but that the one always appeared when the other was away, was suggestive. So were the tinted spectacles and the curious voice, which both hinted at a disguise, as did the bushy whiskers. My suspicions were all confirmed by his peculiar action in typewriting his signature, which, of course, inferred that his handwriting was so familiar to her that she would recognise even the smallest sample of it. You see all these isolated facts, together with many minor ones, all pointed in the same direction.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how did you verify them?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Having once spotted my man, it was easy to get corroboration. I knew the firm for which this man worked. Having taken the printed description. I eliminated everything from it which could be the result of a disguise—the whiskers, the glasses, the voice, and I sent it to the firm, with a request that they would inform me whether it answered to the description of any of their travellers. I had already noticed the peculiarities of the typewriter, and I wrote to the man himself at his business address asking him if he would come here. As I expected, his reply was typewritten and revealed the same trivial but characteristic defects. The same post brought me a letter from Westhouse &amp; Marbank, of Fenchurch Street, to say that the description tallied in every respect with that of their employé, James Windibank. <i>Voilà tout</i>!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And Miss Sutherland?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If I tell her she will not believe me. You may remember the old Persian saying, ‘There is danger for him who taketh the tiger cub, and danger also for whoso snatches a delusion from a woman.’ There is as much sense in Hafiz as in Horace, and as much knowledge of the world.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a> IV.<br>\nTHE BOSCOMBE VALLEY MYSTERY</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">W</span>e were seated at breakfast one morning, my wife and I, when the maid brought in a telegram. It was from Sherlock Holmes and ran in this way:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you a couple of days to spare? Have just been wired for from the west of England in connection with Boscombe Valley tragedy. Shall be glad if you will come with me. Air and scenery perfect. Leave Paddington by the 11:15.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you say, dear?” said my wife, looking across at me. “Will you go?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I really don’t know what to say. I have a fairly long list at present.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, Anstruther would do your work for you. You have been looking a little pale lately. I think that the change would do you good, and you are always so interested in Mr. Sherlock Holmes’ cases.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should be ungrateful if I were not, seeing what I gained through one of them,” I answered. “But if I am to go, I must pack at once, for I have only half an hour.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My experience of camp life in Afghanistan had at least had the effect of making me a prompt and ready traveller. My wants were few and simple, so that in less than the time stated I was in a cab with my valise, rattling away to Paddington Station. Sherlock Holmes was pacing up and down the platform, his tall, gaunt figure made even gaunter and taller by his long grey travelling-cloak and close-fitting cloth cap.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is really very good of you to come, Watson,” said he. “It makes a considerable difference to me, having someone with me on whom I can thoroughly rely. Local aid is always either worthless or else biassed. If you will keep the two corner seats I shall get the tickets.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had the carriage to ourselves save for an immense litter of papers which Holmes had brought with him. Among these he rummaged and read, with intervals of note-taking and of meditation, until we were past Reading. Then he suddenly rolled them all into a gigantic ball and tossed them up onto the rack.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you heard anything of the case?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not a word. I have not seen a paper for some days.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The London press has not had very full accounts. I have just been looking through all the recent papers in order to master the particulars. It seems, from what I gather, to be one of those simple cases which are so extremely difficult.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That sounds a little paradoxical.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it is profoundly true. Singularity is almost invariably a clue. The more featureless and commonplace a crime is, the more difficult it is to bring it home. In this case, however, they have established a very serious case against the son of the murdered man.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is a murder, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it is conjectured to be so. I shall take nothing for granted until I have the opportunity of looking personally into it. I will explain the state of things to you, as far as I have been able to understand it, in a very few words.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Boscombe Valley is a country district not very far from Ross, in Herefordshire. The largest landed proprietor in that part is a Mr. John Turner, who made his money in Australia and returned some years ago to the old country. One of the farms which he held, that of Hatherley, was let to Mr. Charles McCarthy, who was also an ex-Australian. The men had known each other in the colonies, so that it was not unnatural that when they came to settle down they should do so as near each other as possible. Turner was apparently the richer man, so McCarthy became his tenant but still remained, it seems, upon terms of perfect equality, as they were frequently together. McCarthy had one son, a lad of eighteen, and Turner had an only daughter of the same age, but neither of them had wives living. They appear to have avoided the society of the neighbouring English families and to have led retired lives, though both the McCarthys were fond of sport and were frequently seen at the race-meetings of the neighbourhood. McCarthy kept two servants—a man and a girl. Turner had a considerable household, some half-dozen at the least. That is as much as I have been able to gather about the families. Now for the facts.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On June 3rd, that is, on Monday last, McCarthy left his house at Hatherley about three in the afternoon and walked down to the Boscombe Pool, which is a small lake formed by the spreading out of the stream which runs down the Boscombe Valley. He had been out with his serving-man in the morning at Ross, and he had told the man that he must hurry, as he had an appointment of importance to keep at three. From that appointment he never came back alive.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“From Hatherley Farmhouse to the Boscombe Pool is a quarter of a mile, and two people saw him as he passed over this ground. One was an old woman, whose name is not mentioned, and the other was William Crowder, a game-keeper in the employ of Mr. Turner. Both these witnesses depose that Mr. McCarthy was walking alone. The game-keeper adds that within a few minutes of his seeing Mr. McCarthy pass he had seen his son, Mr. James McCarthy, going the same way with a gun under his arm. To the best of his belief, the father was actually in sight at the time, and the son was following him. He thought no more of the matter until he heard in the evening of the tragedy that had occurred.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The two McCarthys were seen after the time when William Crowder, the game-keeper, lost sight of them. The Boscombe Pool is thickly wooded round, with just a fringe of grass and of reeds round the edge. A girl of fourteen, Patience Moran, who is the daughter of the lodge-keeper of the Boscombe Valley estate, was in one of the woods picking flowers. She states that while she was there she saw, at the border of the wood and close by the lake, Mr. McCarthy and his son, and that they appeared to be having a violent quarrel. She heard Mr. McCarthy the elder using very strong language to his son, and she saw the latter raise up his hand as if to strike his father. She was so frightened by their violence that she ran away and told her mother when she reached home that she had left the two McCarthys quarrelling near Boscombe Pool, and that she was afraid that they were going to fight. She had hardly said the words when young Mr. McCarthy came running up to the lodge to say that he had found his father dead in the wood, and to ask for the help of the lodge-keeper. He was much excited, without either his gun or his hat, and his right hand and sleeve were observed to be stained with fresh blood. On following him they found the dead body stretched out upon the grass beside the pool. The head had been beaten in by repeated blows of some heavy and blunt weapon. The injuries were such as might very well have been inflicted by the butt-end of his son’s gun, which was found lying on the grass within a few paces of the body. Under these circumstances the young man was instantly arrested, and a verdict of ‘wilful murder’ having been returned at the inquest on Tuesday, he was on Wednesday brought before the magistrates at Ross, who have referred the case to the next Assizes. Those are the main facts of the case as they came out before the coroner and the police-court.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I could hardly imagine a more damning case,” I remarked. “If ever circumstantial evidence pointed to a criminal it does so here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Circumstantial evidence is a very tricky thing,” answered Holmes thoughtfully. “It may seem to point very straight to one thing, but if you shift your own point of view a little, you may find it pointing in an equally uncompromising manner to something entirely different. It must be confessed, however, that the case looks exceedingly grave against the young man, and it is very possible that he is indeed the culprit. There are several people in the neighbourhood, however, and among them Miss Turner, the daughter of the neighbouring landowner, who believe in his innocence, and who have retained Lestrade, whom you may recollect in connection with the Study in Scarlet, to work out the case in his interest. Lestrade, being rather puzzled, has referred the case to me, and hence it is that two middle-aged gentlemen are flying westward at fifty miles an hour instead of quietly digesting their breakfasts at home.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am afraid,” said I, “that the facts are so obvious that you will find little credit to be gained out of this case.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is nothing more deceptive than an obvious fact,” he answered, laughing. “Besides, we may chance to hit upon some other obvious facts which may have been by no means obvious to Mr. Lestrade. You know me too well to think that I am boasting when I say that I shall either confirm or destroy his theory by means which he is quite incapable of employing, or even of understanding. To take the first example to hand, I very clearly perceive that in your bedroom the window is upon the right-hand side, and yet I question whether Mr. Lestrade would have noted even so self-evident a thing as that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How on earth—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear fellow, I know you well. I know the military neatness which characterises you. You shave every morning, and in this season you shave by the sunlight; but since your shaving is less and less complete as we get farther back on the left side, until it becomes positively slovenly as we get round the angle of the jaw, it is surely very clear that that side is less illuminated than the other. I could not imagine a man of your habits looking at himself in an equal light and being satisfied with such a result. I only quote this as a trivial example of observation and inference. Therein lies my <i>métier</i>, and it is just possible that it may be of some service in the investigation which lies before us. There are one or two minor points which were brought out in the inquest, and which are worth considering.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What are they?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It appears that his arrest did not take place at once, but after the return to Hatherley Farm. On the inspector of constabulary informing him that he was a prisoner, he remarked that he was not surprised to hear it, and that it was no more than his deserts. This observation of his had the natural effect of removing any traces of doubt which might have remained in the minds of the coroner’s jury.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was a confession,” I ejaculated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, for it was followed by a protestation of innocence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Coming on the top of such a damning series of events, it was at least a most suspicious remark.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary,” said Holmes, “it is the brightest rift which I can at present see in the clouds. However innocent he might be, he could not be such an absolute imbecile as not to see that the circumstances were very black against him. Had he appeared surprised at his own arrest, or feigned indignation at it, I should have looked upon it as highly suspicious, because such surprise or anger would not be natural under the circumstances, and yet might appear to be the best policy to a scheming man. His frank acceptance of the situation marks him as either an innocent man, or else as a man of considerable self-restraint and firmness. As to his remark about his deserts, it was also not unnatural if you consider that he stood beside the dead body of his father, and that there is no doubt that he had that very day so far forgotten his filial duty as to bandy words with him, and even, according to the little girl whose evidence is so important, to raise his hand as if to strike him. The self-reproach and contrition which are displayed in his remark appear to me to be the signs of a healthy mind rather than of a guilty one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shook my head. “Many men have been hanged on far slighter evidence,” I remarked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So they have. And many men have been wrongfully hanged.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is the young man’s own account of the matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is, I am afraid, not very encouraging to his supporters, though there are one or two points in it which are suggestive. You will find it here, and may read it for yourself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He picked out from his bundle a copy of the local Herefordshire paper, and having turned down the sheet he pointed out the paragraph in which the unfortunate young man had given his own statement of what had occurred. I settled myself down in the corner of the carriage and read it very carefully. It ran in this way:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. James McCarthy, the only son of the deceased, was then called and gave evidence as follows: ‘I had been away from home for three days at Bristol, and had only just returned upon the morning of last Monday, the 3rd. My father was absent from home at the time of my arrival, and I was informed by the maid that he had driven over to Ross with John Cobb, the groom. Shortly after my return I heard the wheels of his trap in the yard, and, looking out of my window, I saw him get out and walk rapidly out of the yard, though I was not aware in which direction he was going. I then took my gun and strolled out in the direction of the Boscombe Pool, with the intention of visiting the rabbit warren which is upon the other side. On my way I saw William Crowder, the game-keeper, as he had stated in his evidence; but he is mistaken in thinking that I was following my father. I had no idea that he was in front of me. When about a hundred yards from the pool I heard a cry of “Cooee!” which was a usual signal between my father and myself. I then hurried forward, and found him standing by the pool. He appeared to be much surprised at seeing me and asked me rather roughly what I was doing there. A conversation ensued which led to high words and almost to blows, for my father was a man of a very violent temper. Seeing that his passion was becoming ungovernable, I left him and returned towards Hatherley Farm. I had not gone more than 150 yards, however, when I heard a hideous outcry behind me, which caused me to run back again. I found my father expiring upon the ground, with his head terribly injured. I dropped my gun and held him in my arms, but he almost instantly expired. I knelt beside him for some minutes, and then made my way to Mr. Turner’s lodge-keeper, his house being the nearest, to ask for assistance. I saw no one near my father when I returned, and I have no idea how he came by his injuries. He was not a popular man, being somewhat cold and forbidding in his manners, but he had, as far as I know, no active enemies. I know nothing further of the matter.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: Did your father make any statement to you before he died?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: He mumbled a few words, but I could only catch some allusion to a rat.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: What did you understand by that?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: It conveyed no meaning to me. I thought that he was delirious.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: What was the point upon which you and your father had this final quarrel?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: I should prefer not to answer.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: I am afraid that I must press it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: It is really impossible for me to tell you. I can assure you that it has nothing to do with the sad tragedy which followed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: That is for the court to decide. I need not point out to you that your refusal to answer will prejudice your case considerably in any future proceedings which may arise.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: I must still refuse.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: I understand that the cry of ‘Cooee’ was a common signal between you and your father?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: It was.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: How was it, then, that he uttered it before he saw you, and before he even knew that you had returned from Bristol?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness (with considerable confusion): I do not know.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A Juryman: Did you see nothing which aroused your suspicions when you returned on hearing the cry and found your father fatally injured?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: Nothing definite.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Coroner: What do you mean?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Witness: I was so disturbed and excited as I rushed out into the open, that I could think of nothing except of my father. Yet I have a vague impression that as I ran forward something lay upon the ground to the left of me. It seemed to me to be something grey in colour, a coat of some sort, or a plaid perhaps. When I rose from my father I looked round for it, but it was gone.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Do you mean that it disappeared before you went for help?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, it was gone.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“ ‘You cannot say what it was?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, I had a feeling something was there.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘How far from the body?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘A dozen yards or so.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And how far from the edge of the wood?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘About the same.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Then if it was removed it was while you were within a dozen yards of it?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, but with my back towards it.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This concluded the examination of the witness.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see,” said I as I glanced down the column, “that the coroner in his concluding remarks was rather severe upon young McCarthy. He calls attention, and with reason, to the discrepancy about his father having signalled to him before seeing him, also to his refusal to give details of his conversation with his father, and his singular account of his father’s dying words. They are all, as he remarks, very much against the son.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes laughed softly to himself and stretched himself out upon the cushioned seat. “Both you and the coroner have been at some pains,” said he, “to single out the very strongest points in the young man’s favour. Don’t you see that you alternately give him credit for having too much imagination and too little? Too little, if he could not invent a cause of quarrel which would give him the sympathy of the jury; too much, if he evolved from his own inner consciousness anything so <i>outré</i> as a dying reference to a rat, and the incident of the vanishing cloth. No, sir, I shall approach this case from the point of view that what this young man says is true, and we shall see whither that hypothesis will lead us. And now here is my pocket Petrarch, and not another word shall I say of this case until we are on the scene of action. We lunch at Swindon, and I see that we shall be there in twenty minutes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was nearly four o’clock when we at last, after passing through the beautiful Stroud Valley, and over the broad gleaming Severn, found ourselves at the pretty little country-town of Ross. A lean, ferret-like man, furtive and sly-looking, was waiting for us upon the platform. In spite of the light brown dustcoat and leather-leggings which he wore in deference to his rustic surroundings, I had no difficulty in recognising Lestrade, of Scotland Yard. With him we drove to the Hereford Arms where a room had already been engaged for us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have ordered a carriage,” said Lestrade as we sat over a cup of tea. “I knew your energetic nature, and that you would not be happy until you had been on the scene of the crime.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was very nice and complimentary of you,” Holmes answered. “It is entirely a question of barometric pressure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade looked startled. “I do not quite follow,” he said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How is the glass? Twenty-nine, I see. No wind, and not a cloud in the sky. I have a caseful of cigarettes here which need smoking, and the sofa is very much superior to the usual country hotel abomination. I do not think that it is probable that I shall use the carriage to-night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade laughed indulgently. “You have, no doubt, already formed your conclusions from the newspapers,” he said. “The case is as plain as a pikestaff, and the more one goes into it the plainer it becomes. Still, of course, one can’t refuse a lady, and such a very positive one, too. She has heard of you, and would have your opinion, though I repeatedly told her that there was nothing which you could do which I had not already done. Why, bless my soul! here is her carriage at the door.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He had hardly spoken before there rushed into the room one of the most lovely young women that I have ever seen in my life. Her violet eyes shining, her lips parted, a pink flush upon her cheeks, all thought of her natural reserve lost in her overpowering excitement and concern.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, Mr. Sherlock Holmes!” she cried, glancing from one to the other of us, and finally, with a woman’s quick intuition, fastening upon my companion, “I am so glad that you have come. I have driven down to tell you so. I know that James didn’t do it. I know it, and I want you to start upon your work knowing it, too. Never let yourself doubt upon that point. We have known each other since we were little children, and I know his faults as no one else does; but he is too tender-hearted to hurt a fly. Such a charge is absurd to anyone who really knows him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I hope we may clear him, Miss Turner,” said Sherlock Holmes. “You may rely upon my doing all that I can.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you have read the evidence. You have formed some conclusion? Do you not see some loophole, some flaw? Do you not yourself think that he is innocent?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that it is very probable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There, now!” she cried, throwing back her head and looking defiantly at Lestrade. “You hear! He gives me hopes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade shrugged his shoulders. “I am afraid that my colleague has been a little quick in forming his conclusions,” he said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But he is right. Oh! I know that he is right. James never did it. And about his quarrel with his father, I am sure that the reason why he would not speak about it to the coroner was because I was concerned in it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In what way?” asked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is no time for me to hide anything. James and his father had many disagreements about me. Mr. McCarthy was very anxious that there should be a marriage between us. James and I have always loved each other as brother and sister; but of course he is young and has seen very little of life yet, and—and—well, he naturally did not wish to do anything like that yet. So there were quarrels, and this, I am sure, was one of them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And your father?” asked Holmes. “Was he in favour of such a union?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, he was averse to it also. No one but Mr. McCarthy was in favour of it.” A quick blush passed over her fresh young face as Holmes shot one of his keen, questioning glances at her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you for this information,” said he. “May I see your father if I call to-morrow?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am afraid the doctor won’t allow it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The doctor?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, have you not heard? Poor father has never been strong for years back, but this has broken him down completely. He has taken to his bed, and Dr. Willows says that he is a wreck and that his nervous system is shattered. Mr. McCarthy was the only man alive who had known dad in the old days in Victoria.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha! In Victoria! That is important.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, at the mines.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so; at the gold-mines, where, as I understand, Mr. Turner made his money.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, certainly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you, Miss Turner. You have been of material assistance to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will tell me if you have any news to-morrow. No doubt you will go to the prison to see James. Oh, if you do, Mr. Holmes, do tell him that I know him to be innocent.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will, Miss Turner.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I must go home now, for dad is very ill, and he misses me so if I leave him. Good-bye, and God help you in your undertaking.” She hurried from the room as impulsively as she had entered, and we heard the wheels of her carriage rattle off down the street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am ashamed of you, Holmes,” said Lestrade with dignity after a few minutes’ silence. “Why should you raise up hopes which you are bound to disappoint? I am not over-tender of heart, but I call it cruel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that I see my way to clearing James McCarthy,” said Holmes. “Have you an order to see him in prison?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but only for you and me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I shall reconsider my resolution about going out. We have still time to take a train to Hereford and see him to-night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ample.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then let us do so. Watson, I fear that you will find it very slow, but I shall only be away a couple of hours.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I walked down to the station with them, and then wandered through the streets of the little town, finally returning to the hotel, where I lay upon the sofa and tried to interest myself in a yellow-backed novel. The puny plot of the story was so thin, however, when compared to the deep mystery through which we were groping, and I found my attention wander so continually from the action to the fact, that I at last flung it across the room and gave myself up entirely to a consideration of the events of the day. Supposing that this unhappy young man’s story were absolutely true, then what hellish thing, what absolutely unforeseen and extraordinary calamity could have occurred between the time when he parted from his father, and the moment when, drawn back by his screams, he rushed into the glade? It was something terrible and deadly. What could it be? Might not the nature of the injuries reveal something to my medical instincts? I rang the bell and called for the weekly county paper, which contained a verbatim account of the inquest. In the surgeon’s deposition it was stated that the posterior third of the left parietal bone and the left half of the occipital bone had been shattered by a heavy blow from a blunt weapon. I marked the spot upon my own head. Clearly such a blow must have been struck from behind. That was to some extent in favour of the accused, as when seen quarrelling he was face to face with his father. Still, it did not go for very much, for the older man might have turned his back before the blow fell. Still, it might be worth while to call Holmes’ attention to it. Then there was the peculiar dying reference to a rat. What could that mean? It could not be delirium. A man dying from a sudden blow does not commonly become delirious. No, it was more likely to be an attempt to explain how he met his fate. But what could it indicate? I cudgelled my brains to find some possible explanation. And then the incident of the grey cloth seen by young McCarthy. If that were true the murderer must have dropped some part of his dress, presumably his overcoat, in his flight, and must have had the hardihood to return and to carry it away at the instant when the son was kneeling with his back turned not a dozen paces off. What a tissue of mysteries and improbabilities the whole thing was! I did not wonder at Lestrade’s opinion, and yet I had so much faith in Sherlock Holmes’ insight that I could not lose hope as long as every fresh fact seemed to strengthen his conviction of young McCarthy’s innocence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was late before Sherlock Holmes returned. He came back alone, for Lestrade was staying in lodgings in the town.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The glass still keeps very high,” he remarked as he sat down. “It is of importance that it should not rain before we are able to go over the ground. On the other hand, a man should be at his very best and keenest for such nice work as that, and I did not wish to do it when fagged by a long journey. I have seen young McCarthy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what did you learn from him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Could he throw no light?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None at all. I was inclined to think at one time that he knew who had done it and was screening him or her, but I am convinced now that he is as puzzled as everyone else. He is not a very quick-witted youth, though comely to look at and, I should think, sound at heart.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot admire his taste,” I remarked, “if it is indeed a fact that he was averse to a marriage with so charming a young lady as this Miss Turner.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, thereby hangs a rather painful tale. This fellow is madly, insanely, in love with her, but some two years ago, when he was only a lad, and before he really knew her, for she had been away five years at a boarding-school, what does the idiot do but get into the clutches of a barmaid in Bristol and marry her at a registry office? No one knows a word of the matter, but you can imagine how maddening it must be to him to be upbraided for not doing what he would give his very eyes to do, but what he knows to be absolutely impossible. It was sheer frenzy of this sort which made him throw his hands up into the air when his father, at their last interview, was goading him on to propose to Miss Turner. On the other hand, he had no means of supporting himself, and his father, who was by all accounts a very hard man, would have thrown him over utterly had he known the truth. It was with his barmaid wife that he had spent the last three days in Bristol, and his father did not know where he was. Mark that point. It is of importance. Good has come out of evil, however, for the barmaid, finding from the papers that he is in serious trouble and likely to be hanged, has thrown him over utterly and has written to him to say that she has a husband already in the Bermuda Dockyard, so that there is really no tie between them. I think that that bit of news has consoled young McCarthy for all that he has suffered.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But if he is innocent, who has done it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! who? I would call your attention very particularly to two points. One is that the murdered man had an appointment with someone at the pool, and that the someone could not have been his son, for his son was away, and he did not know when he would return. The second is that the murdered man was heard to cry ‘Cooee!’ before he knew that his son had returned. Those are the crucial points upon which the case depends. And now let us talk about George Meredith, if you please, and we shall leave all minor matters until to-morrow.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was no rain, as Holmes had foretold, and the morning broke bright and cloudless. At nine o’clock Lestrade called for us with the carriage, and we set off for Hatherley Farm and the Boscombe Pool.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is serious news this morning,” Lestrade observed. “It is said that Mr. Turner, of the Hall, is so ill that his life is despaired of.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“An elderly man, I presume?” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“About sixty; but his constitution has been shattered by his life abroad, and he has been in failing health for some time. This business has had a very bad effect upon him. He was an old friend of McCarthy’s, and, I may add, a great benefactor to him, for I have learned that he gave him Hatherley Farm rent free.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed! That is interesting,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes! In a hundred other ways he has helped him. Everybody about here speaks of his kindness to him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really! Does it not strike you as a little singular that this McCarthy, who appears to have had little of his own, and to have been under such obligations to Turner, should still talk of marrying his son to Turner’s daughter, who is, presumably, heiress to the estate, and that in such a very cocksure manner, as if it were merely a case of a proposal and all else would follow? It is the more strange, since we know that Turner himself was averse to the idea. The daughter told us as much. Do you not deduce something from that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have got to the deductions and the inferences,” said Lestrade, winking at me. “I find it hard enough to tackle facts, Holmes, without flying away after theories and fancies.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are right,” said Holmes demurely; “you do find it very hard to tackle the facts.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Anyhow, I have grasped one fact which you seem to find it difficult to get hold of,” replied Lestrade with some warmth.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that is—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That McCarthy senior met his death from McCarthy junior and that all theories to the contrary are the merest moonshine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, moonshine is a brighter thing than fog,” said Holmes, laughing. “But I am very much mistaken if this is not Hatherley Farm upon the left.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, that is it.” It was a widespread, comfortable-looking building, two-storied, slate-roofed, with great yellow blotches of lichen upon the grey walls. The drawn blinds and the smokeless chimneys, however, gave it a stricken look, as though the weight of this horror still lay heavy upon it. We called at the door, when the maid, at Holmes’ request, showed us the boots which her master wore at the time of his death, and also a pair of the son’s, though not the pair which he had then had. Having measured these very carefully from seven or eight different points, Holmes desired to be led to the court-yard, from which we all followed the winding track which led to Boscombe Pool.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes was transformed when he was hot upon such a scent as this. Men who had only known the quiet thinker and logician of Baker Street would have failed to recognise him. His face flushed and darkened. His brows were drawn into two hard black lines, while his eyes shone out from beneath them with a steely glitter. His face was bent downward, his shoulders bowed, his lips compressed, and the veins stood out like whipcord in his long, sinewy neck. His nostrils seemed to dilate with a purely animal lust for the chase, and his mind was so absolutely concentrated upon the matter before him that a question or remark fell unheeded upon his ears, or, at the most, only provoked a quick, impatient snarl in reply. Swiftly and silently he made his way along the track which ran through the meadows, and so by way of the woods to the Boscombe Pool. It was damp, marshy ground, as is all that district, and there were marks of many feet, both upon the path and amid the short grass which bounded it on either side. Sometimes Holmes would hurry on, sometimes stop dead, and once he made quite a little detour into the meadow. Lestrade and I walked behind him, the detective indifferent and contemptuous, while I watched my friend with the interest which sprang from the conviction that every one of his actions was directed towards a definite end.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Boscombe Pool, which is a little reed-girt sheet of water some fifty yards across, is situated at the boundary between the Hatherley Farm and the private park of the wealthy Mr. Turner. Above the woods which lined it upon the farther side we could see the red, jutting pinnacles which marked the site of the rich landowner’s dwelling. On the Hatherley side of the pool the woods grew very thick, and there was a narrow belt of sodden grass twenty paces across between the edge of the trees and the reeds which lined the lake. Lestrade showed us the exact spot at which the body had been found, and, indeed, so moist was the ground, that I could plainly see the traces which had been left by the fall of the stricken man. To Holmes, as I could see by his eager face and peering eyes, very many other things were to be read upon the trampled grass. He ran round, like a dog who is picking up a scent, and then turned upon my companion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What did you go into the pool for?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I fished about with a rake. I thought there might be some weapon or other trace. But how on earth—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, tut, tut! I have no time! That left foot of yours with its inward twist is all over the place. A mole could trace it, and there it vanishes among the reeds. Oh, how simple it would all have been had I been here before they came like a herd of buffalo and wallowed all over it. Here is where the party with the lodge-keeper came, and they have covered all tracks for six or eight feet round the body. But here are three separate tracks of the same feet.” He drew out a lens and lay down upon his waterproof to have a better view, talking all the time rather to himself than to us. “These are young McCarthy’s feet. Twice he was walking, and once he ran swiftly, so that the soles are deeply marked and the heels hardly visible. That bears out his story. He ran when he saw his father on the ground. Then here are the father’s feet as he paced up and down. What is this, then? It is the butt-end of the gun as the son stood listening. And this? Ha, ha! What have we here? Tiptoes! tiptoes! Square, too, quite unusual boots! They come, they go, they come again—of course that was for the cloak. Now where did they come from?” He ran up and down, sometimes losing, sometimes finding the track until we were well within the edge of the wood and under the shadow of a great beech, the largest tree in the neighbourhood. Holmes traced his way to the farther side of this and lay down once more upon his face with a little cry of satisfaction. For a long time he remained there, turning over the leaves and dried sticks, gathering up what seemed to me to be dust into an envelope and examining with his lens not only the ground but even the bark of the tree as far as he could reach. A jagged stone was lying among the moss, and this also he carefully examined and retained. Then he followed a pathway through the wood until he came to the highroad, where all traces were lost.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It has been a case of considerable interest,” he remarked, returning to his natural manner. “I fancy that this grey house on the right must be the lodge. I think that I will go in and have a word with Moran, and perhaps write a little note. Having done that, we may drive back to our luncheon. You may walk to the cab, and I shall be with you presently.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was about ten minutes before we regained our cab and drove back into Ross, Holmes still carrying with him the stone which he had picked up in the wood.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This may interest you, Lestrade,” he remarked, holding it out. “The murder was done with it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see no marks.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There are none.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How do you know, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The grass was growing under it. It had only lain there a few days. There was no sign of a place whence it had been taken. It corresponds with the injuries. There is no sign of any other weapon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the murderer?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is a tall man, left-handed, limps with the right leg, wears thick-soled shooting-boots and a grey cloak, smokes Indian cigars, uses a cigar-holder, and carries a blunt pen-knife in his pocket. There are several other indications, but these may be enough to aid us in our search.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade laughed. “I am afraid that I am still a sceptic,” he said. “Theories are all very well, but we have to deal with a hard-headed British jury.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Nous verrons</i>,” answered Holmes calmly. “You work your own method, and I shall work mine. I shall be busy this afternoon, and shall probably return to London by the evening train.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And leave your case unfinished?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, finished.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But the mystery?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is solved.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who was the criminal, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The gentleman I describe.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But who is he?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Surely it would not be difficult to find out. This is not such a populous neighbourhood.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade shrugged his shoulders. “I am a practical man,” he said, “and I really cannot undertake to go about the country looking for a left-handed gentleman with a game leg. I should become the laughing-stock of Scotland Yard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“All right,” said Holmes quietly. “I have given you the chance. Here are your lodgings. Good-bye. I shall drop you a line before I leave.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Having left Lestrade at his rooms, we drove to our hotel, where we found lunch upon the table. Holmes was silent and buried in thought with a pained expression upon his face, as one who finds himself in a perplexing position.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look here, Watson,” he said when the cloth was cleared “just sit down in this chair and let me preach to you for a little. I don’t know quite what to do, and I should value your advice. Light a cigar and let me expound.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray do so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, now, in considering this case there are two points about young McCarthy’s narrative which struck us both instantly, although they impressed me in his favour and you against him. One was the fact that his father should, according to his account, cry ‘Cooee!’ before seeing him. The other was his singular dying reference to a rat. He mumbled several words, you understand, but that was all that caught the son’s ear. Now from this double point our research must commence, and we will begin it by presuming that what the lad says is absolutely true.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What of this ‘Cooee!’ then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, obviously it could not have been meant for the son. The son, as far as he knew, was in Bristol. It was mere chance that he was within earshot. The ‘Cooee!’ was meant to attract the attention of whoever it was that he had the appointment with. But ‘Cooee’ is a distinctly Australian cry, and one which is used between Australians. There is a strong presumption that the person whom McCarthy expected to meet him at Boscombe Pool was someone who had been in Australia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What of the rat, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes took a folded paper from his pocket and flattened it out on the table. “This is a map of the Colony of Victoria,” he said. “I wired to Bristol for it last night.” He put his hand over part of the map. “What do you read?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“ARAT,” I read.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And now?” He raised his hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“BALLARAT.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. That was the word the man uttered, and of which his son only caught the last two syllables. He was trying to utter the name of his murderer. So and so, of Ballarat.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is wonderful!” I exclaimed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is obvious. And now, you see, I had narrowed the field down considerably. The possession of a grey garment was a third point which, granting the son’s statement to be correct, was a certainty. We have come now out of mere vagueness to the definite conception of an Australian from Ballarat with a grey cloak.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And one who was at home in the district, for the pool can only be approached by the farm or by the estate, where strangers could hardly wander.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then comes our expedition of to-day. By an examination of the ground I gained the trifling details which I gave to that imbecile Lestrade, as to the personality of the criminal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But how did you gain them?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You know my method. It is founded upon the observation of trifles.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“His height I know that you might roughly judge from the length of his stride. His boots, too, might be told from their traces.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, they were peculiar boots.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But his lameness?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The impression of his right foot was always less distinct than his left. He put less weight upon it. Why? Because he limped—he was lame.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But his left-handedness.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You were yourself struck by the nature of the injury as recorded by the surgeon at the inquest. The blow was struck from immediately behind, and yet was upon the left side. Now, how can that be unless it were by a left-handed man? He had stood behind that tree during the interview between the father and son. He had even smoked there. I found the ash of a cigar, which my special knowledge of tobacco ashes enables me to pronounce as an Indian cigar. I have, as you know, devoted some attention to this, and written a little monograph on the ashes of 140 different varieties of pipe, cigar, and cigarette tobacco. Having found the ash, I then looked round and discovered the stump among the moss where he had tossed it. It was an Indian cigar, of the variety which are rolled in Rotterdam.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the cigar-holder?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I could see that the end had not been in his mouth. Therefore he used a holder. The tip had been cut off, not bitten off, but the cut was not a clean one, so I deduced a blunt pen-knife.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Holmes,” I said, “you have drawn a net round this man from which he cannot escape, and you have saved an innocent human life as truly as if you had cut the cord which was hanging him. I see the direction in which all this points. The culprit is—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. John Turner,” cried the hotel waiter, opening the door of our sitting-room, and ushering in a visitor.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man who entered was a strange and impressive figure. His slow, limping step and bowed shoulders gave the appearance of decrepitude, and yet his hard, deep-lined, craggy features, and his enormous limbs showed that he was possessed of unusual strength of body and of character. His tangled beard, grizzled hair, and outstanding, drooping eyebrows combined to give an air of dignity and power to his appearance, but his face was of an ashen white, while his lips and the corners of his nostrils were tinged with a shade of blue. It was clear to me at a glance that he was in the grip of some deadly and chronic disease.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray sit down on the sofa,” said Holmes gently. “You had my note?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, the lodge-keeper brought it up. You said that you wished to see me here to avoid scandal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I thought people would talk if I went to the Hall.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And why did you wish to see me?” He looked across at my companion with despair in his weary eyes, as though his question was already answered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” said Holmes, answering the look rather than the words. “It is so. I know all about McCarthy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The old man sank his face in his hands. “God help me!” he cried. “But I would not have let the young man come to harm. I give you my word that I would have spoken out if it went against him at the Assizes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am glad to hear you say so,” said Holmes gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I would have spoken now had it not been for my dear girl. It would break her heart—it will break her heart when she hears that I am arrested.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It may not come to that,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am no official agent. I understand that it was your daughter who required my presence here, and I am acting in her interests. Young McCarthy must be got off, however.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am a dying man,” said old Turner. “I have had diabetes for years. My doctor says it is a question whether I shall live a month. Yet I would rather die under my own roof than in a gaol.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes rose and sat down at the table with his pen in his hand and a bundle of paper before him. “Just tell us the truth,” he said. “I shall jot down the facts. You will sign it, and Watson here can witness it. Then I could produce your confession at the last extremity to save young McCarthy. I promise you that I shall not use it unless it is absolutely needed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s as well,” said the old man; “it’s a question whether I shall live to the Assizes, so it matters little to me, but I should wish to spare Alice the shock. And now I will make the thing clear to you; it has been a long time in the acting, but will not take me long to tell.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You didn’t know this dead man, McCarthy. He was a devil incarnate. I tell you that. God keep you out of the clutches of such a man as he. His grip has been upon me these twenty years, and he has blasted my life. I’ll tell you first how I came to be in his power.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was in the early ’60’s at the diggings. I was a young chap then, hot-blooded and reckless, ready to turn my hand at anything; I got among bad companions, took to drink, had no luck with my claim, took to the bush, and in a word became what you would call over here a highway robber. There were six of us, and we had a wild, free life of it, sticking up a station from time to time, or stopping the wagons on the road to the diggings. Black Jack of Ballarat was the name I went under, and our party is still remembered in the colony as the Ballarat Gang.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One day a gold convoy came down from Ballarat to Melbourne, and we lay in wait for it and attacked it. There were six troopers and six of us, so it was a close thing, but we emptied four of their saddles at the first volley. Three of our boys were killed, however, before we got the swag. I put my pistol to the head of the wagon-driver, who was this very man McCarthy. I wish to the Lord that I had shot him then, but I spared him, though I saw his wicked little eyes fixed on my face, as though to remember every feature. We got away with the gold, became wealthy men, and made our way over to England without being suspected. There I parted from my old pals and determined to settle down to a quiet and respectable life. I bought this estate, which chanced to be in the market, and I set myself to do a little good with my money, to make up for the way in which I had earned it. I married, too, and though my wife died young she left me my dear little Alice. Even when she was just a baby her wee hand seemed to lead me down the right path as nothing else had ever done. In a word, I turned over a new leaf and did my best to make up for the past. All was going well when McCarthy laid his grip upon me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I had gone up to town about an investment, and I met him in Regent Street with hardly a coat to his back or a boot to his foot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Here we are, Jack,’ says he, touching me on the arm; ‘we’ll be as good as a family to you. There’s two of us, me and my son, and you can have the keeping of us. If you don’t—it’s a fine, law-abiding country is England, and there’s always a policeman within hail.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, down they came to the west country, there was no shaking them off, and there they have lived rent free on my best land ever since. There was no rest for me, no peace, no forgetfulness; turn where I would, there was his cunning, grinning face at my elbow. It grew worse as Alice grew up, for he soon saw I was more afraid of her knowing my past than of the police. Whatever he wanted he must have, and whatever it was I gave him without question, land, money, houses, until at last he asked a thing which I could not give. He asked for Alice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“His son, you see, had grown up, and so had my girl, and as I was known to be in weak health, it seemed a fine stroke to him that his lad should step into the whole property. But there I was firm. I would not have his cursed stock mixed with mine; not that I had any dislike to the lad, but his blood was in him, and that was enough. I stood firm. McCarthy threatened. I braved him to do his worst. We were to meet at the pool midway between our houses to talk it over.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I went down there I found him talking with his son, so I smoked a cigar and waited behind a tree until he should be alone. But as I listened to his talk all that was black and bitter in me seemed to come uppermost. He was urging his son to marry my daughter with as little regard for what she might think as if she were a slut from off the streets. It drove me mad to think that I and all that I held most dear should be in the power of such a man as this. Could I not snap the bond? I was already a dying and a desperate man. Though clear of mind and fairly strong of limb, I knew that my own fate was sealed. But my memory and my girl! Both could be saved if I could but silence that foul tongue. I did it, Mr. Holmes. I would do it again. Deeply as I have sinned, I have led a life of martyrdom to atone for it. But that my girl should be entangled in the same meshes which held me was more than I could suffer. I struck him down with no more compunction than if he had been some foul and venomous beast. His cry brought back his son; but I had gained the cover of the wood, though I was forced to go back to fetch the cloak which I had dropped in my flight. That is the true story, gentlemen, of all that occurred.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it is not for me to judge you,” said Holmes as the old man signed the statement which had been drawn out. “I pray that we may never be exposed to such a temptation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I pray not, sir. And what do you intend to do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In view of your health, nothing. You are yourself aware that you will soon have to answer for your deed at a higher court than the Assizes. I will keep your confession, and if McCarthy is condemned I shall be forced to use it. If not, it shall never be seen by mortal eye; and your secret, whether you be alive or dead, shall be safe with us.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Farewell, then,” said the old man solemnly. “Your own deathbeds, when they come, will be the easier for the thought of the peace which you have given to mine.” Tottering and shaking in all his giant frame, he stumbled slowly from the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“God help us!” said Holmes after a long silence. “Why does fate play such tricks with poor, helpless worms? I never hear of such a case as this that I do not think of Baxter’s words, and say, ‘There, but for the grace of God, goes Sherlock Holmes.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>James McCarthy was acquitted at the Assizes on the strength of a number of objections which had been drawn out by Holmes and submitted to the defending counsel. Old Turner lived for seven months after our interview, but he is now dead; and there is every prospect that the son and daughter may come to live happily together in ignorance of the black cloud which rests upon their past.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>V.<br>\nTHE FIVE ORANGE PIPS</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">W</span>hen I glance over my notes and records of the Sherlock Holmes cases between the years ’82 and ’90, I am faced by so many which present strange and interesting features that it is no easy matter to know which to choose and which to leave. Some, however, have already gained publicity through the papers, and others have not offered a field for those peculiar qualities which my friend possessed in so high a degree, and which it is the object of these papers to illustrate. Some, too, have baffled his analytical skill, and would be, as narratives, beginnings without an ending, while others have been but partially cleared up, and have their explanations founded rather upon conjecture and surmise than on that absolute logical proof which was so dear to him. There is, however, one of these last which was so remarkable in its details and so startling in its results that I am tempted to give some account of it in spite of the fact that there are points in connection with it which never have been, and probably never will be, entirely cleared up.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The year ’87 furnished us with a long series of cases of greater or less interest, of which I retain the records. Among my headings under this one twelve months I find an account of the adventure of the Paradol Chamber, of the Amateur Mendicant Society, who held a luxurious club in the lower vault of a furniture warehouse, of the facts connected with the loss of the British barque <i>Sophy Anderson</i>, of the singular adventures of the Grice Patersons in the island of Uffa, and finally of the Camberwell poisoning case. In the latter, as may be remembered, Sherlock Holmes was able, by winding up the dead man’s watch, to prove that it had been wound up two hours before, and that therefore the deceased had gone to bed within that time—a deduction which was of the greatest importance in clearing up the case. All these I may sketch out at some future date, but none of them present such singular features as the strange train of circumstances which I have now taken up my pen to describe.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was in the latter days of September, and the equinoctial gales had set in with exceptional violence. All day the wind had screamed and the rain had beaten against the windows, so that even here in the heart of great, hand-made London we were forced to raise our minds for the instant from the routine of life and to recognise the presence of those great elemental forces which shriek at mankind through the bars of his civilisation, like untamed beasts in a cage. As evening drew in, the storm grew higher and louder, and the wind cried and sobbed like a child in the chimney. Sherlock Holmes sat moodily at one side of the fireplace cross-indexing his records of crime, while I at the other was deep in one of Clark Russell’s fine sea-stories until the howl of the gale from without seemed to blend with the text, and the splash of the rain to lengthen out into the long swash of the sea waves. My wife was on a visit to her mother’s, and for a few days I was a dweller once more in my old quarters at Baker Street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why,” said I, glancing up at my companion, “that was surely the bell. Who could come to-night? Some friend of yours, perhaps?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Except yourself I have none,” he answered. “I do not encourage visitors.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A client, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If so, it is a serious case. Nothing less would bring a man out on such a day and at such an hour. But I take it that it is more likely to be some crony of the landlady’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes was wrong in his conjecture, however, for there came a step in the passage and a tapping at the door. He stretched out his long arm to turn the lamp away from himself and towards the vacant chair upon which a newcomer must sit.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come in!” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man who entered was young, some two-and-twenty at the outside, well-groomed and trimly clad, with something of refinement and delicacy in his bearing. The streaming umbrella which he held in his hand, and his long shining waterproof told of the fierce weather through which he had come. He looked about him anxiously in the glare of the lamp, and I could see that his face was pale and his eyes heavy, like those of a man who is weighed down with some great anxiety.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I owe you an apology,” he said, raising his golden pince-nez to his eyes. “I trust that I am not intruding. I fear that I have brought some traces of the storm and rain into your snug chamber.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Give me your coat and umbrella,” said Holmes. “They may rest here on the hook and will be dry presently. You have come up from the south-west, I see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, from Horsham.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That clay and chalk mixture which I see upon your toe caps is quite distinctive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have come for advice.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is easily got.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And help.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is not always so easy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have heard of you, Mr. Holmes. I heard from Major Prendergast how you saved him in the Tankerville Club scandal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, of course. He was wrongfully accused of cheating at cards.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He said that you could solve anything.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He said too much.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That you are never beaten.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have been beaten four times—three times by men, and once by a woman.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what is that compared with the number of your successes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is true that I have been generally successful.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you may be so with me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I beg that you will draw your chair up to the fire and favour me with some details as to your case.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is no ordinary one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None of those which come to me are. I am the last court of appeal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And yet I question, sir, whether, in all your experience, you have ever listened to a more mysterious and inexplicable chain of events than those which have happened in my own family.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You fill me with interest,” said Holmes. “Pray give us the essential facts from the commencement, and I can afterwards question you as to those details which seem to me to be most important.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The young man pulled his chair up and pushed his wet feet out towards the blaze.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My name,” said he, “is John Openshaw, but my own affairs have, as far as I can understand, little to do with this awful business. It is a hereditary matter; so in order to give you an idea of the facts, I must go back to the commencement of the affair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You must know that my grandfather had two sons—my uncle Elias and my father Joseph. My father had a small factory at Coventry, which he enlarged at the time of the invention of bicycling. He was a patentee of the Openshaw unbreakable tire, and his business met with such success that he was able to sell it and to retire upon a handsome competence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My uncle Elias emigrated to America when he was a young man and became a planter in Florida, where he was reported to have done very well. At the time of the war he fought in Jackson’s army, and afterwards under Hood, where he rose to be a colonel. When Lee laid down his arms my uncle returned to his plantation, where he remained for three or four years. About 1869 or 1870 he came back to Europe and took a small estate in Sussex, near Horsham. He had made a very considerable fortune in the States, and his reason for leaving them was his aversion to the negroes, and his dislike of the Republican policy in extending the franchise to them. He was a singular man, fierce and quick-tempered, very foul-mouthed when he was angry, and of a most retiring disposition. During all the years that he lived at Horsham, I doubt if ever he set foot in the town. He had a garden and two or three fields round his house, and there he would take his exercise, though very often for weeks on end he would never leave his room. He drank a great deal of brandy and smoked very heavily, but he would see no society and did not want any friends, not even his own brother.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He didn’t mind me; in fact, he took a fancy to me, for at the time when he saw me first I was a youngster of twelve or so. This would be in the year 1878, after he had been eight or nine years in England. He begged my father to let me live with him and he was very kind to me in his way. When he was sober he used to be fond of playing backgammon and draughts with me, and he would make me his representative both with the servants and with the tradespeople, so that by the time that I was sixteen I was quite master of the house. I kept all the keys and could go where I liked and do what I liked, so long as I did not disturb him in his privacy. There was one singular exception, however, for he had a single room, a lumber-room up among the attics, which was invariably locked, and which he would never permit either me or anyone else to enter. With a boy’s curiosity I have peeped through the keyhole, but I was never able to see more than such a collection of old trunks and bundles as would be expected in such a room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One day—it was in March, 1883—a letter with a foreign stamp lay upon the table in front of the colonel’s plate. It was not a common thing for him to receive letters, for his bills were all paid in ready money, and he had no friends of any sort. ‘From India!’ said he as he took it up, ‘Pondicherry postmark! What can this be?’ Opening it hurriedly, out there jumped five little dried orange pips, which pattered down upon his plate. I began to laugh at this, but the laugh was struck from my lips at the sight of his face. His lip had fallen, his eyes were protruding, his skin the colour of putty, and he glared at the envelope which he still held in his trembling hand, ‘K. K. K.!’ he shrieked, and then, ‘My God, my God, my sins have overtaken me!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What is it, uncle?’ I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Death,’ said he, and rising from the table he retired to his room, leaving me palpitating with horror. I took up the envelope and saw scrawled in red ink upon the inner flap, just above the gum, the letter K three times repeated. There was nothing else save the five dried pips. What could be the reason of his overpowering terror? I left the breakfast-table, and as I ascended the stair I met him coming down with an old rusty key, which must have belonged to the attic, in one hand, and a small brass box, like a cashbox, in the other.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘They may do what they like, but I’ll checkmate them still,’ said he with an oath. ‘Tell Mary that I shall want a fire in my room to-day, and send down to Fordham, the Horsham lawyer.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did as he ordered, and when the lawyer arrived I was asked to step up to the room. The fire was burning brightly, and in the grate there was a mass of black, fluffy ashes, as of burned paper, while the brass box stood open and empty beside it. As I glanced at the box I noticed, with a start, that upon the lid was printed the treble K which I had read in the morning upon the envelope.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I wish you, John,’ said my uncle, ‘to witness my will. I leave my estate, with all its advantages and all its disadvantages, to my brother, your father, whence it will, no doubt, descend to you. If you can enjoy it in peace, well and good! If you find you cannot, take my advice, my boy, and leave it to your deadliest enemy. I am sorry to give you such a two-edged thing, but I can’t say what turn things are going to take. Kindly sign the paper where Mr. Fordham shows you.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I signed the paper as directed, and the lawyer took it away with him. The singular incident made, as you may think, the deepest impression upon me, and I pondered over it and turned it every way in my mind without being able to make anything of it. Yet I could not shake off the vague feeling of dread which it left behind, though the sensation grew less keen as the weeks passed and nothing happened to disturb the usual routine of our lives. I could see a change in my uncle, however. He drank more than ever, and he was less inclined for any sort of society. Most of his time he would spend in his room, with the door locked upon the inside, but sometimes he would emerge in a sort of drunken frenzy and would burst out of the house and tear about the garden with a revolver in his hand, screaming out that he was afraid of no man, and that he was not to be cooped up, like a sheep in a pen, by man or devil. When these hot fits were over, however, he would rush tumultuously in at the door and lock and bar it behind him, like a man who can brazen it out no longer against the terror which lies at the roots of his soul. At such times I have seen his face, even on a cold day, glisten with moisture, as though it were new raised from a basin.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, to come to an end of the matter, Mr. Holmes, and not to abuse your patience, there came a night when he made one of those drunken sallies from which he never came back. We found him, when we went to search for him, face downward in a little green-scummed pool, which lay at the foot of the garden. There was no sign of any violence, and the water was but two feet deep, so that the jury, having regard to his known eccentricity, brought in a verdict of ‘suicide.’ But I, who knew how he winced from the very thought of death, had much ado to persuade myself that he had gone out of his way to meet it. The matter passed, however, and my father entered into possession of the estate, and of some £ 14,000, which lay to his credit at the bank.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One moment,” Holmes interposed, “your statement is, I foresee, one of the most remarkable to which I have ever listened. Let me have the date of the reception by your uncle of the letter, and the date of his supposed suicide.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The letter arrived on March 10, 1883. His death was seven weeks later, upon the night of May 2nd.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. Pray proceed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When my father took over the Horsham property, he, at my request, made a careful examination of the attic, which had been always locked up. We found the brass box there, although its contents had been destroyed. On the inside of the cover was a paper label, with the initials of K. K. K. repeated upon it, and ‘Letters, memoranda, receipts, and a register’ written beneath. These, we presume, indicated the nature of the papers which had been destroyed by Colonel Openshaw. For the rest, there was nothing of much importance in the attic save a great many scattered papers and note-books bearing upon my uncle’s life in America. Some of them were of the war time and showed that he had done his duty well and had borne the repute of a brave soldier. Others were of a date during the reconstruction of the Southern states, and were mostly concerned with politics, for he had evidently taken a strong part in opposing the carpet-bag politicians who had been sent down from the North.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it was the beginning of ’84 when my father came to live at Horsham, and all went as well as possible with us until the January of ’85. On the fourth day after the new year I heard my father give a sharp cry of surprise as we sat together at the breakfast-table. There he was, sitting with a newly opened envelope in one hand and five dried orange pips in the outstretched palm of the other one. He had always laughed at what he called my cock-and-bull story about the colonel, but he looked very scared and puzzled now that the same thing had come upon himself.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Why, what on earth does this mean, John?’ he stammered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My heart had turned to lead. ‘It is K. K. K.,’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He looked inside the envelope. ‘So it is,’ he cried. ‘Here are the very letters. But what is this written above them?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Put the papers on the sundial,’ I read, peeping over his shoulder.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What papers? What sundial?’ he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The sundial in the garden. There is no other,’ said I; ‘but the papers must be those that are destroyed.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Pooh!’ said he, gripping hard at his courage. ‘We are in a civilised land here, and we can’t have tomfoolery of this kind. Where does the thing come from?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘From Dundee,’ I answered, glancing at the postmark.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Some preposterous practical joke,’ said he. ‘What have I to do with sundials and papers? I shall take no notice of such nonsense.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I should certainly speak to the police,’ I said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And be laughed at for my pains. Nothing of the sort.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Then let me do so?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, I forbid you. I won’t have a fuss made about such nonsense.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was in vain to argue with him, for he was a very obstinate man. I went about, however, with a heart which was full of forebodings.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the third day after the coming of the letter my father went from home to visit an old friend of his, Major Freebody, who is in command of one of the forts upon Portsdown Hill. I was glad that he should go, for it seemed to me that he was farther from danger when he was away from home. In that, however, I was in error. Upon the second day of his absence I received a telegram from the major, imploring me to come at once. My father had fallen over one of the deep chalk-pits which abound in the neighbourhood, and was lying senseless, with a shattered skull. I hurried to him, but he passed away without having ever recovered his consciousness. He had, as it appears, been returning from Fareham in the twilight, and as the country was unknown to him, and the chalk-pit unfenced, the jury had no hesitation in bringing in a verdict of ‘death from accidental causes.’ Carefully as I examined every fact connected with his death, I was unable to find anything which could suggest the idea of murder. There were no signs of violence, no footmarks, no robbery, no record of strangers having been seen upon the roads. And yet I need not tell you that my mind was far from at ease, and that I was well-nigh certain that some foul plot had been woven round him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In this sinister way I came into my inheritance. You will ask me why I did not dispose of it? I answer, because I was well convinced that our troubles were in some way dependent upon an incident in my uncle’s life, and that the danger would be as pressing in one house as in another.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was in January, ’85, that my poor father met his end, and two years and eight months have elapsed since then. During that time I have lived happily at Horsham, and I had begun to hope that this curse had passed away from the family, and that it had ended with the last generation. I had begun to take comfort too soon, however; yesterday morning the blow fell in the very shape in which it had come upon my father.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The young man took from his waistcoat a crumpled envelope, and turning to the table he shook out upon it five little dried orange pips.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is the envelope,” he continued. “The postmark is London—eastern division. Within are the very words which were upon my father’s last message: ‘K. K. K.’; and then ‘Put the papers on the sundial.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What have you done?” asked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To tell the truth”—he sank his face into his thin, white hands—“I have felt helpless. I have felt like one of those poor rabbits when the snake is writhing towards it. I seem to be in the grasp of some resistless, inexorable evil, which no foresight and no precautions can guard against.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Tut! tut!” cried Sherlock Holmes. “You must act, man, or you are lost. Nothing but energy can save you. This is no time for despair.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have seen the police.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But they listened to my story with a smile. I am convinced that the inspector has formed the opinion that the letters are all practical jokes, and that the deaths of my relations were really accidents, as the jury stated, and were not to be connected with the warnings.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes shook his clenched hands in the air. “Incredible imbecility!” he cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They have, however, allowed me a policeman, who may remain in the house with me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Has he come with you to-night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. His orders were to stay in the house.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Again Holmes raved in the air.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why did you come to me?” he said, “and, above all, why did you not come at once?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did not know. It was only to-day that I spoke to Major Prendergast about my troubles and was advised by him to come to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is really two days since you had the letter. We should have acted before this. You have no further evidence, I suppose, than that which you have placed before us—no suggestive detail which might help us?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is one thing,” said John Openshaw. He rummaged in his coat pocket, and, drawing out a piece of discoloured, blue-tinted paper, he laid it out upon the table. “I have some remembrance,” said he, “that on the day when my uncle burned the papers I observed that the small, unburned margins which lay amid the ashes were of this particular colour. I found this single sheet upon the floor of his room, and I am inclined to think that it may be one of the papers which has, perhaps, fluttered out from among the others, and in that way has escaped destruction. Beyond the mention of pips, I do not see that it helps us much. I think myself that it is a page from some private diary. The writing is undoubtedly my uncle’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes moved the lamp, and we both bent over the sheet of paper, which showed by its ragged edge that it had indeed been torn from a book. It was headed, “March, 1869,” and beneath were the following enigmatical notices:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“4th. Hudson came. Same old platform.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“7th. Set the pips on McCauley, Paramore, and John Swain of St. Augustine.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“9th. McCauley cleared.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“10th. John Swain cleared.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“12th. Visited Paramore. All well.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you!” said Holmes, folding up the paper and returning it to our visitor. “And now you must on no account lose another instant. We cannot spare time even to discuss what you have told me. You must get home instantly and act.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What shall I do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is but one thing to do. It must be done at once. You must put this piece of paper which you have shown us into the brass box which you have described. You must also put in a note to say that all the other papers were burned by your uncle, and that this is the only one which remains. You must assert that in such words as will carry conviction with them. Having done this, you must at once put the box out upon the sundial, as directed. Do you understand?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Entirely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do not think of revenge, or anything of the sort, at present. I think that we may gain that by means of the law; but we have our web to weave, while theirs is already woven. The first consideration is to remove the pressing danger which threatens you. The second is to clear up the mystery and to punish the guilty parties.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I thank you,” said the young man, rising and pulling on his overcoat. “You have given me fresh life and hope. I shall certainly do as you advise.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do not lose an instant. And, above all, take care of yourself in the meanwhile, for I do not think that there can be a doubt that you are threatened by a very real and imminent danger. How do you go back?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By train from Waterloo.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is not yet nine. The streets will be crowded, so I trust that you may be in safety. And yet you cannot guard yourself too closely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am armed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is well. To-morrow I shall set to work upon your case.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall see you at Horsham, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, your secret lies in London. It is there that I shall seek it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I shall call upon you in a day, or in two days, with news as to the box and the papers. I shall take your advice in every particular.” He shook hands with us and took his leave. Outside the wind still screamed and the rain splashed and pattered against the windows. This strange, wild story seemed to have come to us from amid the mad elements—blown in upon us like a sheet of sea-weed in a gale—and now to have been reabsorbed by them once more.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes sat for some time in silence, with his head sunk forward and his eyes bent upon the red glow of the fire. Then he lit his pipe, and leaning back in his chair he watched the blue smoke-rings as they chased each other up to the ceiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think, Watson,” he remarked at last, “that of all our cases we have had none more fantastic than this.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Save, perhaps, the Sign of Four.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, yes. Save, perhaps, that. And yet this John Openshaw seems to me to be walking amid even greater perils than did the Sholtos.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But have you,” I asked, “formed any definite conception as to what these perils are?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There can be no question as to their nature,” he answered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then what are they? Who is this K. K. K., and why does he pursue this unhappy family?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes closed his eyes and placed his elbows upon the arms of his chair, with his finger-tips together. “The ideal reasoner,” he remarked, “would, when he had once been shown a single fact in all its bearings, deduce from it not only all the chain of events which led up to it but also all the results which would follow from it. As Cuvier could correctly describe a whole animal by the contemplation of a single bone, so the observer who has thoroughly understood one link in a series of incidents should be able to accurately state all the other ones, both before and after. We have not yet grasped the results which the reason alone can attain to. Problems may be solved in the study which have baffled all those who have sought a solution by the aid of their senses. To carry the art, however, to its highest pitch, it is necessary that the reasoner should be able to utilise all the facts which have come to his knowledge; and this in itself implies, as you will readily see, a possession of all knowledge, which, even in these days of free education and encyclopædias, is a somewhat rare accomplishment. It is not so impossible, however, that a man should possess all knowledge which is likely to be useful to him in his work, and this I have endeavoured in my case to do. If I remember rightly, you on one occasion, in the early days of our friendship, defined my limits in a very precise fashion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” I answered, laughing. “It was a singular document. Philosophy, astronomy, and politics were marked at zero, I remember. Botany variable, geology profound as regards the mud-stains from any region within fifty miles of town, chemistry eccentric, anatomy unsystematic, sensational literature and crime records unique, violin-player, boxer, swordsman, lawyer, and self-poisoner by cocaine and tobacco. Those, I think, were the main points of my analysis.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes grinned at the last item. “Well,” he said, “I say now, as I said then, that a man should keep his little brain-attic stocked with all the furniture that he is likely to use, and the rest he can put away in the lumber-room of his library, where he can get it if he wants it. Now, for such a case as the one which has been submitted to us to-night, we need certainly to muster all our resources. Kindly hand me down the letter K of the <i>American Encyclopædia</i> which stands upon the shelf beside you. Thank you. Now let us consider the situation and see what may be deduced from it. In the first place, we may start with a strong presumption that Colonel Openshaw had some very strong reason for leaving America. Men at his time of life do not change all their habits and exchange willingly the charming climate of Florida for the lonely life of an English provincial town. His extreme love of solitude in England suggests the idea that he was in fear of someone or something, so we may assume as a working hypothesis that it was fear of someone or something which drove him from America. As to what it was he feared, we can only deduce that by considering the formidable letters which were received by himself and his successors. Did you remark the postmarks of those letters?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The first was from Pondicherry, the second from Dundee, and the third from London.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“From East London. What do you deduce from that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They are all seaports. That the writer was on board of a ship.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excellent. We have already a clue. There can be no doubt that the probability—the strong probability—is that the writer was on board of a ship. And now let us consider another point. In the case of Pondicherry, seven weeks elapsed between the threat and its fulfilment, in Dundee it was only some three or four days. Does that suggest anything?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A greater distance to travel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But the letter had also a greater distance to come.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I do not see the point.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is at least a presumption that the vessel in which the man or men are is a sailing-ship. It looks as if they always send their singular warning or token before them when starting upon their mission. You see how quickly the deed followed the sign when it came from Dundee. If they had come from Pondicherry in a steamer they would have arrived almost as soon as their letter. But, as a matter of fact, seven weeks elapsed. I think that those seven weeks represented the difference between the mail-boat which brought the letter and the sailing vessel which brought the writer.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is possible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“More than that. It is probable. And now you see the deadly urgency of this new case, and why I urged young Openshaw to caution. The blow has always fallen at the end of the time which it would take the senders to travel the distance. But this one comes from London, and therefore we cannot count upon delay.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good God!” I cried. “What can it mean, this relentless persecution?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The papers which Openshaw carried are obviously of vital importance to the person or persons in the sailing-ship. I think that it is quite clear that there must be more than one of them. A single man could not have carried out two deaths in such a way as to deceive a coroner’s jury. There must have been several in it, and they must have been men of resource and determination. Their papers they mean to have, be the holder of them who it may. In this way you see K. K. K. ceases to be the initials of an individual and becomes the badge of a society.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But of what society?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you never—” said Sherlock Holmes, bending forward and sinking his voice—“have you never heard of the Ku Klux Klan?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I never have.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes turned over the leaves of the book upon his knee. “Here it is,” said he presently:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Ku Klux Klan. A name derived from the fanciful resemblance to the sound produced by cocking a rifle. This terrible secret society was formed by some ex-Confederate soldiers in the Southern states after the Civil War, and it rapidly formed local branches in different parts of the country, notably in Tennessee, Louisiana, the Carolinas, Georgia, and Florida. Its power was used for political purposes, principally for the terrorising of the negro voters and the murdering and driving from the country of those who were opposed to its views. Its outrages were usually preceded by a warning sent to the marked man in some fantastic but generally recognised shape—a sprig of oak-leaves in some parts, melon seeds or orange pips in others. On receiving this the victim might either openly abjure his former ways, or might fly from the country. If he braved the matter out, death would unfailingly come upon him, and usually in some strange and unforeseen manner. So perfect was the organisation of the society, and so systematic its methods, that there is hardly a case upon record where any man succeeded in braving it with impunity, or in which any of its outrages were traced home to the perpetrators. For some years the organisation flourished in spite of the efforts of the United States government and of the better classes of the community in the South. Eventually, in the year 1869, the movement rather suddenly collapsed, although there have been sporadic outbreaks of the same sort since that date.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will observe,” said Holmes, laying down the volume, “that the sudden breaking up of the society was coincident with the disappearance of Openshaw from America with their papers. It may well have been cause and effect. It is no wonder that he and his family have some of the more implacable spirits upon their track. You can understand that this register and diary may implicate some of the first men in the South, and that there may be many who will not sleep easy at night until it is recovered.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then the page we have seen—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is such as we might expect. It ran, if I remember right, ‘sent the pips to A, B, and C’—that is, sent the society’s warning to them. Then there are successive entries that A and B cleared, or left the country, and finally that C was visited, with, I fear, a sinister result for C. Well, I think, Doctor, that we may let some light into this dark place, and I believe that the only chance young Openshaw has in the meantime is to do what I have told him. There is nothing more to be said or to be done to-night, so hand me over my violin and let us try to forget for half an hour the miserable weather and the still more miserable ways of our fellow men.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">It had cleared in the morning, and the sun was shining with a subdued brightness through the dim veil which hangs over the great city. Sherlock Holmes was already at breakfast when I came down.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will excuse me for not waiting for you,” said he; “I have, I foresee, a very busy day before me in looking into this case of young Openshaw’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What steps will you take?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It will very much depend upon the results of my first inquiries. I may have to go down to Horsham, after all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will not go there first?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I shall commence with the City. Just ring the bell and the maid will bring up your coffee.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As I waited, I lifted the unopened newspaper from the table and glanced my eye over it. It rested upon a heading which sent a chill to my heart.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Holmes,” I cried, “you are too late.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” said he, laying down his cup, “I feared as much. How was it done?” He spoke calmly, but I could see that he was deeply moved.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My eye caught the name of Openshaw, and the heading ‘Tragedy Near Waterloo Bridge.’ Here is the account:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Between nine and ten last night Police-Constable Cook, of the H Division, on duty near Waterloo Bridge, heard a cry for help and a splash in the water. The night, however, was extremely dark and stormy, so that, in spite of the help of several passers-by, it was quite impossible to effect a rescue. The alarm, however, was given, and, by the aid of the water-police, the body was eventually recovered. It proved to be that of a young gentleman whose name, as it appears from an envelope which was found in his pocket, was John Openshaw, and whose residence is near Horsham. It is conjectured that he may have been hurrying down to catch the last train from Waterloo Station, and that in his haste and the extreme darkness he missed his path and walked over the edge of one of the small landing-places for river steamboats. The body exhibited no traces of violence, and there can be no doubt that the deceased had been the victim of an unfortunate accident, which should have the effect of calling the attention of the authorities to the condition of the riverside landing-stages.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We sat in silence for some minutes, Holmes more depressed and shaken than I had ever seen him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That hurts my pride, Watson,” he said at last. “It is a petty feeling, no doubt, but it hurts my pride. It becomes a personal matter with me now, and, if God sends me health, I shall set my hand upon this gang. That he should come to me for help, and that I should send him away to his death—!” He sprang from his chair and paced about the room in uncontrollable agitation, with a flush upon his sallow cheeks and a nervous clasping and unclasping of his long thin hands.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They must be cunning devils,” he exclaimed at last. “How could they have decoyed him down there? The Embankment is not on the direct line to the station. The bridge, no doubt, was too crowded, even on such a night, for their purpose. Well, Watson, we shall see who will win in the long run. I am going out now!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To the police?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No; I shall be my own police. When I have spun the web they may take the flies, but not before.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>All day I was engaged in my professional work, and it was late in the evening before I returned to Baker Street. Sherlock Holmes had not come back yet. It was nearly ten o’clock before he entered, looking pale and worn. He walked up to the sideboard, and tearing a piece from the loaf he devoured it voraciously, washing it down with a long draught of water.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are hungry,” I remarked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Starving. It had escaped my memory. I have had nothing since breakfast.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not a bite. I had no time to think of it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how have you succeeded?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have a clue?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have them in the hollow of my hand. Young Openshaw shall not long remain unavenged. Why, Watson, let us put their own devilish trade-mark upon them. It is well thought of!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He took an orange from the cupboard, and tearing it to pieces he squeezed out the pips upon the table. Of these he took five and thrust them into an envelope. On the inside of the flap he wrote “S. H. for J. O.” Then he sealed it and addressed it to “Captain James Calhoun, Barque <i>Lone Star</i>, Savannah, Georgia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That will await him when he enters port,” said he, chuckling. “It may give him a sleepless night. He will find it as sure a precursor of his fate as Openshaw did before him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And who is this Captain Calhoun?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The leader of the gang. I shall have the others, but he first.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did you trace it, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He took a large sheet of paper from his pocket, all covered with dates and names.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have spent the whole day,” said he, “over Lloyd’s registers and files of the old papers, following the future career of every vessel which touched at Pondicherry in January and February in ’83. There were thirty-six ships of fair tonnage which were reported there during those months. Of these, one, the <i>Lone Star</i>, instantly attracted my attention, since, although it was reported as having cleared from London, the name is that which is given to one of the states of the Union.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Texas, I think.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was not and am not sure which; but I knew that the ship must have an American origin.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I searched the Dundee records, and when I found that the barque <i>Lone Star</i> was there in January, ’85, my suspicion became a certainty. I then inquired as to the vessels which lay at present in the port of London.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The <i>Lone Star</i> had arrived here last week. I went down to the Albert Dock and found that she had been taken down the river by the early tide this morning, homeward bound to Savannah. I wired to Gravesend and learned that she had passed some time ago, and as the wind is easterly I have no doubt that she is now past the Goodwins and not very far from the Isle of Wight.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What will you do, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, I have my hand upon him. He and the two mates, are as I learn, the only native-born Americans in the ship. The others are Finns and Germans. I know, also, that they were all three away from the ship last night. I had it from the stevedore who has been loading their cargo. By the time that their sailing-ship reaches Savannah the mail-boat will have carried this letter, and the cable will have informed the police of Savannah that these three gentlemen are badly wanted here upon a charge of murder.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There is ever a flaw, however, in the best laid of human plans, and the murderers of John Openshaw were never to receive the orange pips which would show them that another, as cunning and as resolute as themselves, was upon their track. Very long and very severe were the equinoctial gales that year. We waited long for news of the <i>Lone Star</i> of Savannah, but none ever reached us. We did at last hear that somewhere far out in the Atlantic a shattered stern-post of a boat was seen swinging in the trough of a wave, with the letters “L. S.” carved upon it, and that is all which we shall ever know of the fate of the <i>Lone Star</i>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>VI.<br>\nTHE MAN WITH THE TWISTED LIP</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">I</span>sa Whitney, brother of the late Elias Whitney, D.D., Principal of the Theological College of St. George’s, was much addicted to opium. The habit grew upon him, as I understand, from some foolish freak when he was at college; for having read De Quincey’s description of his dreams and sensations, he had drenched his tobacco with laudanum in an attempt to produce the same effects. He found, as so many more have done, that the practice is easier to attain than to get rid of, and for many years he continued to be a slave to the drug, an object of mingled horror and pity to his friends and relatives. I can see him now, with yellow, pasty face, drooping lids, and pin-point pupils, all huddled in a chair, the wreck and ruin of a noble man.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>One night—it was in June, ’89—there came a ring to my bell, about the hour when a man gives his first yawn and glances at the clock. I sat up in my chair, and my wife laid her needle-work down in her lap and made a little face of disappointment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A patient!” said she. “You’ll have to go out.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I groaned, for I was newly come back from a weary day.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We heard the door open, a few hurried words, and then quick steps upon the linoleum. Our own door flew open, and a lady, clad in some dark-coloured stuff, with a black veil, entered the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will excuse my calling so late,” she began, and then, suddenly losing her self-control, she ran forward, threw her arms about my wife’s neck, and sobbed upon her shoulder. “Oh, I’m in such trouble!” she cried; “I do so want a little help.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why,” said my wife, pulling up her veil, “it is Kate Whitney. How you startled me, Kate! I had not an idea who you were when you came in.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I didn’t know what to do, so I came straight to you.” That was always the way. Folk who were in grief came to my wife like birds to a lighthouse.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was very sweet of you to come. Now, you must have some wine and water, and sit here comfortably and tell us all about it. Or should you rather that I sent James off to bed?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, no, no! I want the doctor’s advice and help, too. It’s about Isa. He has not been home for two days. I am so frightened about him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was not the first time that she had spoken to us of her husband’s trouble, to me as a doctor, to my wife as an old friend and school companion. We soothed and comforted her by such words as we could find. Did she know where her husband was? Was it possible that we could bring him back to her?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It seems that it was. She had the surest information that of late he had, when the fit was on him, made use of an opium den in the farthest east of the City. Hitherto his orgies had always been confined to one day, and he had come back, twitching and shattered, in the evening. But now the spell had been upon him eight-and-forty hours, and he lay there, doubtless among the dregs of the docks, breathing in the poison or sleeping off the effects. There he was to be found, she was sure of it, at the Bar of Gold, in Upper Swandam Lane. But what was she to do? How could she, a young and timid woman, make her way into such a place and pluck her husband out from among the ruffians who surrounded him?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was the case, and of course there was but one way out of it. Might I not escort her to this place? And then, as a second thought, why should she come at all? I was Isa Whitney’s medical adviser, and as such I had influence over him. I could manage it better if I were alone. I promised her on my word that I would send him home in a cab within two hours if he were indeed at the address which she had given me. And so in ten minutes I had left my armchair and cheery sitting-room behind me, and was speeding eastward in a hansom on a strange errand, as it seemed to me at the time, though the future only could show how strange it was to be.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But there was no great difficulty in the first stage of my adventure. Upper Swandam Lane is a vile alley lurking behind the high wharves which line the north side of the river to the east of London Bridge. Between a slop-shop and a gin-shop, approached by a steep flight of steps leading down to a black gap like the mouth of a cave, I found the den of which I was in search. Ordering my cab to wait, I passed down the steps, worn hollow in the centre by the ceaseless tread of drunken feet; and by the light of a flickering oil-lamp above the door I found the latch and made my way into a long, low room, thick and heavy with the brown opium smoke, and terraced with wooden berths, like the forecastle of an emigrant ship.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Through the gloom one could dimly catch a glimpse of bodies lying in strange fantastic poses, bowed shoulders, bent knees, heads thrown back, and chins pointing upward, with here and there a dark, lack-lustre eye turned upon the newcomer. Out of the black shadows there glimmered little red circles of light, now bright, now faint, as the burning poison waxed or waned in the bowls of the metal pipes. The most lay silent, but some muttered to themselves, and others talked together in a strange, low, monotonous voice, their conversation coming in gushes, and then suddenly tailing off into silence, each mumbling out his own thoughts and paying little heed to the words of his neighbour. At the farther end was a small brazier of burning charcoal, beside which on a three-legged wooden stool there sat a tall, thin old man, with his jaw resting upon his two fists, and his elbows upon his knees, staring into the fire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As I entered, a sallow Malay attendant had hurried up with a pipe for me and a supply of the drug, beckoning me to an empty berth.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. I have not come to stay,” said I. “There is a friend of mine here, Mr. Isa Whitney, and I wish to speak with him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a movement and an exclamation from my right, and peering through the gloom, I saw Whitney, pale, haggard, and unkempt, staring out at me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My God! It’s Watson,” said he. He was in a pitiable state of reaction, with every nerve in a twitter. “I say, Watson, what o’clock is it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nearly eleven.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of what day?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of Friday, June 19th.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens! I thought it was Wednesday. It is Wednesday. What d’you want to frighten a chap for?” He sank his face onto his arms and began to sob in a high treble key.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I tell you that it is Friday, man. Your wife has been waiting this two days for you. You should be ashamed of yourself!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So I am. But you’ve got mixed, Watson, for I have only been here a few hours, three pipes, four pipes—I forget how many. But I’ll go home with you. I wouldn’t frighten Kate—poor little Kate. Give me your hand! Have you a cab?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I have one waiting.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I shall go in it. But I must owe something. Find what I owe, Watson. I am all off colour. I can do nothing for myself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I walked down the narrow passage between the double row of sleepers, holding my breath to keep out the vile, stupefying fumes of the drug, and looking about for the manager. As I passed the tall man who sat by the brazier I felt a sudden pluck at my skirt, and a low voice whispered, “Walk past me, and then look back at me.” The words fell quite distinctly upon my ear. I glanced down. They could only have come from the old man at my side, and yet he sat now as absorbed as ever, very thin, very wrinkled, bent with age, an opium pipe dangling down from between his knees, as though it had dropped in sheer lassitude from his fingers. I took two steps forward and looked back. It took all my self-control to prevent me from breaking out into a cry of astonishment. He had turned his back so that none could see him but I. His form had filled out, his wrinkles were gone, the dull eyes had regained their fire, and there, sitting by the fire and grinning at my surprise, was none other than Sherlock Holmes. He made a slight motion to me to approach him, and instantly, as he turned his face half round to the company once more, subsided into a doddering, loose-lipped senility.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Holmes!” I whispered, “what on earth are you doing in this den?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As low as you can,” he answered; “I have excellent ears. If you would have the great kindness to get rid of that sottish friend of yours I should be exceedingly glad to have a little talk with you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have a cab outside.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then pray send him home in it. You may safely trust him, for he appears to be too limp to get into any mischief. I should recommend you also to send a note by the cabman to your wife to say that you have thrown in your lot with me. If you will wait outside, I shall be with you in five minutes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was difficult to refuse any of Sherlock Holmes’ requests, for they were always so exceedingly definite, and put forward with such a quiet air of mastery. I felt, however, that when Whitney was once confined in the cab my mission was practically accomplished; and for the rest, I could not wish anything better than to be associated with my friend in one of those singular adventures which were the normal condition of his existence. In a few minutes I had written my note, paid Whitney’s bill, led him out to the cab, and seen him driven through the darkness. In a very short time a decrepit figure had emerged from the opium den, and I was walking down the street with Sherlock Holmes. For two streets he shuffled along with a bent back and an uncertain foot. Then, glancing quickly round, he straightened himself out and burst into a hearty fit of laughter.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I suppose, Watson,” said he, “that you imagine that I have added opium-smoking to cocaine injections, and all the other little weaknesses on which you have favoured me with your medical views.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was certainly surprised to find you there.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But not more so than I to find you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I came to find a friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I to find an enemy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“An enemy?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; one of my natural enemies, or, shall I say, my natural prey. Briefly, Watson, I am in the midst of a very remarkable inquiry, and I have hoped to find a clue in the incoherent ramblings of these sots, as I have done before now. Had I been recognised in that den my life would not have been worth an hour’s purchase; for I have used it before now for my own purposes, and the rascally Lascar who runs it has sworn to have vengeance upon me. There is a trap-door at the back of that building, near the corner of Paul’s Wharf, which could tell some strange tales of what has passed through it upon the moonless nights.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What! You do not mean bodies?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ay, bodies, Watson. We should be rich men if we had £ 1000 for every poor devil who has been done to death in that den. It is the vilest murder-trap on the whole riverside, and I fear that Neville St. Clair has entered it never to leave it more. But our trap should be here.” He put his two forefingers between his teeth and whistled shrilly—a signal which was answered by a similar whistle from the distance, followed shortly by the rattle of wheels and the clink of horses’ hoofs.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, Watson,” said Holmes, as a tall dog-cart dashed up through the gloom, throwing out two golden tunnels of yellow light from its side lanterns. “You’ll come with me, won’t you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If I can be of use.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, a trusty comrade is always of use; and a chronicler still more so. My room at The Cedars is a double-bedded one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Cedars?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; that is Mr. St. Clair’s house. I am staying there while I conduct the inquiry.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where is it, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Near Lee, in Kent. We have a seven-mile drive before us.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I am all in the dark.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course you are. You’ll know all about it presently. Jump up here. All right, John; we shall not need you. Here’s half a crown. Look out for me to-morrow, about eleven. Give her her head. So long, then!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He flicked the horse with his whip, and we dashed away through the endless succession of sombre and deserted streets, which widened gradually, until we were flying across a broad balustraded bridge, with the murky river flowing sluggishly beneath us. Beyond lay another dull wilderness of bricks and mortar, its silence broken only by the heavy, regular footfall of the policeman, or the songs and shouts of some belated party of revellers. A dull wrack was drifting slowly across the sky, and a star or two twinkled dimly here and there through the rifts of the clouds. Holmes drove in silence, with his head sunk upon his breast, and the air of a man who is lost in thought, while I sat beside him, curious to learn what this new quest might be which seemed to tax his powers so sorely, and yet afraid to break in upon the current of his thoughts. We had driven several miles, and were beginning to get to the fringe of the belt of suburban villas, when he shook himself, shrugged his shoulders, and lit up his pipe with the air of a man who has satisfied himself that he is acting for the best.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have a grand gift of silence, Watson,” said he. “It makes you quite invaluable as a companion. ’Pon my word, it is a great thing for me to have someone to talk to, for my own thoughts are not over-pleasant. I was wondering what I should say to this dear little woman to-night when she meets me at the door.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You forget that I know nothing about it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall just have time to tell you the facts of the case before we get to Lee. It seems absurdly simple, and yet, somehow I can get nothing to go upon. There’s plenty of thread, no doubt, but I can’t get the end of it into my hand. Now, I’ll state the case clearly and concisely to you, Watson, and maybe you can see a spark where all is dark to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Proceed, then.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Some years ago—to be definite, in May, 1884—there came to Lee a gentleman, Neville St. Clair by name, who appeared to have plenty of money. He took a large villa, laid out the grounds very nicely, and lived generally in good style. By degrees he made friends in the neighbourhood, and in 1887 he married the daughter of a local brewer, by whom he now has two children. He had no occupation, but was interested in several companies and went into town as a rule in the morning, returning by the 5:14 from Cannon Street every night. Mr. St. Clair is now thirty-seven years of age, is a man of temperate habits, a good husband, a very affectionate father, and a man who is popular with all who know him. I may add that his whole debts at the present moment, as far as we have been able to ascertain, amount to £ 88 10<i>s</i>., while he has £ 220 standing to his credit in the Capital and Counties Bank. There is no reason, therefore, to think that money troubles have been weighing upon his mind.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Last Monday Mr. Neville St. Clair went into town rather earlier than usual, remarking before he started that he had two important commissions to perform, and that he would bring his little boy home a box of bricks. Now, by the merest chance, his wife received a telegram upon this same Monday, very shortly after his departure, to the effect that a small parcel of considerable value which she had been expecting was waiting for her at the offices of the Aberdeen Shipping Company. Now, if you are well up in your London, you will know that the office of the company is in Fresno Street, which branches out of Upper Swandam Lane, where you found me to-night. Mrs. St. Clair had her lunch, started for the City, did some shopping, proceeded to the company’s office, got her packet, and found herself at exactly 4:35 walking through Swandam Lane on her way back to the station. Have you followed me so far?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is very clear.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you remember, Monday was an exceedingly hot day, and Mrs. St. Clair walked slowly, glancing about in the hope of seeing a cab, as she did not like the neighbourhood in which she found herself. While she was walking in this way down Swandam Lane, she suddenly heard an ejaculation or cry, and was struck cold to see her husband looking down at her and, as it seemed to her, beckoning to her from a second-floor window. The window was open, and she distinctly saw his face, which she describes as being terribly agitated. He waved his hands frantically to her, and then vanished from the window so suddenly that it seemed to her that he had been plucked back by some irresistible force from behind. One singular point which struck her quick feminine eye was that although he wore some dark coat, such as he had started to town in, he had on neither collar nor necktie.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Convinced that something was amiss with him, she rushed down the steps—for the house was none other than the opium den in which you found me to-night—and running through the front room she attempted to ascend the stairs which led to the first floor. At the foot of the stairs, however, she met this Lascar scoundrel of whom I have spoken, who thrust her back and, aided by a Dane, who acts as assistant there, pushed her out into the street. Filled with the most maddening doubts and fears, she rushed down the lane and, by rare good-fortune, met in Fresno Street a number of constables with an inspector, all on their way to their beat. The inspector and two men accompanied her back, and in spite of the continued resistance of the proprietor, they made their way to the room in which Mr. St. Clair had last been seen. There was no sign of him there. In fact, in the whole of that floor there was no one to be found save a crippled wretch of hideous aspect, who, it seems, made his home there. Both he and the Lascar stoutly swore that no one else had been in the front room during the afternoon. So determined was their denial that the inspector was staggered, and had almost come to believe that Mrs. St. Clair had been deluded when, with a cry, she sprang at a small deal box which lay upon the table and tore the lid from it. Out there fell a cascade of children’s bricks. It was the toy which he had promised to bring home.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This discovery, and the evident confusion which the cripple showed, made the inspector realise that the matter was serious. The rooms were carefully examined, and results all pointed to an abominable crime. The front room was plainly furnished as a sitting-room and led into a small bedroom, which looked out upon the back of one of the wharves. Between the wharf and the bedroom window is a narrow strip, which is dry at low tide but is covered at high tide with at least four and a half feet of water. The bedroom window was a broad one and opened from below. On examination traces of blood were to be seen upon the windowsill, and several scattered drops were visible upon the wooden floor of the bedroom. Thrust away behind a curtain in the front room were all the clothes of Mr. Neville St. Clair, with the exception of his coat. His boots, his socks, his hat, and his watch—all were there. There were no signs of violence upon any of these garments, and there were no other traces of Mr. Neville St. Clair. Out of the window he must apparently have gone for no other exit could be discovered, and the ominous bloodstains upon the sill gave little promise that he could save himself by swimming, for the tide was at its very highest at the moment of the tragedy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And now as to the villains who seemed to be immediately implicated in the matter. The Lascar was known to be a man of the vilest antecedents, but as, by Mrs. St. Clair’s story, he was known to have been at the foot of the stair within a very few seconds of her husband’s appearance at the window, he could hardly have been more than an accessory to the crime. His defence was one of absolute ignorance, and he protested that he had no knowledge as to the doings of Hugh Boone, his lodger, and that he could not account in any way for the presence of the missing gentleman’s clothes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So much for the Lascar manager. Now for the sinister cripple who lives upon the second floor of the opium den, and who was certainly the last human being whose eyes rested upon Neville St. Clair. His name is Hugh Boone, and his hideous face is one which is familiar to every man who goes much to the City. He is a professional beggar, though in order to avoid the police regulations he pretends to a small trade in wax vestas. Some little distance down Threadneedle Street, upon the left-hand side, there is, as you may have remarked, a small angle in the wall. Here it is that this creature takes his daily seat, cross-legged with his tiny stock of matches on his lap, and as he is a piteous spectacle a small rain of charity descends into the greasy leather cap which lies upon the pavement beside him. I have watched the fellow more than once before ever I thought of making his professional acquaintance, and I have been surprised at the harvest which he has reaped in a short time. His appearance, you see, is so remarkable that no one can pass him without observing him. A shock of orange hair, a pale face disfigured by a horrible scar, which, by its contraction, has turned up the outer edge of his upper lip, a bulldog chin, and a pair of very penetrating dark eyes, which present a singular contrast to the colour of his hair, all mark him out from amid the common crowd of mendicants and so, too, does his wit, for he is ever ready with a reply to any piece of chaff which may be thrown at him by the passers-by. This is the man whom we now learn to have been the lodger at the opium den, and to have been the last man to see the gentleman of whom we are in quest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But a cripple!” said I. “What could he have done single-handed against a man in the prime of life?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is a cripple in the sense that he walks with a limp; but in other respects he appears to be a powerful and well-nurtured man. Surely your medical experience would tell you, Watson, that weakness in one limb is often compensated for by exceptional strength in the others.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray continue your narrative.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mrs. St. Clair had fainted at the sight of the blood upon the window, and she was escorted home in a cab by the police, as her presence could be of no help to them in their investigations. Inspector Barton, who had charge of the case, made a very careful examination of the premises, but without finding anything which threw any light upon the matter. One mistake had been made in not arresting Boone instantly, as he was allowed some few minutes during which he might have communicated with his friend the Lascar, but this fault was soon remedied, and he was seized and searched, without anything being found which could incriminate him. There were, it is true, some blood-stains upon his right shirt-sleeve, but he pointed to his ring-finger, which had been cut near the nail, and explained that the bleeding came from there, adding that he had been to the window not long before, and that the stains which had been observed there came doubtless from the same source. He denied strenuously having ever seen Mr. Neville St. Clair and swore that the presence of the clothes in his room was as much a mystery to him as to the police. As to Mrs. St. Clair’s assertion that she had actually seen her husband at the window, he declared that she must have been either mad or dreaming. He was removed, loudly protesting, to the police-station, while the inspector remained upon the premises in the hope that the ebbing tide might afford some fresh clue.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And it did, though they hardly found upon the mud-bank what they had feared to find. It was Neville St. Clair’s coat, and not Neville St. Clair, which lay uncovered as the tide receded. And what do you think they found in the pockets?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot imagine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I don’t think you would guess. Every pocket stuffed with pennies and half-pennies—421 pennies and 270 half-pennies. It was no wonder that it had not been swept away by the tide. But a human body is a different matter. There is a fierce eddy between the wharf and the house. It seemed likely enough that the weighted coat had remained when the stripped body had been sucked away into the river.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I understand that all the other clothes were found in the room. Would the body be dressed in a coat alone?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir, but the facts might be met speciously enough. Suppose that this man Boone had thrust Neville St. Clair through the window, there is no human eye which could have seen the deed. What would he do then? It would of course instantly strike him that he must get rid of the tell-tale garments. He would seize the coat, then, and be in the act of throwing it out, when it would occur to him that it would swim and not sink. He has little time, for he has heard the scuffle downstairs when the wife tried to force her way up, and perhaps he has already heard from his Lascar confederate that the police are hurrying up the street. There is not an instant to be lost. He rushes to some secret hoard, where he has accumulated the fruits of his beggary, and he stuffs all the coins upon which he can lay his hands into the pockets to make sure of the coat’s sinking. He throws it out, and would have done the same with the other garments had not he heard the rush of steps below, and only just had time to close the window when the police appeared.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It certainly sounds feasible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, we will take it as a working hypothesis for want of a better. Boone, as I have told you, was arrested and taken to the station, but it could not be shown that there had ever before been anything against him. He had for years been known as a professional beggar, but his life appeared to have been a very quiet and innocent one. There the matter stands at present, and the questions which have to be solved—what Neville St. Clair was doing in the opium den, what happened to him when there, where is he now, and what Hugh Boone had to do with his disappearance—are all as far from a solution as ever. I confess that I cannot recall any case within my experience which looked at the first glance so simple and yet which presented such difficulties.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>While Sherlock Holmes had been detailing this singular series of events, we had been whirling through the outskirts of the great town until the last straggling houses had been left behind, and we rattled along with a country hedge upon either side of us. Just as he finished, however, we drove through two scattered villages, where a few lights still glimmered in the windows.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We are on the outskirts of Lee,” said my companion. “We have touched on three English counties in our short drive, starting in Middlesex, passing over an angle of Surrey, and ending in Kent. See that light among the trees? That is The Cedars, and beside that lamp sits a woman whose anxious ears have already, I have little doubt, caught the clink of our horse’s feet.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But why are you not conducting the case from Baker Street?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because there are many inquiries which must be made out here. Mrs. St. Clair has most kindly put two rooms at my disposal, and you may rest assured that she will have nothing but a welcome for my friend and colleague. I hate to meet her, Watson, when I have no news of her husband. Here we are. Whoa, there, whoa!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had pulled up in front of a large villa which stood within its own grounds. A stable-boy had run out to the horse’s head, and springing down, I followed Holmes up the small, winding gravel-drive which led to the house. As we approached, the door flew open, and a little blonde woman stood in the opening, clad in some sort of light mousseline de soie, with a touch of fluffy pink chiffon at her neck and wrists. She stood with her figure outlined against the flood of light, one hand upon the door, one half-raised in her eagerness, her body slightly bent, her head and face protruded, with eager eyes and parted lips, a standing question.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?” she cried, “well?” And then, seeing that there were two of us, she gave a cry of hope which sank into a groan as she saw that my companion shook his head and shrugged his shoulders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No good news?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No bad?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank God for that. But come in. You must be weary, for you have had a long day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is my friend, Dr. Watson. He has been of most vital use to me in several of my cases, and a lucky chance has made it possible for me to bring him out and associate him with this investigation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am delighted to see you,” said she, pressing my hand warmly. “You will, I am sure, forgive anything that may be wanting in our arrangements, when you consider the blow which has come so suddenly upon us.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear madam,” said I, “I am an old campaigner, and if I were not I can very well see that no apology is needed. If I can be of any assistance, either to you or to my friend here, I shall be indeed happy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, Mr. Sherlock Holmes,” said the lady as we entered a well-lit dining-room, upon the table of which a cold supper had been laid out, “I should very much like to ask you one or two plain questions, to which I beg that you will give a plain answer.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly, madam.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do not trouble about my feelings. I am not hysterical, nor given to fainting. I simply wish to hear your real, real opinion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Upon what point?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In your heart of hearts, do you think that Neville is alive?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes seemed to be embarrassed by the question. “Frankly, now!” she repeated, standing upon the rug and looking keenly down at him as he leaned back in a basket-chair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Frankly, then, madam, I do not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You think that he is dead?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Murdered?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t say that. Perhaps.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And on what day did he meet his death?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On Monday.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then perhaps, Mr. Holmes, you will be good enough to explain how it is that I have received a letter from him to-day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes sprang out of his chair as if he had been galvanised.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What!” he roared.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, to-day.” She stood smiling, holding up a little slip of paper in the air.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“May I see it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He snatched it from her in his eagerness, and smoothing it out upon the table he drew over the lamp and examined it intently. I had left my chair and was gazing at it over his shoulder. The envelope was a very coarse one and was stamped with the Gravesend postmark and with the date of that very day, or rather of the day before, for it was considerably after midnight.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Coarse writing,” murmured Holmes. “Surely this is not your husband’s writing, madam.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but the enclosure is.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I perceive also that whoever addressed the envelope had to go and inquire as to the address.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How can you tell that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The name, you see, is in perfectly black ink, which has dried itself. The rest is of the greyish colour, which shows that blotting-paper has been used. If it had been written straight off, and then blotted, none would be of a deep black shade. This man has written the name, and there has then been a pause before he wrote the address, which can only mean that he was not familiar with it. It is, of course, a trifle, but there is nothing so important as trifles. Let us now see the letter. Ha! there has been an enclosure here!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, there was a ring. His signet-ring.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you are sure that this is your husband’s hand?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One of his hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“His hand when he wrote hurriedly. It is very unlike his usual writing, and yet I know it well.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Dearest do not be frightened. All will come well. There is a huge error which it may take some little time to rectify. Wait in patience.—NEVILLE.’ Written in pencil upon the fly-leaf of a book, octavo size, no water-mark. Hum! Posted to-day in Gravesend by a man with a dirty thumb. Ha! And the flap has been gummed, if I am not very much in error, by a person who had been chewing tobacco. And you have no doubt that it is your husband’s hand, madam?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None. Neville wrote those words.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And they were posted to-day at Gravesend. Well, Mrs. St. Clair, the clouds lighten, though I should not venture to say that the danger is over.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But he must be alive, Mr. Holmes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Unless this is a clever forgery to put us on the wrong scent. The ring, after all, proves nothing. It may have been taken from him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no; it is, it is his very own writing!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well. It may, however, have been written on Monday and only posted to-day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is possible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If so, much may have happened between.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, you must not discourage me, Mr. Holmes. I know that all is well with him. There is so keen a sympathy between us that I should know if evil came upon him. On the very day that I saw him last he cut himself in the bedroom, and yet I in the dining-room rushed upstairs instantly with the utmost certainty that something had happened. Do you think that I would respond to such a trifle and yet be ignorant of his death?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have seen too much not to know that the impression of a woman may be more valuable than the conclusion of an analytical reasoner. And in this letter you certainly have a very strong piece of evidence to corroborate your view. But if your husband is alive and able to write letters, why should he remain away from you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot imagine. It is unthinkable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And on Monday he made no remarks before leaving you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you were surprised to see him in Swandam Lane?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very much so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was the window open?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then he might have called to you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He might.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He only, as I understand, gave an inarticulate cry?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A call for help, you thought?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. He waved his hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it might have been a cry of surprise. Astonishment at the unexpected sight of you might cause him to throw up his hands?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is possible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you thought he was pulled back?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He disappeared so suddenly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He might have leaped back. You did not see anyone else in the room?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but this horrible man confessed to having been there, and the Lascar was at the foot of the stairs.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. Your husband, as far as you could see, had his ordinary clothes on?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But without his collar or tie. I distinctly saw his bare throat.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Had he ever spoken of Swandam Lane?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Had he ever showed any signs of having taken opium?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you, Mrs. St. Clair. Those are the principal points about which I wished to be absolutely clear. We shall now have a little supper and then retire, for we may have a very busy day to-morrow.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A large and comfortable double-bedded room had been placed at our disposal, and I was quickly between the sheets, for I was weary after my night of adventure. Sherlock Holmes was a man, however, who, when he had an unsolved problem upon his mind, would go for days, and even for a week, without rest, turning it over, rearranging his facts, looking at it from every point of view until he had either fathomed it or convinced himself that his data were insufficient. It was soon evident to me that he was now preparing for an all-night sitting. He took off his coat and waistcoat, put on a large blue dressing-gown, and then wandered about the room collecting pillows from his bed and cushions from the sofa and armchairs. With these he constructed a sort of Eastern divan, upon which he perched himself cross-legged, with an ounce of shag tobacco and a box of matches laid out in front of him. In the dim light of the lamp I saw him sitting there, an old briar pipe between his lips, his eyes fixed vacantly upon the corner of the ceiling, the blue smoke curling up from him, silent, motionless, with the light shining upon his strong-set aquiline features. So he sat as I dropped off to sleep, and so he sat when a sudden ejaculation caused me to wake up, and I found the summer sun shining into the apartment. The pipe was still between his lips, the smoke still curled upward, and the room was full of a dense tobacco haze, but nothing remained of the heap of shag which I had seen upon the previous night.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Awake, Watson?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Game for a morning drive?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then dress. No one is stirring yet, but I know where the stable-boy sleeps, and we shall soon have the trap out.” He chuckled to himself as he spoke, his eyes twinkled, and he seemed a different man to the sombre thinker of the previous night.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As I dressed I glanced at my watch. It was no wonder that no one was stirring. It was twenty-five minutes past four. I had hardly finished when Holmes returned with the news that the boy was putting in the horse.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I want to test a little theory of mine,” said he, pulling on his boots. “I think, Watson, that you are now standing in the presence of one of the most absolute fools in Europe. I deserve to be kicked from here to Charing Cross. But I think I have the key of the affair now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And where is it?” I asked, smiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the bathroom,” he answered. “Oh, yes, I am not joking,” he continued, seeing my look of incredulity. “I have just been there, and I have taken it out, and I have got it in this Gladstone bag. Come on, my boy, and we shall see whether it will not fit the lock.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We made our way downstairs as quietly as possible, and out into the bright morning sunshine. In the road stood our horse and trap, with the half-clad stable-boy waiting at the head. We both sprang in, and away we dashed down the London Road. A few country carts were stirring, bearing in vegetables to the metropolis, but the lines of villas on either side were as silent and lifeless as some city in a dream.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It has been in some points a singular case,” said Holmes, flicking the horse on into a gallop. “I confess that I have been as blind as a mole, but it is better to learn wisdom late than never to learn it at all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In town the earliest risers were just beginning to look sleepily from their windows as we drove through the streets of the Surrey side. Passing down the Waterloo Bridge Road we crossed over the river, and dashing up Wellington Street wheeled sharply to the right and found ourselves in Bow Street. Sherlock Holmes was well known to the force, and the two constables at the door saluted him. One of them held the horse’s head while the other led us in.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who is on duty?” asked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Inspector Bradstreet, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, Bradstreet, how are you?” A tall, stout official had come down the stone-flagged passage, in a peaked cap and frogged jacket. “I wish to have a quiet word with you, Bradstreet.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly, Mr. Holmes. Step into my room here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a small, office-like room, with a huge ledger upon the table, and a telephone projecting from the wall. The inspector sat down at his desk.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What can I do for you, Mr. Holmes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I called about that beggarman, Boone—the one who was charged with being concerned in the disappearance of Mr. Neville St. Clair, of Lee.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. He was brought up and remanded for further inquiries.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So I heard. You have him here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the cells.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is he quiet?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, he gives no trouble. But he is a dirty scoundrel.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dirty?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it is all we can do to make him wash his hands, and his face is as black as a tinker’s. Well, when once his case has been settled, he will have a regular prison bath; and I think, if you saw him, you would agree with me that he needed it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should like to see him very much.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Would you? That is easily done. Come this way. You can leave your bag.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I think that I’ll take it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very good. Come this way, if you please.” He led us down a passage, opened a barred door, passed down a winding stair, and brought us to a whitewashed corridor with a line of doors on each side.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The third on the right is his,” said the inspector. “Here it is!” He quietly shot back a panel in the upper part of the door and glanced through.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is asleep,” said he. “You can see him very well.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We both put our eyes to the grating. The prisoner lay with his face towards us, in a very deep sleep, breathing slowly and heavily. He was a middle-sized man, coarsely clad as became his calling, with a coloured shirt protruding through the rent in his tattered coat. He was, as the inspector had said, extremely dirty, but the grime which covered his face could not conceal its repulsive ugliness. A broad wheal from an old scar ran right across it from eye to chin, and by its contraction had turned up one side of the upper lip, so that three teeth were exposed in a perpetual snarl. A shock of very bright red hair grew low over his eyes and forehead.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s a beauty, isn’t he?” said the inspector.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He certainly needs a wash,” remarked Holmes. “I had an idea that he might, and I took the liberty of bringing the tools with me.” He opened the Gladstone bag as he spoke, and took out, to my astonishment, a very large bath-sponge.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He! he! You are a funny one,” chuckled the inspector.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, if you will have the great goodness to open that door very quietly, we will soon make him cut a much more respectable figure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I don’t know why not,” said the inspector. “He doesn’t look a credit to the Bow Street cells, does he?” He slipped his key into the lock, and we all very quietly entered the cell. The sleeper half turned, and then settled down once more into a deep slumber. Holmes stooped to the water-jug, moistened his sponge, and then rubbed it twice vigorously across and down the prisoner’s face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let me introduce you,” he shouted, “to Mr. Neville St. Clair, of Lee, in the county of Kent.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Never in my life have I seen such a sight. The man’s face peeled off under the sponge like the bark from a tree. Gone was the coarse brown tint! Gone, too, was the horrid scar which had seamed it across, and the twisted lip which had given the repulsive sneer to the face! A twitch brought away the tangled red hair, and there, sitting up in his bed, was a pale, sad-faced, refined-looking man, black-haired and smooth-skinned, rubbing his eyes and staring about him with sleepy bewilderment. Then suddenly realising the exposure, he broke into a scream and threw himself down with his face to the pillow.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Great heavens!” cried the inspector, “it is, indeed, the missing man. I know him from the photograph.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The prisoner turned with the reckless air of a man who abandons himself to his destiny. “Be it so,” said he. “And pray what am I charged with?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“With making away with Mr. Neville St.— Oh, come, you can’t be charged with that unless they make a case of attempted suicide of it,” said the inspector with a grin. “Well, I have been twenty-seven years in the force, but this really takes the cake.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If I am Mr. Neville St. Clair, then it is obvious that no crime has been committed, and that, therefore, I am illegally detained.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No crime, but a very great error has been committed,” said Holmes. “You would have done better to have trusted your wife.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was not the wife; it was the children,” groaned the prisoner. “God help me, I would not have them ashamed of their father. My God! What an exposure! What can I do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes sat down beside him on the couch and patted him kindly on the shoulder.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you leave it to a court of law to clear the matter up,” said he, “of course you can hardly avoid publicity. On the other hand, if you convince the police authorities that there is no possible case against you, I do not know that there is any reason that the details should find their way into the papers. Inspector Bradstreet would, I am sure, make notes upon anything which you might tell us and submit it to the proper authorities. The case would then never go into court at all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“God bless you!” cried the prisoner passionately. “I would have endured imprisonment, ay, even execution, rather than have left my miserable secret as a family blot to my children.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are the first who have ever heard my story. My father was a schoolmaster in Chesterfield, where I received an excellent education. I travelled in my youth, took to the stage, and finally became a reporter on an evening paper in London. One day my editor wished to have a series of articles upon begging in the metropolis, and I volunteered to supply them. There was the point from which all my adventures started. It was only by trying begging as an amateur that I could get the facts upon which to base my articles. When an actor I had, of course, learned all the secrets of making up, and had been famous in the green-room for my skill. I took advantage now of my attainments. I painted my face, and to make myself as pitiable as possible I made a good scar and fixed one side of my lip in a twist by the aid of a small slip of flesh-coloured plaster. Then with a red head of hair, and an appropriate dress, I took my station in the business part of the city, ostensibly as a match-seller but really as a beggar. For seven hours I plied my trade, and when I returned home in the evening I found to my surprise that I had received no less than 26<i>s</i>. 4<i>d</i>.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I wrote my articles and thought little more of the matter until, some time later, I backed a bill for a friend and had a writ served upon me for £ 25. I was at my wit’s end where to get the money, but a sudden idea came to me. I begged a fortnight’s grace from the creditor, asked for a holiday from my employers, and spent the time in begging in the City under my disguise. In ten days I had the money and had paid the debt.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, you can imagine how hard it was to settle down to arduous work at £ 2 a week when I knew that I could earn as much in a day by smearing my face with a little paint, laying my cap on the ground, and sitting still. It was a long fight between my pride and the money, but the dollars won at last, and I threw up reporting and sat day after day in the corner which I had first chosen, inspiring pity by my ghastly face and filling my pockets with coppers. Only one man knew my secret. He was the keeper of a low den in which I used to lodge in Swandam Lane, where I could every morning emerge as a squalid beggar and in the evenings transform myself into a well-dressed man about town. This fellow, a Lascar, was well paid by me for his rooms, so that I knew that my secret was safe in his possession.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, very soon I found that I was saving considerable sums of money. I do not mean that any beggar in the streets of London could earn £ 700 a year—which is less than my average takings—but I had exceptional advantages in my power of making up, and also in a facility of repartee, which improved by practice and made me quite a recognised character in the City. All day a stream of pennies, varied by silver, poured in upon me, and it was a very bad day in which I failed to take £ 2.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As I grew richer I grew more ambitious, took a house in the country, and eventually married, without anyone having a suspicion as to my real occupation. My dear wife knew that I had business in the City. She little knew what.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Last Monday I had finished for the day and was dressing in my room above the opium den when I looked out of my window and saw, to my horror and astonishment, that my wife was standing in the street, with her eyes fixed full upon me. I gave a cry of surprise, threw up my arms to cover my face, and, rushing to my confidant, the Lascar, entreated him to prevent anyone from coming up to me. I heard her voice downstairs, but I knew that she could not ascend. Swiftly I threw off my clothes, pulled on those of a beggar, and put on my pigments and wig. Even a wife’s eyes could not pierce so complete a disguise. But then it occurred to me that there might be a search in the room, and that the clothes might betray me. I threw open the window, reopening by my violence a small cut which I had inflicted upon myself in the bedroom that morning. Then I seized my coat, which was weighted by the coppers which I had just transferred to it from the leather bag in which I carried my takings. I hurled it out of the window, and it disappeared into the Thames. The other clothes would have followed, but at that moment there was a rush of constables up the stair, and a few minutes after I found, rather, I confess, to my relief, that instead of being identified as Mr. Neville St. Clair, I was arrested as his murderer.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not know that there is anything else for me to explain. I was determined to preserve my disguise as long as possible, and hence my preference for a dirty face. Knowing that my wife would be terribly anxious, I slipped off my ring and confided it to the Lascar at a moment when no constable was watching me, together with a hurried scrawl, telling her that she had no cause to fear.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That note only reached her yesterday,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good God! What a week she must have spent!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The police have watched this Lascar,” said Inspector Bradstreet, “and I can quite understand that he might find it difficult to post a letter unobserved. Probably he handed it to some sailor customer of his, who forgot all about it for some days.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That was it,” said Holmes, nodding approvingly; “I have no doubt of it. But have you never been prosecuted for begging?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Many times; but what was a fine to me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It must stop here, however,” said Bradstreet. “If the police are to hush this thing up, there must be no more of Hugh Boone.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have sworn it by the most solemn oaths which a man can take.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In that case I think that it is probable that no further steps may be taken. But if you are found again, then all must come out. I am sure, Mr. Holmes, that we are very much indebted to you for having cleared the matter up. I wish I knew how you reach your results.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I reached this one,” said my friend, “by sitting upon five pillows and consuming an ounce of shag. I think, Watson, that if we drive to Baker Street we shall just be in time for breakfast.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>VII.<br>\nTHE ADVENTURE OF THE BLUE CARBUNCLE</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">I</span> had called upon my friend Sherlock Holmes upon the second morning after Christmas, with the intention of wishing him the compliments of the season. He was lounging upon the sofa in a purple dressing-gown, a pipe-rack within his reach upon the right, and a pile of crumpled morning papers, evidently newly studied, near at hand. Beside the couch was a wooden chair, and on the angle of the back hung a very seedy and disreputable hard-felt hat, much the worse for wear, and cracked in several places. A lens and a forceps lying upon the seat of the chair suggested that the hat had been suspended in this manner for the purpose of examination.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are engaged,” said I; “perhaps I interrupt you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. I am glad to have a friend with whom I can discuss my results. The matter is a perfectly trivial one”—he jerked his thumb in the direction of the old hat—“but there are points in connection with it which are not entirely devoid of interest and even of instruction.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I seated myself in his armchair and warmed my hands before his crackling fire, for a sharp frost had set in, and the windows were thick with the ice crystals. “I suppose,” I remarked, “that, homely as it looks, this thing has some deadly story linked on to it—that it is the clue which will guide you in the solution of some mystery and the punishment of some crime.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no. No crime,” said Sherlock Holmes, laughing. “Only one of those whimsical little incidents which will happen when you have four million human beings all jostling each other within the space of a few square miles. Amid the action and reaction of so dense a swarm of humanity, every possible combination of events may be expected to take place, and many a little problem will be presented which may be striking and bizarre without being criminal. We have already had experience of such.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So much so,” I remarked, “that of the last six cases which I have added to my notes, three have been entirely free of any legal crime.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely. You allude to my attempt to recover the Irene Adler papers, to the singular case of Miss Mary Sutherland, and to the adventure of the man with the twisted lip. Well, I have no doubt that this small matter will fall into the same innocent category. You know Peterson, the commissionaire?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is to him that this trophy belongs.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is his hat.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, he found it. Its owner is unknown. I beg that you will look upon it not as a battered billycock but as an intellectual problem. And, first, as to how it came here. It arrived upon Christmas morning, in company with a good fat goose, which is, I have no doubt, roasting at this moment in front of Peterson’s fire. The facts are these: about four o’clock on Christmas morning, Peterson, who, as you know, is a very honest fellow, was returning from some small jollification and was making his way homeward down Tottenham Court Road. In front of him he saw, in the gaslight, a tallish man, walking with a slight stagger, and carrying a white goose slung over his shoulder. As he reached the corner of Goodge Street, a row broke out between this stranger and a little knot of roughs. One of the latter knocked off the man’s hat, on which he raised his stick to defend himself and, swinging it over his head, smashed the shop window behind him. Peterson had rushed forward to protect the stranger from his assailants; but the man, shocked at having broken the window, and seeing an official-looking person in uniform rushing towards him, dropped his goose, took to his heels, and vanished amid the labyrinth of small streets which lie at the back of Tottenham Court Road. The roughs had also fled at the appearance of Peterson, so that he was left in possession of the field of battle, and also of the spoils of victory in the shape of this battered hat and a most unimpeachable Christmas goose.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which surely he restored to their owner?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear fellow, there lies the problem. It is true that ‘For Mrs. Henry Baker’ was printed upon a small card which was tied to the bird’s left leg, and it is also true that the initials ‘H. B.’ are legible upon the lining of this hat, but as there are some thousands of Bakers, and some hundreds of Henry Bakers in this city of ours, it is not easy to restore lost property to any one of them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What, then, did Peterson do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He brought round both hat and goose to me on Christmas morning, knowing that even the smallest problems are of interest to me. The goose we retained until this morning, when there were signs that, in spite of the slight frost, it would be well that it should be eaten without unnecessary delay. Its finder has carried it off, therefore, to fulfil the ultimate destiny of a goose, while I continue to retain the hat of the unknown gentleman who lost his Christmas dinner.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did he not advertise?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, what clue could you have as to his identity?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Only as much as we can deduce.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“From his hat?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you are joking. What can you gather from this old battered felt?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here is my lens. You know my methods. What can you gather yourself as to the individuality of the man who has worn this article?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I took the tattered object in my hands and turned it over rather ruefully. It was a very ordinary black hat of the usual round shape, hard and much the worse for wear. The lining had been of red silk, but was a good deal discoloured. There was no maker’s name; but, as Holmes had remarked, the initials “H. B.” were scrawled upon one side. It was pierced in the brim for a hat-securer, but the elastic was missing. For the rest, it was cracked, exceedingly dusty, and spotted in several places, although there seemed to have been some attempt to hide the discoloured patches by smearing them with ink.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I can see nothing,” said I, handing it back to my friend.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary, Watson, you can see everything. You fail, however, to reason from what you see. You are too timid in drawing your inferences.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, pray tell me what it is that you can infer from this hat?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He picked it up and gazed at it in the peculiar introspective fashion which was characteristic of him. “It is perhaps less suggestive than it might have been,” he remarked, “and yet there are a few inferences which are very distinct, and a few others which represent at least a strong balance of probability. That the man was highly intellectual is of course obvious upon the face of it, and also that he was fairly well-to-do within the last three years, although he has now fallen upon evil days. He had foresight, but has less now than formerly, pointing to a moral retrogression, which, when taken with the decline of his fortunes, seems to indicate some evil influence, probably drink, at work upon him. This may account also for the obvious fact that his wife has ceased to love him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Holmes!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He has, however, retained some degree of self-respect,” he continued, disregarding my remonstrance. “He is a man who leads a sedentary life, goes out little, is out of training entirely, is middle-aged, has grizzled hair which he has had cut within the last few days, and which he anoints with lime-cream. These are the more patent facts which are to be deduced from his hat. Also, by the way, that it is extremely improbable that he has gas laid on in his house.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are certainly joking, Holmes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not in the least. Is it possible that even now, when I give you these results, you are unable to see how they are attained?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have no doubt that I am very stupid, but I must confess that I am unable to follow you. For example, how did you deduce that this man was intellectual?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For answer Holmes clapped the hat upon his head. It came right over the forehead and settled upon the bridge of his nose. “It is a question of cubic capacity,” said he; “a man with so large a brain must have something in it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The decline of his fortunes, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This hat is three years old. These flat brims curled at the edge came in then. It is a hat of the very best quality. Look at the band of ribbed silk and the excellent lining. If this man could afford to buy so expensive a hat three years ago, and has had no hat since, then he has assuredly gone down in the world.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, that is clear enough, certainly. But how about the foresight and the moral retrogression?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes laughed. “Here is the foresight,” said he putting his finger upon the little disc and loop of the hat-securer. “They are never sold upon hats. If this man ordered one, it is a sign of a certain amount of foresight, since he went out of his way to take this precaution against the wind. But since we see that he has broken the elastic and has not troubled to replace it, it is obvious that he has less foresight now than formerly, which is a distinct proof of a weakening nature. On the other hand, he has endeavoured to conceal some of these stains upon the felt by daubing them with ink, which is a sign that he has not entirely lost his self-respect.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your reasoning is certainly plausible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The further points, that he is middle-aged, that his hair is grizzled, that it has been recently cut, and that he uses lime-cream, are all to be gathered from a close examination of the lower part of the lining. The lens discloses a large number of hair-ends, clean cut by the scissors of the barber. They all appear to be adhesive, and there is a distinct odour of lime-cream. This dust, you will observe, is not the gritty, grey dust of the street but the fluffy brown dust of the house, showing that it has been hung up indoors most of the time, while the marks of moisture upon the inside are proof positive that the wearer perspired very freely, and could therefore, hardly be in the best of training.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But his wife—you said that she had ceased to love him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This hat has not been brushed for weeks. When I see you, my dear Watson, with a week’s accumulation of dust upon your hat, and when your wife allows you to go out in such a state, I shall fear that you also have been unfortunate enough to lose your wife’s affection.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But he might be a bachelor.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nay, he was bringing home the goose as a peace-offering to his wife. Remember the card upon the bird’s leg.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have an answer to everything. But how on earth do you deduce that the gas is not laid on in his house?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One tallow stain, or even two, might come by chance; but when I see no less than five, I think that there can be little doubt that the individual must be brought into frequent contact with burning tallow—walks upstairs at night probably with his hat in one hand and a guttering candle in the other. Anyhow, he never got tallow-stains from a gas-jet. Are you satisfied?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it is very ingenious,” said I, laughing; “but since, as you said just now, there has been no crime committed, and no harm done save the loss of a goose, all this seems to be rather a waste of energy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes had opened his mouth to reply, when the door flew open, and Peterson, the commissionaire, rushed into the apartment with flushed cheeks and the face of a man who is dazed with astonishment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The goose, Mr. Holmes! The goose, sir!” he gasped.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Eh? What of it, then? Has it returned to life and flapped off through the kitchen window?” Holmes twisted himself round upon the sofa to get a fairer view of the man’s excited face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“See here, sir! See what my wife found in its crop!” He held out his hand and displayed upon the centre of the palm a brilliantly scintillating blue stone, rather smaller than a bean in size, but of such purity and radiance that it twinkled like an electric point in the dark hollow of his hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes sat up with a whistle. “By Jove, Peterson!” said he, “this is treasure trove indeed. I suppose you know what you have got?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A diamond, sir? A precious stone. It cuts into glass as though it were putty.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s more than a precious stone. It is <i>the</i> precious stone.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not the Countess of Morcar’s blue carbuncle!” I ejaculated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely so. I ought to know its size and shape, seeing that I have read the advertisement about it in <i>The Times</i> every day lately. It is absolutely unique, and its value can only be conjectured, but the reward offered of £ 1000 is certainly not within a twentieth part of the market price.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A thousand pounds! Great Lord of mercy!” The commissionaire plumped down into a chair and stared from one to the other of us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is the reward, and I have reason to know that there are sentimental considerations in the background which would induce the Countess to part with half her fortune if she could but recover the gem.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was lost, if I remember aright, at the Hotel Cosmopolitan,” I remarked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely so, on December 22nd, just five days ago. John Horner, a plumber, was accused of having abstracted it from the lady’s jewel-case. The evidence against him was so strong that the case has been referred to the Assizes. I have some account of the matter here, I believe.” He rummaged amid his newspapers, glancing over the dates, until at last he smoothed one out, doubled it over, and read the following paragraph:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hotel Cosmopolitan Jewel Robbery. John Horner, 26, plumber, was brought up upon the charge of having upon the 22nd inst., abstracted from the jewel-case of the Countess of Morcar the valuable gem known as the blue carbuncle. James Ryder, upper-attendant at the hotel, gave his evidence to the effect that he had shown Horner up to the dressing-room of the Countess of Morcar upon the day of the robbery in order that he might solder the second bar of the grate, which was loose. He had remained with Horner some little time, but had finally been called away. On returning, he found that Horner had disappeared, that the bureau had been forced open, and that the small morocco casket in which, as it afterwards transpired, the Countess was accustomed to keep her jewel, was lying empty upon the dressing-table. Ryder instantly gave the alarm, and Horner was arrested the same evening; but the stone could not be found either upon his person or in his rooms. Catherine Cusack, maid to the Countess, deposed to having heard Ryder’s cry of dismay on discovering the robbery, and to having rushed into the room, where she found matters as described by the last witness. Inspector Bradstreet, B division, gave evidence as to the arrest of Horner, who struggled frantically, and protested his innocence in the strongest terms. Evidence of a previous conviction for robbery having been given against the prisoner, the magistrate refused to deal summarily with the offence, but referred it to the Assizes. Horner, who had shown signs of intense emotion during the proceedings, fainted away at the conclusion and was carried out of court.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hum! So much for the police-court,” said Holmes thoughtfully, tossing aside the paper. “The question for us now to solve is the sequence of events leading from a rifled jewel-case at one end to the crop of a goose in Tottenham Court Road at the other. You see, Watson, our little deductions have suddenly assumed a much more important and less innocent aspect. Here is the stone; the stone came from the goose, and the goose came from Mr. Henry Baker, the gentleman with the bad hat and all the other characteristics with which I have bored you. So now we must set ourselves very seriously to finding this gentleman and ascertaining what part he has played in this little mystery. To do this, we must try the simplest means first, and these lie undoubtedly in an advertisement in all the evening papers. If this fail, I shall have recourse to other methods.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What will you say?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Give me a pencil and that slip of paper. Now, then: ‘Found at the corner of Goodge Street, a goose and a black felt hat. Mr. Henry Baker can have the same by applying at 6:30 this evening at 221B, Baker Street.’ That is clear and concise.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very. But will he see it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, he is sure to keep an eye on the papers, since, to a poor man, the loss was a heavy one. He was clearly so scared by his mischance in breaking the window and by the approach of Peterson that he thought of nothing but flight, but since then he must have bitterly regretted the impulse which caused him to drop his bird. Then, again, the introduction of his name will cause him to see it, for everyone who knows him will direct his attention to it. Here you are, Peterson, run down to the advertising agency and have this put in the evening papers.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In which, sir?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, in the <i>Globe</i>, <i>Star</i>, <i>Pall Mall</i>, <i>St. James’s Gazette</i>, <i>Evening News</i>, <i>Standard</i>, <i>Echo</i>, and any others that occur to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well, sir. And this stone?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, yes, I shall keep the stone. Thank you. And, I say, Peterson, just buy a goose on your way back and leave it here with me, for we must have one to give to this gentleman in place of the one which your family is now devouring.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>When the commissionaire had gone, Holmes took up the stone and held it against the light. “It’s a bonny thing,” said he. “Just see how it glints and sparkles. Of course it is a nucleus and focus of crime. Every good stone is. They are the devil’s pet baits. In the larger and older jewels every facet may stand for a bloody deed. This stone is not yet twenty years old. It was found in the banks of the Amoy River in southern China and is remarkable in having every characteristic of the carbuncle, save that it is blue in shade instead of ruby red. In spite of its youth, it has already a sinister history. There have been two murders, a vitriol-throwing, a suicide, and several robberies brought about for the sake of this forty-grain weight of crystallised charcoal. Who would think that so pretty a toy would be a purveyor to the gallows and the prison? I’ll lock it up in my strong box now and drop a line to the Countess to say that we have it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you think that this man Horner is innocent?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot tell.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, then, do you imagine that this other one, Henry Baker, had anything to do with the matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is, I think, much more likely that Henry Baker is an absolutely innocent man, who had no idea that the bird which he was carrying was of considerably more value than if it were made of solid gold. That, however, I shall determine by a very simple test if we have an answer to our advertisement.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you can do nothing until then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In that case I shall continue my professional round. But I shall come back in the evening at the hour you have mentioned, for I should like to see the solution of so tangled a business.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very glad to see you. I dine at seven. There is a woodcock, I believe. By the way, in view of recent occurrences, perhaps I ought to ask Mrs. Hudson to examine its crop.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had been delayed at a case, and it was a little after half-past six when I found myself in Baker Street once more. As I approached the house I saw a tall man in a Scotch bonnet with a coat which was buttoned up to his chin waiting outside in the bright semicircle which was thrown from the fanlight. Just as I arrived the door was opened, and we were shown up together to Holmes’ room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Henry Baker, I believe,” said he, rising from his armchair and greeting his visitor with the easy air of geniality which he could so readily assume. “Pray take this chair by the fire, Mr. Baker. It is a cold night, and I observe that your circulation is more adapted for summer than for winter. Ah, Watson, you have just come at the right time. Is that your hat, Mr. Baker?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, that is undoubtedly my hat.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He was a large man with rounded shoulders, a massive head, and a broad, intelligent face, sloping down to a pointed beard of grizzled brown. A touch of red in nose and cheeks, with a slight tremor of his extended hand, recalled Holmes’ surmise as to his habits. His rusty black frock-coat was buttoned right up in front, with the collar turned up, and his lank wrists protruded from his sleeves without a sign of cuff or shirt. He spoke in a slow staccato fashion, choosing his words with care, and gave the impression generally of a man of learning and letters who had had ill-usage at the hands of fortune.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have retained these things for some days,” said Holmes, “because we expected to see an advertisement from you giving your address. I am at a loss to know now why you did not advertise.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our visitor gave a rather shamefaced laugh. “Shillings have not been so plentiful with me as they once were,” he remarked. “I had no doubt that the gang of roughs who assaulted me had carried off both my hat and the bird. I did not care to spend more money in a hopeless attempt at recovering them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very naturally. By the way, about the bird, we were compelled to eat it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To eat it!” Our visitor half rose from his chair in his excitement.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it would have been of no use to anyone had we not done so. But I presume that this other goose upon the sideboard, which is about the same weight and perfectly fresh, will answer your purpose equally well?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, certainly, certainly,” answered Mr. Baker with a sigh of relief.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course, we still have the feathers, legs, crop, and so on of your own bird, so if you wish—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man burst into a hearty laugh. “They might be useful to me as relics of my adventure,” said he, “but beyond that I can hardly see what use the <i>disjecta membra</i> of my late acquaintance are going to be to me. No, sir, I think that, with your permission, I will confine my attentions to the excellent bird which I perceive upon the sideboard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes glanced sharply across at me with a slight shrug of his shoulders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is your hat, then, and there your bird,” said he. “By the way, would it bore you to tell me where you got the other one from? I am somewhat of a fowl fancier, and I have seldom seen a better grown goose.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly, sir,” said Baker, who had risen and tucked his newly gained property under his arm. “There are a few of us who frequent the Alpha Inn, near the Museum—we are to be found in the Museum itself during the day, you understand. This year our good host, Windigate by name, instituted a goose club, by which, on consideration of some few pence every week, we were each to receive a bird at Christmas. My pence were duly paid, and the rest is familiar to you. I am much indebted to you, sir, for a Scotch bonnet is fitted neither to my years nor my gravity.” With a comical pomposity of manner he bowed solemnly to both of us and strode off upon his way.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So much for Mr. Henry Baker,” said Holmes when he had closed the door behind him. “It is quite certain that he knows nothing whatever about the matter. Are you hungry, Watson?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not particularly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I suggest that we turn our dinner into a supper and follow up this clue while it is still hot.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By all means.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a bitter night, so we drew on our ulsters and wrapped cravats about our throats. Outside, the stars were shining coldly in a cloudless sky, and the breath of the passers-by blew out into smoke like so many pistol shots. Our footfalls rang out crisply and loudly as we swung through the doctors’ quarter, Wimpole Street, Harley Street, and so through Wigmore Street into Oxford Street. In a quarter of an hour we were in Bloomsbury at the Alpha Inn, which is a small public-house at the corner of one of the streets which runs down into Holborn. Holmes pushed open the door of the private bar and ordered two glasses of beer from the ruddy-faced, white-aproned landlord.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your beer should be excellent if it is as good as your geese,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My geese!” The man seemed surprised.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I was speaking only half an hour ago to Mr. Henry Baker, who was a member of your goose club.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! yes, I see. But you see, sir, them’s not <i>our</i> geese.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed! Whose, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I got the two dozen from a salesman in Covent Garden.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed? I know some of them. Which was it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Breckinridge is his name.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! I don’t know him. Well, here’s your good health landlord, and prosperity to your house. Good-night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now for Mr. Breckinridge,” he continued, buttoning up his coat as we came out into the frosty air. “Remember, Watson that though we have so homely a thing as a goose at one end of this chain, we have at the other a man who will certainly get seven years’ penal servitude unless we can establish his innocence. It is possible that our inquiry may but confirm his guilt; but, in any case, we have a line of investigation which has been missed by the police, and which a singular chance has placed in our hands. Let us follow it out to the bitter end. Faces to the south, then, and quick march!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We passed across Holborn, down Endell Street, and so through a zigzag of slums to Covent Garden Market. One of the largest stalls bore the name of Breckinridge upon it, and the proprietor a horsey-looking man, with a sharp face and trim side-whiskers was helping a boy to put up the shutters.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good-evening. It’s a cold night,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The salesman nodded and shot a questioning glance at my companion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Sold out of geese, I see,” continued Holmes, pointing at the bare slabs of marble.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let you have five hundred to-morrow morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s no good.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, there are some on the stall with the gas-flare.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, but I was recommended to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who by?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The landlord of the Alpha.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes; I sent him a couple of dozen.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Fine birds they were, too. Now where did you get them from?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>To my surprise the question provoked a burst of anger from the salesman.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, then, mister,” said he, with his head cocked and his arms akimbo, “what are you driving at? Let’s have it straight, now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is straight enough. I should like to know who sold you the geese which you supplied to the Alpha.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well then, I shan’t tell you. So now!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, it is a matter of no importance; but I don’t know why you should be so warm over such a trifle.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Warm! You’d be as warm, maybe, if you were as pestered as I am. When I pay good money for a good article there should be an end of the business; but it’s ‘Where are the geese?’ and ‘Who did you sell the geese to?’ and ‘What will you take for the geese?’ One would think they were the only geese in the world, to hear the fuss that is made over them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I have no connection with any other people who have been making inquiries,” said Holmes carelessly. “If you won’t tell us the bet is off, that is all. But I’m always ready to back my opinion on a matter of fowls, and I have a fiver on it that the bird I ate is country bred.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, then, you’ve lost your fiver, for it’s town bred,” snapped the salesman.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s nothing of the kind.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I say it is.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t believe it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“D’you think you know more about fowls than I, who have handled them ever since I was a nipper? I tell you, all those birds that went to the Alpha were town bred.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’ll never persuade me to believe that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Will you bet, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s merely taking your money, for I know that I am right. But I’ll have a sovereign on with you, just to teach you not to be obstinate.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The salesman chuckled grimly. “Bring me the books, Bill,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The small boy brought round a small thin volume and a great greasy-backed one, laying them out together beneath the hanging lamp.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now then, Mr. Cocksure,” said the salesman, “I thought that I was out of geese, but before I finish you’ll find that there is still one left in my shop. You see this little book?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s the list of the folk from whom I buy. D’you see? Well, then, here on this page are the country folk, and the numbers after their names are where their accounts are in the big ledger. Now, then! You see this other page in red ink? Well, that is a list of my town suppliers. Now, look at that third name. Just read it out to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mrs. Oakshott, 117, Brixton Road—249,” read Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. Now turn that up in the ledger.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes turned to the page indicated. “Here you are, ‘Mrs. Oakshott, 117, Brixton Road, egg and poultry supplier.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, then, what’s the last entry?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘December 22nd. Twenty-four geese at 7<i>s</i>. 6<i>d</i>.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. There you are. And underneath?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Sold to Mr. Windigate of the Alpha, at 12<i>s</i>.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What have you to say now?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes looked deeply chagrined. He drew a sovereign from his pocket and threw it down upon the slab, turning away with the air of a man whose disgust is too deep for words. A few yards off he stopped under a lamp-post and laughed in the hearty, noiseless fashion which was peculiar to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When you see a man with whiskers of that cut and the ‘Pink ’un’ protruding out of his pocket, you can always draw him by a bet,” said he. “I daresay that if I had put £ 100 down in front of him, that man would not have given me such complete information as was drawn from him by the idea that he was doing me on a wager. Well, Watson, we are, I fancy, nearing the end of our quest, and the only point which remains to be determined is whether we should go on to this Mrs. Oakshott to-night, or whether we should reserve it for to-morrow. It is clear from what that surly fellow said that there are others besides ourselves who are anxious about the matter, and I should—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>His remarks were suddenly cut short by a loud hubbub which broke out from the stall which we had just left. Turning round we saw a little rat-faced fellow standing in the centre of the circle of yellow light which was thrown by the swinging lamp, while Breckinridge, the salesman, framed in the door of his stall, was shaking his fists fiercely at the cringing figure.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ve had enough of you and your geese,” he shouted. “I wish you were all at the devil together. If you come pestering me any more with your silly talk I’ll set the dog at you. You bring Mrs. Oakshott here and I’ll answer her, but what have you to do with it? Did I buy the geese off you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No; but one of them was mine all the same,” whined the little man.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, then, ask Mrs. Oakshott for it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She told me to ask you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, you can ask the King of Proosia, for all I care. I’ve had enough of it. Get out of this!” He rushed fiercely forward, and the inquirer flitted away into the darkness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha! this may save us a visit to Brixton Road,” whispered Holmes. “Come with me, and we will see what is to be made of this fellow.” Striding through the scattered knots of people who lounged round the flaring stalls, my companion speedily overtook the little man and touched him upon the shoulder. He sprang round, and I could see in the gas-light that every vestige of colour had been driven from his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who are you, then? What do you want?” he asked in a quavering voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will excuse me,” said Holmes blandly, “but I could not help overhearing the questions which you put to the salesman just now. I think that I could be of assistance to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You? Who are you? How could you know anything of the matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My name is Sherlock Holmes. It is my business to know what other people don’t know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you can know nothing of this?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excuse me, I know everything of it. You are endeavouring to trace some geese which were sold by Mrs. Oakshott, of Brixton Road, to a salesman named Breckinridge, by him in turn to Mr. Windigate, of the Alpha, and by him to his club, of which Mr. Henry Baker is a member.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, sir, you are the very man whom I have longed to meet,” cried the little fellow with outstretched hands and quivering fingers. “I can hardly explain to you how interested I am in this matter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes hailed a four-wheeler which was passing. “In that case we had better discuss it in a cosy room rather than in this wind-swept market-place,” said he. “But pray tell me, before we go farther, who it is that I have the pleasure of assisting.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man hesitated for an instant. “My name is John Robinson,” he answered with a sidelong glance.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no; the real name,” said Holmes sweetly. “It is always awkward doing business with an alias.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A flush sprang to the white cheeks of the stranger. “Well then,” said he, “my real name is James Ryder.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely so. Head attendant at the Hotel Cosmopolitan. Pray step into the cab, and I shall soon be able to tell you everything which you would wish to know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The little man stood glancing from one to the other of us with half-frightened, half-hopeful eyes, as one who is not sure whether he is on the verge of a windfall or of a catastrophe. Then he stepped into the cab, and in half an hour we were back in the sitting-room at Baker Street. Nothing had been said during our drive, but the high, thin breathing of our new companion, and the claspings and unclaspings of his hands, spoke of the nervous tension within him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here we are!” said Holmes cheerily as we filed into the room. “The fire looks very seasonable in this weather. You look cold, Mr. Ryder. Pray take the basket-chair. I will just put on my slippers before we settle this little matter of yours. Now, then! You want to know what became of those geese?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Or rather, I fancy, of that goose. It was one bird, I imagine in which you were interested—white, with a black bar across the tail.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Ryder quivered with emotion. “Oh, sir,” he cried, “can you tell me where it went to?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It came here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, and a most remarkable bird it proved. I don’t wonder that you should take an interest in it. It laid an egg after it was dead—the bonniest, brightest little blue egg that ever was seen. I have it here in my museum.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our visitor staggered to his feet and clutched the mantelpiece with his right hand. Holmes unlocked his strong-box and held up the blue carbuncle, which shone out like a star, with a cold, brilliant, many-pointed radiance. Ryder stood glaring with a drawn face, uncertain whether to claim or to disown it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The game’s up, Ryder,” said Holmes quietly. “Hold up, man, or you’ll be into the fire! Give him an arm back into his chair, Watson. He’s not got blood enough to go in for felony with impunity. Give him a dash of brandy. So! Now he looks a little more human. What a shrimp it is, to be sure!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For a moment he had staggered and nearly fallen, but the brandy brought a tinge of colour into his cheeks, and he sat staring with frightened eyes at his accuser.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have almost every link in my hands, and all the proofs which I could possibly need, so there is little which you need tell me. Still, that little may as well be cleared up to make the case complete. You had heard, Ryder, of this blue stone of the Countess of Morcar’s?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was Catherine Cusack who told me of it,” said he in a crackling voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see—her ladyship’s waiting-maid. Well, the temptation of sudden wealth so easily acquired was too much for you, as it has been for better men before you; but you were not very scrupulous in the means you used. It seems to me, Ryder, that there is the making of a very pretty villain in you. You knew that this man Horner, the plumber, had been concerned in some such matter before, and that suspicion would rest the more readily upon him. What did you do, then? You made some small job in my lady’s room—you and your confederate Cusack—and you managed that he should be the man sent for. Then, when he had left, you rifled the jewel-case, raised the alarm, and had this unfortunate man arrested. You then—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Ryder threw himself down suddenly upon the rug and clutched at my companion’s knees. “For God’s sake, have mercy!” he shrieked. “Think of my father! Of my mother! It would break their hearts. I never went wrong before! I never will again. I swear it. I’ll swear it on a Bible. Oh, don’t bring it into court! For Christ’s sake, don’t!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Get back into your chair!” said Holmes sternly. “It is very well to cringe and crawl now, but you thought little enough of this poor Horner in the dock for a crime of which he knew nothing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will fly, Mr. Holmes. I will leave the country, sir. Then the charge against him will break down.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hum! We will talk about that. And now let us hear a true account of the next act. How came the stone into the goose, and how came the goose into the open market? Tell us the truth, for there lies your only hope of safety.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Ryder passed his tongue over his parched lips. “I will tell you it just as it happened, sir,” said he. “When Horner had been arrested, it seemed to me that it would be best for me to get away with the stone at once, for I did not know at what moment the police might not take it into their heads to search me and my room. There was no place about the hotel where it would be safe. I went out, as if on some commission, and I made for my sister’s house. She had married a man named Oakshott, and lived in Brixton Road, where she fattened fowls for the market. All the way there every man I met seemed to me to be a policeman or a detective; and, for all that it was a cold night, the sweat was pouring down my face before I came to the Brixton Road. My sister asked me what was the matter, and why I was so pale; but I told her that I had been upset by the jewel robbery at the hotel. Then I went into the back yard and smoked a pipe and wondered what it would be best to do.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I had a friend once called Maudsley, who went to the bad, and has just been serving his time in Pentonville. One day he had met me, and fell into talk about the ways of thieves, and how they could get rid of what they stole. I knew that he would be true to me, for I knew one or two things about him; so I made up my mind to go right on to Kilburn, where he lived, and take him into my confidence. He would show me how to turn the stone into money. But how to get to him in safety? I thought of the agonies I had gone through in coming from the hotel. I might at any moment be seized and searched, and there would be the stone in my waistcoat pocket. I was leaning against the wall at the time and looking at the geese which were waddling about round my feet, and suddenly an idea came into my head which showed me how I could beat the best detective that ever lived.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My sister had told me some weeks before that I might have the pick of her geese for a Christmas present, and I knew that she was always as good as her word. I would take my goose now, and in it I would carry my stone to Kilburn. There was a little shed in the yard, and behind this I drove one of the birds—a fine big one, white, with a barred tail. I caught it, and prying its bill open, I thrust the stone down its throat as far as my finger could reach. The bird gave a gulp, and I felt the stone pass along its gullet and down into its crop. But the creature flapped and struggled, and out came my sister to know what was the matter. As I turned to speak to her the brute broke loose and fluttered off among the others.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Whatever were you doing with that bird, Jem?’ says she.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well,’ said I, ‘you said you’d give me one for Christmas, and I was feeling which was the fattest.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh,’ says she, ‘we’ve set yours aside for you—Jem’s bird, we call it. It’s the big white one over yonder. There’s twenty-six of them, which makes one for you, and one for us, and two dozen for the market.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Thank you, Maggie,’ says I; ‘but if it is all the same to you, I’d rather have that one I was handling just now.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The other is a good three pound heavier,’ said she, ‘and we fattened it expressly for you.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Never mind. I’ll have the other, and I’ll take it now,’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, just as you like,’ said she, a little huffed. ‘Which is it you want, then?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘That white one with the barred tail, right in the middle of the flock.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, very well. Kill it and take it with you.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I did what she said, Mr. Holmes, and I carried the bird all the way to Kilburn. I told my pal what I had done, for he was a man that it was easy to tell a thing like that to. He laughed until he choked, and we got a knife and opened the goose. My heart turned to water, for there was no sign of the stone, and I knew that some terrible mistake had occurred. I left the bird, rushed back to my sister’s, and hurried into the back yard. There was not a bird to be seen there.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Where are they all, Maggie?’ I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Gone to the dealer’s, Jem.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Which dealer’s?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Breckinridge, of Covent Garden.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘But was there another with a barred tail?’ I asked, ‘the same as the one I chose?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, Jem; there were two barred-tailed ones, and I could never tell them apart.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, then, of course I saw it all, and I ran off as hard as my feet would carry me to this man Breckinridge; but he had sold the lot at once, and not one word would he tell me as to where they had gone. You heard him yourselves to-night. Well, he has always answered me like that. My sister thinks that I am going mad. Sometimes I think that I am myself. And now—and now I am myself a branded thief, without ever having touched the wealth for which I sold my character. God help me! God help me!” He burst into convulsive sobbing, with his face buried in his hands.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a long silence, broken only by his heavy breathing and by the measured tapping of Sherlock Holmes’ finger-tips upon the edge of the table. Then my friend rose and threw open the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Get out!” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What, sir! Oh, Heaven bless you!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No more words. Get out!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And no more words were needed. There was a rush, a clatter upon the stairs, the bang of a door, and the crisp rattle of running footfalls from the street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“After all, Watson,” said Holmes, reaching up his hand for his clay pipe, “I am not retained by the police to supply their deficiencies. If Horner were in danger it would be another thing; but this fellow will not appear against him, and the case must collapse. I suppose that I am commuting a felony, but it is just possible that I am saving a soul. This fellow will not go wrong again; he is too terribly frightened. Send him to gaol now, and you make him a gaol-bird for life. Besides, it is the season of forgiveness. Chance has put in our way a most singular and whimsical problem, and its solution is its own reward. If you will have the goodness to touch the bell, Doctor, we will begin another investigation, in which, also a bird will be the chief feature.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>VIII.<br>\nTHE ADVENTURE OF THE SPECKLED BAND</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">O</span>n glancing over my notes of the seventy odd cases in which I have during the last eight years studied the methods of my friend Sherlock Holmes, I find many tragic, some comic, a large number merely strange, but none commonplace; for, working as he did rather for the love of his art than for the acquirement of wealth, he refused to associate himself with any investigation which did not tend towards the unusual, and even the fantastic. Of all these varied cases, however, I cannot recall any which presented more singular features than that which was associated with the well-known Surrey family of the Roylotts of Stoke Moran. The events in question occurred in the early days of my association with Holmes, when we were sharing rooms as bachelors in Baker Street. It is possible that I might have placed them upon record before, but a promise of secrecy was made at the time, from which I have only been freed during the last month by the untimely death of the lady to whom the pledge was given. It is perhaps as well that the facts should now come to light, for I have reasons to know that there are widespread rumours as to the death of Dr. Grimesby Roylott which tend to make the matter even more terrible than the truth.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was early in April in the year ’83 that I woke one morning to find Sherlock Holmes standing, fully dressed, by the side of my bed. He was a late riser, as a rule, and as the clock on the mantelpiece showed me that it was only a quarter-past seven, I blinked up at him in some surprise, and perhaps just a little resentment, for I was myself regular in my habits.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very sorry to knock you up, Watson,” said he, “but it’s the common lot this morning. Mrs. Hudson has been knocked up, she retorted upon me, and I on you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it, then—a fire?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No; a client. It seems that a young lady has arrived in a considerable state of excitement, who insists upon seeing me. She is waiting now in the sitting-room. Now, when young ladies wander about the metropolis at this hour of the morning, and knock sleepy people up out of their beds, I presume that it is something very pressing which they have to communicate. Should it prove to be an interesting case, you would, I am sure, wish to follow it from the outset. I thought, at any rate, that I should call you and give you the chance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear fellow, I would not miss it for anything.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had no keener pleasure than in following Holmes in his professional investigations, and in admiring the rapid deductions, as swift as intuitions, and yet always founded on a logical basis with which he unravelled the problems which were submitted to him. I rapidly threw on my clothes and was ready in a few minutes to accompany my friend down to the sitting-room. A lady dressed in black and heavily veiled, who had been sitting in the window, rose as we entered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good-morning, madam,” said Holmes cheerily. “My name is Sherlock Holmes. This is my intimate friend and associate, Dr. Watson, before whom you can speak as freely as before myself. Ha! I am glad to see that Mrs. Hudson has had the good sense to light the fire. Pray draw up to it, and I shall order you a cup of hot coffee, for I observe that you are shivering.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is not cold which makes me shiver,” said the woman in a low voice, changing her seat as requested.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is fear, Mr. Holmes. It is terror.” She raised her veil as she spoke, and we could see that she was indeed in a pitiable state of agitation, her face all drawn and grey, with restless frightened eyes, like those of some hunted animal. Her features and figure were those of a woman of thirty, but her hair was shot with premature grey, and her expression was weary and haggard. Sherlock Holmes ran her over with one of his quick, all-comprehensive glances.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You must not fear,” said he soothingly, bending forward and patting her forearm. “We shall soon set matters right, I have no doubt. You have come in by train this morning, I see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You know me, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but I observe the second half of a return ticket in the palm of your left glove. You must have started early, and yet you had a good drive in a dog-cart, along heavy roads, before you reached the station.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The lady gave a violent start and stared in bewilderment at my companion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is no mystery, my dear madam,” said he, smiling. “The left arm of your jacket is spattered with mud in no less than seven places. The marks are perfectly fresh. There is no vehicle save a dog-cart which throws up mud in that way, and then only when you sit on the left-hand side of the driver.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Whatever your reasons may be, you are perfectly correct,” said she. “I started from home before six, reached Leatherhead at twenty past, and came in by the first train to Waterloo. Sir, I can stand this strain no longer; I shall go mad if it continues. I have no one to turn to—none, save only one, who cares for me, and he, poor fellow, can be of little aid. I have heard of you, Mr. Holmes; I have heard of you from Mrs. Farintosh, whom you helped in the hour of her sore need. It was from her that I had your address. Oh, sir, do you not think that you could help me, too, and at least throw a little light through the dense darkness which surrounds me? At present it is out of my power to reward you for your services, but in a month or six weeks I shall be married, with the control of my own income, and then at least you shall not find me ungrateful.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes turned to his desk and, unlocking it, drew out a small case-book, which he consulted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Farintosh,” said he. “Ah yes, I recall the case; it was concerned with an opal tiara. I think it was before your time, Watson. I can only say, madam, that I shall be happy to devote the same care to your case as I did to that of your friend. As to reward, my profession is its own reward; but you are at liberty to defray whatever expenses I may be put to, at the time which suits you best. And now I beg that you will lay before us everything that may help us in forming an opinion upon the matter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Alas!” replied our visitor, “the very horror of my situation lies in the fact that my fears are so vague, and my suspicions depend so entirely upon small points, which might seem trivial to another, that even he to whom of all others I have a right to look for help and advice looks upon all that I tell him about it as the fancies of a nervous woman. He does not say so, but I can read it from his soothing answers and averted eyes. But I have heard, Mr. Holmes, that you can see deeply into the manifold wickedness of the human heart. You may advise me how to walk amid the dangers which encompass me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am all attention, madam.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My name is Helen Stoner, and I am living with my stepfather, who is the last survivor of one of the oldest Saxon families in England, the Roylotts of Stoke Moran, on the western border of Surrey.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes nodded his head. “The name is familiar to me,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The family was at one time among the richest in England, and the estates extended over the borders into Berkshire in the north, and Hampshire in the west. In the last century, however, four successive heirs were of a dissolute and wasteful disposition, and the family ruin was eventually completed by a gambler in the days of the Regency. Nothing was left save a few acres of ground, and the two-hundred-year-old house, which is itself crushed under a heavy mortgage. The last squire dragged out his existence there, living the horrible life of an aristocratic pauper; but his only son, my stepfather, seeing that he must adapt himself to the new conditions, obtained an advance from a relative, which enabled him to take a medical degree and went out to Calcutta, where, by his professional skill and his force of character, he established a large practice. In a fit of anger, however, caused by some robberies which had been perpetrated in the house, he beat his native butler to death and narrowly escaped a capital sentence. As it was, he suffered a long term of imprisonment and afterwards returned to England a morose and disappointed man.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When Dr. Roylott was in India he married my mother, Mrs. Stoner, the young widow of Major-General Stoner, of the Bengal Artillery. My sister Julia and I were twins, and we were only two years old at the time of my mother’s re-marriage. She had a considerable sum of money—not less than £ 1000 a year—and this she bequeathed to Dr. Roylott entirely while we resided with him, with a provision that a certain annual sum should be allowed to each of us in the event of our marriage. Shortly after our return to England my mother died—she was killed eight years ago in a railway accident near Crewe. Dr. Roylott then abandoned his attempts to establish himself in practice in London and took us to live with him in the old ancestral house at Stoke Moran. The money which my mother had left was enough for all our wants, and there seemed to be no obstacle to our happiness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But a terrible change came over our stepfather about this time. Instead of making friends and exchanging visits with our neighbours, who had at first been overjoyed to see a Roylott of Stoke Moran back in the old family seat, he shut himself up in his house and seldom came out save to indulge in ferocious quarrels with whoever might cross his path. Violence of temper approaching to mania has been hereditary in the men of the family, and in my stepfather’s case it had, I believe, been intensified by his long residence in the tropics. A series of disgraceful brawls took place, two of which ended in the police-court, until at last he became the terror of the village, and the folks would fly at his approach, for he is a man of immense strength, and absolutely uncontrollable in his anger.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Last week he hurled the local blacksmith over a parapet into a stream, and it was only by paying over all the money which I could gather together that I was able to avert another public exposure. He had no friends at all save the wandering gipsies, and he would give these vagabonds leave to encamp upon the few acres of bramble-covered land which represent the family estate, and would accept in return the hospitality of their tents, wandering away with them sometimes for weeks on end. He has a passion also for Indian animals, which are sent over to him by a correspondent, and he has at this moment a cheetah and a baboon, which wander freely over his grounds and are feared by the villagers almost as much as their master.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You can imagine from what I say that my poor sister Julia and I had no great pleasure in our lives. No servant would stay with us, and for a long time we did all the work of the house. She was but thirty at the time of her death, and yet her hair had already begun to whiten, even as mine has.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your sister is dead, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She died just two years ago, and it is of her death that I wish to speak to you. You can understand that, living the life which I have described, we were little likely to see anyone of our own age and position. We had, however, an aunt, my mother’s maiden sister, Miss Honoria Westphail, who lives near Harrow, and we were occasionally allowed to pay short visits at this lady’s house. Julia went there at Christmas two years ago, and met there a half-pay major of marines, to whom she became engaged. My stepfather learned of the engagement when my sister returned and offered no objection to the marriage; but within a fortnight of the day which had been fixed for the wedding, the terrible event occurred which has deprived me of my only companion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes had been leaning back in his chair with his eyes closed and his head sunk in a cushion, but he half opened his lids now and glanced across at his visitor.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray be precise as to details,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is easy for me to be so, for every event of that dreadful time is seared into my memory. The manor-house is, as I have already said, very old, and only one wing is now inhabited. The bedrooms in this wing are on the ground floor, the sitting-rooms being in the central block of the buildings. Of these bedrooms the first is Dr. Roylott’s, the second my sister’s, and the third my own. There is no communication between them, but they all open out into the same corridor. Do I make myself plain?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perfectly so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The windows of the three rooms open out upon the lawn. That fatal night Dr. Roylott had gone to his room early, though we knew that he had not retired to rest, for my sister was troubled by the smell of the strong Indian cigars which it was his custom to smoke. She left her room, therefore, and came into mine, where she sat for some time, chatting about her approaching wedding. At eleven o’clock she rose to leave me, but she paused at the door and looked back.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Tell me, Helen,’ said she, ‘have you ever heard anyone whistle in the dead of the night?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Never,’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I suppose that you could not possibly whistle, yourself, in your sleep?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Certainly not. But why?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000002999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Because during the last few nights I have always, about three in the morning, heard a low, clear whistle. I am a light sleeper, and it has awakened me. I cannot tell where it came from—perhaps from the next room, perhaps from the lawn. I thought that I would just ask you whether you had heard it.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, I have not. It must be those wretched gipsies in the plantation.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Very likely. And yet if it were on the lawn, I wonder that you did not hear it also.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Ah, but I sleep more heavily than you.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well, it is of no great consequence, at any rate.’ She smiled back at me, closed my door, and a few moments later I heard her key turn in the lock.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed,” said Holmes. “Was it your custom always to lock yourselves in at night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Always.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that I mentioned to you that the Doctor kept a cheetah and a baboon. We had no feeling of security unless our doors were locked.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. Pray proceed with your statement.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I could not sleep that night. A vague feeling of impending misfortune impressed me. My sister and I, you will recollect, were twins, and you know how subtle are the links which bind two souls which are so closely allied. It was a wild night. The wind was howling outside, and the rain was beating and splashing against the windows. Suddenly, amid all the hubbub of the gale, there burst forth the wild scream of a terrified woman. I knew that it was my sister’s voice. I sprang from my bed, wrapped a shawl round me, and rushed into the corridor. As I opened my door I seemed to hear a low whistle, such as my sister described, and a few moments later a clanging sound, as if a mass of metal had fallen. As I ran down the passage, my sister’s door was unlocked, and revolved slowly upon its hinges. I stared at it horror-stricken, not knowing what was about to issue from it. By the light of the corridor-lamp I saw my sister appear at the opening, her face blanched with terror, her hands groping for help, her whole figure swaying to and fro like that of a drunkard. I ran to her and threw my arms round her, but at that moment her knees seemed to give way and she fell to the ground. She writhed as one who is in terrible pain, and her limbs were dreadfully convulsed. At first I thought that she had not recognised me, but as I bent over her she suddenly shrieked out in a voice which I shall never forget, ‘Oh, my God! Helen! It was the band! The speckled band!’ There was something else which she would fain have said, and she stabbed with her finger into the air in the direction of the Doctor’s room, but a fresh convulsion seized her and choked her words. I rushed out, calling loudly for my stepfather, and I met him hastening from his room in his dressing-gown. When he reached my sister’s side she was unconscious, and though he poured brandy down her throat and sent for medical aid from the village, all efforts were in vain, for she slowly sank and died without having recovered her consciousness. Such was the dreadful end of my beloved sister.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One moment,” said Holmes, “are you sure about this whistle and metallic sound? Could you swear to it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That was what the county coroner asked me at the inquiry. It is my strong impression that I heard it, and yet, among the crash of the gale and the creaking of an old house, I may possibly have been deceived.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was your sister dressed?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, she was in her night-dress. In her right hand was found the charred stump of a match, and in her left a match-box.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Showing that she had struck a light and looked about her when the alarm took place. That is important. And what conclusions did the coroner come to?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He investigated the case with great care, for Dr. Roylott’s conduct had long been notorious in the county, but he was unable to find any satisfactory cause of death. My evidence showed that the door had been fastened upon the inner side, and the windows were blocked by old-fashioned shutters with broad iron bars, which were secured every night. The walls were carefully sounded, and were shown to be quite solid all round, and the flooring was also thoroughly examined, with the same result. The chimney is wide, but is barred up by four large staples. It is certain, therefore, that my sister was quite alone when she met her end. Besides, there were no marks of any violence upon her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How about poison?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The doctors examined her for it, but without success.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you think that this unfortunate lady died of, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is my belief that she died of pure fear and nervous shock, though what it was that frightened her I cannot imagine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Were there gipsies in the plantation at the time?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, there are nearly always some there.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, and what did you gather from this allusion to a band—a speckled band?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Sometimes I have thought that it was merely the wild talk of delirium, sometimes that it may have referred to some band of people, perhaps to these very gipsies in the plantation. I do not know whether the spotted handkerchiefs which so many of them wear over their heads might have suggested the strange adjective which she used.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes shook his head like a man who is far from being satisfied.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“These are very deep waters,” said he; “pray go on with your narrative.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Two years have passed since then, and my life has been until lately lonelier than ever. A month ago, however, a dear friend, whom I have known for many years, has done me the honour to ask my hand in marriage. His name is Armitage—Percy Armitage—the second son of Mr. Armitage, of Crane Water, near Reading. My stepfather has offered no opposition to the match, and we are to be married in the course of the spring. Two days ago some repairs were started in the west wing of the building, and my bedroom wall has been pierced, so that I have had to move into the chamber in which my sister died, and to sleep in the very bed in which she slept. Imagine, then, my thrill of terror when last night, as I lay awake, thinking over her terrible fate, I suddenly heard in the silence of the night the low whistle which had been the herald of her own death. I sprang up and lit the lamp, but nothing was to be seen in the room. I was too shaken to go to bed again, however, so I dressed, and as soon as it was daylight I slipped down, got a dog-cart at the Crown Inn, which is opposite, and drove to Leatherhead, from whence I have come on this morning with the one object of seeing you and asking your advice.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have done wisely,” said my friend. “But have you told me all?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Roylott, you have not. You are screening your stepfather.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, what do you mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For answer Holmes pushed back the frill of black lace which fringed the hand that lay upon our visitor’s knee. Five little livid spots, the marks of four fingers and a thumb, were printed upon the white wrist.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have been cruelly used,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The lady coloured deeply and covered over her injured wrist. “He is a hard man,” she said, “and perhaps he hardly knows his own strength.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a long silence, during which Holmes leaned his chin upon his hands and stared into the crackling fire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is a very deep business,” he said at last. “There are a thousand details which I should desire to know before I decide upon our course of action. Yet we have not a moment to lose. If we were to come to Stoke Moran to-day, would it be possible for us to see over these rooms without the knowledge of your stepfather?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As it happens, he spoke of coming into town to-day upon some most important business. It is probable that he will be away all day, and that there would be nothing to disturb you. We have a housekeeper now, but she is old and foolish, and I could easily get her out of the way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excellent. You are not averse to this trip, Watson?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By no means.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then we shall both come. What are you going to do yourself?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have one or two things which I would wish to do now that I am in town. But I shall return by the twelve o’clock train, so as to be there in time for your coming.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you may expect us early in the afternoon. I have myself some small business matters to attend to. Will you not wait and breakfast?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I must go. My heart is lightened already since I have confided my trouble to you. I shall look forward to seeing you again this afternoon.” She dropped her thick black veil over her face and glided from the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what do you think of it all, Watson?” asked Sherlock Holmes, leaning back in his chair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It seems to me to be a most dark and sinister business.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dark enough and sinister enough.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yet if the lady is correct in saying that the flooring and walls are sound, and that the door, window, and chimney are impassable, then her sister must have been undoubtedly alone when she met her mysterious end.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What becomes, then, of these nocturnal whistles, and what of the very peculiar words of the dying woman?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot think.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When you combine the ideas of whistles at night, the presence of a band of gipsies who are on intimate terms with this old doctor, the fact that we have every reason to believe that the doctor has an interest in preventing his stepdaughter’s marriage, the dying allusion to a band, and, finally, the fact that Miss Helen Stoner heard a metallic clang, which might have been caused by one of those metal bars that secured the shutters falling back into its place, I think that there is good ground to think that the mystery may be cleared along those lines.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what, then, did the gipsies do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot imagine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see many objections to any such theory.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And so do I. It is precisely for that reason that we are going to Stoke Moran this day. I want to see whether the objections are fatal, or if they may be explained away. But what in the name of the devil!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The ejaculation had been drawn from my companion by the fact that our door had been suddenly dashed open, and that a huge man had framed himself in the aperture. His costume was a peculiar mixture of the professional and of the agricultural, having a black top-hat, a long frock-coat, and a pair of high gaiters, with a hunting-crop swinging in his hand. So tall was he that his hat actually brushed the cross bar of the doorway, and his breadth seemed to span it across from side to side. A large face, seared with a thousand wrinkles, burned yellow with the sun, and marked with every evil passion, was turned from one to the other of us, while his deep-set, bile-shot eyes, and his high, thin, fleshless nose, gave him somewhat the resemblance to a fierce old bird of prey.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which of you is Holmes?” asked this apparition.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My name, sir; but you have the advantage of me,” said my companion quietly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am Dr. Grimesby Roylott, of Stoke Moran.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed, Doctor,” said Holmes blandly. “Pray take a seat.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will do nothing of the kind. My stepdaughter has been here. I have traced her. What has she been saying to you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is a little cold for the time of the year,” said Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What has she been saying to you?” screamed the old man furiously.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I have heard that the crocuses promise well,” continued my companion imperturbably.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha! You put me off, do you?” said our new visitor, taking a step forward and shaking his hunting-crop. “I know you, you scoundrel! I have heard of you before. You are Holmes, the meddler.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My friend smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Holmes, the busybody!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>His smile broadened.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Holmes, the Scotland Yard Jack-in-office!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes chuckled heartily. “Your conversation is most entertaining,” said he. “When you go out close the door, for there is a decided draught.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will go when I have had my say. Don’t you dare to meddle with my affairs. I know that Miss Stoner has been here. I traced her! I am a dangerous man to fall foul of! See here.” He stepped swiftly forward, seized the poker, and bent it into a curve with his huge brown hands.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“See that you keep yourself out of my grip,” he snarled, and hurling the twisted poker into the fireplace he strode out of the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He seems a very amiable person,” said Holmes, laughing. “I am not quite so bulky, but if he had remained I might have shown him that my grip was not much more feeble than his own.” As he spoke he picked up the steel poker and, with a sudden effort, straightened it out again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Fancy his having the insolence to confound me with the official detective force! This incident gives zest to our investigation, however, and I only trust that our little friend will not suffer from her imprudence in allowing this brute to trace her. And now, Watson, we shall order breakfast, and afterwards I shall walk down to Doctors’ Commons, where I hope to get some data which may help us in this matter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">It was nearly one o’clock when Sherlock Holmes returned from his excursion. He held in his hand a sheet of blue paper, scrawled over with notes and figures.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have seen the will of the deceased wife,” said he. “To determine its exact meaning I have been obliged to work out the present prices of the investments with which it is concerned. The total income, which at the time of the wife’s death was little short of £ 1,100, is now, through the fall in agricultural prices, not more than £ 750. Each daughter can claim an income of £ 250, in case of marriage. It is evident, therefore, that if both girls had married, this beauty would have had a mere pittance, while even one of them would cripple him to a very serious extent. My morning’s work has not been wasted, since it has proved that he has the very strongest motives for standing in the way of anything of the sort. And now, Watson, this is too serious for dawdling, especially as the old man is aware that we are interesting ourselves in his affairs; so if you are ready, we shall call a cab and drive to Waterloo. I should be very much obliged if you would slip your revolver into your pocket. An Eley’s No. 2 is an excellent argument with gentlemen who can twist steel pokers into knots. That and a tooth-brush are, I think, all that we need.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At Waterloo we were fortunate in catching a train for Leatherhead, where we hired a trap at the station inn and drove for four or five miles through the lovely Surrey lanes. It was a perfect day, with a bright sun and a few fleecy clouds in the heavens. The trees and wayside hedges were just throwing out their first green shoots, and the air was full of the pleasant smell of the moist earth. To me at least there was a strange contrast between the sweet promise of the spring and this sinister quest upon which we were engaged. My companion sat in the front of the trap, his arms folded, his hat pulled down over his eyes, and his chin sunk upon his breast, buried in the deepest thought. Suddenly, however, he started, tapped me on the shoulder, and pointed over the meadows.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look there!” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A heavily timbered park stretched up in a gentle slope, thickening into a grove at the highest point. From amid the branches there jutted out the grey gables and high roof-tree of a very old mansion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Stoke Moran?” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, that be the house of Dr. Grimesby Roylott,” remarked the driver.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is some building going on there,” said Holmes; “that is where we are going.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There’s the village,” said the driver, pointing to a cluster of roofs some distance to the left; “but if you want to get to the house, you’ll find it shorter to get over this stile, and so by the footpath over the fields. There it is, where the lady is walking.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the lady, I fancy, is Miss Stoner,” observed Holmes, shading his eyes. “Yes, I think we had better do as you suggest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We got off, paid our fare, and the trap rattled back on its way to Leatherhead.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I thought it as well,” said Holmes as we climbed the stile, “that this fellow should think we had come here as architects, or on some definite business. It may stop his gossip. Good-afternoon, Miss Stoner. You see that we have been as good as our word.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our client of the morning had hurried forward to meet us with a face which spoke her joy. “I have been waiting so eagerly for you,” she cried, shaking hands with us warmly. “All has turned out splendidly. Dr. Roylott has gone to town, and it is unlikely that he will be back before evening.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have had the pleasure of making the Doctor’s acquaintance,” said Holmes, and in a few words he sketched out what had occurred. Miss Stoner turned white to the lips as she listened.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” she cried, “he has followed me, then.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So it appears.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is so cunning that I never know when I am safe from him. What will he say when he returns?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He must guard himself, for he may find that there is someone more cunning than himself upon his track. You must lock yourself up from him to-night. If he is violent, we shall take you away to your aunt’s at Harrow. Now, we must make the best use of our time, so kindly take us at once to the rooms which we are to examine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The building was of grey, lichen-blotched stone, with a high central portion and two curving wings, like the claws of a crab, thrown out on each side. In one of these wings the windows were broken and blocked with wooden boards, while the roof was partly caved in, a picture of ruin. The central portion was in little better repair, but the right-hand block was comparatively modern, and the blinds in the windows, with the blue smoke curling up from the chimneys, showed that this was where the family resided. Some scaffolding had been erected against the end wall, and the stone-work had been broken into, but there were no signs of any workmen at the moment of our visit. Holmes walked slowly up and down the ill-trimmed lawn and examined with deep attention the outsides of the windows.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This, I take it, belongs to the room in which you used to sleep, the centre one to your sister’s, and the one next to the main building to Dr. Roylott’s chamber?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly so. But I am now sleeping in the middle one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pending the alterations, as I understand. By the way, there does not seem to be any very pressing need for repairs at that end wall.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There were none. I believe that it was an excuse to move me from my room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! that is suggestive. Now, on the other side of this narrow wing runs the corridor from which these three rooms open. There are windows in it, of course?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but very small ones. Too narrow for anyone to pass through.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As you both locked your doors at night, your rooms were unapproachable from that side. Now, would you have the kindness to go into your room and bar your shutters?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Stoner did so, and Holmes, after a careful examination through the open window, endeavoured in every way to force the shutter open, but without success. There was no slit through which a knife could be passed to raise the bar. Then with his lens he tested the hinges, but they were of solid iron, built firmly into the massive masonry. “Hum!” said he, scratching his chin in some perplexity, “my theory certainly presents some difficulties. No one could pass these shutters if they were bolted. Well, we shall see if the inside throws any light upon the matter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A small side door led into the whitewashed corridor from which the three bedrooms opened. Holmes refused to examine the third chamber, so we passed at once to the second, that in which Miss Stoner was now sleeping, and in which her sister had met with her fate. It was a homely little room, with a low ceiling and a gaping fireplace, after the fashion of old country-houses. A brown chest of drawers stood in one corner, a narrow white-counterpaned bed in another, and a dressing-table on the left-hand side of the window. These articles, with two small wicker-work chairs, made up all the furniture in the room save for a square of Wilton carpet in the centre. The boards round and the panelling of the walls were of brown, worm-eaten oak, so old and discoloured that it may have dated from the original building of the house. Holmes drew one of the chairs into a corner and sat silent, while his eyes travelled round and round and up and down, taking in every detail of the apartment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where does that bell communicate with?” he asked at last pointing to a thick bell-rope which hung down beside the bed, the tassel actually lying upon the pillow.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It goes to the housekeeper’s room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It looks newer than the other things?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it was only put there a couple of years ago.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your sister asked for it, I suppose?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I never heard of her using it. We used always to get what we wanted for ourselves.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed, it seemed unnecessary to put so nice a bell-pull there. You will excuse me for a few minutes while I satisfy myself as to this floor.” He threw himself down upon his face with his lens in his hand and crawled swiftly backward and forward, examining minutely the cracks between the boards. Then he did the same with the wood-work with which the chamber was panelled. Finally he walked over to the bed and spent some time in staring at it and in running his eye up and down the wall. Finally he took the bell-rope in his hand and gave it a brisk tug.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, it’s a dummy,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Won’t it ring?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, it is not even attached to a wire. This is very interesting. You can see now that it is fastened to a hook just above where the little opening for the ventilator is.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How very absurd! I never noticed that before.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very strange!” muttered Holmes, pulling at the rope. “There are one or two very singular points about this room. For example, what a fool a builder must be to open a ventilator into another room, when, with the same trouble, he might have communicated with the outside air!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is also quite modern,” said the lady.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Done about the same time as the bell-rope?” remarked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, there were several little changes carried out about that time.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They seem to have been of a most interesting character—dummy bell-ropes, and ventilators which do not ventilate. With your permission, Miss Stoner, we shall now carry our researches into the inner apartment.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dr. Grimesby Roylott’s chamber was larger than that of his step-daughter, but was as plainly furnished. A camp-bed, a small wooden shelf full of books, mostly of a technical character, an armchair beside the bed, a plain wooden chair against the wall, a round table, and a large iron safe were the principal things which met the eye. Holmes walked slowly round and examined each and all of them with the keenest interest.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What’s in here?” he asked, tapping the safe.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My stepfather’s business papers.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh! you have seen inside, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Only once, some years ago. I remember that it was full of papers.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There isn’t a cat in it, for example?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. What a strange idea!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, look at this!” He took up a small saucer of milk which stood on the top of it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No; we don’t keep a cat. But there is a cheetah and a baboon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, yes, of course! Well, a cheetah is just a big cat, and yet a saucer of milk does not go very far in satisfying its wants, I daresay. There is one point which I should wish to determine.” He squatted down in front of the wooden chair and examined the seat of it with the greatest attention.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. That is quite settled,” said he, rising and putting his lens in his pocket. “Hullo! Here is something interesting!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The object which had caught his eye was a small dog lash hung on one corner of the bed. The lash, however, was curled upon itself and tied so as to make a loop of whipcord.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you make of that, Watson?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s a common enough lash. But I don’t know why it should be tied.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is not quite so common, is it? Ah, me! it’s a wicked world, and when a clever man turns his brains to crime it is the worst of all. I think that I have seen enough now, Miss Stoner, and with your permission we shall walk out upon the lawn.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had never seen my friend’s face so grim or his brow so dark as it was when we turned from the scene of this investigation. We had walked several times up and down the lawn, neither Miss Stoner nor myself liking to break in upon his thoughts before he roused himself from his reverie.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is very essential, Miss Stoner,” said he, “that you should absolutely follow my advice in every respect.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall most certainly do so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The matter is too serious for any hesitation. Your life may depend upon your compliance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I assure you that I am in your hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the first place, both my friend and I must spend the night in your room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Both Miss Stoner and I gazed at him in astonishment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it must be so. Let me explain. I believe that that is the village inn over there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, that is the Crown.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very good. Your windows would be visible from there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You must confine yourself to your room, on pretence of a headache, when your stepfather comes back. Then when you hear him retire for the night, you must open the shutters of your window, undo the hasp, put your lamp there as a signal to us, and then withdraw quietly with everything which you are likely to want into the room which you used to occupy. I have no doubt that, in spite of the repairs, you could manage there for one night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, easily.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The rest you will leave in our hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what will you do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We shall spend the night in your room, and we shall investigate the cause of this noise which has disturbed you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I believe, Mr. Holmes, that you have already made up your mind,” said Miss Stoner, laying her hand upon my companion’s sleeve.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps I have.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, for pity’s sake, tell me what was the cause of my sister’s death.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should prefer to have clearer proofs before I speak.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You can at least tell me whether my own thought is correct, and if she died from some sudden fright.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I do not think so. I think that there was probably some more tangible cause. And now, Miss Stoner, we must leave you for if Dr. Roylott returned and saw us our journey would be in vain. Good-bye, and be brave, for if you will do what I have told you, you may rest assured that we shall soon drive away the dangers that threaten you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes and I had no difficulty in engaging a bedroom and sitting-room at the Crown Inn. They were on the upper floor, and from our window we could command a view of the avenue gate, and of the inhabited wing of Stoke Moran Manor House. At dusk we saw Dr. Grimesby Roylott drive past, his huge form looming up beside the little figure of the lad who drove him. The boy had some slight difficulty in undoing the heavy iron gates, and we heard the hoarse roar of the Doctor’s voice and saw the fury with which he shook his clinched fists at him. The trap drove on, and a few minutes later we saw a sudden light spring up among the trees as the lamp was lit in one of the sitting-rooms.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you know, Watson,” said Holmes as we sat together in the gathering darkness, “I have really some scruples as to taking you to-night. There is a distinct element of danger.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Can I be of assistance?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your presence might be invaluable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I shall certainly come.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is very kind of you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You speak of danger. You have evidently seen more in these rooms than was visible to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but I fancy that I may have deduced a little more. I imagine that you saw all that I did.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I saw nothing remarkable save the bell-rope, and what purpose that could answer I confess is more than I can imagine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You saw the ventilator, too?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but I do not think that it is such a very unusual thing to have a small opening between two rooms. It was so small that a rat could hardly pass through.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I knew that we should find a ventilator before ever we came to Stoke Moran.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Holmes!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, I did. You remember in her statement she said that her sister could smell Dr. Roylott’s cigar. Now, of course that suggested at once that there must be a communication between the two rooms. It could only be a small one, or it would have been remarked upon at the coroner’s inquiry. I deduced a ventilator.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what harm can there be in that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, there is at least a curious coincidence of dates. A ventilator is made, a cord is hung, and a lady who sleeps in the bed dies. Does not that strike you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot as yet see any connection.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you observe anything very peculiar about that bed?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was clamped to the floor. Did you ever see a bed fastened like that before?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot say that I have.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The lady could not move her bed. It must always be in the same relative position to the ventilator and to the rope—or so we may call it, since it was clearly never meant for a bell-pull.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Holmes,” I cried, “I seem to see dimly what you are hinting at. We are only just in time to prevent some subtle and horrible crime.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Subtle enough and horrible enough. When a doctor does go wrong he is the first of criminals. He has nerve and he has knowledge. Palmer and Pritchard were among the heads of their profession. This man strikes even deeper, but I think, Watson, that we shall be able to strike deeper still. But we shall have horrors enough before the night is over; for goodness’ sake let us have a quiet pipe and turn our minds for a few hours to something more cheerful.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">About nine o’clock the light among the trees was extinguished, and all was dark in the direction of the Manor House. Two hours passed slowly away, and then, suddenly, just at the stroke of eleven, a single bright light shone out right in front of us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is our signal,” said Holmes, springing to his feet; “it comes from the middle window.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we passed out he exchanged a few words with the landlord, explaining that we were going on a late visit to an acquaintance, and that it was possible that we might spend the night there. A moment later we were out on the dark road, a chill wind blowing in our faces, and one yellow light twinkling in front of us through the gloom to guide us on our sombre errand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was little difficulty in entering the grounds, for unrepaired breaches gaped in the old park wall. Making our way among the trees, we reached the lawn, crossed it, and were about to enter through the window when out from a clump of laurel bushes there darted what seemed to be a hideous and distorted child, who threw itself upon the grass with writhing limbs and then ran swiftly across the lawn into the darkness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My God!” I whispered; “did you see it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes was for the moment as startled as I. His hand closed like a vice upon my wrist in his agitation. Then he broke into a low laugh and put his lips to my ear.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is a nice household,” he murmured. “That is the baboon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had forgotten the strange pets which the Doctor affected. There was a cheetah, too; perhaps we might find it upon our shoulders at any moment. I confess that I felt easier in my mind when, after following Holmes’ example and slipping off my shoes, I found myself inside the bedroom. My companion noiselessly closed the shutters, moved the lamp onto the table, and cast his eyes round the room. All was as we had seen it in the daytime. Then creeping up to me and making a trumpet of his hand, he whispered into my ear again so gently that it was all that I could do to distinguish the words:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The least sound would be fatal to our plans.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I nodded to show that I had heard.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We must sit without light. He would see it through the ventilator.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I nodded again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do not go asleep; your very life may depend upon it. Have your pistol ready in case we should need it. I will sit on the side of the bed, and you in that chair.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I took out my revolver and laid it on the corner of the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes had brought up a long thin cane, and this he placed upon the bed beside him. By it he laid the box of matches and the stump of a candle. Then he turned down the lamp, and we were left in darkness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>How shall I ever forget that dreadful vigil? I could not hear a sound, not even the drawing of a breath, and yet I knew that my companion sat open-eyed, within a few feet of me, in the same state of nervous tension in which I was myself. The shutters cut off the least ray of light, and we waited in absolute darkness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>From outside came the occasional cry of a night-bird, and once at our very window a long drawn catlike whine, which told us that the cheetah was indeed at liberty. Far away we could hear the deep tones of the parish clock, which boomed out every quarter of an hour. How long they seemed, those quarters! Twelve struck, and one and two and three, and still we sat waiting silently for whatever might befall.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Suddenly there was the momentary gleam of a light up in the direction of the ventilator, which vanished immediately, but was succeeded by a strong smell of burning oil and heated metal. Someone in the next room had lit a dark-lantern. I heard a gentle sound of movement, and then all was silent once more, though the smell grew stronger. For half an hour I sat with straining ears. Then suddenly another sound became audible—a very gentle, soothing sound, like that of a small jet of steam escaping continually from a kettle. The instant that we heard it, Holmes sprang from the bed, struck a match, and lashed furiously with his cane at the bell-pull.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You see it, Watson?” he yelled. “You see it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But I saw nothing. At the moment when Holmes struck the light I heard a low, clear whistle, but the sudden glare flashing into my weary eyes made it impossible for me to tell what it was at which my friend lashed so savagely. I could, however, see that his face was deadly pale and filled with horror and loathing. He had ceased to strike and was gazing up at the ventilator when suddenly there broke from the silence of the night the most horrible cry to which I have ever listened. It swelled up louder and louder, a hoarse yell of pain and fear and anger all mingled in the one dreadful shriek. They say that away down in the village, and even in the distant parsonage, that cry raised the sleepers from their beds. It struck cold to our hearts, and I stood gazing at Holmes, and he at me, until the last echoes of it had died away into the silence from which it rose.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What can it mean?” I gasped.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It means that it is all over,” Holmes answered. “And perhaps, after all, it is for the best. Take your pistol, and we will enter Dr. Roylott’s room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a grave face he lit the lamp and led the way down the corridor. Twice he struck at the chamber door without any reply from within. Then he turned the handle and entered, I at his heels, with the cocked pistol in my hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a singular sight which met our eyes. On the table stood a dark-lantern with the shutter half open, throwing a brilliant beam of light upon the iron safe, the door of which was ajar. Beside this table, on the wooden chair, sat Dr. Grimesby Roylott clad in a long grey dressing-gown, his bare ankles protruding beneath, and his feet thrust into red heelless Turkish slippers. Across his lap lay the short stock with the long lash which we had noticed during the day. His chin was cocked upward and his eyes were fixed in a dreadful, rigid stare at the corner of the ceiling. Round his brow he had a peculiar yellow band, with brownish speckles, which seemed to be bound tightly round his head. As we entered he made neither sound nor motion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The band! the speckled band!” whispered Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I took a step forward. In an instant his strange headgear began to move, and there reared itself from among his hair the squat diamond-shaped head and puffed neck of a loathsome serpent.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is a swamp adder!” cried Holmes; “the deadliest snake in India. He has died within ten seconds of being bitten. Violence does, in truth, recoil upon the violent, and the schemer falls into the pit which he digs for another. Let us thrust this creature back into its den, and we can then remove Miss Stoner to some place of shelter and let the county police know what has happened.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As he spoke he drew the dog-whip swiftly from the dead man’s lap, and throwing the noose round the reptile’s neck he drew it from its horrid perch and, carrying it at arm’s length, threw it into the iron safe, which he closed upon it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">Such are the true facts of the death of Dr. Grimesby Roylott, of Stoke Moran. It is not necessary that I should prolong a narrative which has already run to too great a length by telling how we broke the sad news to the terrified girl, how we conveyed her by the morning train to the care of her good aunt at Harrow, of how the slow process of official inquiry came to the conclusion that the doctor met his fate while indiscreetly playing with a dangerous pet. The little which I had yet to learn of the case was told me by Sherlock Holmes as we travelled back next day.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I had,” said he, “come to an entirely erroneous conclusion which shows, my dear Watson, how dangerous it always is to reason from insufficient data. The presence of the gipsies, and the use of the word ‘band,’ which was used by the poor girl, no doubt, to explain the appearance which she had caught a hurried glimpse of by the light of her match, were sufficient to put me upon an entirely wrong scent. I can only claim the merit that I instantly reconsidered my position when, however, it became clear to me that whatever danger threatened an occupant of the room could not come either from the window or the door. My attention was speedily drawn, as I have already remarked to you, to this ventilator, and to the bell-rope which hung down to the bed. The discovery that this was a dummy, and that the bed was clamped to the floor, instantly gave rise to the suspicion that the rope was there as a bridge for something passing through the hole and coming to the bed. The idea of a snake instantly occurred to me, and when I coupled it with my knowledge that the doctor was furnished with a supply of creatures from India, I felt that I was probably on the right track. The idea of using a form of poison which could not possibly be discovered by any chemical test was just such a one as would occur to a clever and ruthless man who had had an Eastern training. The rapidity with which such a poison would take effect would also, from his point of view, be an advantage. It would be a sharp-eyed coroner, indeed, who could distinguish the two little dark punctures which would show where the poison fangs had done their work. Then I thought of the whistle. Of course he must recall the snake before the morning light revealed it to the victim. He had trained it, probably by the use of the milk which we saw, to return to him when summoned. He would put it through this ventilator at the hour that he thought best, with the certainty that it would crawl down the rope and land on the bed. It might or might not bite the occupant, perhaps she might escape every night for a week, but sooner or later she must fall a victim.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I had come to these conclusions before ever I had entered his room. An inspection of his chair showed me that he had been in the habit of standing on it, which of course would be necessary in order that he should reach the ventilator. The sight of the safe, the saucer of milk, and the loop of whipcord were enough to finally dispel any doubts which may have remained. The metallic clang heard by Miss Stoner was obviously caused by her stepfather hastily closing the door of his safe upon its terrible occupant. Having once made up my mind, you know the steps which I took in order to put the matter to the proof. I heard the creature hiss as I have no doubt that you did also, and I instantly lit the light and attacked it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“With the result of driving it through the ventilator.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And also with the result of causing it to turn upon its master at the other side. Some of the blows of my cane came home and roused its snakish temper, so that it flew upon the first person it saw. In this way I am no doubt indirectly responsible for Dr. Grimesby Roylott’s death, and I cannot say that it is likely to weigh very heavily upon my conscience.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>IX.<br>\nTHE ADVENTURE OF THE ENGINEER’S THUMB</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">O</span>f all the problems which have been submitted to my friend, Mr. Sherlock Holmes, for solution during the years of our intimacy, there were only two which I was the means of introducing to his notice—that of Mr. Hatherley’s thumb, and that of Colonel Warburton’s madness. Of these the latter may have afforded a finer field for an acute and original observer, but the other was so strange in its inception and so dramatic in its details that it may be the more worthy of being placed upon record, even if it gave my friend fewer openings for those deductive methods of reasoning by which he achieved such remarkable results. The story has, I believe, been told more than once in the newspapers, but, like all such narratives, its effect is much less striking when set forth <i>en bloc</i> in a single half-column of print than when the facts slowly evolve before your own eyes, and the mystery clears gradually away as each new discovery furnishes a step which leads on to the complete truth. At the time the circumstances made a deep impression upon me, and the lapse of two years has hardly served to weaken the effect.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was in the summer of ’89, not long after my marriage, that the events occurred which I am now about to summarise. I had returned to civil practice and had finally abandoned Holmes in his Baker Street rooms, although I continually visited him and occasionally even persuaded him to forgo his Bohemian habits so far as to come and visit us. My practice had steadily increased, and as I happened to live at no very great distance from Paddington Station, I got a few patients from among the officials. One of these, whom I had cured of a painful and lingering disease, was never weary of advertising my virtues and of endeavouring to send me on every sufferer over whom he might have any influence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>One morning, at a little before seven o’clock, I was awakened by the maid tapping at the door to announce that two men had come from Paddington and were waiting in the consulting-room. I dressed hurriedly, for I knew by experience that railway cases were seldom trivial, and hastened downstairs. As I descended, my old ally, the guard, came out of the room and closed the door tightly behind him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ve got him here,” he whispered, jerking his thumb over his shoulder; “he’s all right.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it, then?” I asked, for his manner suggested that it was some strange creature which he had caged up in my room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s a new patient,” he whispered. “I thought I’d bring him round myself; then he couldn’t slip away. There he is, all safe and sound. I must go now, Doctor; I have my dooties, just the same as you.” And off he went, this trusty tout, without even giving me time to thank him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I entered my consulting-room and found a gentleman seated by the table. He was quietly dressed in a suit of heather tweed with a soft cloth cap which he had laid down upon my books. Round one of his hands he had a handkerchief wrapped, which was mottled all over with bloodstains. He was young, not more than five-and-twenty, I should say, with a strong, masculine face; but he was exceedingly pale and gave me the impression of a man who was suffering from some strong agitation, which it took all his strength of mind to control.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am sorry to knock you up so early, Doctor,” said he, “but I have had a very serious accident during the night. I came in by train this morning, and on inquiring at Paddington as to where I might find a doctor, a worthy fellow very kindly escorted me here. I gave the maid a card, but I see that she has left it upon the side-table.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I took it up and glanced at it. “Mr. Victor Hatherley, hydraulic engineer, 16A, Victoria Street (3rd floor).” That was the name, style, and abode of my morning visitor. “I regret that I have kept you waiting,” said I, sitting down in my library-chair. “You are fresh from a night journey, I understand, which is in itself a monotonous occupation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, my night could not be called monotonous,” said he, and laughed. He laughed very heartily, with a high, ringing note, leaning back in his chair and shaking his sides. All my medical instincts rose up against that laugh.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Stop it!” I cried; “pull yourself together!” and I poured out some water from a caraffe.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was useless, however. He was off in one of those hysterical outbursts which come upon a strong nature when some great crisis is over and gone. Presently he came to himself once more, very weary and pale-looking.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have been making a fool of myself,” he gasped.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. Drink this.” I dashed some brandy into the water, and the colour began to come back to his bloodless cheeks.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s better!” said he. “And now, Doctor, perhaps you would kindly attend to my thumb, or rather to the place where my thumb used to be.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He unwound the handkerchief and held out his hand. It gave even my hardened nerves a shudder to look at it. There were four protruding fingers and a horrid red, spongy surface where the thumb should have been. It had been hacked or torn right out from the roots.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” I cried, “this is a terrible injury. It must have bled considerably.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it did. I fainted when it was done, and I think that I must have been senseless for a long time. When I came to I found that it was still bleeding, so I tied one end of my handkerchief very tightly round the wrist and braced it up with a twig.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excellent! You should have been a surgeon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is a question of hydraulics, you see, and came within my own province.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This has been done,” said I, examining the wound, “by a very heavy and sharp instrument.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A thing like a cleaver,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“An accident, I presume?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By no means.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What! a murderous attack?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very murderous indeed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You horrify me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I sponged the wound, cleaned it, dressed it, and finally covered it over with cotton wadding and carbolised bandages. He lay back without wincing, though he bit his lip from time to time.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How is that?” I asked when I had finished.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Capital! Between your brandy and your bandage, I feel a new man. I was very weak, but I have had a good deal to go through.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps you had better not speak of the matter. It is evidently trying to your nerves.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, no, not now. I shall have to tell my tale to the police; but, between ourselves, if it were not for the convincing evidence of this wound of mine, I should be surprised if they believed my statement, for it is a very extraordinary one, and I have not much in the way of proof with which to back it up; and, even if they believe me, the clues which I can give them are so vague that it is a question whether justice will be done.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha!” cried I, “if it is anything in the nature of a problem which you desire to see solved, I should strongly recommend you to come to my friend, Mr. Sherlock Holmes, before you go to the official police.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, I have heard of that fellow,” answered my visitor, “and I should be very glad if he would take the matter up, though of course I must use the official police as well. Would you give me an introduction to him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ll do better. I’ll take you round to him myself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should be immensely obliged to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We’ll call a cab and go together. We shall just be in time to have a little breakfast with him. Do you feel equal to it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; I shall not feel easy until I have told my story.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then my servant will call a cab, and I shall be with you in an instant.” I rushed upstairs, explained the matter shortly to my wife, and in five minutes was inside a hansom, driving with my new acquaintance to Baker Street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes was, as I expected, lounging about his sitting-room in his dressing-gown, reading the agony column of <i>The Times</i> and smoking his before-breakfast pipe, which was composed of all the plugs and dottles left from his smokes of the day before, all carefully dried and collected on the corner of the mantelpiece. He received us in his quietly genial fashion, ordered fresh rashers and eggs, and joined us in a hearty meal. When it was concluded he settled our new acquaintance upon the sofa, placed a pillow beneath his head, and laid a glass of brandy and water within his reach.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is easy to see that your experience has been no common one, Mr. Hatherley,” said he. “Pray, lie down there and make yourself absolutely at home. Tell us what you can, but stop when you are tired and keep up your strength with a little stimulant.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you,” said my patient, “but I have felt another man since the doctor bandaged me, and I think that your breakfast has completed the cure. I shall take up as little of your valuable time as possible, so I shall start at once upon my peculiar experiences.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes sat in his big armchair with the weary, heavy-lidded expression which veiled his keen and eager nature, while I sat opposite to him, and we listened in silence to the strange story which our visitor detailed to us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You must know,” said he, “that I am an orphan and a bachelor, residing alone in lodgings in London. By profession I am a hydraulic engineer, and I have had considerable experience of my work during the seven years that I was apprenticed to Venner &amp; Matheson, the well-known firm, of Greenwich. Two years ago, having served my time, and having also come into a fair sum of money through my poor father’s death, I determined to start in business for myself and took professional chambers in Victoria Street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I suppose that everyone finds his first independent start in business a dreary experience. To me it has been exceptionally so. During two years I have had three consultations and one small job, and that is absolutely all that my profession has brought me. My gross takings amount to £ 27 10<i>s</i>. Every day, from nine in the morning until four in the afternoon, I waited in my little den, until at last my heart began to sink, and I came to believe that I should never have any practice at all.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yesterday, however, just as I was thinking of leaving the office, my clerk entered to say there was a gentleman waiting who wished to see me upon business. He brought up a card, too, with the name of ‘Colonel Lysander Stark’ engraved upon it. Close at his heels came the colonel himself, a man rather over the middle size, but of an exceeding thinness. I do not think that I have ever seen so thin a man. His whole face sharpened away into nose and chin, and the skin of his cheeks was drawn quite tense over his outstanding bones. Yet this emaciation seemed to be his natural habit, and due to no disease, for his eye was bright, his step brisk, and his bearing assured. He was plainly but neatly dressed, and his age, I should judge, would be nearer forty than thirty.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Mr. Hatherley?’ said he, with something of a German accent. ‘You have been recommended to me, Mr. Hatherley, as being a man who is not only proficient in his profession but is also discreet and capable of preserving a secret.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I bowed, feeling as flattered as any young man would at such an address. ‘May I ask who it was who gave me so good a character?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well, perhaps it is better that I should not tell you that just at this moment. I have it from the same source that you are both an orphan and a bachelor and are residing alone in London.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘That is quite correct,’ I answered; ‘but you will excuse me if I say that I cannot see how all this bears upon my professional qualifications. I understand that it was on a professional matter that you wished to speak to me?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Undoubtedly so. But you will find that all I say is really to the point. I have a professional commission for you, but absolute secrecy is quite essential—absolute secrecy, you understand, and of course we may expect that more from a man who is alone than from one who lives in the bosom of his family.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘If I promise to keep a secret,’ said I, ‘you may absolutely depend upon my doing so.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He looked very hard at me as I spoke, and it seemed to me that I had never seen so suspicious and questioning an eye.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Do you promise, then?’ said he at last.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, I promise.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Absolute and complete silence before, during, and after? No reference to the matter at all, either in word or writing?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I have already given you my word.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Very good.’ He suddenly sprang up, and darting like lightning across the room he flung open the door. The passage outside was empty.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘That’s all right,’ said he, coming back. ‘I know that clerks are sometimes curious as to their master’s affairs. Now we can talk in safety.’ He drew up his chair very close to mine and began to stare at me again with the same questioning and thoughtful look.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A feeling of repulsion, and of something akin to fear had begun to rise within me at the strange antics of this fleshless man. Even my dread of losing a client could not restrain me from showing my impatience.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I beg that you will state your business, sir,’ said I; ‘my time is of value.’ Heaven forgive me for that last sentence, but the words came to my lips.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘How would fifty guineas for a night’s work suit you?’ he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Most admirably.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I say a night’s work, but an hour’s would be nearer the mark. I simply want your opinion about a hydraulic stamping machine which has got out of gear. If you show us what is wrong we shall soon set it right ourselves. What do you think of such a commission as that?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The work appears to be light and the pay munificent.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Precisely so. We shall want you to come to-night by the last train.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Where to?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘To Eyford, in Berkshire. It is a little place near the borders of Oxfordshire, and within seven miles of Reading. There is a train from Paddington which would bring you there at about 11:15.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Very good.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I shall come down in a carriage to meet you.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘There is a drive, then?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, our little place is quite out in the country. It is a good seven miles from Eyford Station.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Then we can hardly get there before midnight. I suppose there would be no chance of a train back. I should be compelled to stop the night.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, we could easily give you a shake-down.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘That is very awkward. Could I not come at some more convenient hour?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘We have judged it best that you should come late. It is to recompense you for any inconvenience that we are paying to you, a young and unknown man, a fee which would buy an opinion from the very heads of your profession. Still, of course, if you would like to draw out of the business, there is plenty of time to do so.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I thought of the fifty guineas, and of how very useful they would be to me. ‘Not at all,’ said I, ‘I shall be very happy to accommodate myself to your wishes. I should like, however, to understand a little more clearly what it is that you wish me to do.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Quite so. It is very natural that the pledge of secrecy which we have exacted from you should have aroused your curiosity. I have no wish to commit you to anything without your having it all laid before you. I suppose that we are absolutely safe from eavesdroppers?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Entirely.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Then the matter stands thus. You are probably aware that fuller’s-earth is a valuable product, and that it is only found in one or two places in England?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I have heard so.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Some little time ago I bought a small place—a very small place—within ten miles of Reading. I was fortunate enough to discover that there was a deposit of fuller’s-earth in one of my fields. On examining it, however, I found that this deposit was a comparatively small one, and that it formed a link between two very much larger ones upon the right and left—both of them, however, in the grounds of my neighbours. These good people were absolutely ignorant that their land contained that which was quite as valuable as a gold-mine. Naturally, it was to my interest to buy their land before they discovered its true value, but unfortunately I had no capital by which I could do this. I took a few of my friends into the secret, however, and they suggested that we should quietly and secretly work our own little deposit and that in this way we should earn the money which would enable us to buy the neighbouring fields. This we have now been doing for some time, and in order to help us in our operations we erected a hydraulic press. This press, as I have already explained, has got out of order, and we wish your advice upon the subject. We guard our secret very jealously, however, and if it once became known that we had hydraulic engineers coming to our little house, it would soon rouse inquiry, and then, if the facts came out, it would be good-bye to any chance of getting these fields and carrying out our plans. That is why I have made you promise me that you will not tell a human being that you are going to Eyford to-night. I hope that I make it all plain?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I quite follow you,’ said I. ‘The only point which I could not quite understand was what use you could make of a hydraulic press in excavating fuller’s-earth, which, as I understand, is dug out like gravel from a pit.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Ah!’ said he carelessly, ‘we have our own process. We compress the earth into bricks, so as to remove them without revealing what they are. But that is a mere detail. I have taken you fully into my confidence now, Mr. Hatherley, and I have shown you how I trust you.’ He rose as he spoke. ‘I shall expect you, then, at Eyford at 11:15.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I shall certainly be there.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And not a word to a soul.’ He looked at me with a last long, questioning gaze, and then, pressing my hand in a cold, dank grasp, he hurried from the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, when I came to think it all over in cool blood I was very much astonished, as you may both think, at this sudden commission which had been intrusted to me. On the one hand, of course, I was glad, for the fee was at least tenfold what I should have asked had I set a price upon my own services, and it was possible that this order might lead to other ones. On the other hand, the face and manner of my patron had made an unpleasant impression upon me, and I could not think that his explanation of the fuller’s-earth was sufficient to explain the necessity for my coming at midnight, and his extreme anxiety lest I should tell anyone of my errand. However, I threw all fears to the winds, ate a hearty supper, drove to Paddington, and started off, having obeyed to the letter the injunction as to holding my tongue.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At Reading I had to change not only my carriage but my station. However, I was in time for the last train to Eyford, and I reached the little dim-lit station after eleven o’clock. I was the only passenger who got out there, and there was no one upon the platform save a single sleepy porter with a lantern. As I passed out through the wicket gate, however, I found my acquaintance of the morning waiting in the shadow upon the other side. Without a word he grasped my arm and hurried me into a carriage, the door of which was standing open. He drew up the windows on either side, tapped on the wood-work, and away we went as fast as the horse could go.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One horse?” interjected Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, only one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you observe the colour?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I saw it by the side-lights when I was stepping into the carriage. It was a chestnut.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Tired-looking or fresh?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, fresh and glossy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. I am sorry to have interrupted you. Pray continue your most interesting statement.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Away we went then, and we drove for at least an hour. Colonel Lysander Stark had said that it was only seven miles, but I should think, from the rate that we seemed to go, and from the time that we took, that it must have been nearer twelve. He sat at my side in silence all the time, and I was aware, more than once when I glanced in his direction, that he was looking at me with great intensity. The country roads seem to be not very good in that part of the world, for we lurched and jolted terribly. I tried to look out of the windows to see something of where we were, but they were made of frosted glass, and I could make out nothing save the occasional bright blur of a passing light. Now and then I hazarded some remark to break the monotony of the journey, but the colonel answered only in monosyllables, and the conversation soon flagged. At last, however, the bumping of the road was exchanged for the crisp smoothness of a gravel-drive, and the carriage came to a stand. Colonel Lysander Stark sprang out, and, as I followed after him, pulled me swiftly into a porch which gaped in front of us. We stepped, as it were, right out of the carriage and into the hall, so that I failed to catch the most fleeting glance of the front of the house. The instant that I had crossed the threshold the door slammed heavily behind us, and I heard faintly the rattle of the wheels as the carriage drove away.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was pitch dark inside the house, and the colonel fumbled about looking for matches and muttering under his breath. Suddenly a door opened at the other end of the passage, and a long, golden bar of light shot out in our direction. It grew broader, and a woman appeared with a lamp in her hand, which she held above her head, pushing her face forward and peering at us. I could see that she was pretty, and from the gloss with which the light shone upon her dark dress I knew that it was a rich material. She spoke a few words in a foreign tongue in a tone as though asking a question, and when my companion answered in a gruff monosyllable she gave such a start that the lamp nearly fell from her hand. Colonel Stark went up to her, whispered something in her ear, and then, pushing her back into the room from whence she had come, he walked towards me again with the lamp in his hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Perhaps you will have the kindness to wait in this room for a few minutes,’ said he, throwing open another door. It was a quiet, little, plainly furnished room, with a round table in the centre, on which several German books were scattered. Colonel Stark laid down the lamp on the top of a harmonium beside the door. ‘I shall not keep you waiting an instant,’ said he, and vanished into the darkness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I glanced at the books upon the table, and in spite of my ignorance of German I could see that two of them were treatises on science, the others being volumes of poetry. Then I walked across to the window, hoping that I might catch some glimpse of the country-side, but an oak shutter, heavily barred, was folded across it. It was a wonderfully silent house. There was an old clock ticking loudly somewhere in the passage, but otherwise everything was deadly still. A vague feeling of uneasiness began to steal over me. Who were these German people, and what were they doing living in this strange, out-of-the-way place? And where was the place? I was ten miles or so from Eyford, that was all I knew, but whether north, south, east, or west I had no idea. For that matter, Reading, and possibly other large towns, were within that radius, so the place might not be so secluded, after all. Yet it was quite certain, from the absolute stillness, that we were in the country. I paced up and down the room, humming a tune under my breath to keep up my spirits and feeling that I was thoroughly earning my fifty-guinea fee.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Suddenly, without any preliminary sound in the midst of the utter stillness, the door of my room swung slowly open. The woman was standing in the aperture, the darkness of the hall behind her, the yellow light from my lamp beating upon her eager and beautiful face. I could see at a glance that she was sick with fear, and the sight sent a chill to my own heart. She held up one shaking finger to warn me to be silent, and she shot a few whispered words of broken English at me, her eyes glancing back, like those of a frightened horse, into the gloom behind her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I would go,’ said she, trying hard, as it seemed to me, to speak calmly; ‘I would go. I should not stay here. There is no good for you to do.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘But, madam,’ said I, ‘I have not yet done what I came for. I cannot possibly leave until I have seen the machine.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It is not worth your while to wait,’ she went on. ‘You can pass through the door; no one hinders.’ And then, seeing that I smiled and shook my head, she suddenly threw aside her constraint and made a step forward, with her hands wrung together. ‘For the love of Heaven!’ she whispered, ‘get away from here before it is too late!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I am somewhat headstrong by nature, and the more ready to engage in an affair when there is some obstacle in the way. I thought of my fifty-guinea fee, of my wearisome journey, and of the unpleasant night which seemed to be before me. Was it all to go for nothing? Why should I slink away without having carried out my commission, and without the payment which was my due? This woman might, for all I knew, be a monomaniac. With a stout bearing, therefore, though her manner had shaken me more than I cared to confess, I still shook my head and declared my intention of remaining where I was. She was about to renew her entreaties when a door slammed overhead, and the sound of several footsteps was heard upon the stairs. She listened for an instant, threw up her hands with a despairing gesture, and vanished as suddenly and as noiselessly as she had come.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The newcomers were Colonel Lysander Stark and a short thick man with a chinchilla beard growing out of the creases of his double chin, who was introduced to me as Mr. Ferguson.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘This is my secretary and manager,’ said the colonel. ‘By the way, I was under the impression that I left this door shut just now. I fear that you have felt the draught.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘On the contrary,’ said I, ‘I opened the door myself because I felt the room to be a little close.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He shot one of his suspicious looks at me. ‘Perhaps we had better proceed to business, then,’ said he. ‘Mr. Ferguson and I will take you up to see the machine.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I had better put my hat on, I suppose.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, no, it is in the house.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What, you dig fuller’s-earth in the house?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, no. This is only where we compress it. But never mind that. All we wish you to do is to examine the machine and to let us know what is wrong with it.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We went upstairs together, the colonel first with the lamp, the fat manager and I behind him. It was a labyrinth of an old house, with corridors, passages, narrow winding staircases, and little low doors, the thresholds of which were hollowed out by the generations who had crossed them. There were no carpets and no signs of any furniture above the ground floor, while the plaster was peeling off the walls, and the damp was breaking through in green, unhealthy blotches. I tried to put on as unconcerned an air as possible, but I had not forgotten the warnings of the lady, even though I disregarded them, and I kept a keen eye upon my two companions. Ferguson appeared to be a morose and silent man, but I could see from the little that he said that he was at least a fellow-countryman.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Colonel Lysander Stark stopped at last before a low door, which he unlocked. Within was a small, square room, in which the three of us could hardly get at one time. Ferguson remained outside, and the colonel ushered me in.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘We are now,’ said he, ‘actually within the hydraulic press, and it would be a particularly unpleasant thing for us if anyone were to turn it on. The ceiling of this small chamber is really the end of the descending piston, and it comes down with the force of many tons upon this metal floor. There are small lateral columns of water outside which receive the force, and which transmit and multiply it in the manner which is familiar to you. The machine goes readily enough, but there is some stiffness in the working of it, and it has lost a little of its force. Perhaps you will have the goodness to look it over and to show us how we can set it right.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I took the lamp from him, and I examined the machine very thoroughly. It was indeed a gigantic one, and capable of exercising enormous pressure. When I passed outside, however, and pressed down the levers which controlled it, I knew at once by the whishing sound that there was a slight leakage, which allowed a regurgitation of water through one of the side cylinders. An examination showed that one of the india-rubber bands which was round the head of a driving-rod had shrunk so as not quite to fill the socket along which it worked. This was clearly the cause of the loss of power, and I pointed it out to my companions, who followed my remarks very carefully and asked several practical questions as to how they should proceed to set it right. When I had made it clear to them, I returned to the main chamber of the machine and took a good look at it to satisfy my own curiosity. It was obvious at a glance that the story of the fuller’s-earth was the merest fabrication, for it would be absurd to suppose that so powerful an engine could be designed for so inadequate a purpose. The walls were of wood, but the floor consisted of a large iron trough, and when I came to examine it I could see a crust of metallic deposit all over it. I had stooped and was scraping at this to see exactly what it was when I heard a muttered exclamation in German and saw the cadaverous face of the colonel looking down at me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘What are you doing there?’ he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I felt angry at having been tricked by so elaborate a story as that which he had told me. ‘I was admiring your fuller’s-earth,’ said I; ‘I think that I should be better able to advise you as to your machine if I knew what the exact purpose was for which it was used.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The instant that I uttered the words I regretted the rashness of my speech. His face set hard, and a baleful light sprang up in his grey eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Very well,’ said he, ‘you shall know all about the machine.’ He took a step backward, slammed the little door, and turned the key in the lock. I rushed towards it and pulled at the handle, but it was quite secure, and did not give in the least to my kicks and shoves. ‘Hullo!’ I yelled. ‘Hullo! Colonel! Let me out!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And then suddenly in the silence I heard a sound which sent my heart into my mouth. It was the clank of the levers and the swish of the leaking cylinder. He had set the engine at work. The lamp still stood upon the floor where I had placed it when examining the trough. By its light I saw that the black ceiling was coming down upon me, slowly, jerkily, but, as none knew better than myself, with a force which must within a minute grind me to a shapeless pulp. I threw myself, screaming, against the door, and dragged with my nails at the lock. I implored the colonel to let me out, but the remorseless clanking of the levers drowned my cries. The ceiling was only a foot or two above my head, and with my hand upraised I could feel its hard, rough surface. Then it flashed through my mind that the pain of my death would depend very much upon the position in which I met it. If I lay on my face the weight would come upon my spine, and I shuddered to think of that dreadful snap. Easier the other way, perhaps; and yet, had I the nerve to lie and look up at that deadly black shadow wavering down upon me? Already I was unable to stand erect, when my eye caught something which brought a gush of hope back to my heart.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have said that though the floor and ceiling were of iron, the walls were of wood. As I gave a last hurried glance around, I saw a thin line of yellow light between two of the boards, which broadened and broadened as a small panel was pushed backward. For an instant I could hardly believe that here was indeed a door which led away from death. The next instant I threw myself through, and lay half-fainting upon the other side. The panel had closed again behind me, but the crash of the lamp, and a few moments afterwards the clang of the two slabs of metal, told me how narrow had been my escape.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was recalled to myself by a frantic plucking at my wrist, and I found myself lying upon the stone floor of a narrow corridor, while a woman bent over me and tugged at me with her left hand, while she held a candle in her right. It was the same good friend whose warning I had so foolishly rejected.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Come! come!’ she cried breathlessly. ‘They will be here in a moment. They will see that you are not there. Oh, do not waste the so-precious time, but come!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This time, at least, I did not scorn her advice. I staggered to my feet and ran with her along the corridor and down a winding stair. The latter led to another broad passage, and just as we reached it we heard the sound of running feet and the shouting of two voices, one answering the other from the floor on which we were and from the one beneath. My guide stopped and looked about her like one who is at her wit’s end. Then she threw open a door which led into a bedroom, through the window of which the moon was shining brightly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It is your only chance,’ said she. ‘It is high, but it may be that you can jump it.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As she spoke a light sprang into view at the further end of the passage, and I saw the lean figure of Colonel Lysander Stark rushing forward with a lantern in one hand and a weapon like a butcher’s cleaver in the other. I rushed across the bedroom, flung open the window, and looked out. How quiet and sweet and wholesome the garden looked in the moonlight, and it could not be more than thirty feet down. I clambered out upon the sill, but I hesitated to jump until I should have heard what passed between my saviour and the ruffian who pursued me. If she were ill-used, then at any risks I was determined to go back to her assistance. The thought had hardly flashed through my mind before he was at the door, pushing his way past her; but she threw her arms round him and tried to hold him back.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Fritz! Fritz!’ she cried in English, ‘remember your promise after the last time. You said it should not be again. He will be silent! Oh, he will be silent!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You are mad, Elise!’ he shouted, struggling to break away from her. ‘You will be the ruin of us. He has seen too much. Let me pass, I say!’ He dashed her to one side, and, rushing to the window, cut at me with his heavy weapon. I had let myself go, and was hanging by the hands to the sill, when his blow fell. I was conscious of a dull pain, my grip loosened, and I fell into the garden below.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was shaken but not hurt by the fall; so I picked myself up and rushed off among the bushes as hard as I could run, for I understood that I was far from being out of danger yet. Suddenly, however, as I ran, a deadly dizziness and sickness came over me. I glanced down at my hand, which was throbbing painfully, and then, for the first time, saw that my thumb had been cut off and that the blood was pouring from my wound. I endeavoured to tie my handkerchief round it, but there came a sudden buzzing in my ears, and next moment I fell in a dead faint among the rose-bushes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How long I remained unconscious I cannot tell. It must have been a very long time, for the moon had sunk, and a bright morning was breaking when I came to myself. My clothes were all sodden with dew, and my coat-sleeve was drenched with blood from my wounded thumb. The smarting of it recalled in an instant all the particulars of my night’s adventure, and I sprang to my feet with the feeling that I might hardly yet be safe from my pursuers. But to my astonishment, when I came to look round me, neither house nor garden were to be seen. I had been lying in an angle of the hedge close by the highroad, and just a little lower down was a long building, which proved, upon my approaching it, to be the very station at which I had arrived upon the previous night. Were it not for the ugly wound upon my hand, all that had passed during those dreadful hours might have been an evil dream.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Half dazed, I went into the station and asked about the morning train. There would be one to Reading in less than an hour. The same porter was on duty, I found, as had been there when I arrived. I inquired of him whether he had ever heard of Colonel Lysander Stark. The name was strange to him. Had he observed a carriage the night before waiting for me? No, he had not. Was there a police-station anywhere near? There was one about three miles off.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was too far for me to go, weak and ill as I was. I determined to wait until I got back to town before telling my story to the police. It was a little past six when I arrived, so I went first to have my wound dressed, and then the doctor was kind enough to bring me along here. I put the case into your hands and shall do exactly what you advise.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We both sat in silence for some little time after listening to this extraordinary narrative. Then Sherlock Holmes pulled down from the shelf one of the ponderous commonplace books in which he placed his cuttings.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here is an advertisement which will interest you,” said he. “It appeared in all the papers about a year ago. Listen to this: ‘Lost, on the 9th inst., Mr. Jeremiah Hayling, aged twenty-six, a hydraulic engineer. Left his lodgings at ten o’clock at night, and has not been heard of since. Was dressed in,’ etc., etc. Ha! That represents the last time that the colonel needed to have his machine overhauled, I fancy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” cried my patient. “Then that explains what the girl said.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Undoubtedly. It is quite clear that the colonel was a cool and desperate man, who was absolutely determined that nothing should stand in the way of his little game, like those out-and-out pirates who will leave no survivor from a captured ship. Well, every moment now is precious, so if you feel equal to it we shall go down to Scotland Yard at once as a preliminary to starting for Eyford.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Some three hours or so afterwards we were all in the train together, bound from Reading to the little Berkshire village. There were Sherlock Holmes, the hydraulic engineer, Inspector Bradstreet, of Scotland Yard, a plain-clothes man, and myself. Bradstreet had spread an ordnance map of the county out upon the seat and was busy with his compasses drawing a circle with Eyford for its centre.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There you are,” said he. “That circle is drawn at a radius of ten miles from the village. The place we want must be somewhere near that line. You said ten miles, I think, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was an hour’s good drive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you think that they brought you back all that way when you were unconscious?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They must have done so. I have a confused memory, too, of having been lifted and conveyed somewhere.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What I cannot understand,” said I, “is why they should have spared you when they found you lying fainting in the garden. Perhaps the villain was softened by the woman’s entreaties.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I hardly think that likely. I never saw a more inexorable face in my life.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, we shall soon clear up all that,” said Bradstreet. “Well, I have drawn my circle, and I only wish I knew at what point upon it the folk that we are in search of are to be found.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think I could lay my finger on it,” said Holmes quietly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really, now!” cried the inspector, “you have formed your opinion! Come, now, we shall see who agrees with you. I say it is south, for the country is more deserted there.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I say east,” said my patient.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am for west,” remarked the plain-clothes man. “There are several quiet little villages up there.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I am for north,” said I, “because there are no hills there, and our friend says that he did not notice the carriage go up any.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come,” cried the inspector, laughing; “it’s a very pretty diversity of opinion. We have boxed the compass among us. Who do you give your casting vote to?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are all wrong.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But we can’t all be.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, you can. This is my point.” He placed his finger in the centre of the circle. “This is where we shall find them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But the twelve-mile drive?” gasped Hatherley.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Six out and six back. Nothing simpler. You say yourself that the horse was fresh and glossy when you got in. How could it be that if it had gone twelve miles over heavy roads?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed, it is a likely ruse enough,” observed Bradstreet thoughtfully. “Of course there can be no doubt as to the nature of this gang.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None at all,” said Holmes. “They are coiners on a large scale, and have used the machine to form the amalgam which has taken the place of silver.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have known for some time that a clever gang was at work,” said the inspector. “They have been turning out half-crowns by the thousand. We even traced them as far as Reading, but could get no farther, for they had covered their traces in a way that showed that they were very old hands. But now, thanks to this lucky chance, I think that we have got them right enough.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But the inspector was mistaken, for those criminals were not destined to fall into the hands of justice. As we rolled into Eyford Station we saw a gigantic column of smoke which streamed up from behind a small clump of trees in the neighbourhood and hung like an immense ostrich feather over the landscape.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A house on fire?” asked Bradstreet as the train steamed off again on its way.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir!” said the station-master.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When did it break out?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I hear that it was during the night, sir, but it has got worse, and the whole place is in a blaze.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Whose house is it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dr. Becher’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Tell me,” broke in the engineer, “is Dr. Becher a German, very thin, with a long, sharp nose?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The station-master laughed heartily. “No, sir, Dr. Becher is an Englishman, and there isn’t a man in the parish who has a better-lined waistcoat. But he has a gentleman staying with him, a patient, as I understand, who is a foreigner, and he looks as if a little good Berkshire beef would do him no harm.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The station-master had not finished his speech before we were all hastening in the direction of the fire. The road topped a low hill, and there was a great widespread whitewashed building in front of us, spouting fire at every chink and window, while in the garden in front three fire-engines were vainly striving to keep the flames under.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s it!” cried Hatherley, in intense excitement. “There is the gravel-drive, and there are the rose-bushes where I lay. That second window is the one that I jumped from.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, at least,” said Holmes, “you have had your revenge upon them. There can be no question that it was your oil-lamp which, when it was crushed in the press, set fire to the wooden walls, though no doubt they were too excited in the chase after you to observe it at the time. Now keep your eyes open in this crowd for your friends of last night, though I very much fear that they are a good hundred miles off by now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And Holmes’ fears came to be realised, for from that day to this no word has ever been heard either of the beautiful woman, the sinister German, or the morose Englishman. Early that morning a peasant had met a cart containing several people and some very bulky boxes driving rapidly in the direction of Reading, but there all traces of the fugitives disappeared, and even Holmes’ ingenuity failed ever to discover the least clue as to their whereabouts.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The firemen had been much perturbed at the strange arrangements which they had found within, and still more so by discovering a newly severed human thumb upon a window-sill of the second floor. About sunset, however, their efforts were at last successful, and they subdued the flames, but not before the roof had fallen in, and the whole place been reduced to such absolute ruin that, save some twisted cylinders and iron piping, not a trace remained of the machinery which had cost our unfortunate acquaintance so dearly. Large masses of nickel and of tin were discovered stored in an out-house, but no coins were to be found, which may have explained the presence of those bulky boxes which have been already referred to.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>How our hydraulic engineer had been conveyed from the garden to the spot where he recovered his senses might have remained forever a mystery were it not for the soft mould, which told us a very plain tale. He had evidently been carried down by two persons, one of whom had remarkably small feet and the other unusually large ones. On the whole, it was most probable that the silent Englishman, being less bold or less murderous than his companion, had assisted the woman to bear the unconscious man out of the way of danger.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” said our engineer ruefully as we took our seats to return once more to London, “it has been a pretty business for me! I have lost my thumb and I have lost a fifty-guinea fee, and what have I gained?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Experience,” said Holmes, laughing. “Indirectly it may be of value, you know; you have only to put it into words to gain the reputation of being excellent company for the remainder of your existence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>X.<br>\nTHE ADVENTURE OF THE NOBLE BACHELOR</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">T</span>he Lord St. Simon marriage, and its curious termination, have long ceased to be a subject of interest in those exalted circles in which the unfortunate bridegroom moves. Fresh scandals have eclipsed it, and their more piquant details have drawn the gossips away from this four-year-old drama. As I have reason to believe, however, that the full facts have never been revealed to the general public, and as my friend Sherlock Holmes had a considerable share in clearing the matter up, I feel that no memoir of him would be complete without some little sketch of this remarkable episode.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a few weeks before my own marriage, during the days when I was still sharing rooms with Holmes in Baker Street, that he came home from an afternoon stroll to find a letter on the table waiting for him. I had remained indoors all day, for the weather had taken a sudden turn to rain, with high autumnal winds, and the jezail bullet which I had brought back in one of my limbs as a relic of my Afghan campaign throbbed with dull persistence. With my body in one easy-chair and my legs upon another, I had surrounded myself with a cloud of newspapers until at last, saturated with the news of the day, I tossed them all aside and lay listless, watching the huge crest and monogram upon the envelope upon the table and wondering lazily who my friend’s noble correspondent could be.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here is a very fashionable epistle,” I remarked as he entered. “Your morning letters, if I remember right, were from a fish-monger and a tide-waiter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, my correspondence has certainly the charm of variety,” he answered, smiling, “and the humbler are usually the more interesting. This looks like one of those unwelcome social summonses which call upon a man either to be bored or to lie.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He broke the seal and glanced over the contents.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, come, it may prove to be something of interest, after all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not social, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, distinctly professional.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And from a noble client?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One of the highest in England.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear fellow, I congratulate you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I assure you, Watson, without affectation, that the status of my client is a matter of less moment to me than the interest of his case. It is just possible, however, that that also may not be wanting in this new investigation. You have been reading the papers diligently of late, have you not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It looks like it,” said I ruefully, pointing to a huge bundle in the corner. “I have had nothing else to do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is fortunate, for you will perhaps be able to post me up. I read nothing except the criminal news and the agony column. The latter is always instructive. But if you have followed recent events so closely you must have read about Lord St. Simon and his wedding?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, with the deepest interest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is well. The letter which I hold in my hand is from Lord St. Simon. I will read it to you, and in return you must turn over these papers and let me have whatever bears upon the matter. This is what he says:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“‘MY DEAR MR. SHERLOCK HOLMES,—Lord Backwater tells me that I may place implicit reliance upon your judgment and discretion. I have determined, therefore, to call upon you and to consult you in reference to the very painful event which has occurred in connection with my wedding. Mr. Lestrade, of Scotland Yard, is acting already in the matter, but he assures me that he sees no objection to your co-operation, and that he even thinks that it might be of some assistance. I will call at four o’clock in the afternoon, and, should you have any other engagement at that time, I hope that you will postpone it, as this matter is of paramount importance. Yours faithfully,</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"right\">“‘ROBERT ST. SIMON.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“It is dated from Grosvenor Mansions, written with a quill pen, and the noble lord has had the misfortune to get a smear of ink upon the outer side of his right little finger,” remarked Holmes as he folded up the epistle.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He says four o’clock. It is three now. He will be here in an hour.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I have just time, with your assistance, to get clear upon the subject. Turn over those papers and arrange the extracts in their order of time, while I take a glance as to who our client is.” He picked a red-covered volume from a line of books of reference beside the mantelpiece. “Here he is,” said he, sitting down and flattening it out upon his knee. “‘Lord Robert Walsingham de Vere St. Simon, second son of the Duke of Balmoral.’ Hum! ‘Arms: Azure, three caltrops in chief over a fess sable. Born in 1846.’ He’s forty-one years of age, which is mature for marriage. Was Under-Secretary for the colonies in a late administration. The Duke, his father, was at one time Secretary for Foreign Affairs. They inherit Plantagenet blood by direct descent, and Tudor on the distaff side. Ha! Well, there is nothing very instructive in all this. I think that I must turn to you Watson, for something more solid.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have very little difficulty in finding what I want,” said I, “for the facts are quite recent, and the matter struck me as remarkable. I feared to refer them to you, however, as I knew that you had an inquiry on hand and that you disliked the intrusion of other matters.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, you mean the little problem of the Grosvenor Square furniture van. That is quite cleared up now—though, indeed, it was obvious from the first. Pray give me the results of your newspaper selections.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here is the first notice which I can find. It is in the personal column of the <i>Morning Post</i>, and dates, as you see, some weeks back: ‘A marriage has been arranged,’ it says, ‘and will, if rumour is correct, very shortly take place, between Lord Robert St. Simon, second son of the Duke of Balmoral, and Miss Hatty Doran, the only daughter of Aloysius Doran. Esq., of San Francisco, Cal., U.S.A.’ That is all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Terse and to the point,” remarked Holmes, stretching his long, thin legs towards the fire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There was a paragraph amplifying this in one of the society papers of the same week. Ah, here it is: ‘There will soon be a call for protection in the marriage market, for the present free-trade principle appears to tell heavily against our home product. One by one the management of the noble houses of Great Britain is passing into the hands of our fair cousins from across the Atlantic. An important addition has been made during the last week to the list of the prizes which have been borne away by these charming invaders. Lord St. Simon, who has shown himself for over twenty years proof against the little god’s arrows, has now definitely announced his approaching marriage with Miss Hatty Doran, the fascinating daughter of a California millionaire. Miss Doran, whose graceful figure and striking face attracted much attention at the Westbury House festivities, is an only child, and it is currently reported that her dowry will run to considerably over the six figures, with expectancies for the future. As it is an open secret that the Duke of Balmoral has been compelled to sell his pictures within the last few years, and as Lord St. Simon has no property of his own save the small estate of Birchmoor, it is obvious that the Californian heiress is not the only gainer by an alliance which will enable her to make the easy and common transition from a Republican lady to a British peeress.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Anything else?” asked Holmes, yawning.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes; plenty. Then there is another note in the <i>Morning Post</i> to say that the marriage would be an absolutely quiet one, that it would be at St. George’s, Hanover Square, that only half a dozen intimate friends would be invited, and that the party would return to the furnished house at Lancaster Gate which has been taken by Mr. Aloysius Doran. Two days later—that is, on Wednesday last—there is a curt announcement that the wedding had taken place, and that the honeymoon would be passed at Lord Backwater’s place, near Petersfield. Those are all the notices which appeared before the disappearance of the bride.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Before the what?” asked Holmes with a start.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The vanishing of the lady.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When did she vanish, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At the wedding breakfast.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed. This is more interesting than it promised to be; quite dramatic, in fact.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; it struck me as being a little out of the common.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They often vanish before the ceremony, and occasionally during the honeymoon; but I cannot call to mind anything quite so prompt as this. Pray let me have the details.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I warn you that they are very incomplete.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps we may make them less so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Such as they are, they are set forth in a single article of a morning paper of yesterday, which I will read to you. It is headed, ‘Singular Occurrence at a Fashionable Wedding’:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The family of Lord Robert St. Simon has been thrown into the greatest consternation by the strange and painful episodes which have taken place in connection with his wedding. The ceremony, as shortly announced in the papers of yesterday, occurred on the previous morning; but it is only now that it has been possible to confirm the strange rumours which have been so persistently floating about. In spite of the attempts of the friends to hush the matter up, so much public attention has now been drawn to it that no good purpose can be served by affecting to disregard what is a common subject for conversation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The ceremony, which was performed at St. George’s, Hanover Square, was a very quiet one, no one being present save the father of the bride, Mr. Aloysius Doran, the Duchess of Balmoral, Lord Backwater, Lord Eustace and Lady Clara St. Simon (the younger brother and sister of the bridegroom), and Lady Alicia Whittington. The whole party proceeded afterwards to the house of Mr. Aloysius Doran, at Lancaster Gate, where breakfast had been prepared. It appears that some little trouble was caused by a woman, whose name has not been ascertained, who endeavoured to force her way into the house after the bridal party, alleging that she had some claim upon Lord St. Simon. It was only after a painful and prolonged scene that she was ejected by the butler and the footman. The bride, who had fortunately entered the house before this unpleasant interruption, had sat down to breakfast with the rest, when she complained of a sudden indisposition and retired to her room. Her prolonged absence having caused some comment, her father followed her, but learned from her maid that she had only come up to her chamber for an instant, caught up an ulster and bonnet, and hurried down to the passage. One of the footmen declared that he had seen a lady leave the house thus apparelled, but had refused to credit that it was his mistress, believing her to be with the company. On ascertaining that his daughter had disappeared, Mr. Aloysius Doran, in conjunction with the bridegroom, instantly put themselves in communication with the police, and very energetic inquiries are being made, which will probably result in a speedy clearing up of this very singular business. Up to a late hour last night, however, nothing had transpired as to the whereabouts of the missing lady. There are rumours of foul play in the matter, and it is said that the police have caused the arrest of the woman who had caused the original disturbance, in the belief that, from jealousy or some other motive, she may have been concerned in the strange disappearance of the bride.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And is that all?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Only one little item in another of the morning papers, but it is a suggestive one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And it is—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That Miss Flora Millar, the lady who had caused the disturbance, has actually been arrested. It appears that she was formerly a <i>danseuse</i> at the Allegro, and that she has known the bridegroom for some years. There are no further particulars, and the whole case is in your hands now—so far as it has been set forth in the public press.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And an exceedingly interesting case it appears to be. I would not have missed it for worlds. But there is a ring at the bell, Watson, and as the clock makes it a few minutes after four, I have no doubt that this will prove to be our noble client. Do not dream of going, Watson, for I very much prefer having a witness, if only as a check to my own memory.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Lord Robert St. Simon,” announced our page-boy, throwing open the door. A gentleman entered, with a pleasant, cultured face, high-nosed and pale, with something perhaps of petulance about the mouth, and with the steady, well-opened eye of a man whose pleasant lot it had ever been to command and to be obeyed. His manner was brisk, and yet his general appearance gave an undue impression of age, for he had a slight forward stoop and a little bend of the knees as he walked. His hair, too, as he swept off his very curly-brimmed hat, was grizzled round the edges and thin upon the top. As to his dress, it was careful to the verge of foppishness, with high collar, black frock-coat, white waistcoat, yellow gloves, patent-leather shoes, and light-coloured gaiters. He advanced slowly into the room, turning his head from left to right, and swinging in his right hand the cord which held his golden eyeglasses.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good-day, Lord St. Simon,” said Holmes, rising and bowing. “Pray take the basket-chair. This is my friend and colleague, Dr. Watson. Draw up a little to the fire, and we will talk this matter over.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A most painful matter to me, as you can most readily imagine, Mr. Holmes. I have been cut to the quick. I understand that you have already managed several delicate cases of this sort, sir, though I presume that they were hardly from the same class of society.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I am descending.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I beg pardon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My last client of the sort was a king.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, really! I had no idea. And which king?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The King of Scandinavia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What! Had he lost his wife?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You can understand,” said Holmes suavely, “that I extend to the affairs of my other clients the same secrecy which I promise to you in yours.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course! Very right! very right! I’m sure I beg pardon. As to my own case, I am ready to give you any information which may assist you in forming an opinion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. I have already learned all that is in the public prints, nothing more. I presume that I may take it as correct—this article, for example, as to the disappearance of the bride.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lord St. Simon glanced over it. “Yes, it is correct, as far as it goes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it needs a great deal of supplementing before anyone could offer an opinion. I think that I may arrive at my facts most directly by questioning you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray do so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When did you first meet Miss Hatty Doran?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In San Francisco, a year ago.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You were travelling in the States?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you become engaged then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you were on a friendly footing?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was amused by her society, and she could see that I was amused.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Her father is very rich?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is said to be the richest man on the Pacific slope.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how did he make his money?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In mining. He had nothing a few years ago. Then he struck gold, invested it, and came up by leaps and bounds.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, what is your own impression as to the young lady’s—your wife’s character?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The nobleman swung his glasses a little faster and stared down into the fire. “You see, Mr. Holmes,” said he, “my wife was twenty before her father became a rich man. During that time she ran free in a mining camp and wandered through woods or mountains, so that her education has come from Nature rather than from the schoolmaster. She is what we call in England a tomboy, with a strong nature, wild and free, unfettered by any sort of traditions. She is impetuous—volcanic, I was about to say. She is swift in making up her mind and fearless in carrying out her resolutions. On the other hand, I would not have given her the name which I have the honour to bear”—he gave a little stately cough—“had I not thought her to be at bottom a noble woman. I believe that she is capable of heroic self-sacrifice and that anything dishonourable would be repugnant to her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you her photograph?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I brought this with me.” He opened a locket and showed us the full face of a very lovely woman. It was not a photograph but an ivory miniature, and the artist had brought out the full effect of the lustrous black hair, the large dark eyes, and the exquisite mouth. Holmes gazed long and earnestly at it. Then he closed the locket and handed it back to Lord St. Simon.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The young lady came to London, then, and you renewed your acquaintance?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, her father brought her over for this last London season. I met her several times, became engaged to her, and have now married her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She brought, I understand, a considerable dowry?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A fair dowry. Not more than is usual in my family.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And this, of course, remains to you, since the marriage is a <i>fait accompli</i>?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I really have made no inquiries on the subject.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very naturally not. Did you see Miss Doran on the day before the wedding?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was she in good spirits?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never better. She kept talking of what we should do in our future lives.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed! That is very interesting. And on the morning of the wedding?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She was as bright as possible—at least until after the ceremony.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And did you observe any change in her then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, to tell the truth, I saw then the first signs that I had ever seen that her temper was just a little sharp. The incident however, was too trivial to relate and can have no possible bearing upon the case.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray let us have it, for all that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, it is childish. She dropped her bouquet as we went towards the vestry. She was passing the front pew at the time, and it fell over into the pew. There was a moment’s delay, but the gentleman in the pew handed it up to her again, and it did not appear to be the worse for the fall. Yet when I spoke to her of the matter, she answered me abruptly; and in the carriage, on our way home, she seemed absurdly agitated over this trifling cause.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed! You say that there was a gentleman in the pew. Some of the general public were present, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes. It is impossible to exclude them when the church is open.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This gentleman was not one of your wife’s friends?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no; I call him a gentleman by courtesy, but he was quite a common-looking person. I hardly noticed his appearance. But really I think that we are wandering rather far from the point.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Lady St. Simon, then, returned from the wedding in a less cheerful frame of mind than she had gone to it. What did she do on re-entering her father’s house?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I saw her in conversation with her maid.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And who is her maid?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Alice is her name. She is an American and came from California with her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A confidential servant?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A little too much so. It seemed to me that her mistress allowed her to take great liberties. Still, of course, in America they look upon these things in a different way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How long did she speak to this Alice?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, a few minutes. I had something else to think of.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You did not overhear what they said?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Lady St. Simon said something about ‘jumping a claim.’ She was accustomed to use slang of the kind. I have no idea what she meant.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“American slang is very expressive sometimes. And what did your wife do when she finished speaking to her maid?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She walked into the breakfast-room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On your arm?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000003999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, alone. She was very independent in little matters like that. Then, after we had sat down for ten minutes or so, she rose hurriedly, muttered some words of apology, and left the room. She never came back.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But this maid, Alice, as I understand, deposes that she went to her room, covered her bride’s dress with a long ulster, put on a bonnet, and went out.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. And she was afterwards seen walking into Hyde Park in company with Flora Millar, a woman who is now in custody, and who had already made a disturbance at Mr. Doran’s house that morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, yes. I should like a few particulars as to this young lady, and your relations to her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lord St. Simon shrugged his shoulders and raised his eyebrows. “We have been on a friendly footing for some years—I may say on a <i>very</i> friendly footing. She used to be at the Allegro. I have not treated her ungenerously, and she had no just cause of complaint against me, but you know what women are, Mr. Holmes. Flora was a dear little thing, but exceedingly hot-headed and devotedly attached to me. She wrote me dreadful letters when she heard that I was about to be married, and, to tell the truth, the reason why I had the marriage celebrated so quietly was that I feared lest there might be a scandal in the church. She came to Mr. Doran’s door just after we returned, and she endeavoured to push her way in, uttering very abusive expressions towards my wife, and even threatening her, but I had foreseen the possibility of something of the sort, and I had two police fellows there in private clothes, who soon pushed her out again. She was quiet when she saw that there was no good in making a row.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did your wife hear all this?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, thank goodness, she did not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And she was seen walking with this very woman afterwards?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. That is what Mr. Lestrade, of Scotland Yard, looks upon as so serious. It is thought that Flora decoyed my wife out and laid some terrible trap for her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it is a possible supposition.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You think so, too?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did not say a probable one. But you do not yourself look upon this as likely?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not think Flora would hurt a fly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still, jealousy is a strange transformer of characters. Pray what is your own theory as to what took place?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, really, I came to seek a theory, not to propound one. I have given you all the facts. Since you ask me, however, I may say that it has occurred to me as possible that the excitement of this affair, the consciousness that she had made so immense a social stride, had the effect of causing some little nervous disturbance in my wife.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In short, that she had become suddenly deranged?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, really, when I consider that she has turned her back—I will not say upon me, but upon so much that many have aspired to without success—I can hardly explain it in any other fashion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, certainly that is also a conceivable hypothesis,” said Holmes, smiling. “And now, Lord St. Simon, I think that I have nearly all my data. May I ask whether you were seated at the breakfast-table so that you could see out of the window?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We could see the other side of the road and the Park.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. Then I do not think that I need to detain you longer. I shall communicate with you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Should you be fortunate enough to solve this problem,” said our client, rising.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have solved it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Eh? What was that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I say that I have solved it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where, then, is my wife?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is a detail which I shall speedily supply.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lord St. Simon shook his head. “I am afraid that it will take wiser heads than yours or mine,” he remarked, and bowing in a stately, old-fashioned manner he departed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is very good of Lord St. Simon to honour my head by putting it on a level with his own,” said Sherlock Holmes, laughing. “I think that I shall have a whisky and soda and a cigar after all this cross-questioning. I had formed my conclusions as to the case before our client came into the room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Holmes!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have notes of several similar cases, though none, as I remarked before, which were quite as prompt. My whole examination served to turn my conjecture into a certainty. Circumstantial evidence is occasionally very convincing, as when you find a trout in the milk, to quote Thoreau’s example.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I have heard all that you have heard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Without, however, the knowledge of pre-existing cases which serves me so well. There was a parallel instance in Aberdeen some years back, and something on very much the same lines at Munich the year after the Franco-Prussian War. It is one of these cases—but, hullo, here is Lestrade! Good-afternoon, Lestrade! You will find an extra tumbler upon the sideboard, and there are cigars in the box.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The official detective was attired in a pea-jacket and cravat, which gave him a decidedly nautical appearance, and he carried a black canvas bag in his hand. With a short greeting he seated himself and lit the cigar which had been offered to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What’s up, then?” asked Holmes with a twinkle in his eye. “You look dissatisfied.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I feel dissatisfied. It is this infernal St. Simon marriage case. I can make neither head nor tail of the business.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really! You surprise me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who ever heard of such a mixed affair? Every clue seems to slip through my fingers. I have been at work upon it all day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And very wet it seems to have made you,” said Holmes laying his hand upon the arm of the pea-jacket.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I have been dragging the Serpentine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In Heaven’s name, what for?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In search of the body of Lady St. Simon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes leaned back in his chair and laughed heartily.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you dragged the basin of Trafalgar Square fountain?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why? What do you mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because you have just as good a chance of finding this lady in the one as in the other.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade shot an angry glance at my companion. “I suppose you know all about it,” he snarled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I have only just heard the facts, but my mind is made up.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, indeed! Then you think that the Serpentine plays no part in the matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think it very unlikely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then perhaps you will kindly explain how it is that we found this in it?” He opened his bag as he spoke, and tumbled onto the floor a wedding-dress of watered silk, a pair of white satin shoes and a bride’s wreath and veil, all discoloured and soaked in water. “There,” said he, putting a new wedding-ring upon the top of the pile. “There is a little nut for you to crack, Master Holmes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, indeed!” said my friend, blowing blue rings into the air. “You dragged them from the Serpentine?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. They were found floating near the margin by a park-keeper. They have been identified as her clothes, and it seemed to me that if the clothes were there the body would not be far off.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By the same brilliant reasoning, every man’s body is to be found in the neighbourhood of his wardrobe. And pray what did you hope to arrive at through this?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At some evidence implicating Flora Millar in the disappearance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am afraid that you will find it difficult.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Are you, indeed, now?” cried Lestrade with some bitterness. “I am afraid, Holmes, that you are not very practical with your deductions and your inferences. You have made two blunders in as many minutes. This dress does implicate Miss Flora Millar.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the dress is a pocket. In the pocket is a card-case. In the card-case is a note. And here is the very note.” He slapped it down upon the table in front of him. “Listen to this: ‘You will see me when all is ready. Come at once. F. H. M.’ Now my theory all along has been that Lady St. Simon was decoyed away by Flora Millar, and that she, with confederates, no doubt, was responsible for her disappearance. Here, signed with her initials, is the very note which was no doubt quietly slipped into her hand at the door and which lured her within their reach.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very good, Lestrade,” said Holmes, laughing. “You really are very fine indeed. Let me see it.” He took up the paper in a listless way, but his attention instantly became riveted, and he gave a little cry of satisfaction. “This is indeed important,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha! you find it so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Extremely so. I congratulate you warmly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade rose in his triumph and bent his head to look. “Why,” he shrieked, “you’re looking at the wrong side!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary, this is the right side.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The right side? You’re mad! Here is the note written in pencil over here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And over here is what appears to be the fragment of a hotel bill, which interests me deeply.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There’s nothing in it. I looked at it before,” said Lestrade. “‘Oct. 4th, rooms 8<i>s</i>., breakfast 2<i>s</i>. 6<i>d</i>., cocktail 1<i>s</i>., lunch 2<i>s</i>. 6<i>d</i>., glass sherry, 8<i>d</i>.’ I see nothing in that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very likely not. It is most important, all the same. As to the note, it is important also, or at least the initials are, so I congratulate you again.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ve wasted time enough,” said Lestrade, rising. “I believe in hard work and not in sitting by the fire spinning fine theories. Good-day, Mr. Holmes, and we shall see which gets to the bottom of the matter first.” He gathered up the garments, thrust them into the bag, and made for the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Just one hint to you, Lestrade,” drawled Holmes before his rival vanished; “I will tell you the true solution of the matter. Lady St. Simon is a myth. There is not, and there never has been, any such person.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lestrade looked sadly at my companion. Then he turned to me, tapped his forehead three times, shook his head solemnly, and hurried away.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He had hardly shut the door behind him when Holmes rose to put on his overcoat. “There is something in what the fellow says about outdoor work,” he remarked, “so I think, Watson, that I must leave you to your papers for a little.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was after five o’clock when Sherlock Holmes left me, but I had no time to be lonely, for within an hour there arrived a confectioner’s man with a very large flat box. This he unpacked with the help of a youth whom he had brought with him, and presently, to my very great astonishment, a quite epicurean little cold supper began to be laid out upon our humble lodging-house mahogany. There were a couple of brace of cold woodcock, a pheasant, a <i>pâté de foie gras</i> pie with a group of ancient and cobwebby bottles. Having laid out all these luxuries, my two visitors vanished away, like the genii of the Arabian Nights, with no explanation save that the things had been paid for and were ordered to this address.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Just before nine o’clock Sherlock Holmes stepped briskly into the room. His features were gravely set, but there was a light in his eye which made me think that he had not been disappointed in his conclusions.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They have laid the supper, then,” he said, rubbing his hands.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You seem to expect company. They have laid for five.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I fancy we may have some company dropping in,” said he. “I am surprised that Lord St. Simon has not already arrived. Ha! I fancy that I hear his step now upon the stairs.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was indeed our visitor of the afternoon who came bustling in, dangling his glasses more vigorously than ever, and with a very perturbed expression upon his aristocratic features.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My messenger reached you, then?” asked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, and I confess that the contents startled me beyond measure. Have you good authority for what you say?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The best possible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lord St. Simon sank into a chair and passed his hand over his forehead.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What will the Duke say,” he murmured, “when he hears that one of the family has been subjected to such humiliation?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is the purest accident. I cannot allow that there is any humiliation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, you look on these things from another standpoint.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I fail to see that anyone is to blame. I can hardly see how the lady could have acted otherwise, though her abrupt method of doing it was undoubtedly to be regretted. Having no mother, she had no one to advise her at such a crisis.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was a slight, sir, a public slight,” said Lord St. Simon, tapping his fingers upon the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You must make allowance for this poor girl, placed in so unprecedented a position.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will make no allowance. I am very angry indeed, and I have been shamefully used.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that I heard a ring,” said Holmes. “Yes, there are steps on the landing. If I cannot persuade you to take a lenient view of the matter, Lord St. Simon, I have brought an advocate here who may be more successful.” He opened the door and ushered in a lady and gentleman. “Lord St. Simon,” said he “allow me to introduce you to Mr. and Mrs. Francis Hay Moulton. The lady, I think, you have already met.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At the sight of these newcomers our client had sprung from his seat and stood very erect, with his eyes cast down and his hand thrust into the breast of his frock-coat, a picture of offended dignity. The lady had taken a quick step forward and had held out her hand to him, but he still refused to raise his eyes. It was as well for his resolution, perhaps, for her pleading face was one which it was hard to resist.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’re angry, Robert,” said she. “Well, I guess you have every cause to be.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray make no apology to me,” said Lord St. Simon bitterly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, I know that I have treated you real bad and that I should have spoken to you before I went; but I was kind of rattled, and from the time when I saw Frank here again I just didn’t know what I was doing or saying. I only wonder I didn’t fall down and do a faint right there before the altar.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps, Mrs. Moulton, you would like my friend and me to leave the room while you explain this matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If I may give an opinion,” remarked the strange gentleman, “we’ve had just a little too much secrecy over this business already. For my part, I should like all Europe and America to hear the rights of it.” He was a small, wiry, sunburnt man, clean-shaven, with a sharp face and alert manner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I’ll tell our story right away,” said the lady. “Frank here and I met in ’84, in McQuire’s camp, near the Rockies, where Pa was working a claim. We were engaged to each other, Frank and I; but then one day father struck a rich pocket and made a pile, while poor Frank here had a claim that petered out and came to nothing. The richer Pa grew the poorer was Frank; so at last Pa wouldn’t hear of our engagement lasting any longer, and he took me away to ’Frisco. Frank wouldn’t throw up his hand, though; so he followed me there, and he saw me without Pa knowing anything about it. It would only have made him mad to know, so we just fixed it all up for ourselves. Frank said that he would go and make his pile, too, and never come back to claim me until he had as much as Pa. So then I promised to wait for him to the end of time and pledged myself not to marry anyone else while he lived. ‘Why shouldn’t we be married right away, then,’ said he, ‘and then I will feel sure of you; and I won’t claim to be your husband until I come back?’ Well, we talked it over, and he had fixed it all up so nicely, with a clergyman all ready in waiting, that we just did it right there; and then Frank went off to seek his fortune, and I went back to Pa.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The next I heard of Frank was that he was in Montana, and then he went prospecting in Arizona, and then I heard of him from New Mexico. After that came a long newspaper story about how a miners’ camp had been attacked by Apache Indians, and there was my Frank’s name among the killed. I fainted dead away, and I was very sick for months after. Pa thought I had a decline and took me to half the doctors in ’Frisco. Not a word of news came for a year and more, so that I never doubted that Frank was really dead. Then Lord St. Simon came to ’Frisco, and we came to London, and a marriage was arranged, and Pa was very pleased, but I felt all the time that no man on this earth would ever take the place in my heart that had been given to my poor Frank.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still, if I had married Lord St. Simon, of course I’d have done my duty by him. We can’t command our love, but we can our actions. I went to the altar with him with the intention to make him just as good a wife as it was in me to be. But you may imagine what I felt when, just as I came to the altar rails, I glanced back and saw Frank standing and looking at me out of the first pew. I thought it was his ghost at first; but when I looked again there he was still, with a kind of question in his eyes, as if to ask me whether I were glad or sorry to see him. I wonder I didn’t drop. I know that everything was turning round, and the words of the clergyman were just like the buzz of a bee in my ear. I didn’t know what to do. Should I stop the service and make a scene in the church? I glanced at him again, and he seemed to know what I was thinking, for he raised his finger to his lips to tell me to be still. Then I saw him scribble on a piece of paper, and I knew that he was writing me a note. As I passed his pew on the way out I dropped my bouquet over to him, and he slipped the note into my hand when he returned me the flowers. It was only a line asking me to join him when he made the sign to me to do so. Of course I never doubted for a moment that my first duty was now to him, and I determined to do just whatever he might direct.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I got back I told my maid, who had known him in California, and had always been his friend. I ordered her to say nothing, but to get a few things packed and my ulster ready. I know I ought to have spoken to Lord St. Simon, but it was dreadful hard before his mother and all those great people. I just made up my mind to run away and explain afterwards. I hadn’t been at the table ten minutes before I saw Frank out of the window at the other side of the road. He beckoned to me and then began walking into the Park. I slipped out, put on my things, and followed him. Some woman came talking something or other about Lord St. Simon to me—seemed to me from the little I heard as if he had a little secret of his own before marriage also—but I managed to get away from her and soon overtook Frank. We got into a cab together, and away we drove to some lodgings he had taken in Gordon Square, and that was my true wedding after all those years of waiting. Frank had been a prisoner among the Apaches, had escaped, came on to ’Frisco, found that I had given him up for dead and had gone to England, followed me there, and had come upon me at last on the very morning of my second wedding.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I saw it in a paper,” explained the American. “It gave the name and the church but not where the lady lived.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then we had a talk as to what we should do, and Frank was all for openness, but I was so ashamed of it all that I felt as if I should like to vanish away and never see any of them again—just sending a line to Pa, perhaps, to show him that I was alive. It was awful to me to think of all those lords and ladies sitting round that breakfast-table and waiting for me to come back. So Frank took my wedding-clothes and things and made a bundle of them, so that I should not be traced, and dropped them away somewhere where no one could find them. It is likely that we should have gone on to Paris to-morrow, only that this good gentleman, Mr. Holmes, came round to us this evening, though how he found us is more than I can think, and he showed us very clearly and kindly that I was wrong and that Frank was right, and that we should be putting ourselves in the wrong if we were so secret. Then he offered to give us a chance of talking to Lord St. Simon alone, and so we came right away round to his rooms at once. Now, Robert, you have heard it all, and I am very sorry if I have given you pain, and I hope that you do not think very meanly of me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lord St. Simon had by no means relaxed his rigid attitude, but had listened with a frowning brow and a compressed lip to this long narrative.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excuse me,” he said, “but it is not my custom to discuss my most intimate personal affairs in this public manner.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you won’t forgive me? You won’t shake hands before I go?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, certainly, if it would give you any pleasure.” He put out his hand and coldly grasped that which she extended to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I had hoped,” suggested Holmes, “that you would have joined us in a friendly supper.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that there you ask a little too much,” responded his Lordship. “I may be forced to acquiesce in these recent developments, but I can hardly be expected to make merry over them. I think that with your permission I will now wish you all a very good-night.” He included us all in a sweeping bow and stalked out of the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I trust that you at least will honour me with your company,” said Sherlock Holmes. “It is always a joy to meet an American, Mr. Moulton, for I am one of those who believe that the folly of a monarch and the blundering of a minister in far-gone years will not prevent our children from being some day citizens of the same world-wide country under a flag which shall be a quartering of the Union Jack with the Stars and Stripes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“The case has been an interesting one,” remarked Holmes when our visitors had left us, “because it serves to show very clearly how simple the explanation may be of an affair which at first sight seems to be almost inexplicable. Nothing could be more natural than the sequence of events as narrated by this lady, and nothing stranger than the result when viewed, for instance, by Mr. Lestrade of Scotland Yard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You were not yourself at fault at all, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“From the first, two facts were very obvious to me, the one that the lady had been quite willing to undergo the wedding ceremony, the other that she had repented of it within a few minutes of returning home. Obviously something had occurred during the morning, then, to cause her to change her mind. What could that something be? She could not have spoken to anyone when she was out, for she had been in the company of the bridegroom. Had she seen someone, then? If she had, it must be someone from America because she had spent so short a time in this country that she could hardly have allowed anyone to acquire so deep an influence over her that the mere sight of him would induce her to change her plans so completely. You see we have already arrived, by a process of exclusion, at the idea that she might have seen an American. Then who could this American be, and why should he possess so much influence over her? It might be a lover; it might be a husband. Her young womanhood had, I knew, been spent in rough scenes and under strange conditions. So far I had got before I ever heard Lord St. Simon’s narrative. When he told us of a man in a pew, of the change in the bride’s manner, of so transparent a device for obtaining a note as the dropping of a bouquet, of her resort to her confidential maid, and of her very significant allusion to claim-jumping—which in miners’ parlance means taking possession of that which another person has a prior claim to—the whole situation became absolutely clear. She had gone off with a man, and the man was either a lover or was a previous husband—the chances being in favour of the latter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how in the world did you find them?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It might have been difficult, but friend Lestrade held information in his hands the value of which he did not himself know. The initials were, of course, of the highest importance, but more valuable still was it to know that within a week he had settled his bill at one of the most select London hotels.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did you deduce the select?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By the select prices. Eight shillings for a bed and eightpence for a glass of sherry pointed to one of the most expensive hotels. There are not many in London which charge at that rate. In the second one which I visited in Northumberland Avenue, I learned by an inspection of the book that Francis H. Moulton, an American gentleman, had left only the day before, and on looking over the entries against him, I came upon the very items which I had seen in the duplicate bill. His letters were to be forwarded to 226 Gordon Square; so thither I travelled, and being fortunate enough to find the loving couple at home, I ventured to give them some paternal advice and to point out to them that it would be better in every way that they should make their position a little clearer both to the general public and to Lord St. Simon in particular. I invited them to meet him here, and, as you see, I made him keep the appointment.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But with no very good result,” I remarked. “His conduct was certainly not very gracious.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, Watson,” said Holmes, smiling, “perhaps you would not be very gracious either, if, after all the trouble of wooing and wedding, you found yourself deprived in an instant of wife and of fortune. I think that we may judge Lord St. Simon very mercifully and thank our stars that we are never likely to find ourselves in the same position. Draw your chair up and hand me my violin, for the only problem we have still to solve is how to while away these bleak autumnal evenings.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>XI.<br>\nTHE ADVENTURE OF THE BERYL CORONET</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">“H</span>olmes,” said I as I stood one morning in our bow-window looking down the street, “here is a madman coming along. It seems rather sad that his relatives should allow him to come out alone.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My friend rose lazily from his armchair and stood with his hands in the pockets of his dressing-gown, looking over my shoulder. It was a bright, crisp February morning, and the snow of the day before still lay deep upon the ground, shimmering brightly in the wintry sun. Down the centre of Baker Street it had been ploughed into a brown crumbly band by the traffic, but at either side and on the heaped-up edges of the footpaths it still lay as white as when it fell. The grey pavement had been cleaned and scraped, but was still dangerously slippery, so that there were fewer passengers than usual. Indeed, from the direction of the Metropolitan Station no one was coming save the single gentleman whose eccentric conduct had drawn my attention.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He was a man of about fifty, tall, portly, and imposing, with a massive, strongly marked face and a commanding figure. He was dressed in a sombre yet rich style, in black frock-coat, shining hat, neat brown gaiters, and well-cut pearl-grey trousers. Yet his actions were in absurd contrast to the dignity of his dress and features, for he was running hard, with occasional little springs, such as a weary man gives who is little accustomed to set any tax upon his legs. As he ran he jerked his hands up and down, waggled his head, and writhed his face into the most extraordinary contortions.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What on earth can be the matter with him?” I asked. “He is looking up at the numbers of the houses.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I believe that he is coming here,” said Holmes, rubbing his hands.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; I rather think he is coming to consult me professionally. I think that I recognise the symptoms. Ha! did I not tell you?” As he spoke, the man, puffing and blowing, rushed at our door and pulled at our bell until the whole house resounded with the clanging.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A few moments later he was in our room, still puffing, still gesticulating, but with so fixed a look of grief and despair in his eyes that our smiles were turned in an instant to horror and pity. For a while he could not get his words out, but swayed his body and plucked at his hair like one who has been driven to the extreme limits of his reason. Then, suddenly springing to his feet, he beat his head against the wall with such force that we both rushed upon him and tore him away to the centre of the room. Sherlock Holmes pushed him down into the easy-chair and, sitting beside him, patted his hand and chatted with him in the easy, soothing tones which he knew so well how to employ.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have come to me to tell your story, have you not?” said he. “You are fatigued with your haste. Pray wait until you have recovered yourself, and then I shall be most happy to look into any little problem which you may submit to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The man sat for a minute or more with a heaving chest, fighting against his emotion. Then he passed his handkerchief over his brow, set his lips tight, and turned his face towards us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No doubt you think me mad?” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see that you have had some great trouble,” responded Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“God knows I have!—a trouble which is enough to unseat my reason, so sudden and so terrible is it. Public disgrace I might have faced, although I am a man whose character has never yet borne a stain. Private affliction also is the lot of every man; but the two coming together, and in so frightful a form, have been enough to shake my very soul. Besides, it is not I alone. The very noblest in the land may suffer unless some way be found out of this horrible affair.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray compose yourself, sir,” said Holmes, “and let me have a clear account of who you are and what it is that has befallen you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My name,” answered our visitor, “is probably familiar to your ears. I am Alexander Holder, of the banking firm of Holder &amp; Stevenson, of Threadneedle Street.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The name was indeed well known to us as belonging to the senior partner in the second largest private banking concern in the City of London. What could have happened, then, to bring one of the foremost citizens of London to this most pitiable pass? We waited, all curiosity, until with another effort he braced himself to tell his story.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I feel that time is of value,” said he; “that is why I hastened here when the police inspector suggested that I should secure your co-operation. I came to Baker Street by the Underground and hurried from there on foot, for the cabs go slowly through this snow. That is why I was so out of breath, for I am a man who takes very little exercise. I feel better now, and I will put the facts before you as shortly and yet as clearly as I can.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is, of course, well known to you that in a successful banking business as much depends upon our being able to find remunerative investments for our funds as upon our increasing our connection and the number of our depositors. One of our most lucrative means of laying out money is in the shape of loans, where the security is unimpeachable. We have done a good deal in this direction during the last few years, and there are many noble families to whom we have advanced large sums upon the security of their pictures, libraries, or plate.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yesterday morning I was seated in my office at the bank when a card was brought in to me by one of the clerks. I started when I saw the name, for it was that of none other than—well, perhaps even to you I had better say no more than that it was a name which is a household word all over the earth—one of the highest, noblest, most exalted names in England. I was overwhelmed by the honour and attempted, when he entered, to say so, but he plunged at once into business with the air of a man who wishes to hurry quickly through a disagreeable task.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Mr. Holder,’ said he, ‘I have been informed that you are in the habit of advancing money.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The firm does so when the security is good.’ I answered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It is absolutely essential to me,’ said he, ‘that I should have £ 50,000 at once. I could, of course, borrow so trifling a sum ten times over from my friends, but I much prefer to make it a matter of business and to carry out that business myself. In my position you can readily understand that it is unwise to place one’s self under obligations.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘For how long, may I ask, do you want this sum?’ I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Next Monday I have a large sum due to me, and I shall then most certainly repay what you advance, with whatever interest you think it right to charge. But it is very essential to me that the money should be paid at once.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I should be happy to advance it without further parley from my own private purse,’ said I, ‘were it not that the strain would be rather more than it could bear. If, on the other hand, I am to do it in the name of the firm, then in justice to my partner I must insist that, even in your case, every businesslike precaution should be taken.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I should much prefer to have it so,’ said he, raising up a square, black morocco case which he had laid beside his chair. ‘You have doubtless heard of the Beryl Coronet?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘One of the most precious public possessions of the empire,’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Precisely.’ He opened the case, and there, imbedded in soft, flesh-coloured velvet, lay the magnificent piece of jewellery which he had named. ‘There are thirty-nine enormous beryls,’ said he, ‘and the price of the gold chasing is incalculable. The lowest estimate would put the worth of the coronet at double the sum which I have asked. I am prepared to leave it with you as my security.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I took the precious case into my hands and looked in some perplexity from it to my illustrious client.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You doubt its value?’ he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Not at all. I only doubt—’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The propriety of my leaving it. You may set your mind at rest about that. I should not dream of doing so were it not absolutely certain that I should be able in four days to reclaim it. It is a pure matter of form. Is the security sufficient?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Ample.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You understand, Mr. Holder, that I am giving you a strong proof of the confidence which I have in you, founded upon all that I have heard of you. I rely upon you not only to be discreet and to refrain from all gossip upon the matter but, above all, to preserve this coronet with every possible precaution because I need not say that a great public scandal would be caused if any harm were to befall it. Any injury to it would be almost as serious as its complete loss, for there are no beryls in the world to match these, and it would be impossible to replace them. I leave it with you, however, with every confidence, and I shall call for it in person on Monday morning.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Seeing that my client was anxious to leave, I said no more but, calling for my cashier, I ordered him to pay over fifty £ 1000 notes. When I was alone once more, however, with the precious case lying upon the table in front of me, I could not but think with some misgivings of the immense responsibility which it entailed upon me. There could be no doubt that, as it was a national possession, a horrible scandal would ensue if any misfortune should occur to it. I already regretted having ever consented to take charge of it. However, it was too late to alter the matter now, so I locked it up in my private safe and turned once more to my work.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When evening came I felt that it would be an imprudence to leave so precious a thing in the office behind me. Bankers’ safes had been forced before now, and why should not mine be? If so, how terrible would be the position in which I should find myself! I determined, therefore, that for the next few days I would always carry the case backward and forward with me, so that it might never be really out of my reach. With this intention, I called a cab and drove out to my house at Streatham, carrying the jewel with me. I did not breathe freely until I had taken it upstairs and locked it in the bureau of my dressing-room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And now a word as to my household, Mr. Holmes, for I wish you to thoroughly understand the situation. My groom and my page sleep out of the house, and may be set aside altogether. I have three maid-servants who have been with me a number of years and whose absolute reliability is quite above suspicion. Another, Lucy Parr, the second waiting-maid, has only been in my service a few months. She came with an excellent character, however, and has always given me satisfaction. She is a very pretty girl and has attracted admirers who have occasionally hung about the place. That is the only drawback which we have found to her, but we believe her to be a thoroughly good girl in every way.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So much for the servants. My family itself is so small that it will not take me long to describe it. I am a widower and have an only son, Arthur. He has been a disappointment to me, Mr. Holmes—a grievous disappointment. I have no doubt that I am myself to blame. People tell me that I have spoiled him. Very likely I have. When my dear wife died I felt that he was all I had to love. I could not bear to see the smile fade even for a moment from his face. I have never denied him a wish. Perhaps it would have been better for both of us had I been sterner, but I meant it for the best.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was naturally my intention that he should succeed me in my business, but he was not of a business turn. He was wild, wayward, and, to speak the truth, I could not trust him in the handling of large sums of money. When he was young he became a member of an aristocratic club, and there, having charming manners, he was soon the intimate of a number of men with long purses and expensive habits. He learned to play heavily at cards and to squander money on the turf, until he had again and again to come to me and implore me to give him an advance upon his allowance, that he might settle his debts of honour. He tried more than once to break away from the dangerous company which he was keeping, but each time the influence of his friend, Sir George Burnwell, was enough to draw him back again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And, indeed, I could not wonder that such a man as Sir George Burnwell should gain an influence over him, for he has frequently brought him to my house, and I have found myself that I could hardly resist the fascination of his manner. He is older than Arthur, a man of the world to his finger-tips, one who had been everywhere, seen everything, a brilliant talker, and a man of great personal beauty. Yet when I think of him in cold blood, far away from the glamour of his presence, I am convinced from his cynical speech and the look which I have caught in his eyes that he is one who should be deeply distrusted. So I think, and so, too, thinks my little Mary, who has a woman’s quick insight into character.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And now there is only she to be described. She is my niece; but when my brother died five years ago and left her alone in the world I adopted her, and have looked upon her ever since as my daughter. She is a sunbeam in my house—sweet, loving, beautiful, a wonderful manager and housekeeper, yet as tender and quiet and gentle as a woman could be. She is my right hand. I do not know what I could do without her. In only one matter has she ever gone against my wishes. Twice my boy has asked her to marry him, for he loves her devotedly, but each time she has refused him. I think that if anyone could have drawn him into the right path it would have been she, and that his marriage might have changed his whole life; but now, alas! it is too late—forever too late!</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, Mr. Holmes, you know the people who live under my roof, and I shall continue with my miserable story.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When we were taking coffee in the drawing-room that night after dinner, I told Arthur and Mary my experience, and of the precious treasure which we had under our roof, suppressing only the name of my client. Lucy Parr, who had brought in the coffee, had, I am sure, left the room; but I cannot swear that the door was closed. Mary and Arthur were much interested and wished to see the famous coronet, but I thought it better not to disturb it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Where have you put it?’ asked Arthur.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘In my own bureau.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well, I hope to goodness the house won’t be burgled during the night.’ said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It is locked up,’ I answered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, any old key will fit that bureau. When I was a youngster I have opened it myself with the key of the box-room cupboard.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He often had a wild way of talking, so that I thought little of what he said. He followed me to my room, however, that night with a very grave face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Look here, dad,’ said he with his eyes cast down, ‘can you let me have £ 200?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, I cannot!’ I answered sharply. ‘I have been far too generous with you in money matters.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You have been very kind,’ said he, ‘but I must have this money, or else I can never show my face inside the club again.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And a very good thing, too!’ I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, but you would not have me leave it a dishonoured man,’ said he. ‘I could not bear the disgrace. I must raise the money in some way, and if you will not let me have it, then I must try other means.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was very angry, for this was the third demand during the month. ‘You shall not have a farthing from me,’ I cried, on which he bowed and left the room without another word.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When he was gone I unlocked my bureau, made sure that my treasure was safe, and locked it again. Then I started to go round the house to see that all was secure—a duty which I usually leave to Mary but which I thought it well to perform myself that night. As I came down the stairs I saw Mary herself at the side window of the hall, which she closed and fastened as I approached.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Tell me, dad,’ said she, looking, I thought, a little disturbed, ‘did you give Lucy, the maid, leave to go out to-night?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Certainly not.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘She came in just now by the back door. I have no doubt that she has only been to the side gate to see someone, but I think that it is hardly safe and should be stopped.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You must speak to her in the morning, or I will if you prefer it. Are you sure that everything is fastened?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Quite sure, dad.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Then, good-night.’ I kissed her and went up to my bedroom again, where I was soon asleep.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am endeavouring to tell you everything, Mr. Holmes, which may have any bearing upon the case, but I beg that you will question me upon any point which I do not make clear.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary, your statement is singularly lucid.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I come to a part of my story now in which I should wish to be particularly so. I am not a very heavy sleeper, and the anxiety in my mind tended, no doubt, to make me even less so than usual. About two in the morning, then, I was awakened by some sound in the house. It had ceased ere I was wide awake, but it had left an impression behind it as though a window had gently closed somewhere. I lay listening with all my ears. Suddenly, to my horror, there was a distinct sound of footsteps moving softly in the next room. I slipped out of bed, all palpitating with fear, and peeped round the corner of my dressing-room door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Arthur!’ I screamed, ‘you villain! you thief! How dare you touch that coronet?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The gas was half up, as I had left it, and my unhappy boy, dressed only in his shirt and trousers, was standing beside the light, holding the coronet in his hands. He appeared to be wrenching at it, or bending it with all his strength. At my cry he dropped it from his grasp and turned as pale as death. I snatched it up and examined it. One of the gold corners, with three of the beryls in it, was missing.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You blackguard!’ I shouted, beside myself with rage. ‘You have destroyed it! You have dishonoured me forever! Where are the jewels which you have stolen?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Stolen!’ he cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, thief!’ I roared, shaking him by the shoulder.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘There are none missing. There cannot be any missing,’ said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘There are three missing. And you know where they are. Must I call you a liar as well as a thief? Did I not see you trying to tear off another piece?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You have called me names enough,’ said he, ‘I will not stand it any longer. I shall not say another word about this business, since you have chosen to insult me. I will leave your house in the morning and make my own way in the world.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You shall leave it in the hands of the police!’ I cried half-mad with grief and rage. ‘I shall have this matter probed to the bottom.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You shall learn nothing from me,’ said he with a passion such as I should not have thought was in his nature. ‘If you choose to call the police, let the police find what they can.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By this time the whole house was astir, for I had raised my voice in my anger. Mary was the first to rush into my room, and, at the sight of the coronet and of Arthur’s face, she read the whole story and, with a scream, fell down senseless on the ground. I sent the housemaid for the police and put the investigation into their hands at once. When the inspector and a constable entered the house, Arthur, who had stood sullenly with his arms folded, asked me whether it was my intention to charge him with theft. I answered that it had ceased to be a private matter, but had become a public one, since the ruined coronet was national property. I was determined that the law should have its way in everything.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘At least,’ said he, ‘you will not have me arrested at once. It would be to your advantage as well as mine if I might leave the house for five minutes.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘That you may get away, or perhaps that you may conceal what you have stolen,’ said I. And then, realising the dreadful position in which I was placed, I implored him to remember that not only my honour but that of one who was far greater than I was at stake; and that he threatened to raise a scandal which would convulse the nation. He might avert it all if he would but tell me what he had done with the three missing stones.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You may as well face the matter,’ said I; ‘you have been caught in the act, and no confession could make your guilt more heinous. If you but make such reparation as is in your power, by telling us where the beryls are, all shall be forgiven and forgotten.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Keep your forgiveness for those who ask for it,’ he answered, turning away from me with a sneer. I saw that he was too hardened for any words of mine to influence him. There was but one way for it. I called in the inspector and gave him into custody. A search was made at once not only of his person but of his room and of every portion of the house where he could possibly have concealed the gems; but no trace of them could be found, nor would the wretched boy open his mouth for all our persuasions and our threats. This morning he was removed to a cell, and I, after going through all the police formalities, have hurried round to you to implore you to use your skill in unravelling the matter. The police have openly confessed that they can at present make nothing of it. You may go to any expense which you think necessary. I have already offered a reward of £ 1000. My God, what shall I do! I have lost my honour, my gems, and my son in one night. Oh, what shall I do!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He put a hand on either side of his head and rocked himself to and fro, droning to himself like a child whose grief has got beyond words.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes sat silent for some few minutes, with his brows knitted and his eyes fixed upon the fire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you receive much company?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None save my partner with his family and an occasional friend of Arthur’s. Sir George Burnwell has been several times lately. No one else, I think.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you go out much in society?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Arthur does. Mary and I stay at home. We neither of us care for it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is unusual in a young girl.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She is of a quiet nature. Besides, she is not so very young. She is four-and-twenty.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This matter, from what you say, seems to have been a shock to her also.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Terrible! She is even more affected than I.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have neither of you any doubt as to your son’s guilt?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How can we have when I saw him with my own eyes with the coronet in his hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I hardly consider that a conclusive proof. Was the remainder of the coronet at all injured?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it was twisted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you not think, then, that he might have been trying to straighten it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“God bless you! You are doing what you can for him and for me. But it is too heavy a task. What was he doing there at all? If his purpose were innocent, why did he not say so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely. And if it were guilty, why did he not invent a lie? His silence appears to me to cut both ways. There are several singular points about the case. What did the police think of the noise which awoke you from your sleep?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They considered that it might be caused by Arthur’s closing his bedroom door.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A likely story! As if a man bent on felony would slam his door so as to wake a household. What did they say, then, of the disappearance of these gems?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They are still sounding the planking and probing the furniture in the hope of finding them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have they thought of looking outside the house?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, they have shown extraordinary energy. The whole garden has already been minutely examined.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, my dear sir,” said Holmes, “is it not obvious to you now that this matter really strikes very much deeper than either you or the police were at first inclined to think? It appeared to you to be a simple case; to me it seems exceedingly complex. Consider what is involved by your theory. You suppose that your son came down from his bed, went, at great risk, to your dressing-room, opened your bureau, took out your coronet, broke off by main force a small portion of it, went off to some other place, concealed three gems out of the thirty-nine, with such skill that nobody can find them, and then returned with the other thirty-six into the room in which he exposed himself to the greatest danger of being discovered. I ask you now, is such a theory tenable?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what other is there?” cried the banker with a gesture of despair. “If his motives were innocent, why does he not explain them?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is our task to find that out,” replied Holmes; “so now, if you please, Mr. Holder, we will set off for Streatham together, and devote an hour to glancing a little more closely into details.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My friend insisted upon my accompanying them in their expedition, which I was eager enough to do, for my curiosity and sympathy were deeply stirred by the story to which we had listened. I confess that the guilt of the banker’s son appeared to me to be as obvious as it did to his unhappy father, but still I had such faith in Holmes’ judgment that I felt that there must be some grounds for hope as long as he was dissatisfied with the accepted explanation. He hardly spoke a word the whole way out to the southern suburb, but sat with his chin upon his breast and his hat drawn over his eyes, sunk in the deepest thought. Our client appeared to have taken fresh heart at the little glimpse of hope which had been presented to him, and he even broke into a desultory chat with me over his business affairs. A short railway journey and a shorter walk brought us to Fairbank, the modest residence of the great financier.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Fairbank was a good-sized square house of white stone, standing back a little from the road. A double carriage-sweep, with a snow-clad lawn, stretched down in front to two large iron gates which closed the entrance. On the right side was a small wooden thicket, which led into a narrow path between two neat hedges stretching from the road to the kitchen door, and forming the tradesmen’s entrance. On the left ran a lane which led to the stables, and was not itself within the grounds at all, being a public, though little used, thoroughfare. Holmes left us standing at the door and walked slowly all round the house, across the front, down the tradesmen’s path, and so round by the garden behind into the stable lane. So long was he that Mr. Holder and I went into the dining-room and waited by the fire until he should return. We were sitting there in silence when the door opened and a young lady came in. She was rather above the middle height, slim, with dark hair and eyes, which seemed the darker against the absolute pallor of her skin. I do not think that I have ever seen such deadly paleness in a woman’s face. Her lips, too, were bloodless, but her eyes were flushed with crying. As she swept silently into the room she impressed me with a greater sense of grief than the banker had done in the morning, and it was the more striking in her as she was evidently a woman of strong character, with immense capacity for self-restraint. Disregarding my presence, she went straight to her uncle and passed her hand over his head with a sweet womanly caress.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have given orders that Arthur should be liberated, have you not, dad?” she asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, my girl, the matter must be probed to the bottom.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I am so sure that he is innocent. You know what woman’s instincts are. I know that he has done no harm and that you will be sorry for having acted so harshly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why is he silent, then, if he is innocent?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who knows? Perhaps because he was so angry that you should suspect him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How could I help suspecting him, when I actually saw him with the coronet in his hand?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, but he had only picked it up to look at it. Oh, do, do take my word for it that he is innocent. Let the matter drop and say no more. It is so dreadful to think of our dear Arthur in prison!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall never let it drop until the gems are found—never, Mary! Your affection for Arthur blinds you as to the awful consequences to me. Far from hushing the thing up, I have brought a gentleman down from London to inquire more deeply into it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This gentleman?” she asked, facing round to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, his friend. He wished us to leave him alone. He is round in the stable lane now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The stable lane?” She raised her dark eyebrows. “What can he hope to find there? Ah! this, I suppose, is he. I trust, sir, that you will succeed in proving, what I feel sure is the truth, that my cousin Arthur is innocent of this crime.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I fully share your opinion, and I trust, with you, that we may prove it,” returned Holmes, going back to the mat to knock the snow from his shoes. “I believe I have the honour of addressing Miss Mary Holder. Might I ask you a question or two?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray do, sir, if it may help to clear this horrible affair up.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You heard nothing yourself last night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing, until my uncle here began to speak loudly. I heard that, and I came down.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You shut up the windows and doors the night before. Did you fasten all the windows?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Were they all fastened this morning?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have a maid who has a sweetheart? I think that you remarked to your uncle last night that she had been out to see him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, and she was the girl who waited in the drawing-room, and who may have heard uncle’s remarks about the coronet.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see. You infer that she may have gone out to tell her sweetheart, and that the two may have planned the robbery.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what is the good of all these vague theories,” cried the banker impatiently, “when I have told you that I saw Arthur with the coronet in his hands?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Wait a little, Mr. Holder. We must come back to that. About this girl, Miss Holder. You saw her return by the kitchen door, I presume?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; when I went to see if the door was fastened for the night I met her slipping in. I saw the man, too, in the gloom.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you know him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes! he is the greengrocer who brings our vegetables round. His name is Francis Prosper.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He stood,” said Holmes, “to the left of the door—that is to say, farther up the path than is necessary to reach the door?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, he did.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And he is a man with a wooden leg?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Something like fear sprang up in the young lady’s expressive black eyes. “Why, you are like a magician,” said she. “How do you know that?” She smiled, but there was no answering smile in Holmes’ thin, eager face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should be very glad now to go upstairs,” said he. “I shall probably wish to go over the outside of the house again. Perhaps I had better take a look at the lower windows before I go up.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He walked swiftly round from one to the other, pausing only at the large one which looked from the hall onto the stable lane. This he opened and made a very careful examination of the sill with his powerful magnifying lens. “Now we shall go upstairs,” said he at last.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The banker’s dressing-room was a plainly furnished little chamber, with a grey carpet, a large bureau, and a long mirror. Holmes went to the bureau first and looked hard at the lock.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which key was used to open it?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That which my son himself indicated—that of the cupboard of the lumber-room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you it here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is it on the dressing-table.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sherlock Holmes took it up and opened the bureau.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is a noiseless lock,” said he. “It is no wonder that it did not wake you. This case, I presume, contains the coronet. We must have a look at it.” He opened the case, and taking out the diadem he laid it upon the table. It was a magnificent specimen of the jeweller’s art, and the thirty-six stones were the finest that I have ever seen. At one side of the coronet was a cracked edge, where a corner holding three gems had been torn away.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, Mr. Holder,” said Holmes, “here is the corner which corresponds to that which has been so unfortunately lost. Might I beg that you will break it off.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The banker recoiled in horror. “I should not dream of trying,” said he.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I will.” Holmes suddenly bent his strength upon it, but without result. “I feel it give a little,” said he; “but, though I am exceptionally strong in the fingers, it would take me all my time to break it. An ordinary man could not do it. Now, what do you think would happen if I did break it, Mr. Holder? There would be a noise like a pistol shot. Do you tell me that all this happened within a few yards of your bed and that you heard nothing of it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not know what to think. It is all dark to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But perhaps it may grow lighter as we go. What do you think, Miss Holder?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I confess that I still share my uncle’s perplexity.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your son had no shoes or slippers on when you saw him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He had nothing on save only his trousers and shirt.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you. We have certainly been favoured with extraordinary luck during this inquiry, and it will be entirely our own fault if we do not succeed in clearing the matter up. With your permission, Mr. Holder, I shall now continue my investigations outside.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He went alone, at his own request, for he explained that any unnecessary footmarks might make his task more difficult. For an hour or more he was at work, returning at last with his feet heavy with snow and his features as inscrutable as ever.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that I have seen now all that there is to see, Mr. Holder,” said he; “I can serve you best by returning to my rooms.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But the gems, Mr. Holmes. Where are they?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot tell.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The banker wrung his hands. “I shall never see them again!” he cried. “And my son? You give me hopes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My opinion is in no way altered.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, for God’s sake, what was this dark business which was acted in my house last night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you can call upon me at my Baker Street rooms to-morrow morning between nine and ten I shall be happy to do what I can to make it clearer. I understand that you give me <i>carte blanche</i> to act for you, provided only that I get back the gems, and that you place no limit on the sum I may draw.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I would give my fortune to have them back.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very good. I shall look into the matter between this and then. Good-bye; it is just possible that I may have to come over here again before evening.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was obvious to me that my companion’s mind was now made up about the case, although what his conclusions were was more than I could even dimly imagine. Several times during our homeward journey I endeavoured to sound him upon the point, but he always glided away to some other topic, until at last I gave it over in despair. It was not yet three when we found ourselves in our rooms once more. He hurried to his chamber and was down again in a few minutes dressed as a common loafer. With his collar turned up, his shiny, seedy coat, his red cravat, and his worn boots, he was a perfect sample of the class.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that this should do,” said he, glancing into the glass above the fireplace. “I only wish that you could come with me, Watson, but I fear that it won’t do. I may be on the trail in this matter, or I may be following a will-o’-the-wisp, but I shall soon know which it is. I hope that I may be back in a few hours.” He cut a slice of beef from the joint upon the sideboard, sandwiched it between two rounds of bread, and thrusting this rude meal into his pocket he started off upon his expedition.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had just finished my tea when he returned, evidently in excellent spirits, swinging an old elastic-sided boot in his hand. He chucked it down into a corner and helped himself to a cup of tea.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I only looked in as I passed,” said he. “I am going right on.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where to?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, to the other side of the West End. It may be some time before I get back. Don’t wait up for me in case I should be late.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How are you getting on?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, so so. Nothing to complain of. I have been out to Streatham since I saw you last, but I did not call at the house. It is a very sweet little problem, and I would not have missed it for a good deal. However, I must not sit gossiping here, but must get these disreputable clothes off and return to my highly respectable self.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I could see by his manner that he had stronger reasons for satisfaction than his words alone would imply. His eyes twinkled, and there was even a touch of colour upon his sallow cheeks. He hastened upstairs, and a few minutes later I heard the slam of the hall door, which told me that he was off once more upon his congenial hunt.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I waited until midnight, but there was no sign of his return, so I retired to my room. It was no uncommon thing for him to be away for days and nights on end when he was hot upon a scent, so that his lateness caused me no surprise. I do not know at what hour he came in, but when I came down to breakfast in the morning there he was with a cup of coffee in one hand and the paper in the other, as fresh and trim as possible.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will excuse my beginning without you, Watson,” said he, “but you remember that our client has rather an early appointment this morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, it is after nine now,” I answered. “I should not be surprised if that were he. I thought I heard a ring.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was, indeed, our friend the financier. I was shocked by the change which had come over him, for his face which was naturally of a broad and massive mould, was now pinched and fallen in, while his hair seemed to me at least a shade whiter. He entered with a weariness and lethargy which was even more painful than his violence of the morning before, and he dropped heavily into the armchair which I pushed forward for him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not know what I have done to be so severely tried,” said he. “Only two days ago I was a happy and prosperous man, without a care in the world. Now I am left to a lonely and dishonoured age. One sorrow comes close upon the heels of another. My niece, Mary, has deserted me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Deserted you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Her bed this morning had not been slept in, her room was empty, and a note for me lay upon the hall table. I had said to her last night, in sorrow and not in anger, that if she had married my boy all might have been well with him. Perhaps it was thoughtless of me to say so. It is to that remark that she refers in this note:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“‘MY DEAREST UNCLE,—I feel that I have brought trouble upon you, and that if I had acted differently this terrible misfortune might never have occurred. I cannot, with this thought in my mind, ever again be happy under your roof, and I feel that I must leave you forever. Do not worry about my future, for that is provided for; and, above all, do not search for me, for it will be fruitless labour and an ill-service to me. In life or in death, I am ever your loving,</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"right\">“‘MARY.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“What could she mean by that note, Mr. Holmes? Do you think it points to suicide?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, nothing of the kind. It is perhaps the best possible solution. I trust, Mr. Holder, that you are nearing the end of your troubles.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha! You say so! You have heard something, Mr. Holmes; you have learned something! Where are the gems?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You would not think £ 1000 apiece an excessive sum for them?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I would pay ten.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That would be unnecessary. Three thousand will cover the matter. And there is a little reward, I fancy. Have you your cheque-book? Here is a pen. Better make it out for £ 4000.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a dazed face the banker made out the required check. Holmes walked over to his desk, took out a little triangular piece of gold with three gems in it, and threw it down upon the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a shriek of joy our client clutched it up.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have it!” he gasped. “I am saved! I am saved!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The reaction of joy was as passionate as his grief had been, and he hugged his recovered gems to his bosom.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is one other thing you owe, Mr. Holder,” said Sherlock Holmes rather sternly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Owe!” He caught up a pen. “Name the sum, and I will pay it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, the debt is not to me. You owe a very humble apology to that noble lad, your son, who has carried himself in this matter as I should be proud to see my own son do, should I ever chance to have one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then it was not Arthur who took them?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I told you yesterday, and I repeat to-day, that it was not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are sure of it! Then let us hurry to him at once to let him know that the truth is known.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He knows it already. When I had cleared it all up I had an interview with him, and finding that he would not tell me the story, I told it to him, on which he had to confess that I was right and to add the very few details which were not yet quite clear to me. Your news of this morning, however, may open his lips.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“For Heaven’s sake, tell me, then, what is this extraordinary mystery!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will do so, and I will show you the steps by which I reached it. And let me say to you, first, that which it is hardest for me to say and for you to hear: there has been an understanding between Sir George Burnwell and your niece Mary. They have now fled together.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My Mary? Impossible!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is unfortunately more than possible; it is certain. Neither you nor your son knew the true character of this man when you admitted him into your family circle. He is one of the most dangerous men in England—a ruined gambler, an absolutely desperate villain, a man without heart or conscience. Your niece knew nothing of such men. When he breathed his vows to her, as he had done to a hundred before her, she flattered herself that she alone had touched his heart. The devil knows best what he said, but at least she became his tool and was in the habit of seeing him nearly every evening.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot, and I will not, believe it!” cried the banker with an ashen face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will tell you, then, what occurred in your house last night. Your niece, when you had, as she thought, gone to your room, slipped down and talked to her lover through the window which leads into the stable lane. His footmarks had pressed right through the snow, so long had he stood there. She told him of the coronet. His wicked lust for gold kindled at the news, and he bent her to his will. I have no doubt that she loved you, but there are women in whom the love of a lover extinguishes all other loves, and I think that she must have been one. She had hardly listened to his instructions when she saw you coming downstairs, on which she closed the window rapidly and told you about one of the servants’ escapade with her wooden-legged lover, which was all perfectly true.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your boy, Arthur, went to bed after his interview with you but he slept badly on account of his uneasiness about his club debts. In the middle of the night he heard a soft tread pass his door, so he rose and, looking out, was surprised to see his cousin walking very stealthily along the passage until she disappeared into your dressing-room. Petrified with astonishment, the lad slipped on some clothes and waited there in the dark to see what would come of this strange affair. Presently she emerged from the room again, and in the light of the passage-lamp your son saw that she carried the precious coronet in her hands. She passed down the stairs, and he, thrilling with horror, ran along and slipped behind the curtain near your door, whence he could see what passed in the hall beneath. He saw her stealthily open the window, hand out the coronet to someone in the gloom, and then closing it once more hurry back to her room, passing quite close to where he stood hid behind the curtain.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As long as she was on the scene he could not take any action without a horrible exposure of the woman whom he loved. But the instant that she was gone he realised how crushing a misfortune this would be for you, and how all-important it was to set it right. He rushed down, just as he was, in his bare feet, opened the window, sprang out into the snow, and ran down the lane, where he could see a dark figure in the moonlight. Sir George Burnwell tried to get away, but Arthur caught him, and there was a struggle between them, your lad tugging at one side of the coronet, and his opponent at the other. In the scuffle, your son struck Sir George and cut him over the eye. Then something suddenly snapped, and your son, finding that he had the coronet in his hands, rushed back, closed the window, ascended to your room, and had just observed that the coronet had been twisted in the struggle and was endeavouring to straighten it when you appeared upon the scene.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is it possible?” gasped the banker.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You then roused his anger by calling him names at a moment when he felt that he had deserved your warmest thanks. He could not explain the true state of affairs without betraying one who certainly deserved little enough consideration at his hands. He took the more chivalrous view, however, and preserved her secret.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that was why she shrieked and fainted when she saw the coronet,” cried Mr. Holder. “Oh, my God! what a blind fool I have been! And his asking to be allowed to go out for five minutes! The dear fellow wanted to see if the missing piece were at the scene of the struggle. How cruelly I have misjudged him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I arrived at the house,” continued Holmes, “I at once went very carefully round it to observe if there were any traces in the snow which might help me. I knew that none had fallen since the evening before, and also that there had been a strong frost to preserve impressions. I passed along the tradesmen’s path, but found it all trampled down and indistinguishable. Just beyond it, however, at the far side of the kitchen door, a woman had stood and talked with a man, whose round impressions on one side showed that he had a wooden leg. I could even tell that they had been disturbed, for the woman had run back swiftly to the door, as was shown by the deep toe and light heel marks, while Wooden-leg had waited a little, and then had gone away. I thought at the time that this might be the maid and her sweetheart, of whom you had already spoken to me, and inquiry showed it was so. I passed round the garden without seeing anything more than random tracks, which I took to be the police; but when I got into the stable lane a very long and complex story was written in the snow in front of me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There was a double line of tracks of a booted man, and a second double line which I saw with delight belonged to a man with naked feet. I was at once convinced from what you had told me that the latter was your son. The first had walked both ways, but the other had run swiftly, and as his tread was marked in places over the depression of the boot, it was obvious that he had passed after the other. I followed them up and found they led to the hall window, where Boots had worn all the snow away while waiting. Then I walked to the other end, which was a hundred yards or more down the lane. I saw where Boots had faced round, where the snow was cut up as though there had been a struggle, and, finally, where a few drops of blood had fallen, to show me that I was not mistaken. Boots had then run down the lane, and another little smudge of blood showed that it was he who had been hurt. When he came to the highroad at the other end, I found that the pavement had been cleared, so there was an end to that clue.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On entering the house, however, I examined, as you remember, the sill and framework of the hall window with my lens, and I could at once see that someone had passed out. I could distinguish the outline of an instep where the wet foot had been placed in coming in. I was then beginning to be able to form an opinion as to what had occurred. A man had waited outside the window; someone had brought the gems; the deed had been overseen by your son; he had pursued the thief; had struggled with him; they had each tugged at the coronet, their united strength causing injuries which neither alone could have effected. He had returned with the prize, but had left a fragment in the grasp of his opponent. So far I was clear. The question now was, who was the man and who was it brought him the coronet?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is an old maxim of mine that when you have excluded the impossible, whatever remains, however improbable, must be the truth. Now, I knew that it was not you who had brought it down, so there only remained your niece and the maids. But if it were the maids, why should your son allow himself to be accused in their place? There could be no possible reason. As he loved his cousin, however, there was an excellent explanation why he should retain her secret—the more so as the secret was a disgraceful one. When I remembered that you had seen her at that window, and how she had fainted on seeing the coronet again, my conjecture became a certainty.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And who could it be who was her confederate? A lover evidently, for who else could outweigh the love and gratitude which she must feel to you? I knew that you went out little, and that your circle of friends was a very limited one. But among them was Sir George Burnwell. I had heard of him before as being a man of evil reputation among women. It must have been he who wore those boots and retained the missing gems. Even though he knew that Arthur had discovered him, he might still flatter himself that he was safe, for the lad could not say a word without compromising his own family.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, your own good sense will suggest what measures I took next. I went in the shape of a loafer to Sir George’s house, managed to pick up an acquaintance with his valet, learned that his master had cut his head the night before, and, finally, at the expense of six shillings, made all sure by buying a pair of his cast-off shoes. With these I journeyed down to Streatham and saw that they exactly fitted the tracks.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I saw an ill-dressed vagabond in the lane yesterday evening,” said Mr. Holder.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely. It was I. I found that I had my man, so I came home and changed my clothes. It was a delicate part which I had to play then, for I saw that a prosecution must be avoided to avert scandal, and I knew that so astute a villain would see that our hands were tied in the matter. I went and saw him. At first, of course, he denied everything. But when I gave him every particular that had occurred, he tried to bluster and took down a life-preserver from the wall. I knew my man, however, and I clapped a pistol to his head before he could strike. Then he became a little more reasonable. I told him that we would give him a price for the stones he held—£ 1000 apiece. That brought out the first signs of grief that he had shown. ‘Why, dash it all!’ said he, ‘I’ve let them go at six hundred for the three!’ I soon managed to get the address of the receiver who had them, on promising him that there would be no prosecution. Off I set to him, and after much chaffering I got our stones at £ 1000 apiece. Then I looked in upon your son, told him that all was right, and eventually got to my bed about two o’clock, after what I may call a really hard day’s work.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A day which has saved England from a great public scandal,” said the banker, rising. “Sir, I cannot find words to thank you, but you shall not find me ungrateful for what you have done. Your skill has indeed exceeded all that I have heard of it. And now I must fly to my dear boy to apologise to him for the wrong which I have done him. As to what you tell me of poor Mary, it goes to my very heart. Not even your skill can inform me where she is now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that we may safely say,” returned Holmes, “that she is wherever Sir George Burnwell is. It is equally certain, too, that whatever her sins are, they will soon receive a more than sufficient punishment.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>XII.<br>\nTHE ADVENTURE OF THE COPPER BEECHES</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"pfirst\"><span class=\"dropcap c10\">“T</span>o the man who loves art for its own sake,” remarked Sherlock Holmes, tossing aside the advertisement sheet of <i>The Daily Telegraph</i>, “it is frequently in its least important and lowliest manifestations that the keenest pleasure is to be derived. It is pleasant to me to observe, Watson, that you have so far grasped this truth that in these little records of our cases which you have been good enough to draw up, and, I am bound to say, occasionally to embellish, you have given prominence not so much to the many <i>causes célèbres</i> and sensational trials in which I have figured but rather to those incidents which may have been trivial in themselves, but which have given room for those faculties of deduction and of logical synthesis which I have made my special province.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And yet,” said I, smiling, “I cannot quite hold myself absolved from the charge of sensationalism which has been urged against my records.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have erred, perhaps,” he observed, taking up a glowing cinder with the tongs and lighting with it the long cherry-wood pipe which was wont to replace his clay when he was in a disputatious rather than a meditative mood—“you have erred perhaps in attempting to put colour and life into each of your statements instead of confining yourself to the task of placing upon record that severe reasoning from cause to effect which is really the only notable feature about the thing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It seems to me that I have done you full justice in the matter,” I remarked with some coldness, for I was repelled by the egotism which I had more than once observed to be a strong factor in my friend’s singular character.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, it is not selfishness or conceit,” said he, answering, as was his wont, my thoughts rather than my words. “If I claim full justice for my art, it is because it is an impersonal thing—a thing beyond myself. Crime is common. Logic is rare. Therefore it is upon the logic rather than upon the crime that you should dwell. You have degraded what should have been a course of lectures into a series of tales.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a cold morning of the early spring, and we sat after breakfast on either side of a cheery fire in the old room at Baker Street. A thick fog rolled down between the lines of dun-coloured houses, and the opposing windows loomed like dark, shapeless blurs through the heavy yellow wreaths. Our gas was lit and shone on the white cloth and glimmer of china and metal, for the table had not been cleared yet. Sherlock Holmes had been silent all the morning, dipping continuously into the advertisement columns of a succession of papers until at last, having apparently given up his search, he had emerged in no very sweet temper to lecture me upon my literary shortcomings.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At the same time,” he remarked after a pause, during which he had sat puffing at his long pipe and gazing down into the fire, “you can hardly be open to a charge of sensationalism, for out of these cases which you have been so kind as to interest yourself in, a fair proportion do not treat of crime, in its legal sense, at all. The small matter in which I endeavoured to help the King of Bohemia, the singular experience of Miss Mary Sutherland, the problem connected with the man with the twisted lip, and the incident of the noble bachelor, were all matters which are outside the pale of the law. But in avoiding the sensational, I fear that you may have bordered on the trivial.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The end may have been so,” I answered, “but the methods I hold to have been novel and of interest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pshaw, my dear fellow, what do the public, the great unobservant public, who could hardly tell a weaver by his tooth or a compositor by his left thumb, care about the finer shades of analysis and deduction! But, indeed, if you are trivial, I cannot blame you, for the days of the great cases are past. Man, or at least criminal man, has lost all enterprise and originality. As to my own little practice, it seems to be degenerating into an agency for recovering lost lead pencils and giving advice to young ladies from boarding-schools. I think that I have touched bottom at last, however. This note I had this morning marks my zero-point, I fancy. Read it!” He tossed a crumpled letter across to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was dated from Montague Place upon the preceding evening, and ran thus:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“DEAR MR. HOLMES,—I am very anxious to consult you as to whether I should or should not accept a situation which has been offered to me as governess. I shall call at half-past ten to-morrow if I do not inconvenience you. Yours faithfully,</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"right\">“VIOLET HUNTER.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“Do you know the young lady?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not I.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is half-past ten now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, and I have no doubt that is her ring.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It may turn out to be of more interest than you think. You remember that the affair of the blue carbuncle, which appeared to be a mere whim at first, developed into a serious investigation. It may be so in this case, also.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, let us hope so. But our doubts will very soon be solved, for here, unless I am much mistaken, is the person in question.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As he spoke the door opened and a young lady entered the room. She was plainly but neatly dressed, with a bright, quick face, freckled like a plover’s egg, and with the brisk manner of a woman who has had her own way to make in the world.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will excuse my troubling you, I am sure,” said she, as my companion rose to greet her, “but I have had a very strange experience, and as I have no parents or relations of any sort from whom I could ask advice, I thought that perhaps you would be kind enough to tell me what I should do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray take a seat, Miss Hunter. I shall be happy to do anything that I can to serve you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I could see that Holmes was favourably impressed by the manner and speech of his new client. He looked her over in his searching fashion, and then composed himself, with his lids drooping and his finger-tips together, to listen to her story.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have been a governess for five years,” said she, “in the family of Colonel Spence Munro, but two months ago the colonel received an appointment at Halifax, in Nova Scotia, and took his children over to America with him, so that I found myself without a situation. I advertised, and I answered advertisements, but without success. At last the little money which I had saved began to run short, and I was at my wit’s end as to what I should do.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is a well-known agency for governesses in the West End called Westaway’s, and there I used to call about once a week in order to see whether anything had turned up which might suit me. Westaway was the name of the founder of the business, but it is really managed by Miss Stoper. She sits in her own little office, and the ladies who are seeking employment wait in an anteroom, and are then shown in one by one, when she consults her ledgers and sees whether she has anything which would suit them.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, when I called last week I was shown into the little office as usual, but I found that Miss Stoper was not alone. A prodigiously stout man with a very smiling face and a great heavy chin which rolled down in fold upon fold over his throat sat at her elbow with a pair of glasses on his nose, looking very earnestly at the ladies who entered. As I came in he gave quite a jump in his chair and turned quickly to Miss Stoper.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘That will do,’ said he; ‘I could not ask for anything better. Capital! capital!’ He seemed quite enthusiastic and rubbed his hands together in the most genial fashion. He was such a comfortable-looking man that it was quite a pleasure to look at him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘You are looking for a situation, miss?’ he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, sir.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘As governess?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Yes, sir.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And what salary do you ask?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I had £ 4 a month in my last place with Colonel Spence Munro.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, tut, tut! sweating—rank sweating!’ he cried, throwing his fat hands out into the air like a man who is in a boiling passion. ‘How could anyone offer so pitiful a sum to a lady with such attractions and accomplishments?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘My accomplishments, sir, may be less than you imagine,’ said I. ‘A little French, a little German, music, and drawing—’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Tut, tut!’ he cried. ‘This is all quite beside the question. The point is, have you or have you not the bearing and deportment of a lady? There it is in a nutshell. If you have not, you are not fitted for the rearing of a child who may some day play a considerable part in the history of the country. But if you have why, then, how could any gentleman ask you to condescend to accept anything under the three figures? Your salary with me, madam, would commence at £ 100 a year.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You may imagine, Mr. Holmes, that to me, destitute as I was, such an offer seemed almost too good to be true. The gentleman, however, seeing perhaps the look of incredulity upon my face, opened a pocket-book and took out a note.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It is also my custom,’ said he, smiling in the most pleasant fashion until his eyes were just two little shining slits amid the white creases of his face, ‘to advance to my young ladies half their salary beforehand, so that they may meet any little expenses of their journey and their wardrobe.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It seemed to me that I had never met so fascinating and so thoughtful a man. As I was already in debt to my tradesmen, the advance was a great convenience, and yet there was something unnatural about the whole transaction which made me wish to know a little more before I quite committed myself.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘May I ask where you live, sir?’ said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Hampshire. Charming rural place. The Copper Beeches, five miles on the far side of Winchester. It is the most lovely country, my dear young lady, and the dearest old country-house.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘And my duties, sir? I should be glad to know what they would be.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘One child—one dear little romper just six years old. Oh, if you could see him killing cockroaches with a slipper! Smack! smack! smack! Three gone before you could wink!’ He leaned back in his chair and laughed his eyes into his head again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was a little startled at the nature of the child’s amusement, but the father’s laughter made me think that perhaps he was joking.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘My sole duties, then,’ I asked, ‘are to take charge of a single child?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, no, not the sole, not the sole, my dear young lady,’ he cried. ‘Your duty would be, as I am sure your good sense would suggest, to obey any little commands my wife might give, provided always that they were such commands as a lady might with propriety obey. You see no difficulty, heh?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I should be happy to make myself useful.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Quite so. In dress now, for example. We are faddy people, you know—faddy but kind-hearted. If you were asked to wear any dress which we might give you, you would not object to our little whim. Heh?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No,’ said I, considerably astonished at his words.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Or to sit here, or sit there, that would not be offensive to you?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, no.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Or to cut your hair quite short before you come to us?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I could hardly believe my ears. As you may observe, Mr. Holmes, my hair is somewhat luxuriant, and of a rather peculiar tint of chestnut. It has been considered artistic. I could not dream of sacrificing it in this offhand fashion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I am afraid that that is quite impossible,’ said I. He had been watching me eagerly out of his small eyes, and I could see a shadow pass over his face as I spoke.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I am afraid that it is quite essential,’ said he. ‘It is a little fancy of my wife’s, and ladies’ fancies, you know, madam, ladies’ fancies must be consulted. And so you won’t cut your hair?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, sir, I really could not,’ I answered firmly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Ah, very well; then that quite settles the matter. It is a pity, because in other respects you would really have done very nicely. In that case, Miss Stoper, I had best inspect a few more of your young ladies.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The manageress had sat all this while busy with her papers without a word to either of us, but she glanced at me now with so much annoyance upon her face that I could not help suspecting that she had lost a handsome commission through my refusal.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Do you desire your name to be kept upon the books?’ she asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘If you please, Miss Stoper.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well, really, it seems rather useless, since you refuse the most excellent offers in this fashion,’ said she sharply. ‘You can hardly expect us to exert ourselves to find another such opening for you. Good-day to you, Miss Hunter.’ She struck a gong upon the table, and I was shown out by the page.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, Mr. Holmes, when I got back to my lodgings and found little enough in the cupboard, and two or three bills upon the table, I began to ask myself whether I had not done a very foolish thing. After all, if these people had strange fads and expected obedience on the most extraordinary matters, they were at least ready to pay for their eccentricity. Very few governesses in England are getting £ 100 a year. Besides, what use was my hair to me? Many people are improved by wearing it short and perhaps I should be among the number. Next day I was inclined to think that I had made a mistake, and by the day after I was sure of it. I had almost overcome my pride so far as to go back to the agency and inquire whether the place was still open when I received this letter from the gentleman himself. I have it here and I will read it to you:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“‘The Copper Beeches, near Winchester.<br>\n“‘DEAR MISS HUNTER,—Miss Stoper has very kindly given me your address, and I write from here to ask you whether you have reconsidered your decision. My wife is very anxious that you should come, for she has been much attracted by my description of you. We are willing to give £ 30 a quarter, or £ 120 a year, so as to recompense you for any little inconvenience which our fads may cause you. They are not very exacting, after all. My wife is fond of a particular shade of electric blue and would like you to wear such a dress indoors in the morning. You need not, however, go to the expense of purchasing one, as we have one belonging to my dear daughter Alice (now in Philadelphia), which would, I should think, fit you very well. Then, as to sitting here or there, or amusing yourself in any manner indicated, that need cause you no inconvenience. As regards your hair, it is no doubt a pity, especially as I could not help remarking its beauty during our short interview, but I am afraid that I must remain firm upon this point, and I only hope that the increased salary may recompense you for the loss. Your duties, as far as the child is concerned, are very light. Now do try to come, and I shall meet you with the dog-cart at Winchester. Let me know your train. Yours faithfully,</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"right\">“‘JEPHRO RUCASTLE.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“That is the letter which I have just received, Mr. Holmes, and my mind is made up that I will accept it. I thought, however, that before taking the final step I should like to submit the whole matter to your consideration.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, Miss Hunter, if your mind is made up, that settles the question,” said Holmes, smiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you would not advise me to refuse?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I confess that it is not the situation which I should like to see a sister of mine apply for.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is the meaning of it all, Mr. Holmes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, I have no data. I cannot tell. Perhaps you have yourself formed some opinion?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, there seems to me to be only one possible solution. Mr. Rucastle seemed to be a very kind, good-natured man. Is it not possible that his wife is a lunatic, that he desires to keep the matter quiet for fear she should be taken to an asylum, and that he humours her fancies in every way in order to prevent an outbreak?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is a possible solution—in fact, as matters stand, it is the most probable one. But in any case it does not seem to be a nice household for a young lady.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But the money, Mr. Holmes, the money!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, yes, of course the pay is good—too good. That is what makes me uneasy. Why should they give you £ 120 a year, when they could have their pick for £ 40? There must be some strong reason behind.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I thought that if I told you the circumstances you would understand afterwards if I wanted your help. I should feel so much stronger if I felt that you were at the back of me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, you may carry that feeling away with you. I assure you that your little problem promises to be the most interesting which has come my way for some months. There is something distinctly novel about some of the features. If you should find yourself in doubt or in danger—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Danger! What danger do you foresee?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes shook his head gravely. “It would cease to be a danger if we could define it,” said he. “But at any time, day or night, a telegram would bring me down to your help.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is enough.” She rose briskly from her chair with the anxiety all swept from her face. “I shall go down to Hampshire quite easy in my mind now. I shall write to Mr. Rucastle at once, sacrifice my poor hair to-night, and start for Winchester to-morrow.” With a few grateful words to Holmes she bade us both good-night and bustled off upon her way.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At least,” said I as we heard her quick, firm steps descending the stairs, “she seems to be a young lady who is very well able to take care of herself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And she would need to be,” said Holmes gravely. “I am much mistaken if we do not hear from her before many days are past.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was not very long before my friend’s prediction was fulfilled. A fortnight went by, during which I frequently found my thoughts turning in her direction and wondering what strange side-alley of human experience this lonely woman had strayed into. The unusual salary, the curious conditions, the light duties, all pointed to something abnormal, though whether a fad or a plot, or whether the man were a philanthropist or a villain, it was quite beyond my powers to determine. As to Holmes, I observed that he sat frequently for half an hour on end, with knitted brows and an abstracted air, but he swept the matter away with a wave of his hand when I mentioned it. “Data! data! data!” he cried impatiently. “I can’t make bricks without clay.” And yet he would always wind up by muttering that no sister of his should ever have accepted such a situation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The telegram which we eventually received came late one night just as I was thinking of turning in and Holmes was settling down to one of those all-night chemical researches which he frequently indulged in, when I would leave him stooping over a retort and a test-tube at night and find him in the same position when I came down to breakfast in the morning. He opened the yellow envelope, and then, glancing at the message, threw it across to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Just look up the trains in Bradshaw,” said he, and turned back to his chemical studies.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The summons was a brief and urgent one.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“Please be at the Black Swan Hotel at Winchester at midday to-morrow,” it said. “Do come! I am at my wit’s end.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"right\">“HUNTER.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">“Will you come with me?” asked Holmes, glancing up.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should wish to.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Just look it up, then.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is a train at half-past nine,” said I, glancing over my Bradshaw. “It is due at Winchester at 11:30.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That will do very nicely. Then perhaps I had better postpone my analysis of the acetones, as we may need to be at our best in the morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"p2\">By eleven o’clock the next day we were well upon our way to the old English capital. Holmes had been buried in the morning papers all the way down, but after we had passed the Hampshire border he threw them down and began to admire the scenery. It was an ideal spring day, a light blue sky, flecked with little fleecy white clouds drifting across from west to east. The sun was shining very brightly, and yet there was an exhilarating nip in the air, which set an edge to a man’s energy. All over the countryside, away to the rolling hills around Aldershot, the little red and grey roofs of the farm-steadings peeped out from amid the light green of the new foliage.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Are they not fresh and beautiful?” I cried with all the enthusiasm of a man fresh from the fogs of Baker Street.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Holmes shook his head gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you know, Watson,” said he, “that it is one of the curses of a mind with a turn like mine that I must look at everything with reference to my own special subject. You look at these scattered houses, and you are impressed by their beauty. I look at them, and the only thought which comes to me is a feeling of their isolation and of the impunity with which crime may be committed there.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” I cried. “Who would associate crime with these dear old homesteads?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They always fill me with a certain horror. It is my belief, Watson, founded upon my experience, that the lowest and vilest alleys in London do not present a more dreadful record of sin than does the smiling and beautiful countryside.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You horrify me!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But the reason is very obvious. The pressure of public opinion can do in the town what the law cannot accomplish. There is no lane so vile that the scream of a tortured child, or the thud of a drunkard’s blow, does not beget sympathy and indignation among the neighbours, and then the whole machinery of justice is ever so close that a word of complaint can set it going, and there is but a step between the crime and the dock. But look at these lonely houses, each in its own fields, filled for the most part with poor ignorant folk who know little of the law. Think of the deeds of hellish cruelty, the hidden wickedness which may go on, year in, year out, in such places, and none the wiser. Had this lady who appeals to us for help gone to live in Winchester, I should never have had a fear for her. It is the five miles of country which makes the danger. Still, it is clear that she is not personally threatened.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. If she can come to Winchester to meet us she can get away.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so. She has her freedom.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What <i>can</i> be the matter, then? Can you suggest no explanation?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have devised seven separate explanations, each of which would cover the facts as far as we know them. But which of these is correct can only be determined by the fresh information which we shall no doubt find waiting for us. Well, there is the tower of the cathedral, and we shall soon learn all that Miss Hunter has to tell.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Black Swan is an inn of repute in the High Street, at no distance from the station, and there we found the young lady waiting for us. She had engaged a sitting-room, and our lunch awaited us upon the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am so delighted that you have come,” she said earnestly. “It is so very kind of you both; but indeed I do not know what I should do. Your advice will be altogether invaluable to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray tell us what has happened to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will do so, and I must be quick, for I have promised Mr. Rucastle to be back before three. I got his leave to come into town this morning, though he little knew for what purpose.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let us have everything in its due order.” Holmes thrust his long thin legs out towards the fire and composed himself to listen.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the first place, I may say that I have met, on the whole, with no actual ill-treatment from Mr. and Mrs. Rucastle. It is only fair to them to say that. But I cannot understand them, and I am not easy in my mind about them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What can you not understand?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Their reasons for their conduct. But you shall have it all just as it occurred. When I came down, Mr. Rucastle met me here and drove me in his dog-cart to the Copper Beeches. It is, as he said, beautifully situated, but it is not beautiful in itself, for it is a large square block of a house, whitewashed, but all stained and streaked with damp and bad weather. There are grounds round it, woods on three sides, and on the fourth a field which slopes down to the Southampton highroad, which curves past about a hundred yards from the front door. This ground in front belongs to the house, but the woods all round are part of Lord Southerton’s preserves. A clump of copper beeches immediately in front of the hall door has given its name to the place.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was driven over by my employer, who was as amiable as ever, and was introduced by him that evening to his wife and the child. There was no truth, Mr. Holmes, in the conjecture which seemed to us to be probable in your rooms at Baker Street. Mrs. Rucastle is not mad. I found her to be a silent, pale-faced woman, much younger than her husband, not more than thirty, I should think, while he can hardly be less than forty-five. From their conversation I have gathered that they have been married about seven years, that he was a widower, and that his only child by the first wife was the daughter who has gone to Philadelphia. Mr. Rucastle told me in private that the reason why she had left them was that she had an unreasoning aversion to her stepmother. As the daughter could not have been less than twenty, I can quite imagine that her position must have been uncomfortable with her father’s young wife.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mrs. Rucastle seemed to me to be colourless in mind as well as in feature. She impressed me neither favourably nor the reverse. She was a nonentity. It was easy to see that she was passionately devoted both to her husband and to her little son. Her light grey eyes wandered continually from one to the other, noting every little want and forestalling it if possible. He was kind to her also in his bluff, boisterous fashion, and on the whole they seemed to be a happy couple. And yet she had some secret sorrow, this woman. She would often be lost in deep thought, with the saddest look upon her face. More than once I have surprised her in tears. I have thought sometimes that it was the disposition of her child which weighed upon her mind, for I have never met so utterly spoiled and so ill-natured a little creature. He is small for his age, with a head which is quite disproportionately large. His whole life appears to be spent in an alternation between savage fits of passion and gloomy intervals of sulking. Giving pain to any creature weaker than himself seems to be his one idea of amusement, and he shows quite remarkable talent in planning the capture of mice, little birds, and insects. But I would rather not talk about the creature, Mr. Holmes, and, indeed, he has little to do with my story.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am glad of all details,” remarked my friend, “whether they seem to you to be relevant or not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I shall try not to miss anything of importance. The one unpleasant thing about the house, which struck me at once, was the appearance and conduct of the servants. There are only two, a man and his wife. Toller, for that is his name, is a rough, uncouth man, with grizzled hair and whiskers, and a perpetual smell of drink. Twice since I have been with them he has been quite drunk, and yet Mr. Rucastle seemed to take no notice of it. His wife is a very tall and strong woman with a sour face, as silent as Mrs. Rucastle and much less amiable. They are a most unpleasant couple, but fortunately I spend most of my time in the nursery and my own room, which are next to each other in one corner of the building.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“For two days after my arrival at the Copper Beeches my life was very quiet; on the third, Mrs. Rucastle came down just after breakfast and whispered something to her husband.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, yes,’ said he, turning to me, ‘we are very much obliged to you, Miss Hunter, for falling in with our whims so far as to cut your hair. I assure you that it has not detracted in the tiniest iota from your appearance. We shall now see how the electric-blue dress will become you. You will find it laid out upon the bed in your room, and if you would be so good as to put it on we should both be extremely obliged.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The dress which I found waiting for me was of a peculiar shade of blue. It was of excellent material, a sort of beige, but it bore unmistakable signs of having been worn before. It could not have been a better fit if I had been measured for it. Both Mr. and Mrs. Rucastle expressed a delight at the look of it, which seemed quite exaggerated in its vehemence. They were waiting for me in the drawing-room, which is a very large room, stretching along the entire front of the house, with three long windows reaching down to the floor. A chair had been placed close to the central window, with its back turned towards it. In this I was asked to sit, and then Mr. Rucastle, walking up and down on the other side of the room, began to tell me a series of the funniest stories that I have ever listened to. You cannot imagine how comical he was, and I laughed until I was quite weary. Mrs. Rucastle, however, who has evidently no sense of humour, never so much as smiled, but sat with her hands in her lap, and a sad, anxious look upon her face. After an hour or so, Mr. Rucastle suddenly remarked that it was time to commence the duties of the day, and that I might change my dress and go to little Edward in the nursery.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Two days later this same performance was gone through under exactly similar circumstances. Again I changed my dress, again I sat in the window, and again I laughed very heartily at the funny stories of which my employer had an immense <i>répertoire</i>, and which he told inimitably. Then he handed me a yellow-backed novel, and moving my chair a little sideways, that my own shadow might not fall upon the page, he begged me to read aloud to him. I read for about ten minutes, beginning in the heart of a chapter, and then suddenly, in the middle of a sentence, he ordered me to cease and to change my dress.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You can easily imagine, Mr. Holmes, how curious I became as to what the meaning of this extraordinary performance could possibly be. They were always very careful, I observed, to turn my face away from the window, so that I became consumed with the desire to see what was going on behind my back. At first it seemed to be impossible, but I soon devised a means. My hand-mirror had been broken, so a happy thought seized me, and I concealed a piece of the glass in my handkerchief. On the next occasion, in the midst of my laughter, I put my handkerchief up to my eyes, and was able with a little management to see all that there was behind me. I confess that I was disappointed. There was nothing. At least that was my first impression. At the second glance, however, I perceived that there was a man standing in the Southampton Road, a small bearded man in a grey suit, who seemed to be looking in my direction. The road is an important highway, and there are usually people there. This man, however, was leaning against the railings which bordered our field and was looking earnestly up. I lowered my handkerchief and glanced at Mrs. Rucastle to find her eyes fixed upon me with a most searching gaze. She said nothing, but I am convinced that she had divined that I had a mirror in my hand and had seen what was behind me. She rose at once.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Jephro,’ said she, ‘there is an impertinent fellow upon the road there who stares up at Miss Hunter.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No friend of yours, Miss Hunter?’ he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, I know no one in these parts.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Dear me! How very impertinent! Kindly turn round and motion to him to go away.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Surely it would be better to take no notice.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘No, no, we should have him loitering here always. Kindly turn round and wave him away like that.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did as I was told, and at the same instant Mrs. Rucastle drew down the blind. That was a week ago, and from that time I have not sat again in the window, nor have I worn the blue dress, nor seen the man in the road.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray continue,” said Holmes. “Your narrative promises to be a most interesting one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will find it rather disconnected, I fear, and there may prove to be little relation between the different incidents of which I speak. On the very first day that I was at the Copper Beeches, Mr. Rucastle took me to a small outhouse which stands near the kitchen door. As we approached it I heard the sharp rattling of a chain, and the sound as of a large animal moving about.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Look in here!’ said Mr. Rucastle, showing me a slit between two planks. ‘Is he not a beauty?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I looked through and was conscious of two glowing eyes, and of a vague figure huddled up in the darkness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Don’t be frightened,’ said my employer, laughing at the start which I had given. ‘It’s only Carlo, my mastiff. I call him mine, but really old Toller, my groom, is the only man who can do anything with him. We feed him once a day, and not too much then, so that he is always as keen as mustard. Toller lets him loose every night, and God help the trespasser whom he lays his fangs upon. For goodness’ sake don’t you ever on any pretext set your foot over the threshold at night, for it’s as much as your life is worth.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The warning was no idle one, for two nights later I happened to look out of my bedroom window about two o’clock in the morning. It was a beautiful moonlight night, and the lawn in front of the house was silvered over and almost as bright as day. I was standing, rapt in the peaceful beauty of the scene, when I was aware that something was moving under the shadow of the copper beeches. As it emerged into the moonshine I saw what it was. It was a giant dog, as large as a calf, tawny tinted, with hanging jowl, black muzzle, and huge projecting bones. It walked slowly across the lawn and vanished into the shadow upon the other side. That dreadful sentinel sent a chill to my heart which I do not think that any burglar could have done.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And now I have a very strange experience to tell you. I had, as you know, cut off my hair in London, and I had placed it in a great coil at the bottom of my trunk. One evening, after the child was in bed, I began to amuse myself by examining the furniture of my room and by rearranging my own little things. There was an old chest of drawers in the room, the two upper ones empty and open, the lower one locked. I had filled the first two with my linen, and as I had still much to pack away I was naturally annoyed at not having the use of the third drawer. It struck me that it might have been fastened by a mere oversight, so I took out my bunch of keys and tried to open it. The very first key fitted to perfection, and I drew the drawer open. There was only one thing in it, but I am sure that you would never guess what it was. It was my coil of hair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I took it up and examined it. It was of the same peculiar tint, and the same thickness. But then the impossibility of the thing obtruded itself upon me. How could my hair have been locked in the drawer? With trembling hands I undid my trunk, turned out the contents, and drew from the bottom my own hair. I laid the two tresses together, and I assure you that they were identical. Was it not extraordinary? Puzzle as I would, I could make nothing at all of what it meant. I returned the strange hair to the drawer, and I said nothing of the matter to the Rucastles as I felt that I had put myself in the wrong by opening a drawer which they had locked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am naturally observant, as you may have remarked, Mr. Holmes, and I soon had a pretty good plan of the whole house in my head. There was one wing, however, which appeared not to be inhabited at all. A door which faced that which led into the quarters of the Tollers opened into this suite, but it was invariably locked. One day, however, as I ascended the stair, I met Mr. Rucastle coming out through this door, his keys in his hand, and a look on his face which made him a very different person to the round, jovial man to whom I was accustomed. His cheeks were red, his brow was all crinkled with anger, and the veins stood out at his temples with passion. He locked the door and hurried past me without a word or a look.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This aroused my curiosity, so when I went out for a walk in the grounds with my charge, I strolled round to the side from which I could see the windows of this part of the house. There were four of them in a row, three of which were simply dirty, while the fourth was shuttered up. They were evidently all deserted. As I strolled up and down, glancing at them occasionally, Mr. Rucastle came out to me, looking as merry and jovial as ever.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Ah!’ said he, ‘you must not think me rude if I passed you without a word, my dear young lady. I was preoccupied with business matters.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I assured him that I was not offended. ‘By the way,’ said I, ‘you seem to have quite a suite of spare rooms up there, and one of them has the shutters up.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He looked surprised and, as it seemed to me, a little startled at my remark.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Photography is one of my hobbies,’ said he. ‘I have made my dark room up there. But, dear me! what an observant young lady we have come upon. Who would have believed it? Who would have ever believed it?’ He spoke in a jesting tone, but there was no jest in his eyes as he looked at me. I read suspicion there and annoyance, but no jest.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, Mr. Holmes, from the moment that I understood that there was something about that suite of rooms which I was not to know, I was all on fire to go over them. It was not mere curiosity, though I have my share of that. It was more a feeling of duty—a feeling that some good might come from my penetrating to this place. They talk of woman’s instinct; perhaps it was woman’s instinct which gave me that feeling. At any rate, it was there, and I was keenly on the lookout for any chance to pass the forbidden door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was only yesterday that the chance came. I may tell you that, besides Mr. Rucastle, both Toller and his wife find something to do in these deserted rooms, and I once saw him carrying a large black linen bag with him through the door. Recently he has been drinking hard, and yesterday evening he was very drunk; and when I came upstairs there was the key in the door. I have no doubt at all that he had left it there. Mr. and Mrs. Rucastle were both downstairs, and the child was with them, so that I had an admirable opportunity. I turned the key gently in the lock, opened the door, and slipped through.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There was a little passage in front of me, unpapered and uncarpeted, which turned at a right angle at the farther end. Round this corner were three doors in a line, the first and third of which were open. They each led into an empty room, dusty and cheerless, with two windows in the one and one in the other, so thick with dirt that the evening light glimmered dimly through them. The centre door was closed, and across the outside of it had been fastened one of the broad bars of an iron bed, padlocked at one end to a ring in the wall, and fastened at the other with stout cord. The door itself was locked as well, and the key was not there. This barricaded door corresponded clearly with the shuttered window outside, and yet I could see by the glimmer from beneath it that the room was not in darkness. Evidently there was a skylight which let in light from above. As I stood in the passage gazing at the sinister door and wondering what secret it might veil, I suddenly heard the sound of steps within the room and saw a shadow pass backward and forward against the little slit of dim light which shone out from under the door. A mad, unreasoning terror rose up in me at the sight, Mr. Holmes. My overstrung nerves failed me suddenly, and I turned and ran—ran as though some dreadful hand were behind me clutching at the skirt of my dress. I rushed down the passage, through the door, and straight into the arms of Mr. Rucastle, who was waiting outside.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘So,’ said he, smiling, ‘it was you, then. I thought that it must be when I saw the door open.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Oh, I am so frightened!’ I panted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘My dear young lady! my dear young lady!’—you cannot think how caressing and soothing his manner was—‘and what has frightened you, my dear young lady?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But his voice was just a little too coaxing. He overdid it. I was keenly on my guard against him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I was foolish enough to go into the empty wing,’ I answered. ‘But it is so lonely and eerie in this dim light that I was frightened and ran out again. Oh, it is so dreadfully still in there!’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Only that?’ said he, looking at me keenly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Why, what did you think?’ I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Why do you think that I lock this door?’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I am sure that I do not know.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘It is to keep people out who have no business there. Do you see?’ He was still smiling in the most amiable manner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘I am sure if I had known—’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Well, then, you know now. And if you ever put your foot over that threshold again’—here in an instant the smile hardened into a grin of rage, and he glared down at me with the face of a demon—‘I’ll throw you to the mastiff.’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was so terrified that I do not know what I did. I suppose that I must have rushed past him into my room. I remember nothing until I found myself lying on my bed trembling all over. Then I thought of you, Mr. Holmes. I could not live there longer without some advice. I was frightened of the house, of the man, of the woman, of the servants, even of the child. They were all horrible to me. If I could only bring you down all would be well. Of course I might have fled from the house, but my curiosity was almost as strong as my fears. My mind was soon made up. I would send you a wire. I put on my hat and cloak, went down to the office, which is about half a mile from the house, and then returned, feeling very much easier. A horrible doubt came into my mind as I approached the door lest the dog might be loose, but I remembered that Toller had drunk himself into a state of insensibility that evening, and I knew that he was the only one in the household who had any influence with the savage creature, or who would venture to set him free. I slipped in in safety and lay awake half the night in my joy at the thought of seeing you. I had no difficulty in getting leave to come into Winchester this morning, but I must be back before three o’clock, for Mr. and Mrs. Rucastle are going on a visit, and will be away all the evening, so that I must look after the child. Now I have told you all my adventures, Mr. Holmes, and I should be very glad if you could tell me what it all means, and, above all, what I should do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes and I had listened spellbound to this extraordinary story. My friend rose now and paced up and down the room, his hands in his pockets, and an expression of the most profound gravity upon his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000004999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is Toller still drunk?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I heard his wife tell Mrs. Rucastle that she could do nothing with him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is well. And the Rucastles go out to-night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is there a cellar with a good strong lock?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, the wine-cellar.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You seem to me to have acted all through this matter like a very brave and sensible girl, Miss Hunter. Do you think that you could perform one more feat? I should not ask it of you if I did not think you a quite exceptional woman.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will try. What is it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We shall be at the Copper Beeches by seven o’clock, my friend and I. The Rucastles will be gone by that time, and Toller will, we hope, be incapable. There only remains Mrs. Toller, who might give the alarm. If you could send her into the cellar on some errand, and then turn the key upon her, you would facilitate matters immensely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will do it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excellent! We shall then look thoroughly into the affair. Of course there is only one feasible explanation. You have been brought there to personate someone, and the real person is imprisoned in this chamber. That is obvious. As to who this prisoner is, I have no doubt that it is the daughter, Miss Alice Rucastle, if I remember right, who was said to have gone to America. You were chosen, doubtless, as resembling her in height, figure, and the colour of your hair. Hers had been cut off, very possibly in some illness through which she has passed, and so, of course, yours had to be sacrificed also. By a curious chance you came upon her tresses. The man in the road was undoubtedly some friend of hers—possibly her <i>fiancé</i>—and no doubt, as you wore the girl’s dress and were so like her, he was convinced from your laughter, whenever he saw you, and afterwards from your gesture, that Miss Rucastle was perfectly happy, and that she no longer desired his attentions. The dog is let loose at night to prevent him from endeavouring to communicate with her. So much is fairly clear. The most serious point in the case is the disposition of the child.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What on earth has that to do with it?” I ejaculated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Watson, you as a medical man are continually gaining light as to the tendencies of a child by the study of the parents. Don’t you see that the converse is equally valid. I have frequently gained my first real insight into the character of parents by studying their children. This child’s disposition is abnormally cruel, merely for cruelty’s sake, and whether he derives this from his smiling father, as I should suspect, or from his mother, it bodes evil for the poor girl who is in their power.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am sure that you are right, Mr. Holmes,” cried our client. “A thousand things come back to me which make me certain that you have hit it. Oh, let us lose not an instant in bringing help to this poor creature.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We must be circumspect, for we are dealing with a very cunning man. We can do nothing until seven o’clock. At that hour we shall be with you, and it will not be long before we solve the mystery.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We were as good as our word, for it was just seven when we reached the Copper Beeches, having put up our trap at a wayside public-house. The group of trees, with their dark leaves shining like burnished metal in the light of the setting sun, were sufficient to mark the house even had Miss Hunter not been standing smiling on the door-step.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you managed it?” asked Holmes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A loud thudding noise came from somewhere downstairs. “That is Mrs. Toller in the cellar,” said she. “Her husband lies snoring on the kitchen rug. Here are his keys, which are the duplicates of Mr. Rucastle’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have done well indeed!” cried Holmes with enthusiasm. “Now lead the way, and we shall soon see the end of this black business.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We passed up the stair, unlocked the door, followed on down a passage, and found ourselves in front of the barricade which Miss Hunter had described. Holmes cut the cord and removed the transverse bar. Then he tried the various keys in the lock, but without success. No sound came from within, and at the silence Holmes’ face clouded over.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I trust that we are not too late,” said he. “I think, Miss Hunter, that we had better go in without you. Now, Watson, put your shoulder to it, and we shall see whether we cannot make our way in.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was an old rickety door and gave at once before our united strength. Together we rushed into the room. It was empty. There was no furniture save a little pallet bed, a small table, and a basketful of linen. The skylight above was open, and the prisoner gone.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There has been some villainy here,” said Holmes; “this beauty has guessed Miss Hunter’s intentions and has carried his victim off.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But how?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Through the skylight. We shall soon see how he managed it.” He swung himself up onto the roof. “Ah, yes,” he cried, “here’s the end of a long light ladder against the eaves. That is how he did it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it is impossible,” said Miss Hunter; “the ladder was not there when the Rucastles went away.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He has come back and done it. I tell you that he is a clever and dangerous man. I should not be very much surprised if this were he whose step I hear now upon the stair. I think, Watson, that it would be as well for you to have your pistol ready.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The words were hardly out of his mouth before a man appeared at the door of the room, a very fat and burly man, with a heavy stick in his hand. Miss Hunter screamed and shrunk against the wall at the sight of him, but Sherlock Holmes sprang forward and confronted him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You villain!” said he, “where’s your daughter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The fat man cast his eyes round, and then up at the open skylight.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is for me to ask you that,” he shrieked, “you thieves! Spies and thieves! I have caught you, have I? You are in my power. I’ll serve you!” He turned and clattered down the stairs as hard as he could go.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s gone for the dog!” cried Miss Hunter.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have my revolver,” said I.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Better close the front door,” cried Holmes, and we all rushed down the stairs together. We had hardly reached the hall when we heard the baying of a hound, and then a scream of agony, with a horrible worrying sound which it was dreadful to listen to. An elderly man with a red face and shaking limbs came staggering out at a side door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My God!” he cried. “Someone has loosed the dog. It’s not been fed for two days. Quick, quick, or it’ll be too late!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Holmes and I rushed out and round the angle of the house, with Toller hurrying behind us. There was the huge famished brute, its black muzzle buried in Rucastle’s throat, while he writhed and screamed upon the ground. Running up, I blew its brains out, and it fell over with its keen white teeth still meeting in the great creases of his neck. With much labour we separated them and carried him, living but horribly mangled, into the house. We laid him upon the drawing-room sofa, and having dispatched the sobered Toller to bear the news to his wife, I did what I could to relieve his pain. We were all assembled round him when the door opened, and a tall, gaunt woman entered the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mrs. Toller!” cried Miss Hunter.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, miss. Mr. Rucastle let me out when he came back before he went up to you. Ah, miss, it is a pity you didn’t let me know what you were planning, for I would have told you that your pains were wasted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ha!” said Holmes, looking keenly at her. “It is clear that Mrs. Toller knows more about this matter than anyone else.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, I do, and I am ready enough to tell what I know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, pray, sit down, and let us hear it for there are several points on which I must confess that I am still in the dark.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will soon make it clear to you,” said she; “and I’d have done so before now if I could ha’ got out from the cellar. If there’s police-court business over this, you’ll remember that I was the one that stood your friend, and that I was Miss Alice’s friend too.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She was never happy at home, Miss Alice wasn’t, from the time that her father married again. She was slighted like and had no say in anything, but it never really became bad for her until after she met Mr. Fowler at a friend’s house. As well as I could learn, Miss Alice had rights of her own by will, but she was so quiet and patient, she was, that she never said a word about them but just left everything in Mr. Rucastle’s hands. He knew he was safe with her; but when there was a chance of a husband coming forward, who would ask for all that the law would give him, then her father thought it time to put a stop on it. He wanted her to sign a paper, so that whether she married or not, he could use her money. When she wouldn’t do it, he kept on worrying her until she got brain-fever, and for six weeks was at death’s door. Then she got better at last, all worn to a shadow, and with her beautiful hair cut off; but that didn’t make no change in her young man, and he stuck to her as true as man could be.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah,” said Holmes, “I think that what you have been good enough to tell us makes the matter fairly clear, and that I can deduce all that remains. Mr. Rucastle then, I presume, took to this system of imprisonment?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And brought Miss Hunter down from London in order to get rid of the disagreeable persistence of Mr. Fowler.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That was it, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But Mr. Fowler being a persevering man, as a good seaman should be, blockaded the house, and having met you succeeded by certain arguments, metallic or otherwise, in convincing you that your interests were the same as his.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Fowler was a very kind-spoken, free-handed gentleman,” said Mrs. Toller serenely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And in this way he managed that your good man should have no want of drink, and that a ladder should be ready at the moment when your master had gone out.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have it, sir, just as it happened.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am sure we owe you an apology, Mrs. Toller,” said Holmes, “for you have certainly cleared up everything which puzzled us. And here comes the country surgeon and Mrs. Rucastle, so I think, Watson, that we had best escort Miss Hunter back to Winchester, as it seems to me that our <i>locus standi</i> now is rather a questionable one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/56eeb2eb314874fa/text/000005103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-9a7134 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-0e3027 twpub-56eeb2eb314874fa-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And thus was solved the mystery of the sinister house with the copper beeches in front of the door. Mr. Rucastle survived, but was always a broken man, kept alive solely through the care of his devoted wife. They still live with their old servants, who probably know so much of Rucastle’s past life that he finds it difficult to part from them. Mr. Fowler and Miss Rucastle were married, by special license, in Southampton the day after their flight, and he is now the holder of a government appointment in the island of Mauritius. As to Miss Violet Hunter, my friend Holmes, rather to my disappointment, manifested no further interest in her when once she had ceased to be the centre of one of his problems, and she is now the head of a private school at Walsall, where I believe that she has met with considerable success.</p></div></div>"
        },
